UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">第</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">甲甲</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">  </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">大吉</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">    </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">詩</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">巍巍獨步向雲間。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">玉殿千官第一班。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">富貴榮華天付汝。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">福如東海壽如山。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此事以穩健的步伐，走向浮華、虛榮。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">—-</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">平步青雲。（不代表所求就能如願，還需視本身條件而定）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">這件事是很高的榮譽，也是很殊勝的名份。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">但必須要有對等的份量、德行、實力，才能享受到這份殊榮。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此榮華富貴是個人過去的功德善行而有今天的福報。（「天」，業力、因果報應是也。但若無此福報，恐不能如願。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">代表這是很大的福報。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">—-</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">福壽雙全。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">本籤重點</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">榮華富貴，來自先福，當行謙恭，言行高雅，多行善事，以保榮譽。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">高官貴族求得本籤者吉，平凡市民求得本籤，則是虛名一場。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若求得本籤者所問事不順遂，此意味本身福報和德行不足，因此難以消受此榮耀。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">本籤有利「貴命」者，不利平民者。若屬居中者，請加把勁。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">（簡要貴賤判斷，以身相判斷：個子高大者為貴，或耳垂寬厚者為貴。以職業判斷：當官者為貴。讀書人、專業研究者，為中（得此籤有功名）。以八字判斷：五兩九以上為貴。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">清涼月解</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆愛情</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問愛情求得本籤者，依身分不同而有不同的結果。若身分屬貴族之流者，屬上吉。若市井小民求得本籤者，似有招架不住此愛情之感。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此籤代表你可以遇到身分尊貴的對象，若能與他有成果，這當然是很高的榮耀。但是，本身也要有對等的尊貴，這才能保住這愛情。因此，就從今天起，培養自己尊貴的言行，敬重每個人，談吐高雅，涵養好，風度佳，這是你要修練的功課了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若當前愛情平順者，問愛情前途，或問當前對象可否結婚。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">你們兩人是「天生一對」，此生相逢這是「天作之合」，因此，將來勢必能「比翼雙飛」，婚姻美滿。請多多提升自己的「德行」，以能安住此愛情。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若當前有心儀的對象，問可否追求。或當前交往對象，問可否繼續或前途。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若能追到他，這是很高的榮耀與福報，此有待你展現尊貴的言行與風範，這有助你們的愛情進展！而是否因此結為夫妻，此看個人福報是否與他相當，也有賴自己的好德行，這才能穩住這愛情。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若愛情陷入困境或分手者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">你們倆有緣相逢，這是難得的機緣，因此不要因為一點小事就吵架或鬧僵，若發生不愉快，恐大不利你們的未來。若你想要維持這感情的話，建議做個有風度的男人（女人），說話時應維持尊重對方，言行舉止務必高雅。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇建議你多多修持</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">愛情學分</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">，這可讓愛情就越來越溫馨了。建議把來自對方的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=11352&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=11351"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">逆境當作修行</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">，這可提升你們結合的力量。若你願意改造自己，這愛情才會有甜美的目標。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若愛情不順遂者，求得本籤者，此顯示對方條件很好，但自己功行不足，以致「罩不住」此愛情，因此常有分手疑慮，若想繼續維持的話，應該全力提升自己的德行。敬重他人，這是你首要修行的功課了，記得在生活中，養成敬重每個人的好習慣。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問各種考試者，此次的應考，若能考上，則是很高的榮耀，因此需要很好的福報和德行、實力，若此能兼備的話，那就能得到這個名份。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">為了加強這些條件，在此建議生活中注意自己的風範、品德，除了當在本業中努力外，也要多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">行善布施</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">，若臨比賽應試時，那多祈求神明保佑，這是可以化險為安的。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆事業、工作、創業</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若問此事業發展方向者，或問事業更換方向者，請選擇與高級、高雅、高貴有關的行業，譬如地點選擇名貴之地，經營對象有高官貴人者，產品內容選擇高級者。除了行業之選擇外，自己的內在涵養、行為風範也要同步提升，若能如此，則有利此事業之發展。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若問事業占此者，事業穩固。若問前途者，綿遠流長。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇若問可否合夥事業，此籤意味著你們的合作，正有相輔相成之功效，可以合作的很好，而後發展順暢。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◇以上求問者，是否因此致富，這要看後天的表現，建議多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">行善布施</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">則有利未來。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆換職</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問可否換工作者，只要你覺得當換那就換。若你的換職可以選擇的話，那名份比較高的那個，最可能錄用你。（請同步提升自己的涵養與德行）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆求職</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">你將可以找到聲望很好的公司就職。在徵選時，頭批就獲得錄取。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆選擇</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問各種選擇者，請選擇源遠流長者、根基穩固者、名份優貴者。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">你的祈求，將可如願。若祈求生子者，請多多行善修德。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">東</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">坡</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">雲間獨步。拔萃超群。名登甲第。談笑功勳。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">終身光顯。皆天所相。祿厚壽高。意稱謀望。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">碧</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">仙</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">註</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">月裡攀丹桂。成名步玉畿。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">求謀皆稱意。萬事定無疑。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">曰</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此籤謀望通達。無不遂意。但各有所主。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">官員占茲。有超越之喜。士人有功名之望。庶人不吉。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若謀望。求財者。有名無實。為語多空虛也。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">釋</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">義</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">上兩句顯仕者之進身。出玉殿千官之上。壽山福海皆天所付。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">不可易得。故不應占。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">得此者勢如騎虎。降得</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">虎</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">者吉降。不得者反被</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">虎</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">所傷。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">千官或作仙官。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">曰</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此籤謀望事緒。無不遂意。但各有所主。官員占此。有超越之喜。士人有功名之慶。占前程者。福壽綿長。占事業者。根基穩固。若謀望求財。多主有名無實。為語多空虛也。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">釋</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">義</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">雲間。青雲之上也。巍巍獨步。許其足踏青雲也。玉殿千官。乃是天曹仙吏。第一班。仙吏之最貴者也。榮華富貴。自天作主。天已付之。自然福壽無涯。如海。言福之廣遠。如山。言壽之堅永。上上大吉。須要人地相當則應。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">    </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">驗</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一士人問功名。占此。自謂非會。即狀久而始第。會試殿試兩科。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">通榜序齒。皆第一授官。山東由知縣。歷州府司道以至撫臺。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">皆不離山東。應在末句。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">漢高祖入關</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">漢高祖。姓劉名邦。字季。沛人也。其時秦法苛暴。天下皆叛。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">楚人項羽起義。立懷王孫心。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">高祖率沛中子弟以從。諸侯兵皆西鄉。回功秦約。以先入關者王之。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">獨高祖先入秦關。除苛法與父老約法三章。秦民大悅。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">秦王子嬰。素車白馬。出軸道以降。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 104.3pt;">
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; height: 104.3pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; height: 104.3pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">十八學士登瀛洲</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">唐太宗李世民未登基還是秦王時，在奉王府設立文學館。招攬讀書人，選出十八位飽學人士。太宗時，文學館升格成翰林院。又舉行科舉考試，一片天下太平樣子。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">瀛洲指仙山</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">史記</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">。登瀛洲即登上仙山。指山雞變鳳凰。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';"><span>         </span><span>               </span></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106"></td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 423pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="564"></td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 1;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">第二籤</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">甲乙</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">  </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">上吉</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">    </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">詩</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">盈虛消息總天時。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">自此君當百事宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問前程歸縮地。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
<span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">更須方寸好修為。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">更須→須憑</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">真假消息隨著時間浮現。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">意即各種耳語、傳說困擾你。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">自此之後，你想做的事情都可以做了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">(</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">這些傳聞已成過去。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問將來當歸屬何方？人生的歸宿當朝哪裡？</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">勸君把做人的分寸拿捏好。意即，把道德、操守做好來，這就是人生的歸宿地了。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">本籤重點</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">各種人生謀求前途如何，此有賴「修德」而得好成果。不管你想要謀求什麼，你只要先把「德」修好就對了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">完整改運、造運請依此經營：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">懺悔</span></a><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">.</span><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">行善</span><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">.</span></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">修德</span></a></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">清涼月解</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆愛情</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">「盈虛消息總天時」，若問愛情者，此代表有關你們愛情之間的傳聞不斷，只是這些消息真真假假，你千萬不要被這些真假消息牽著鼻子走，更不要因為這些消息而雙方鬧的不愉快。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">「自此君當百事宜」，此代表你想要做的事都可以做。想要追心儀的對象可以追求。想要更進一步發展愛情者，也可以發展。想要挽回愛情的，也可以挽回。想要求姻緣來的也可以期待。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">「若問前程歸縮地」，但是，能否順利與幸福呢？此謀求能否有個好結果呢？這要怎麼經營呢？</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">「更須方寸好修為」，若能提升自己的品德、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">道德</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">，行為知分寸，這就是經營之道了，這就是愛情幸福的基礎所在了。若想挽回者，那就展現你的德行與</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">真愛情操</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">，那自然就能挽回了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">德，就是一種無私之心，能為別人著想之心，等等善心都是「德」的一部份，也影響你有多少幸福與成果。因此，就從今天開始，隨時注意自己的德行，這就是你的愛情經營之道了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆事業、工作、求職</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問事業或工作前途者，若想在這方面有好的前途，本籤的提醒重點只有一個，那就是提升你的「德行」，此德行就是你事業興衰的所在了。若你當前正在求職，那求職時要表現你高尚的品德情操，這也是你接受評審時，不知不覺會被評鑑的科目了。若你是做生意的，那與客人互動間，表現你的高品德，這就是為自己做正面宣傳了。若你只是個工人，那把自己本份內的工作做好，不投機取巧，力求品質做到最好，這就是「德」。凡屬此種謀求者，只要把這個「德」做好來，那就是你事業展望的所在了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆求孕求子</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若最近懷孕的話，那就是生女兒。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">你想要生個兒子嗎？能否生兒子和人的性格有關，若夫妻性格屬於精打細算、斤斤計較這類性格者，那就會生女。反之，夫妻性格屬於慷慨大方、不計小節，那就能生男。因此，本籤提醒，提升你的「德」就是能否生兒子的關鍵了。因此建議，平常生活中多多行善修德，只要修個一年後，命中無子女者可得子女。命中無兒子者，可生得兒子。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆考試、競試、考試、錄用</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問未來各種競試結果者，未來各種競試你都值得參與，但是成果如何，則是看你有多少「德」而決定，因此，籤詩提醒你要把做人修為做好來，若你願意這樣的話，那各種競試就能有好成果可期待了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若問治病者，你的疾病只要「修德」就可以痊癒。修行的最基本功課就是「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">」，因此，只要你走修行路線，各種慢性病都大有機會痊癒。若你實在無從修起，那你就多多求神明保佑吧！（但是療效不如靠自己）</span></p>
</p></td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">東</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">坡</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">萬事乘除。隨時而處。否極泰來。事無齟齬。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">能保則吉。更當修為。切莫妄動。萬福來宜。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">能為→收成結果。方寸修為</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">碧</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">仙</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">註</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">禍福從天降。心仁萬事宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>
</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若還無妄作。災散禍消除</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">災除→禍散福相隨</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">曰</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此籤謀望虛。查不宜速進。且須待時。方可成就。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">婚則合。訟宜和。求財有。行人至。孕生女。病宜禱。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">大概以正心修德為要。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">釋</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">義</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">盈滿也。虛空也。消窮也。息渙也。四者皆用天命。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">卜者當順受。不可妄為。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">前程歸縮地。言目下功名。期望遠大。必藉修為。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">乃得病。不可保。訟不可。終其曰。君當百事宜。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">若蓋勉人修為。心地至於縮地。乃縮千里於目前。半步可至。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此壺公授費長房之術也。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">解</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">曰</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">此籤前運不佳。前事蹭蹬。自此以後。漸見順利。若問究竟歸結。全在存心種德。方得成實。倘值境遇遂意。頓忘前因。暗損心術。必至有始無終。自貽後悔。勉之慎之。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">釋</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">義</span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">盈虛消息。天運之常。人生窮通得喪。亦似此無有定在。言占者曾未遇時也。自此相宜。困極而亨。所謀遂意也。前程歸縮。是收成結果之地。方寸修為。戒占者勿損心田。勿害天理。及早積德修因。遂終有慶矣。君子修之吉。小人悖之凶。唯所自擇何如耳。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">    </span></span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">驗</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">一少年患弱病。占此。殞歿。竟棄人間。應在前程歸縮地一句。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">又一人問行人。占此。不數日。其人兼程而至。亦縮地之應也。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">又一人問執業。占此。奔走四方。靡有生涯。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">後遇一選課者傳授心法。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">乃遁跡潯江。自開擇日館。研究趨吉避凶之術。頗精。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">上二句甚驗。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">張子房遊赤松</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">漢朝。張子房本名張良。韓國公說：張良在博浪沙（地名）刺殺秦始皇失敗後，隱居在</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%8B%E9%82%B3"><span style="font-family: 新細明體; color: windowtext; text-decoration: none;">下邳</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">。在橋上遇見穿布衣的老人，故意把鞋子掉到橋下，叫張良下去撿上來。張良照做還跪著幫老人穿好鞋子。老人說：「你這小子值得教導！」</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">五天後老人就把姜太公兵法傳授給張良，說十三年後再來找我，濟北穀城山下的黃石就是我。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">後來張良助漢高祖打天下，被封為留侯。因為感慨「飛鳥盡，良弓藏」，就藉故生病，到白雲山隱居。拜黃石為老師，取號為赤松子。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">韓蘄王西湖騎驢</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">韓世忠（西元</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1089</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">～</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">1151</span></span><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">）字良臣，宋朝延安人。高宗時，平定苗傅、劉正彥的亂事，在黃天蕩（地名）打敗金國人兀朮，當時他的聲望很高，被讚美是中興第一功臣。後來因為秦檜主張和金國人和談，解除韓世忠的帶兵權，韓就絕口不談軍事，隱居在西湖，自號清涼居士。死後諡號忠武，孝宗時追封他為蘄王。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 79.3pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 0.5pt solid; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="font-family: 新細明體;">備註</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom: windowtext 0.5pt solid; border-left: #c0c0c0; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 1.4pt; width: 418.65pt; padding-right: 1.4pt; border-top: #c0c0c0; border-right: windowtext 1.5pt double; padding-top: 0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin: 0cm auto 6pt;">
</p></td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 2;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.奉公謹守莫欺心。<br/>2.自有亨通吉利臨。<br/>3.目下營求且休矣。<br/>4.秋期與子定佳音。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.做事當奉公守法，不要違背良心或違背天理。(本籤的忠告)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若能如此自然萬事亨通好事降臨</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.你當前想要做的事情當停下來<br/>（此有多種意思，一、是欲做之事不當做。二、此事當等待。三、當前的謀望不能如願。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.到了秋天時，這件事情就有好消息了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">等到秋天即能分曉或有個明確的方向。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.目前的憂慮、困頓來自處事觀念不正所致。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.凡做事情，心態一定要正，切莫違背道德、違背良心，若能如此則能安順。<br/>3.若能謹守清廉，那謀望之事在秋天時刻即能分曉。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.若是一連串發生倒楣事者，各種倒楣事到秋天時方才結束。但是，若你能提早修正自己的負面心態、情緒，那倒楣事還是可以提早結束。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身者問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">現在你的你也許為了姻緣而憂心，其實，你的姻緣在秋天的時候就會來囉！請先做好迎接的準備吧！但是，還請先建立好求姻緣的正確觀念。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若有心儀的對象，問可否追求？可否成為情侶？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若你要追他的話，尚不要著急，首先你的追求心態務必要「正」，不可有歪邪或偏差的想法，若能秉持「正念」而經營，這事情才會有好成果。若能如此，當到了秋天時，那就有好消息了！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象未來前途或問可否結婚。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">也許，你擔心著這愛情未來的發展是否有好結果，也許你當前正處在困頓的階段，但是愛情之事不要著急，而要先建立正確的相處觀念和態度</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請自行思考</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。若能如此，那到了秋天的時候，就是你們約定終身的時刻了。請在此段時間好好的思考他與經營他，多多發揮</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，這可鞏固你們的愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情分手欲問挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們兩個到底適不適合，這是你自己要思考的，重要的是，在愛情上「不要欺騙自己」，這是給你自行反思的提示。每次的分手，都是自省的時候，所以，你當檢討一下分手的原因。若你想通了，你當有新的想法與做法。若想了過後要挽回的話，那秋天就是你挽回的時機了，就請自行把握吧！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想要找到好工作的話，那求職的心態很重要，不可有投機的想法，也不要想找個既輕鬆又多錢的工作，先端正自己的求職態度，若能如此，那到了秋天時就能找到好工作了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、生意、合夥、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業、生意、合夥、工作者，做事的原則就是要奉公守法，老實經營，這就是成功的要件了。若能如此經營的話，那就漸漸能擺脫當前煩憂而走向吉利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆選擇<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種事情的抉擇者，目前的你還是不要做決定，若在做各種選擇時，要記得「不要矇蔽了自己」。若能如此，等到秋天時局勢明朗，那你自然知道哪邊是最佳選擇了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、各種應試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試前途者，目前尚須等待，若是在秋天的考試則對你有利，這是上榜的黃金時刻。若在非秋天的考試即使這次沒考上，下次再接再厲還是有希望考上。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，首先要檢討一下自己的內心，是否為了哪些事情而憂鬱？是否哪件事情讓自己耿耿於懷？是否自己哪裡做了虧心事？等等的自我檢討可以讓你找到心理癥結所在，若能自我檢討，則此心結能解，若能如此則疾病也能不藥而癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求生兒子的話，你應該先修一些功德，然後再求。而當前使用的各種生男方法應當停下來。若能如此的話，那到了秋天時，就有懷男嬰的消息了。請記得待人要慷慨，並多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善布施</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">公平處己。切莫自欺。福祿雖有。漸且待時。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若要進取。未可施為。凡百謀望。秋以為期。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">漸<span lang="EN-US">→更</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先難後易莫相欺。謀望營為秋得宜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>謹守定應多福祿。且須從緩待其時。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤目下不宜妄取。只宜守己。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官員占之。必有憂疑。若能謹守。方得吉利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">士人占之。且待時來。庶人占之平順。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病宜服藥。訟宜和。婚有約。謀望先難後易。不可躁進。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">安分守己。秋月方佳也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">貴人占之有刑憲。士人占之進取未遂。秋期方有佳音。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宜好學養重。凡事占之。當正道而行。待時而動為要。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤目下不宜妄取。只宜守己。官員占之。必有憂疑。若能謹守。自有佳音。士人占之。且待時來。飛騰有日。庶人占之。平安。凡有謀望。先難後易。不可躁進。安分守己。交秋自有遇合。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官吏占此。現在風波。儒士占此。目前沉困。官吏須奉公守法。儒士須積德存心。自有亨通之日。秋期佳音。應在秋後。七八九月間。主有好消息也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人少入公門。存心忠厚。久無所遇。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占得此籤。至秋。偶與一貧士結親。聘其女為媳。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">日後其母貴顯。此人父子因而致富。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又泉州有林生。占財氣。得此籤。未幾。賈客郭秋期官。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一林姓店夥。無故自服毒身死。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">林生與認同宗。出為調停。因此得酬金二百。蓋神已先知之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生。占功。弟病。得此<span lang="EN-US">(籤)未歸家。而中途忽聞凶信。是第三句之驗。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竹平王錢敬識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">柳毅傳書<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">唐朝柳毅，考試落第後回到涇陽地方，遇到安子滿在落淚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">她自已說是洞庭龍王之女，嫁與涇陽龍王之子。遭夫婿暴力羞辱。她拿一封信，拜托柳毅送往洞庭湖。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">柳毅</span><span style="">以不能入水中為理由而推辭，女子說湖邊有柳樹一株，你搖它就會有人招呼你。<span style="COLOR:black;">柳毅於是</span>去搖樹，果然水中有人出來把信拿走。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來柳毅就被邀請入龍宮，洞庭龍王就把女兒嫁給他。後來就不知柳毅結局了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">做事需要正確的觀念，若是觀念或心態不對的話，那就會遭惹災禍，這也可以說，創造了壞命運。反之，觀念和態度都健康，那就能創造出好命運。所以，觀念和心態也是影響命運的一部分。而謀得本籤者，代表作事的態度已經有問題了，因此，只要將之修正，那就能改善問題。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解籤範例<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1610103008276"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">特殊問題解籤</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">範例：該網友求得此籤，要問的是選擇題，此網友求職應徵了三家公司，要問哪一家比較好或哪一家會錄用？這三家公司分別是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">奇美、華泰、日月光。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">從籤詩的最後一句「</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋期與子定佳音</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，答案就在其中了</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">……<br/>1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">其中的「秋」，若提到「秋」最突顯的象徵就是「月」，秋就是代表「月」，所以答案是「日月光」錄用他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「秋」中有「火」，「日」代表「火」，如此解法得到的答案也是「日月光」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">句中有「期」，此「期」望中有「月」，以此而解答案也是「日月光」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">綜合以上三種解法，答案都一樣，將答案和籤詩結合，就成了「日月光與子定佳音」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 3;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第四籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲丁</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下下</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">去年百事頗相宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若較今年時運衰。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">好把瓣香告神佛。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莫教福謝悔無追。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">頗→可</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">去年各方面都算還可以。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若比較今年則今年時運算差些。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事情會越來越糟糕</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">拿些香花供果來神佛前禱告。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">以讓神佛能預先保佑你</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莫讓福報過去了，那就後悔也來不及了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">要有預防之道，以免病入膏肓</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">好事已盡，壞事將來，這是預防的時間到了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">因為淡泊名利或退守，反而因此逃過一劫。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">完整的改運請依順序經營：</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身者問姻緣在何方。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">姻緣總出現在好運之年，由於你的好運年已經過去了，所以，今年大不利你尋求姻緣了。除此之外，還提醒你，今年的你還是多多拜神佛，這可預防一些禍患。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">雖然你喜歡他，但是，愛情並非一時喜歡就代表未來會甜蜜。尤其你今年運勢不佳之下，建議你不用追求誰，只勸你把上好的貢品在神佛前祈求平安。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前交往對象的愛情前途者。或問當前交往對象可否結婚。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">儘管過去曾經甜蜜，但是，今年運勢已經不如往年，所以，你要有最壞的打算。屆時，若是論及分手的話，你還是勇敢的接受吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情陷入困境者，或愛情分手者，或夫妻離異者。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甜蜜的愛情已成過去，如今的困境與分手，這正是你脫離此感情的最佳時刻了。所以，你不必要求挽回，也不必寄望愛情能恢復往日的溫馨，而要藉此機會結束這愛情，若能如此，反而可以讓你避開未來的愛情災難。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人生的命運總是有高低潮，儘管過去一年還算順遂，但是，這將成為過去了。接下來的一年，在工作或事業上，不僅要保守，而且要預防各種災難，這是你不可輕忽的。請多多求神佛保佑吧。在此並建議提早</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，這能讓大災化小，小災化無。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職者，人人都期望能順利找到理想的工作，由於你的好運才剛過，所以接下來的求職困境會較多，因此，你當提早</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，若你願意如此，就能順利找到好工作。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你就打算要考試了，也不管是你否剛考完，在這一年當中，時運對你不利，所以各種考試成果都不佳。若想在考試這方面能突破瓶頸，這是需要很大的努力的。若你願意</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，那即使命中無此考運，也會因為你的勤於修行，而得到新的好命運了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">世俗間難癒之疾病只有兩種，一是</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=11251"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障病</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，二是慢性病（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18079&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18001"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;BACKGROUND:#fde6df;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">無明病</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），此兩類疾病靠當今醫藥確實醫不好，只能藉由</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">來減輕病苦與提早病癒。而無明病，則需要以</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=19229&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=19171"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修行治療</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。而以這些方法也是需要長時間去做才有效果。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若是已經有了孩子，那是沒必要再求生孩子的，因為接下來的時運不佳，想要求孕求子都增加了不少的難度。若實在沒有兒子或有生子壓力，那你再求吧。只是，此謀望能否成功，這可操之在你自己。若你願意</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">最少做個一年，那不管是求孕或求子，都有機會成功。若你願意這樣實踐修行，那神明看了也高興，也會自動暗中相助了。所以，只怕你不努力而已。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆投資、理財、買賣</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就算你在過去的一年裡，曾經在這方面小有獲利，但是未來的一年裡，時機已經沒那麼好了。所以，接下來的你，各種投資計畫都當停下來，各種理財行為都要小心可能出了差錯。建議在這未來的一年當中，多多祈求神佛保佑，以度過財務上的危機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">先吉後凶。時運將否。謀事無成。頓非前比。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">秉誠禱神。以求福祉。若無遠慮。悔無及已。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">好事連綿過。時衰禍漸來。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">頂天並拜地。庶可保無災。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">連綿→從前（連綿，河洛話，即將的意思）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤吉事已去。凶將漸來。祈禱神明。以保平安。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">官事臨身。是非自見。凡事謀望主不成。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求財交易不就。所為皆不利也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此言名利之機。禍福之由也。尤當預圖。免致噬臍。悔之晚矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今年時運衰。言謀事不利。眷屬不寧。但當側身祈禱。則變災為福。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事先凶後吉。運字或作漸字。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤吉事已去。凶禍將來。官事臨身。是非自至。凡事謀望不成。求財交易不就。所為皆不利。急宜祈禱神明。積德回天。庶不致貽後悔耳。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">去年相宜。已往之吉。今年運衰。見在之凶。瓣香告神。勸人早植善果。感格神明。庶可轉禍為福。若無神佛扶持。則福力衰謝。殃咎並臨。佇見噬臍之悔。將何及哉。占者宜早修省也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一人平日許下香愿。後患病。占此。輒以未酬香願。為疑不及禱而死。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">瓣香告神佛。福謝悔無追。二語靈甚。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">小秦王三跳澗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">小秦王即唐太宗李世民，他去找劉武周時，被劉武周的部將尉遲恭追殺，逃亡時三次跳過溪澗，幾乎罹難時，幸好秦叔寶趕來救他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張翰憶鱸魚</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張翰在北方洛陽齊王手下做官，秋天到了，秋風掠過，不禁想念起江南家鄉的菰菜羹和鱸魚膾，於是馬上辭掉官職回鄉。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他對人說，人生難得，貴在選擇適合自己的心意，怎麼能為了名利地位而羈絆在數千里之外呢。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不久，齊王敗亡，當時的人都說張翰料事如神，跳出了可怕的政治漩渦。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">古人云，淡泊以明志，而在亂世，淡泊還可以保命啊！而貪圖權勢，</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">同流合污，又有幾人善終？在今天，放眼四望，一切都在應驗著。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"><span></span></font></span> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 4;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第五籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲戊</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">中平</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">子有三般不自由。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">門庭蕭索冷如秋。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若逢牛鼠交承日。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">萬事回春不用憂。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「三般」有多種意義：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="MARGIN-RIGHT:0px;">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">  (1)你有三個包袱或三個擔憂、束縛、記掛。或你有三件不順的事情。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">   (2)人性的心意、口，受到束縛而顯得不自由。或出了問題。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">   (3)「三般」代表富（錢財）、貴（地位）、壽（健康），意即，你在這三方面不順遂。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">   (4)「三般」代表三番兩次，意即事情遊疑不定，不能做主，也代表變換之兆。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">目前的狀況有些淒寒如秋天。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">還好只是寒如秋而非冷如冬。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若遇到陰曆年底的十一、十二月。（這是轉換、轉變的時刻）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一旦到了春天（陰曆年後），一切就好轉不用憂愁了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">1.在這一年當中，你有三件憂心之事，應當守困。此三件事情是有關錢財、地位（事業）、健康。因此要預防：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="MARGIN-RIGHT:0px;">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(1)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「禍從口出」、「禍從口入」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(2)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">錢財損耗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(3)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">地位動搖</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此困境要待年底的轉變，而在陰曆年後好轉。（各種謀求請在此時認真經營）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想積極預防者請看：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前交往對象愛情前途者</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問分手可否挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">雙方當預防因為口角而分手，尤其到了秋天時刻，心情浮躁更容易造成你們的爭吵。若真吵架的話，那年底之前大概就分手了。若是真分手或是愛情困頓了，那要過年之後才能好轉。整體而言，你們的愛情還不確定，也不能就此決定結婚或決定分手。若在春天時刻，你們的感情能有好的發展的話，那你再思考下一步吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀對象可否追求</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在秋天時刻，沒有伴侶感到寂寞悽涼，所以到了年底，你想要伴侶的渴望增強。但是，你的好運在陰曆新年之後，所以，若要求姻緣的話，此刻則是你的良機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情是在春天剛交往者，那到了夏天你們的愛情來往可望更熱絡，但是到了秋天，氣氛恐有變化。若到了年底，雙方若能吵維持良好氣氛的話，那就是個好姻緣了。總之，若能熬過年底之前愛情平順者，這就是好姻緣。反之，就要另求打算了。為了期待好姻緣能出現，建議提早</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，這對於愛情是有幫助的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◆</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職者，你這一年的求職運不佳，你的求職好運是在陰曆新年後，請把握該段時間求職，請儘可能在三個月內謀得工作。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求職應試或面試者，若遇「子、丑」的日子，也值得一試。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作、換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若做生意之類事業問前途者，最近一年當預防財務上的虧損。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若做雇員者，最近有職務更換或換工作的現象。（最可能發生在年底前）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若官員問事業前途者，最近有地位不保的隱憂，此事在年底有遷移職務之兆。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問換職者，由於時局變化，那也不得不更換，當謀得新職之後，未來新的一年就穩定了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇以上變化或虧損，要到陰曆新年後才好轉或穩定。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問健康者，在年底當預防生病，尤其在飲食方面。若果真生病者，要過年之後才好轉。這一年也要小心發生意外而上醫院。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問疾病著，此疾病若能熬過年底，則明年可以平順。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此疾病乃是來自心理的壓力、壓抑，由於心情不順遂而連累身體健康。若能好好調適自己的心情，則有改善之功效。建議多多修行，則能治療各種慢性病。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此外，此病和飲食、口腔、說話有關，若能找到疾病起因，而後從該處著手，則對於治療大有幫助。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問考試前途者，這一年當中，只有春天對你有利，因此，在陰曆年後的考試都是你值得參與的，請把握這時段的考試，全力以赴，以便能順利錄取。若在春天之外，考試日子若遇「子、丑」的日子，也值得一試。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若無子女者求孕，或求生兒子者，農曆新年過後是你最佳受孕時機，請把握此段時間做好懷孕準備。另外，若夫妻相處，請選在逢「子、丑」的日子，則效果更佳。記得請先養精蓄銳。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">另外，若想生兒子者，應外加</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這項功課。</span><u><font color="#0000ff"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font></u></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆訴訟</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問訴訟者，此案件最終吉利收場。最可結案時間在陰曆年後的春天。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">榮枯有時。不由人力。泰運將亨。終於否極。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">月日子丑。凡事皆吉。如木遇春。轉見榮益。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">轉→纔</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事有不如意。當存忍耐心。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">時來皆順受。福至禍無侵。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先憂後喜。三般者。心口意。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十二時中卻得衣食。官員主有遷移之兆。應在子丑。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凶者漸吉。事皆可望也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">由者如意之謂。牛屬十二月。鼠屬十一月也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">牛鼠交承。春氣將回之屬。夏正建寅。萬物之生機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">寓焉言人生壽富貴一般。得之不得。皆由天命。非可強求。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">子雖有於將來而。不能如意於此際。譬如秋景蕭條。庭戶冷落。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">轉盻間而秋去春回。門第生色矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人能順受天命。坐以待時。則當子丑交承之日。春風鼓蕩之際。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不獨名利顯榮。衣食充足。即萬事亦無不遂意。又何足憂之有哉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先憂後喜。見在主意不定。進退無據。景況甚為冷落。等子丑交承之際。遠應年分。近應月日。自有更新氣象。如春來萬物發生。此前大不相同。凡事待時。終有成就。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">三般句。有二解。一作心口意。三者遊移不定。一作富貴壽。三者杳茫無據。總是不能自主之意。秋景冷落。門庭似此。蕭索可知。牛鼠交承。乃是子丑接續之際。言有好光景在後。至此才得遂意。萬事回春。言事事起發。如草木春日向榮。皆足賞心悅目。何憂之有哉。現須耐守為吉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一生歲試。占此。居三等。驗在三般不自由一句。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若值子丑寅月日。又不當以此斷之。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又有一生。科試。占此。縣府院。三處皆取。應子有三般。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">臨場了毋憂。應門庭蕭索。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又一生。院試前占此。放榜之日。竟取進。應子有兩字也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂蒙正守困</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">朝</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂蒙正，字聖初，河南人，呂龜圖與母親不合，就把呂蒙正和母親一起趕出家門。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蒙正倒楣之時，當時又很貧窮，就到龍門過僧人的生活，並以鑿山巖為龕，禁足不出，守困此年。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直到太宗時，蒙正成為進士第一名，且二次當宰相，操守正直，官位做到太師後辭官。一直被封為許國公。死後謚號文穆。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"><span></span></font></span> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 5;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第六籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲己</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下下</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">何勞鼓瑟更吹笙。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">寸步如登萬里程。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">彼此懷疑不相信。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">休將私意憶濃情。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對於此事何必勞師動眾、大費周章、聲張旗鼓、小題大作、虛偽造假</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">……<br/>(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">顯然這其中有問題</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此事走起來有如行萬里路那麼遙遠（以偏差的態度做事，總是會失敗。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">彼此互相猜疑或沒有信心，那將不能成事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">勸君停下以自己的心意，憶想他人的情意。（人是會變心的動物，當防受害、受騙）（不以自己的想法去想別人）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">處事必須雙方都要有足夠的誠信，若有一方不誠，則必失敗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事中有詐，誠意不足。若求和謀，當行審慎。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">害人之心不可有，防人之心不可無。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">信心，也是你成事的基本要件之一。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對於這件事情，隨所問者不同，而有不同的狀況，可能是自己心態有問題，也可能對方有假。也可能雙方心態都不對而不能成事。也有的問題，則是自己信心不夠。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想要結交到一個好對象，那誠心是很重要的，若心態不軌的話，這不僅害人而且害己。所以，若想要得到姻緣來臨之前，一定要端心正意，若能如此則能有好的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=64"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">磁場</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，而能帶來好的姻緣。另外，若你的交往心態是正的，則要預防他人存心不軌，當心被騙，若有感覺不對，那要即刻退出，以免受害。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前交往的對象前途</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤暗示，交往務必誠心誠意，若有方誠意不足，或心懷鬼胎的話，那不僅不能成事，自己也會受害。所以，若問交往前途者，「害人之心不可有，防人之心不可無。」</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">因此你必須審慎這件事，若知對方意圖不軌，那就要立刻退出，以免受害。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手或困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">儘管你很愛他，也要審慎評估對方態度是否真誠，而不能呆呆的愛卻被玩弄，這是不智之舉的。因此，當與這樣的人陷入困頓或分手時，這就是你逃離危機的最佳時候了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若交往多時問可否結婚者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想與他結婚的話，這個結婚的態度是很重要的，若是結婚的態度不對的話，那很容易又會鬧糾紛的。本籤重點在於提醒你，你需要觀照自己結婚的理由與態度是否健康、正確，而後再做決定，以免徒增不必要的困擾。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問共謀事業者，當心合夥者變心或存心不良而受害，因此當盡早退出，並防破財。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作者，當防工作中有</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14792&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14559"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">小人</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在四周圍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試、轉換、求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問各種考試競賽者，信心對你是非常重要的，若是心虛、投機心，或是沒有信心，那此試就難有好成果了。總之，凡事當持「正念」與「信心」方能成就。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問疾病者，每個負面的態度或心念，都會影響健康。從懷疑心到各種負面心念或情緒，也都會讓人生病。若能健康自己的心情、心態，這就是健康自己的身體了。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事勞心。有退無進。謀望不成。懷疑不信。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求合未合。將圓未圓。只宜守己。不宜變遷。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">兩下心平。中間卻好。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">先義後利。庶幾可保。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">兩保→兩下懷疑。咫尺萬里。何用綢繆。從此中止。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤謂人類不齊。有陽為君子。陰為小人者。須防其面是實非之心。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">訟只可和。主有離開。凡事謹慎周密。庶不誤敗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占此者。名利難進易退。謀為多困。彼此私情。互相離間。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">空勞無成。休將者戒其去心地之疑。示人以信。則謀事自和矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鼓瑟吹笙。小雅篇也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤謂之陽為君子。陰為小人。須防有面是背非之人。從此簸弄。彼此懷疑不信。前此濃情。今已中變。何用私意繫戀。自取煩惱。凡事撥開迷妄則吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鼓瑟吹笙。小雅宴嘉賓之詩也。茍非其人。何勞為此。寸步萬里。言覿面不能相識。彼此懷疑。此人已不可交。此事已不可就。即應當幾立斷。若更以私意。憶彼濃情。不唯徒勞罔功。必將更受其累。休將二字。禁止之詞。戒占者急當自悟也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此占凡事皆不遂意。科名亦然。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">惟福建泉州府。一增生占此。中副車。蓋應在寸步如登之句也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">相如完璧歸趙</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰國時代，藺相如。趙國人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時趙國有塊圓形美玉，秦國要用十五座城市和趙國換美玉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">藺相如奉命帶美玉到秦國，而秦國此刻卻違約不給城巿。相如就派部屬抱美玉回趙國，說道理使秦王折服，而後美玉完整地回到趙國。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">只要有藺相如在趙國，秦國始終不能贏趙國。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 6;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第七籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲庚</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">大吉</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙風道骨本天生。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又遇仙宗為主盟。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">指日丹成謝巖谷。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一朝引領向天行。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的先天資質、條件很好</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又遇到好的老師之調教和學習</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">來日當可練成好功夫</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">屆時就能發揮無比的功力了</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">先天優質，後天善調，未來宏圖，指日可待。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">由於先天與後天條件與機緣都很好，故未來將鴻圖大展。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問愛情前途者，你本身的愛情條件很好，喜歡你的人也多，將來也能遇到門當戶對的好對象，屆時愛情還能開花結果，同時走向幸福美滿的人生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職、換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的求職、換職條件很好，又能遇到賞識你的人，故能被錄用，而且將來可以在工作上有卓越的表現。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、創業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問事業、創業前途者，你的事業資材、條件很好，又有好的經營理念，因此將來事業將大有成就，而且還能財富廣進。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆學業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問學業前途者，由於本身資材很好，又遇到好老師，故將來可修成學業得到學位，並發揮無比的能力。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問考試前途者，你的功課和本領一向很好，這次又參與自己擅長的科目競試，這必定可以高分金榜題名或得勝，而且往後也發展的很好。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問疾病者，本身體質很好，又幸巧遇到好醫生治療，若能在二十一天康復好轉者，則屬有效。若此段時間內還不能康復者，則此病凶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的先天福報很好，身體健康也沒有問題，若想生男女，就能如願生男女。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">天生富貴。況得神助。凡骨成仙。昇騰雲路。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">庶人遇貴。財物皆聚。百事大吉。何必疑慮。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">問病三日內。須逢好手扶。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若還求富貴。雲路是亨途。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貴人占之有薦投之喜。（推薦投靠）</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">士人占之有不虞之譽。（預料不到的聲譽）</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">庶人占之有百倍之利。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若占病。當有仙醫扶佑。在三七日內有效。否則凶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂洞賓。唐末避兵。多遊湘湖。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">梁魏間稱回道人。亦稱守谷客人。皆自寓之。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡富貴者占此。事必遂意。諺云有錢十萬可通仙。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若貧賤之人。勢力不勝。不應此籤。遇人扶持。事方亨泰。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">亦恐不久。病有仙遊之約。如過一月。保可無虞。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤貴人占之。有薦拔之喜。仕人占之。有飛騰之兆。庶人占之。有百倍之利。方外占之。有仙昇之期。病患占之。有醫藥之緣。亦恐有正應反應不同。占者審之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">道骨天生。夙有道緣也。仙宗主盟。仙階得路也。指日丹成。沖舉當在指顧間。引領向天。身在雲霄之上矣。方士占之。上上大吉。文士當係玉堂清品。他事則嫌空幻。未可全以吉斷。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">世宗時。羽士陶仲文。占得此籤後。以方枝遭際。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歷官禮部尚書。封恭安伯。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂洞賓煉丹</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝人呂岩</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">或作巖</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">/</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">喦</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">/</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">嵒</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。字洞賓。天寶十四年四月十四日巳時生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">自號純陽子。考取進士，當江州德化縣長。穿官服出遊時，在廬山遇到鍾離真人（鍾離和～八仙之一），教呂天仙劍法。也有人說是遇火龍真人。教呂天遁劍法。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂洞賓了解易經九九數法，學煉丹方法。住深山煉仙丹，煉成後就長生不老了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他常來往在湘（湖南）、鄂（湖北）間。湖南洞庭湖地方太守滕宗諒，曾經在岳陽遇見他，自稱是華州道人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>


</tbody>' WHERE id = 7;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">第八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">甲辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上上</span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">1.年來耕稼苦無收。<br/>2.今歲田疇定有秋。<br/>3.況遇太平無事日。<br/>4.士農工賈百無憂。</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">1.過去幾年的耕耘一直沒有好收成（往事失意）</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">2.今年的努力一定有好結果了（可望在秋天有好成果出現）</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">3.更何況如今是太平之日</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">4.各行各業都安順無憂</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">1.歷盡艱辛，曾逢失意，如今煥然，否極泰來。</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">2.求官者占之，可以得到推薦或引領。</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">3.想要進行之事，可以進行。</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="新細明體">4.陰曆的八、九、十月，稍有不順。（疾病、理財、升官方面）</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◇若問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">你的孤單日子就要結束了，只要等到秋天，你的姻緣就會來囉！<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◇若當前有交往對象，想知道前途者，或問愛情挽回者<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">過去的交往曾經冷淡或有困頓，但是今後將可順遂發展了，當到了秋天時，你們會更濃情蜜意。請多修<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="">愛情學分</span></a>，這更有利愛情發展。</span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">在工作上的困頓或是事業上的獲利不佳，這將成為過去了，往後將可進入佳境，問工作者能擺脫過去的困頓，問事業者也將開始獲利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">也許過去的你，已經找工作一段時間了，即使過去是不順利的，但是今後將開始好轉了，尤其到了秋天時刻，更是容易找到你要的工作，這段期間請務必把握。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">也許過去的你經過多次的考試都不理想，但是從現在開始，各種考試將對你有利了。若是在秋天之考試或各種競試，對你特別有利，可得捷報與金榜題名。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">若問健康者，在陰曆的八、九、十月屬於狀況較差的月份，此期間當預防疾病或原來疾病惡化。過了這些時段，今後可以逐步康復。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">經過多時的官司纏訟，也經歷不利自己的過程，但往後終於可以漸入佳境了，這個官司在秋天之時，可望得到勝訴了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆投資理財、房地產買賣<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">也許過去的你，在投資理財上有些虧損，但是苦日子也會過去，在未來將可逐步獲利。但是在在陰曆的八、九、十這三個月份，則還是要小心，這也是會讓人虧損的月份，只要能預防，那就能避開虧損。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">若問求孕或求子者，過去的你生育一直不順利，今後可望進入順遂階段了，當到了秋天之刻，這是你懷孕生子的黃金時刻，請預先做好懷孕的各種準備，以便能順利的懷孕。請兼作<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><strong><span style="">行善.</span></strong></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><strong><span style="">修德</span></strong></a>的功課，這對於生男特別有幫助。</span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">凡事求謀。昔否今泰。時運將亨。有喜無害。</font><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="新細明體">士農工商。悉逢嘉會。財物倍收。普均內外。</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">時否今逢泰。尤當要守成。</font><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="新細明體">不論貧與富。自此盡通亨。</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">→<span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">昔否今逢泰。謀為耐始終。</font><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="新細明體">休論貧與富。從此盡亨通。</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">此籤宜改圖謀利。凡百事實踐之人皆有望。</font><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="新細明體">問病占訟。先憂後喜。問孕生男。風水吉利。子孫亨嘉也。</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">酉戍亥月日。美中不足。主田士之累。或病疾之憂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">占者多事而過。太平反處無事。耕稼旡收。年來之否也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">定有秋。目下之泰也。占此先凶後吉。訟與功名。秋期捷勝。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">此籤宜安常守分。前雖困頓。今漸有成。譬如田疇。既有荒歉。亦有豐收。幸處光天化日之下。農工商賈。共享昇平。何憂之有。凡事安享自然。時日以秋季為斷。<span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">耕稼無收。指往事失意。今歲有秋。指現在利益。太平日。大有俯仰優遊之樂。百無憂。統言士農工商之儔。占此者。人人獲吉。事事如意。喜氣洋溢之兆也。<span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">一生歲考。占此。案居三等。應太平無事四字。蓋三等乃平過地位也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">又一生類考。占此。案居一等。因起復候廩。應定有秋二句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">大舜耕歷山<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體"><span style="COLOR:black;">大舜</span><span style="COLOR:black;">，就是</span>舜帝，他曾是眼瞎老頭的兒子。他的父親很頑固，母親也很嚴厲，還有個弟弟名叫象，個性高傲。此三人都常常要害他。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">但是舜還是很孝順父母，若受小小責罰就接受。若父母失去理性瘋狂鞭打時，他就逃走。就怕父母背負殺人罪名。當他在歷山耕田時，有象、鳥自動來幫忙耕耘。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">在二十歲時，舜就以孝道聞名於天下。在舜三十歲時，帝<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A0%AF" title="堯"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">堯</span></a>問<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B2%B3" title="四岳"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">四岳</span></a>，天下間有誰能夠繼承共主之位，四岳推薦舜。後來接受堯讓帝位給他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">伊尹耕莘樂道<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">伊尹，名摯，商初的賢相。<span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體">相傳湯（人名）討伐桀（人名），滅夏朝，於是稱王，建商朝。湯死後，湯的孫子太甲（人名）荒誕，伊尹就把太甲放逐到桐宮（地名），等他悔過，再迎接回來復位當帝王。伊尹死時，帝王沃丁用葬天子之禮數埋葬他。<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="新細明體"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 8;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第九籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲壬</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">大吉</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">望渠消息向長安。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">常把菱花仔細看。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">見說文書將入境。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今朝喜色上眉端。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對於這件重要的事，期盼著能有消息。（長安，漢朝國都。代表和此事相關的重要地點）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">常常想像著各種好消息出現。（菱花鏡，鏡子所作成的萬花筒。代表想像此事的美麗之景。盼望的心情所產生的想像。菱花仔細看，也代表當事者由於期盼之心情，故常有自照鏡子的習慣。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">聽說有好消息來了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一朝終於好消息傳來而讓人喜上眉梢了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">久日之盼，消息將至，終獲佳音，喜上眉梢。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤若屬自占者，好消息屬於虛喜。若由他占者，方有實質。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你盼望著愛情已經多時了，也常想像著愛情美景，如今這個美景就要來了，但是不要心急，大約在百日之內就有消息了。（本籤只代表有好消息，但不代表成果。好成果需要自己經營。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手者，或夫妻有第三者，問愛情復合。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你期盼與他的相會已經多時，其實你不用心急，一時的分手是需要時間等待的，百日內你就可以得知他要回到你身邊的信息了，屆時，你就喜上眉梢了。（本籤只代表有好消息，但不代表成果。往後有否好成果，則需靠自己的經營。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇已交往對象可否進一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤代表，你期盼著他，你想要和他有更進一步發展，已經多時了，其實，你可以放心的與他交往，到時候的你們就喜上眉梢。建議多充實些</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">愛情學分</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以讓愛情能有好成果。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">期盼事業能有好的發展，或期盼著能有好的工作，好的結果也是會出現的，只要你再等等，在百日之內，工作就變得順利了，事業開始發達了，到時候你就喜上眉梢了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">盼望著能找到工作已經多時了，也常想像著找工作的景象，其實你不心急，只在百日之內就能找到工作了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你盼望這考試能通過已經多時了，此籤也告訴你將可以順利通過考試。請勿懈怠，用功讀書，不僅能考上而已，而且還能高分上榜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求孕或求子者，你的這個期盼已經多時了，你將可在百日之內有懷孕的消息，請事先做好懷孕準備，以迎接小生命的降臨。若問求子者，請外加</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"><font color="#800080">修德</font></span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">的功課，則生男更順利。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆投資、理財</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在這百日之內，能看到獲利狀態而喜上眉梢，只是，若不知收成的話，恐會是空歡喜一場。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在這百日之內，能看到康復之象，而令人慶幸。若要維持長時間的健康，這還是需要靠有效的身心療養。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">謀望已久。忽得好音。音書到手。喜在目今。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">利有攸往。財獲千金。所謀遂意。凡事稱心。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行人若久望。只在三日至。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">自去自回歸。不出百日內。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤謀事尚遠。自己心急。他人不知。若問遠行。只在百日之內。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">婚姻有期合。病者宜請禱。大概空虛無的實也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">望待也。長安帝畿也。文書入境。有喜信也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若代人問名利。主日下帝畿內。有佳音來報。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本身自占。名利則是虛喜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤謀為之事。旦夕喜信。若問行人。旦夕即至。婚姻和合。疾病回頭。士子科名捷報。仕宦得位超遷。叩問運程。即見好消息也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">望消息。等待已久也。仔細看。把鏡自照也。此是盼望不寧之狀。文書入境。消息已到。喜色眉端。大有揚眉吐氣之概。凡事久而後成。難而後易。不可過急。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">消息菱花與見說。喜色無一字著。實凡百謀望皆空。指望占者詳之。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又一女子占夫之信。得此籤。果有家報至。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋太祖陳橋即位</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">趙匡胤（<span style="COLOR:black;">宋太祖</span>）做檢校太傅殿前都檢點的官，也就是禁軍總將領，五代後周世宗<u>柴榮</u>死後，孩子<u>恭帝</u>即位，不足十歲。趙匡胤奉命去討伐河東，軍隊到陳橋，部下將軍士兵以皇帝年幼，政局混亂為理由，勸趙匡胤自已作皇帝。起初趙匡胤不答應，後來部下趁趙匡胤醉倒，拿皇帝龍袍穿在他身上，就帶兵回到洛陽，接受周恭帝讓位給他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張京兆畫眉</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">《漢書</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張敞傳》：「<u>敞</u>又為太太畫眉，長安中傳說張京兆（京兆即市長）畫的眉毛，比女人自已畫的嫵媚。官吏上奏皇帝。皇帝問張敞。張回答：『我聽說閨房內的快樂，夫妻的私事，有比畫眉更快樂的。』皇帝愛張敞有能力，沒責備他。」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">畫眉之樂一詞，後來被引喻用為夫婦或男女的相愛。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 9;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第十籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">甲癸</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下下</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">病患時時命蹇衰。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">何須打瓦共鑽龜。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直教重見一陽復。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">始可求神仗佛持。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此事就如重病的病患，時時處在性命垂危的邊緣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不必四處占卜</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不必到處算命、改名、改祖墳、刻印鑑等等</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直到不好的觀念、態度、個性、行為、操守等等有所改善後。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直到</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過後。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">再來祈求神佛的庇祐與加持。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若能如此則能減災</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過去若有惡作者，當行</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，痛改前非，若願意如此，才求神明庇祐，事情才能好轉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求得此籤者，代表被業障所困，故各種謀求皆不順遂。若想改運者，請依此而行：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">姻緣至今不來，這是業障所致。若想要求得姻緣，你必須進行</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，這才有機會。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想追求他的話，這是有困難的，因為你們彼此的落差太大，這主要是你自己的姻緣業障太深，因此很難求得喜歡的人。若想改造命運的話，別無他法，只能</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，這對於未來才有姻緣的希望。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇已交往對象可否進一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想持續交往，這必須排除你們之間的業障，要不然也是沒有好成果。你們除了當</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">之外，更需要有好的德行，這對於愛情才有機會好轉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若交往多年者，問此愛情前途或可否結婚者。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想結婚的話，也必須在雙方相處穩定一段時候後才問。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或關係困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就如俗話說的，夫妻是相欠債，也因為是這樣，所以兩人相處就是吵，除了吵架、互相計較之外，還是吵個沒完。因此建議雙方不宜繼續相處。若想維持這段感情的話，那只有痛苦可言。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在工作或事業上，一直處在不順遂或事業面臨倒閉的邊緣，這個惡相直到你改變了自己以後，問題才可能好轉。事業淪落至此，必有其因，這是你要自己檢討的。若你能在神佛前</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，痛改前非，而後再求神佛保佑，則能有生機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">目前若想求孕求子，此不可得，由於業障之故，因此當從</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">開始，若能誠心肯切的懺悔，才有希望如願。若想求生兒子者，則更需要</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，若你願意這樣做個一年以上，則能如願。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病者，此病和業障脫離不了關係，所以當從</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">開始，若你能誠心肯切的懺悔，而後再求神佛保佑，這才有康復指望。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想在各種競試中脫穎而出，這是需要福報的，由於你的業障還在，所以當前的各種競試難有好成果。所以，你還是從</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">開始，若你願意誠心肯切的懺悔，而後再求神佛保佑，這才有上榜指望。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">命運多蹇。疾病連綿。但宜修省。托庇蒼天。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直須冬至。禱神方痊。凡百謀望。作事必全。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宜→須</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">托庇→託在</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">旡妄過凶災。陰人口舌來。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一亦生日後。漸漸福緣開。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過→遇</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">亦→交</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">福緣→笑顏</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤大意。曉然欲惡人知悔過。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問病訟。十月方可。不然莫解。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若作非為。禍患立至。主家神不安也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一陽復生。即有喜之義。泰來之兆也。交生誕冬節候。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">名利漸享。謀為遂意。只當避害向善。慎勿妄動。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君子占之。當式微之運。仿剛正人為援。則立身行己。不為小人排陷。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">小人占此亦宜歛退。不可進陵君子。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">病訟過前月。無事為幸。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤大意曉然。凡有前惡。須宜求神懺悔。若問病訟。冬至後方可。不然莫解。若作非為。禍患立至。占者守分修省可保。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">運途蹇衰。現在欠吉。打瓦鑽龜。卜筮何益。何須為此。及早種福。感格昊蒼。默仗神力。佳期冬至。一陽來復。或七日後。應驗神速。遠斷節氣。近斷時日。萬象回春。以需後祿。遵此修持。聖言不謬矣。不悟修省者終凶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font>&nbsp;</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一生考。遺才。占此不取。應在何須打瓦一句。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又一士傷後。占此。中二十二名。恭十一月冬至。乃一陽末復之候。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">而車見者恰符二十二也。此第三句之驗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">冉伯牛染病</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">冉耕，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%86%89%E5%A7%93" title="冉姓"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">冉</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">氏，字伯牛。</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B" title="中國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中國</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3" title="春秋時代"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">春秋時代</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">末（前</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">544</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">～前</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">439</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%AD%AF%E5%9C%8B" title="魯國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">魯國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人，是</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90" title="孔子"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">孔子</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">的學生之一，患病早逝，孔子十分難過。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">伯牛與</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A2%9C%E6%B8%8A" title="顏淵"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">顏淵</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%AA%9E" title="閔子騫"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">閔子騫</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%BB%B2%E5%BC%93" title="仲弓"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">仲弓</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">同屬</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AD%94%E9%96%80%E5%8D%81%E5%93%B2" title="孔門十哲"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">孔門十哲</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">的德行科哲人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%94%90%E6%9C%9D" title="唐朝"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">唐朝</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%96%8B%E5%85%83" title="開å"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">開元</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二十七年（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/739%E5%B9%B4" title="739年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">739</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）封「鄆侯」，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AE%8B" title="宋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">宋</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">追封為「東平公」，後又改稱「鄆公」。</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾任魯國的中都宰，孔子很器重他。在患有惡疾時，不願見人。孔子於其病危時，特地去探望他，從屋外窗口握住他的手，邊歎息邊說：「死，是命中註定的啊！可是這樣的人怎麼會有這樣的病，這樣的人怎麼會害這樣的病啊！」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">伯牛的德行，與顏淵、閔子騫等並駕，無怪乎孔子哭說這是天命。伯牛以德行見稱於孔子，惜全無事跡可考。僅知其是染患惡疾而逝。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟郊五十登第</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟郊早年生活貧困，曾在湖北、湖南、廣西等地游歷，沒有結交到好朋友，屢次考試不中第。唐貞元年間，張建封當徐州太守時，孟郊曾拜訪他。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">46</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歲（一說</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">45</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歲）時，孟郊才考取進士，寫了一首詩《登科後》：「昔日齷齪不足誇，今朝放蕩思無涯；春風得意馬蹄疾，一日看盡長安花（成語「走馬看花」由來）。」然後前往東方，旅遊汴州</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今河南開封</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、越州（今浙江紹興）。貞元十七年（</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">801</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年），擔任溧陽尉。任期內不做公務，常常寫詩為樂，被罰扣一半薪水。韓愈稱他為「酸寒溧陽尉」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元和元年（</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">806</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年），河南縣長鄭餘慶上奏他為河南水陸轉運從事，試協律郎，定居洛陽。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元和三年（</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">808</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年）為檢校兵部尚書，兼東都留守。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">60</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歲時，因母死辭官。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鄭餘慶轉任山南西道節度使，任興元太守時，又奏孟郊為參謀、試大理評事。郊應邀前往，到閿鄉（今河南靈寶），不幸以暴病去世。孟郊的朋友韓愈等人湊了</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">100</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貫錢為他辦理後事，鄭餘慶派人送</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">300</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貫，當作「遺孀永久的生活費。」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解籤範例</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1509041709739"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">問籤範例一</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">：解；這是做了虧心事，故有此病。因此務必誠心懺悔或償還虧欠，這才能康復。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 10;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十一籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乙甲</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下下</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今年好事一番新。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">富貴榮華萃汝身。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誰道機關難料處。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">到頭獨立轉傷神。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">道→識</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今年的福報或表現有番新氣象</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">榮華富貴都聚集在你身了</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誰料這其中卻還有難以開解之處</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">到頭來卻暗自神傷</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鋒芒太露，易招暗算。吉中有凶，謹慎為要。福中有禍，低調是道。表顯傑出，謙恭為方。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求得此籤者，吉中有凶。當注意好事的後面跟著壞事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人生無常，若處順境，當防逆境。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">做事當防「人心隔肚皮」。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身求姻緣者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身者想要求得姻緣的話，原本一個人清清心心的，當多了一個人相處後，事情可沒有那麼單純了，這反而給你帶來苦惱。因此，若你想要求得姻緣的話，這是你需要有的心理準備。另外，若求姻緣者，當預防被人所騙，要預防甜言蜜語的陷阱。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問與當前交往對象未來前途者，或問當前對象可否結婚者。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一時的甜蜜，只是一時不代表長久，因為人心是隨時會變的。愛你的人，也有可能突然變心的，而到頭來卻令人神傷，這是你要有的心理準備。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若情人分手欲求挽回者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這次的分手雖然挽回不難，但是，挽回後並非就是福，這反而是神傷的開始，因此建議你，還是放下這份愛情為宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇總結，愛情前後過程；雙方的相處剛開始很甜蜜（甚至論及婚嫁），但是後來有人變心了，或發生意想不到之事，而後卻令人神傷不已。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作、創業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問合夥事業者，當防互相陷害或其中有人暗取利益，或為利益糾紛。因此，合夥不宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問創業者，此事業剛開始欣欣向榮，只是好景不長，會有料想不到的損失。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問工作前途者，若在工作表現優異者，恐怕不能得到對等的待遇。也可能表現太好而受人忌妒或被人暗中陷害。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇總結，事業或工作前途，剛開始很好，但是到後來就令人傷神了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職者，雖然能找到喜歡的好工作，但是，看起來很好的工作，恐是個陷阱。意即，找到的工作沒有你想像中那麼好。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前事業或生意可否更換者，過去你的事業經營的算很好，若是更換的話，恐會讓人傷神，因此建議維持原狀經營即可。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問考試能否上榜者，雖然此考試錄取機會很大，只是錄取後，恐是辛苦、傷神的開始。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求孕者，雖然可以懷孕，但是過程卻不順利。若問求子者，雖然可以如願生子，但是生個問題兒，卻也難養。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問疾病者，此病隨時會有料想不到的嚴重性。請利用目前還康健情況下，多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以準備來世的功德資糧。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">命運難亨。亦不如意。吉中有凶。事實無濟。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">切莫貪求。出外不利。如或妄動。福消禍至。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">作事須宜慎。人心隔肚皮。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">用心防算險。百事自合宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">自宜→允相宜</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤宜更改方得財祿。要知足。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不可與人其事。恐機事不密。反成禍敗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">官有旌麾之喜。孕生男。士有超拔之喜。訟者勝。婚不吉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤卻要知道吾人處世。當見機而作。今年命運。雖吉未吉。似亨未亨。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">欲問孕生男。終難長養。底於有成。難料處言。事有變幻。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事占之徒勞心力。若強為。到底無益。立字一作力字。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先吉後凶。先實後虛。先熱鬧後落陷。先稠密。後妒害。識透機關。須是平氣忍受。善自解脫。不可急躁生事。更加纏綿。獨立傷神。明是小人結黨。君子守正。孤立無與。靜以需之。困可亨。否可泰也。反此則凶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一番新。初勢甚為得意。萃汝身。外面亦似光彩。豈知翻雲覆雨。變態無常。爾詐我虞。人情難測。一旦落在機關。殊出意外。獨立傷神。小人道長。君子道消也。於時為剝。剝極自復。君子正固則吉。若以機關敵機關。則失所以處剝之義矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一生到省。考遺才。占此。不錄。至返家時。乏騎步行。應轉傷神也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又兩商人同往茶山採茶。多年蝕本。欲收場。未決。故托人占此。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">或勤再做。一信之。一不聽。遂折股。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">其一人將資本攜歸。中途得病。到歲杪。尚在旅寓獨宿。末句驗甚。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一人再整適茶葉。失收。但人心太寒。無敢買。被獨廣購。果大有獲。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">改因轉賣</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">賣本作左貝右僕心僕去人</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">洋船。乃敗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">全詩俱應。末句到頭獨立。功極。轉傷神三字尤妙。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">韓信功勞不久</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝韓信，准陰人。助漢高帝平定天下。先後打敗魏、趙、燕、齊、楚國。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">建立十大功勞，被封為楚王。高祖劉邦很忌妒他的才能，假裝去湖南玩，捉住韓信逼他投降。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">韓信被封淮陰侯，不知謙虛，愛誇耀自己功勞。才招來殺身滅門的災禍。死時才三十二歲，雖有功勞，卻活不久。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孫臏遇龐涓</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰國時代。孫臏齊國人。龐涓魏國人，同樣拜鬼谷子為老師。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孫臏的學問比龐涓好。龐涓當魏國將軍時與孫臏鬥智，因為輸了就忌妒孫臏，龐涓就用計謀要把孫臏砍斷腳。後來孫臏假裝顛狂，才能脫逃。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">齊威王用孫臏為師，帶兵攻魏。孫臏用減灶增兵的計謀，騙了龐涓，追至馬陵道，用伏兵射死龐涓。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 11;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十二籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乙乙</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">中平</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">營為期望在春前。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誰料秋來又不然。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直遇清江貴公子。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一生活計始安全。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在春天之前就努力經營，並希望有一番氣象</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誰料到了秋天竟然還是不理想</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">直到遇到了這個從遠方而來的貴人。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貴公子代表你所期望的人或事</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一生的生活才終於安定下來。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春去秋來，謀望未果，直遇此機，終獲安定。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當你遇到生命中的貴人（生命中期盼的人或事業）之後，此生終於安定了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你期盼姻緣的到來已經有段時日，只是一直不能實現願望，在不久的未來，你的另一伴就會出現，只是你需要時間上的等待，這也是你當論及婚嫁的正緣了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">自然遇到的對象才是喔！</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求？當前交往的對象可否進一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你盼望與他有所進展已經多時，只是一直不能實現，其實，你當前喜歡的或是來往的對象，還不是你的終身伴侶。在未來，若在生活中自然機緣中相識的，這才是你的終身伴侶！</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">如果他的名字中有「水」字邊的，則是首選了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若情人或夫妻分手者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過去的相處一直不如意，以致發展成分手的局面，其實，你還有個貴公子等著你哪！在未來，你自然會遇到他，這也是讓你安定一生的如意郎君了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">特別去找的人或經人介紹的人都不是喔！</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇總結，當前所遇並非你的終身伴侶，而你的另一伴，將來會和你在自然機緣中相逢，此情人只在近江之處而非遠方，而你的他和「水」有關，此人才是你安定一生的伴侶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病者，此病治療多時，卻一直沒有進展，其實，你找該換個醫生了。只要找到好醫生，那此病就能有所進展了。若是慢性病者，建議依此而醫效果更好</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求孕者，其實你是可以實現的。若問生子者，其實你也是可以達成的，就是有了這個兒子，而使你心靈終於安定了下來。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若你的事業或工作一直做的不理想的話，若你是員工，那你需要換個新的老闆。若你本身是老闆，那你需要雇用賢明的員工。若能如此改變的話，那你的事業或工作就能安定一生了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">最近你想要更換工作，因為過去一直做的不好，也確實，你需要換老闆了。換了新的老闆，此工作就是你安定一生的工作了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問公職考試、國家考試、升學考試者，經歷多次考試的失敗，當你真正考上之後，你才因此安定一生。因此，無論如何你也要考上才行，只要你好好用功，遲早都可以如願的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆訴訟</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此官司當找個貴人來和解，才能吉利。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">作事遲疑。求財未遂。臨江貴人。望之如意。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">萬一他求。徒勞心志。且謹踐修。以俟時至。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事苦難成。好處反傷情。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">好人為主宰。謀望盡皆亨。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">→</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡百苦難告。好事反傷情。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">從今逢引掖。謀望盡皆亨。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先憂繼疑。最後始定。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">謀事須托。傍人扶持。或官場或紳士。方能有成。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">訟宜休。病擇醫。直到秋散後。始獲安全。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">慎勿誤聽讒言。信任非人可也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">營為在春間。主多遂意。交至秋分。則否。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">大抵始吉終凶。清江貴人。謂遠方貴顯之人也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">遇之扶持。則百事遂意。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">舍此他求。徒勞心力財貨。至秋必主清廢。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">訟有變。主貴人和解。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤幾番謀望。事與願違。屢次相左。然遇合有定。須在近江之地。或水旁姓名之人。必有格外投契。一味靠著此人。可保生計安全。此當關係夙緣。不可以有意求。只可以無意遇。莫之為而為。莫之致而致。靜。以俟之可耳。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春後期望。秋又不然。主現在謀為反覆。事多不成。時未至。緣未至也。清江指地。公子指人。將來須遇清江之人。方是真知己。真靠背。一生活計。謂平生衣食所出也。保安全。謂此人永遠扶持。一生豐衣足。專靠此人。不須他求也。若勉強奔馳。只以現前光景。則亦何益之有哉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一士人問終身。得此籤。久而不遇。至晚年。適有淮安宦家聘為西賓。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">大有所得。其家居在清江。浦方悟籤語之靈驗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又一人自泉渡臺收帳。去時與妻約。兩三月便可回來。後經年不歸。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">其妻遣人占此。及至回家時。計其外出之月。恰與牧羊之年數適相符。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">合籤意之巧如此。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又光緒庚辰歲試。林生與友三人合占此。依序猜榜發。惟林取進。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蓋生年最長。故籤言一生是始者。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蘇武牧羊</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。蘇武，字子卿。杜陵地方人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">天漢初，蘇武以中郎將身份出使匈奴。被強留。吃雪吞氈毛過活，拿著使節拐杖牧羊。在海上（匈奴地名）住了十九年，才能返國。被任為典屬國（官名）。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宣帝時，賜蘇武爵位為關內侯，在麒麟閣掛上蘇武圖像。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鮑叔牙薦管仲</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">鮑叔牙（前</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">－</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D644%E5%B9%B4" title="前644年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">644</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A7%92%E5%A7%93" title="姒姓"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">姒姓</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，鮑氏，亦稱「鮑叔」、「鮑子」，是鮑敬叔的兒子。潁上（今屬安徽）人</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/#_note-0"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">[1]</font></span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，春秋時代齊國大夫，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%AE%A1%E4%BB%B2" title="管仲"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">管仲</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">的好朋友。早期管仲貧困，鮑叔牙時常接濟他。後來管仲侍奉</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%BD%8A%E8%A5%84%E5%85%AC" title="齊襄公"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">齊襄公</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">的兒子</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%85%AC%E5%AD%90%E7%B3%BE" title="公子糾"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">公子糾</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，鮑叔牙侍奉公子糾的弟弟</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%85%AC%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%8F%E7%99%BD" title="公子小白"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">公子小白</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。齊國內亂，管仲則隨公子糾出奔</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%AD%AF%E5%9C%8B" title="魯國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">魯</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，鮑叔牙隨公子小白出奔</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%8E%92" title="莒"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">莒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，小白返國繼承君位之後，公子糾被殺，管仲被囚車運送回國。鮑叔牙推薦管仲當上了宰相，被時人譽為「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%AE%A1%E9%AE%91%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%A4" title="管鮑之交"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;FONT-SIZE:11pt;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">管鮑之交</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」、「鮑子遺風」。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E" title="查看維基百科的簡介"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">維基百科</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 12;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十三籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乙丙</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">中平</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君今庚甲未亨通。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">且向江頭作釣翁。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">玉兔重生應發跡。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">萬人頭上逞英雄。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你從庚年到甲年，前途都不得意。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有五年之厄</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">那且就學姜太公那般的等候吧。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">守舊等待為宜</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在逢兔年的時候，重新出發則有發跡的機會。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">兔年是良機</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">屆時，你就萬人頭上當英雄了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇時運不濟，前途未通，尚應等待，熬過五年，逢兔之歲，發跡有望。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇待守之年，充實學問，行善積德，隨時懺悔，以備來日，一舉登魁。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇以下年份都是凶年，在這些年份中各種謀求都不宜。若能多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，則能減少災禍發生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">民國</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">99</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">～</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">103</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">109</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">～</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">113</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">119</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">～</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">123……</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:12pt;">◇本籤是每十年有五年屬凶，每十二年有一年屬吉，若凶吉之年重疊者，該年仍屬吉祥之年，可以進行各種謀求，唯獨占者除了充實學問之外，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';FONT-SIZE:12pt;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a>.<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:12pt;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:12pt;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:12pt;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';FONT-SIZE:12pt;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><span style="">.</span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:12pt;">之功課更需加強不能懈怠，以便能萬人頭上當英雄。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在兔年的時候，是你找到姻緣的年份，而當前的你，則須等待。請自行把握該年。若在其他年份所遇到的對象，則不會有結果。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？目前交往對象可否進一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的姻緣其實還沒到，所以和當前喜歡的對象交往不會有結果。若處在兔年時，你就可以全力爭取自己的姻緣了，而其他年份還請等待為宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若交往多年者，問此愛情前途或可否結婚者。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的愛情屬於晚婚型，因為每十年才有一年的結婚之年，若要結婚請把握每次的兔年，要不然又得等十年。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手，或關係困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的愛情一直不順遂，因為你的姻緣年份未到之故，所以，若不是兔年或每年陰曆二月認識的對象，你都不必挽回，因為不會有結果。若到了兔年，請在這一年好好把握發展愛情，最好在這一年就決定結婚。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的事業發展一直不能有很好的表現，因為你的事業好運每十年才有一年，因此，若沒有等到兔年，你的事業就是好不了。不過，人生的命運也是可以改造的，只要你願意</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></span></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，命運也是可以更好的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職者，你的求職好運在陰曆的二月，請把握此段時間全力找工作。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想換工作者，你的好運在兔年，在這一年當中凡事皆宜。若是處在凶年的話，即使你換工作也一樣不會更好。若在凶年之外想要換工作時，請把握每年的陰曆二月份，這是你換職的最佳良機。但是，有沒有必要更換工作，這是你自己要思考的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問各種考試者，你的發跡之年比較晚，所以尚應等待，若遇到兔年的時候，才是你金榜題名的良機。此外，若考試是在陰曆的二月份，你也可以一試高下。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想求孕或求子者，除了庚年到甲年不利如願外，每年的陰曆二月就是懷孕的良機，請預先做好懷孕準備，以能在這短短的時間內能懷孕成功。若是錯過這個月份不能懷孕的話，則應等待明年。另外，若是在兔年的話，則全年都有懷孕機會。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病者，這個疾病會拖延很久，所以要有長期治療的準備。但是，若你願意修行的話，那疾病的痊癒就加快了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆訴訟</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請注意在凶年期間容易發生災禍，因此宜提早</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以能避免。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若在這些年份發生訴訟事件，則對你都不利。請盡量避免與人打官司為宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">命運當蹇。凡事遲疑。且宜守舊。藏器待時。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年與日月。逢卯則宜。或遇望日。方稱所為。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡→萬</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孕男婚不成。守舊莫紛更。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不貪與不妒。平安福祿生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤。君子占有五年之厄。庶人占有五年之難。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若能守己。轉禍為福。不宜進圖更改。休問訟。免是非也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">江頭釣翁。指呂望。未遇時。釣於渭濱。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">及西伯侯車之載。則萬人上英雄矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今君指卜者說。未亨通。言目下未遇。有五年之厄。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">是自庚至甲也。若能守己。待時至。卯年月。則轉禍為福。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">士人高擢。庶人發福。且不但卯年月日遂意。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若望日。則玉兔重生亦應。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤現在時運未濟。且須安靜耐守。如彼江頭釣翁。何等閒散。宜待卯年月日。大有發跡。士子是時科第。仕宦是時升擢。商賈是時財利。定有高壓萬人之勢。未可以泛常論也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">江頭鈞翁。安閒守分之人。言沉困時。須宜學此。以待運至。玉兔重生。當是年月疊卯之際。應發跡。顯達在此時也。萬人頭上。一時超邁等倫。逞英雄。為所欲為也。占此者。名位超出之選。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一孝廉會試。臨考占此。有為之斷曰。不獲。大喜必遭奇禍。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">以萬人頭上決之。及至就試之日。被人眾躋倒。仆地踐踏而死。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又一生。甲午年。卜秋闈。斷曰。必中。言今科值甲午必亨通。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">科甲未聯捷。後果如其言。應在甲未亨通四字。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又光緒三年。晉江縣。張氏有兩子。俱應意試。其父占此。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">榜發。惟卯年所生之次子。入泮。此固玉兔重生句之驗也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">姜太公釣魚</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">姜太公釣蟠溪</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">周朝。姜尚，字子牙。汲人</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東海許州人</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">道號是飛熊。祖先封地在呂，所以他又叫呂望。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">避商紂王亂事，隱居東海之水邊，在磻溪</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">渭水</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">) </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釣魚。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">魚鉤是直的，可見用意不在釣魚，志向是當宰相。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">文王聽說姜子牙賢明，聘為丞相。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時姜尚八十歲</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來助周文王伐紂，滅商興周。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 13;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十四籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乙丁</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下下</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一見佳人便喜歡。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誰知去後有多般。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人情冷暖君休訝。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歷涉應知行路難。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一看到這個人（或事）就很喜歡。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你可知道這發展下去有多困難。（一時看起來很好之事，若發展下去你才知道事情不簡單）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人情的冷暖變化，你不用驚訝。（局勢、人心等等變化無常，你不用驚訝。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">要走這條路，當了解此路之堅難。（若想做一件事情，你當先了解這事情的難處）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇一時喜歡，不表永久，人心善變，當防未然。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇心地無常，義德為上，事易變遷，樂事易悔。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇各種謀求，當思考其難處，而不要只是看到好處而求。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">雖然，你有機會遇到喜歡的對象，只是，這條愛情路並不好走。單身一個人可以自在過日子，但是多了一個人，就全然不是這麼回事。因此建議目前不宜求姻緣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？當前交往對象可否進一步發展？問此愛情前途或可否結婚？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當前的你，雖然看到他就喜歡，雖然你也可能和他有所來往，但是，人情冷暖變化只在一瞬間。意即，即使你和他進行來往，就算和他能談笑風聲一時，但是隨時都會情緒丕變，翻臉不認人。對於目前已經交往者也是如此，隨時要準備分手發生。而已經交往多時者，現在則不宜論及婚嫁，因為你們的感情尚未穩定。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們的愛情就是在分分合合中渡過，即使當前的分手能復合，但是隨時還是鬧分手。若想讓愛情過的更穩當，建議雙方都應省思自己，檢視己過，多為對方著想，若能如此，那也許，這愛情能延續久些。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇總結</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人在單身時往往渴求愛情，果然有日得到了愛情或是結婚了，而此刻卻又渴望單身了。此話要給求得此籤者自行省思。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問事業（工作）前途者，這個事業（工作）剛開始讓人欣慰，只是事（工作）興衰是有起伏的，經營事業（工作）者，當要有所準備，以度過隨時的難關。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職者，要找個好工作或找到工作，這是不容易的，即使你可以找到喜歡的工作。但是，一時的喜歡不代表永久，所以，當你謀得工作時，也不必高興太早，而要有挫折的心理準備。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆創業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你想要自行創業，雖然前景看起來這麼美好，但是直到你經營之後，才發現事情不簡單。若你想創業的話，此道理就留給你自己思考吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆換職</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若你當前工作的不順遂而想要換工作的話，你當知道重新出發，重新找工作，這也是不容易的。若想事業或工作更順遂，建議還是多多修福報與功德吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、競試</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你興致勃勃的要參與這個考試，但是每個考試都有他的難處，當你多次嘗試之後，你才體會這個考試有多難。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求孕或求子者，求得此籤可懷孕生女，但是，當你有了孩子，才會感受養育兒女的辛酸，因此，若想求孕者，還是要有心理準備。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病、健康</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病的話，也許你可以聽到很多這種疾病的療法，其實，要治療這個疾病並不容易。建議，人生還是要多多修行，若能務實修行，那就是在治療了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事望團圓。反生齟齬。人多不情。恐難憑據。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">只宜自省。無為他誤。戒之戒之。且疑且慮。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乍喜反成憂。虛花總不收。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">世情多反覆。守己是良謀。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先喜後憂。不宜放肆。大概親而又陳。合而復離。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">歷涉險阻。竟無成。尤兢兢業業。庶免後悔。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">大抵此籤。好事難成。親中招怨。惹禍難免。婚不宜成。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占此不可托人。宜自周旋。免得後日之悔。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰樂天諷諫。曰行路難。不在水兮不在山。人情反覆。問是也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">應字或作方字亦通。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤先喜後憂。不宜放肆。大概親而又疏。合而復離。歷涉險阻。竟無成就。兢兢業業。庶免後悔。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">佳人。女子姣好之稱。凡占者相交共事之人。便喜歡。一見浹洽。去後多般。情意反覆也。人情冷暖。大抵如斯。不足詫異。須知世人不可輕信。每受愚弄。過後方知。如遠涉者偏歷險阻。始信行路之難也。戒占者慎重提防。毋貽後悔也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一士父母。為之求婚。己私。占此。不敢竟白。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後果因貧富。久而不諧。六禮將畢而復悔。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">郭華戀王月英</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋朝郭華是洛陽人，去開封參加考試。因為喜愛賣胭脂的女人王月英的美貌，當考試落第沒後，沒回家就逗留在開封。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當郭華與王月英約會時，王月英來了。郭華卻因喝酒太多醉倒了，王月英推他也醒不過來，王月英就脫下自己的花鞋，藏在郭華的懷中，然後才離去。直到郭華醒來，看到鞋子悔恨不已，竟吞下鞋子，昏死了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張耳陳餘交</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（故事源自</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://www.kimen.com.tw/H-03/H-00/H-03.htm"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:10pt;">史記</span><span style="COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:10pt;"><font face="Times New Roman">‧</font></span></a><a span="http://www.kimen.com.tw/H-03/H-00/H-03.htm"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:10pt;">張耳陳餘列傳</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張耳、陳餘是好朋友，但是他們兩人在危急時表現的是置對方的生死於度外。以茍全個人性命為優先考慮，這豈不是對當初「刎頸之交」、「同生死」誓言的諷刺嗎！所以司馬遷對他們兩人的評論是「勢利之交」了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto auto;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 14;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.兩家門戶各相當。<br/>2.不是姻緣莫較量。<br/>3.直待春風好消息。<br/>4.卻調琴瑟向蘭房。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.雙方條件很相當(勢均力敵不相上下)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若彼此沒有緣份的，是不會成事的。（若無對等條件、實力，免想成事）。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.直到春天出現時，就有了好消息。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.卻在屋子內較量琴瑟。（意即，常會鬥嘴）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你想爭取的人或事條件很好，但要有對等的實力方能得勝。若無此實力，那就自行退去吧。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.春天，是經營此事的好時機。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"><br/>其實你的條件也不賴，要找個對象並不難，而你的姻緣可望在春天時出現，屆時請自行把握吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你和他的條件都很相當，若自覺條件差他很多，那就乾脆不要追了。若是自覺條件差不多的話，那在春天的時候，這愛情就有消息了。只是，往後的發展，還是難免會有些口角或較勁。建議，屆時還是多多忍讓，這有利你們的愛情發展。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前發展中的愛情前途<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們兩的條件都很相當，可以說門當戶對，但是要注意的是，要多多保持尊重對方，說話時要維持禮節，個性上不要任性，以免壞了愛情。建議充實些<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，可以減少你們的紛爭。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手欲求挽回<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們兩個就是常常吵嘴，所以鬧分手了，其實，就算你挽回了愛情，這吵嘴還是不可避免，屆時又是分分合合，如此反覆，而這樣的愛情要不要挽回，那你要自己思考了。若是你要挽回的話，建議充實<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，以包容退讓的心情應對，這可以讓你們更好相處。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結<span lang="EN-US"><br/>雙方條件都很好，但是也要對等條件方能成事。因此，若一方條件不佳者，此婚事不能成。若雙方條件具優，則常有紛爭。個性上的嬌、寵，或身份上的自身優越感，而使得雙方容易爭執或分手。若能收斂自己，則有利愛情發展。<br/></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">待春天時刻，可成連理。而婚後，雙方仍有番較量。<span lang="EN-US">(當雙方條件都很優越時，雙方難免會有尊嚴之爭的比試、較勁。)</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請發揮你的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛情操</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以讓琴瑟和鳴。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業或工作者，這份工作或事業是有難度的，若能力不夠的話，是無法勝任的。因此，加強你的專業能力，這是必要的。而你的事業或工作，在春天時刻會比較穩定。而在其他季節中，當預防工作中的不順遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你在工作中作的不順利而想要換工作，其實，這份工作是很有挑戰性的，若沒有對等的實力，這是無法應付的。而當前既然做的不暢快，那建議還是換個自己能勝任的工作吧！建議，若要工作順利的話，一要提升自己的專業能力。二要善於與人相處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、錄用<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種考試者，此考試有難度，若無對等的實力或是沒這個命，恐怕考不上，因此，加強你的實力這是必要的，另外若考試是在春天，則對你的考試有利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆問二選一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">代表此兩者條件都很好，你也都喜歡。若選擇對象是「人」，你可以私下了解對方的意思如何，或他們各方面條件和自己適配程度，整體評估後自行決定。若對象是「物」，則評估它各方面條件哪個好，你就選哪個。此事可望在春天時明朗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆經商合夥<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">代表雙方都滿有實力，各有事業上的優越處。此合作關係若在春天的時候開始，則有利合夥成功。但是在未來的合作事業當中，有些事情還是需要雙方多多協調的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，這要高明的醫師方能診治。直待春天之後，病情好轉，但往後的病情還是有起落，還是要在好環境中調養。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司者，代表雙方實力堅強，各說各有理，誰也不讓誰。建議好好的調解「以和為貴」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆購屋<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">代表這房子高貴，若財力不夠，恐怕買不起。但這房子的管理成本，或無形中的開銷也比較高，而且有些小問題。買或不買，自行決定。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆尋物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問尋物者，此物隱藏的地方玄密，尋找方法高明可得。但是失物稍有損傷需要修理。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求生孩子或生子，這是需要對等的福報，尤其是生兒子，這更需要對等的福德。你當前的這份福德還不夠，所以不管你求孕還是求子，你可以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一年以後再求。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩意未合。宜於待時。防憂與慮。謹慎愆非。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>直待來春。萬事方吉。若或妄動。徒勞心懷。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">慮→患</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">非→期</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉→佳</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩家未合。百事難諧。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>門戶可慮。猷恐成乖。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤名不成。利不就。婚不合。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事卻待新春。方始稱意。若妄作。反勞心力。終不能如人心願也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各相當者。謂情不能諧也。主骨肉有言語口舌之傷矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其物換人移。方得。妻子和合。父母克諧。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若或妄為。徒勞無益。直遇寅卯辰年月日。名利皆有。百事合宜也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤現在謀事。甚不相宜。看似機緣。終竟反覆。即宜捨此另圖。自有好處。春間定得信息。如婚姻前定。自然和合。只可待時。不可妄為。時至自得成就耳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各相當。門戶相等。不是姻緣。強求何益。莫較量。戒占者不須留戀也。好消息。謂另有好音。直待春時應驗。此際琴瑟調和。信屬嘉耦。蘭房。婦人內室也。於此完婚。允遂宜室宜家之願矣。凡事慎重。自有天緣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人春間往楚經商。卜此。謂秋間必返。及到彼。因事羈留。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">剛到明春抵家。末二句驗甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">張君瑞憶鶯鶯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝，張拱</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張珙</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">字君瑞。因有事到蒲東，寄居在普救寺。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">寺的西廂房，住有崔氏母女，她們是張君瑞的表親。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">女生名叫鶯鶯，長得很美。當時正好有流寇作亂，崔母告訴張君瑞，如能保護母女，願將女兒嫁給他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君瑞出面保護，使他們免除災難。後來崔母背棄約定，不嫁女兒給君瑞。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君瑞因此相思成病，有見識的人說君瑞沒考取科名，才會如此。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（君瑞程度不夠，所以儘管有約在前，人家也要背盟。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王羲之坦腹<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%83%97%E9%91%92" title="郗鑒"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">郗鑒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">派門生往王府選婿，王府子弟均刻意保持矜持，唯獨王羲之在東牀上袒腹臥著。郗鑒便認為他是適合的人選，便決定將女兒郗濬嫁給他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(條件相當，即使不刻意追求也能成事。)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 15;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.兩家門戶各相當。<br/>2.不是姻緣莫較量。<br/>3.直待春風好消息。<br/>4.卻調琴瑟向蘭房。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.雙方條件很相當(勢均力敵不相上下)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若彼此沒有緣份的，是不會成事的。（若無對等條件、實力，免想成事）。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.直到春天出現時，就有了好消息。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.卻在屋子內較量琴瑟。（意即，常會鬥嘴）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你想爭取的人或事條件很好，但要有對等的實力方能得勝。若無此實力，那就自行退去吧。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.春天，是經營此事的好時機。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"><br/>其實你的條件也不賴，要找個對象並不難，而你的姻緣可望在春天時出現，屆時請自行把握吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你和他的條件都很相當，若自覺條件差他很多，那就乾脆不要追了。若是自覺條件差不多的話，那在春天的時候，這愛情就有消息了。只是，往後的發展，還是難免會有些口角或較勁。建議，屆時還是多多忍讓，這有利你們的愛情發展。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前發展中的愛情前途<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們兩的條件都很相當，可以說門當戶對，但是要注意的是，要多多保持尊重對方，說話時要維持禮節，個性上不要任性，以免壞了愛情。建議充實些<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，可以減少你們的紛爭。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手欲求挽回<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們兩個就是常常吵嘴，所以鬧分手了，其實，就算你挽回了愛情，這吵嘴還是不可避免，屆時又是分分合合，如此反覆，而這樣的愛情要不要挽回，那你要自己思考了。若是你要挽回的話，建議充實<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，以包容退讓的心情應對，這可以讓你們更好相處。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結<span lang="EN-US"><br/>雙方條件都很好，但是也要對等條件方能成事。因此，若一方條件不佳者，此婚事不能成。若雙方條件具優，則常有紛爭。個性上的嬌、寵，或身份上的自身優越感，而使得雙方容易爭執或分手。若能收斂自己，則有利愛情發展。<br/></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">待春天時刻，可成連理。而婚後，雙方仍有番較量。<span lang="EN-US">(當雙方條件都很優越時，雙方難免會有尊嚴之爭的比試、較勁。)</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請發揮你的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛情操</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以讓琴瑟和鳴。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業或工作者，這份工作或事業是有難度的，若能力不夠的話，是無法勝任的。因此，加強你的專業能力，這是必要的。而你的事業或工作，在春天時刻會比較穩定。而在其他季節中，當預防工作中的不順遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你在工作中作的不順利而想要換工作，其實，這份工作是很有挑戰性的，若沒有對等的實力，這是無法應付的。而當前既然做的不暢快，那建議還是換個自己能勝任的工作吧！建議，若要工作順利的話，一要提升自己的專業能力。二要善於與人相處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、錄用<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種考試者，此考試有難度，若無對等的實力或是沒這個命，恐怕考不上，因此，加強你的實力這是必要的，另外若考試是在春天，則對你的考試有利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆問二選一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">代表此兩者條件都很好，你也都喜歡。若選擇對象是「人」，你可以私下了解對方的意思如何，或他們各方面條件和自己適配程度，整體評估後自行決定。若對象是「物」，則評估它各方面條件哪個好，你就選哪個。此事可望在春天時明朗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆經商合夥<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">代表雙方都滿有實力，各有事業上的優越處。此合作關係若在春天的時候開始，則有利合夥成功。但是在未來的合作事業當中，有些事情還是需要雙方多多協調的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，這要高明的醫師方能診治。直待春天之後，病情好轉，但往後的病情還是有起落，還是要在好環境中調養。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司者，代表雙方實力堅強，各說各有理，誰也不讓誰。建議好好的調解「以和為貴」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆購屋<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">代表這房子高貴，若財力不夠，恐怕買不起。但這房子的管理成本，或無形中的開銷也比較高，而且有些小問題。買或不買，自行決定。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆尋物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問尋物者，此物隱藏的地方玄密，尋找方法高明可得。但是失物稍有損傷需要修理。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求生孩子或生子，這是需要對等的福報，尤其是生兒子，這更需要對等的福德。你當前的這份福德還不夠，所以不管你求孕還是求子，你可以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一年以後再求。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩意未合。宜於待時。防憂與慮。謹慎愆非。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>直待來春。萬事方吉。若或妄動。徒勞心懷。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">慮→患</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">非→期</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉→佳</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩家未合。百事難諧。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>門戶可慮。猷恐成乖。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤名不成。利不就。婚不合。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事卻待新春。方始稱意。若妄作。反勞心力。終不能如人心願也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各相當者。謂情不能諧也。主骨肉有言語口舌之傷矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其物換人移。方得。妻子和合。父母克諧。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若或妄為。徒勞無益。直遇寅卯辰年月日。名利皆有。百事合宜也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤現在謀事。甚不相宜。看似機緣。終竟反覆。即宜捨此另圖。自有好處。春間定得信息。如婚姻前定。自然和合。只可待時。不可妄為。時至自得成就耳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各相當。門戶相等。不是姻緣。強求何益。莫較量。戒占者不須留戀也。好消息。謂另有好音。直待春時應驗。此際琴瑟調和。信屬嘉耦。蘭房。婦人內室也。於此完婚。允遂宜室宜家之願矣。凡事慎重。自有天緣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人春間往楚經商。卜此。謂秋間必返。及到彼。因事羈留。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">剛到明春抵家。末二句驗甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">張君瑞憶鶯鶯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝，張拱</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張珙</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">字君瑞。因有事到蒲東，寄居在普救寺。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">寺的西廂房，住有崔氏母女，她們是張君瑞的表親。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">女生名叫鶯鶯，長得很美。當時正好有流寇作亂，崔母告訴張君瑞，如能保護母女，願將女兒嫁給他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君瑞出面保護，使他們免除災難。後來崔母背棄約定，不嫁女兒給君瑞。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君瑞因此相思成病，有見識的人說君瑞沒考取科名，才會如此。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（君瑞程度不夠，所以儘管有約在前，人家也要背盟。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王羲之坦腹<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%83%97%E9%91%92" title="郗鑒"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">郗鑒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">派門生往王府選婿，王府子弟均刻意保持矜持，唯獨王羲之在東牀上袒腹臥著。郗鑒便認為他是適合的人選，便決定將女兒郗濬嫁給他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(條件相當，即使不刻意追求也能成事。)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 16;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.田園價貫好商量。<br/>2.事到公庭彼此傷。<br/>3.縱使機關圖得勝。<br/>4.定為後世子孫殃。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.不管什麼事都好商量，而不要堅持。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.事若互不退讓而鬧上法院則雙方都受傷。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.即使圖用心機、計策而得勝。（反而害己而利他）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.也因為如此而使未來子孫蒙受災殃。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若欲安然解決此事，則應溫和委婉商量，若用伎倆反自傷。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.退一步保百年身，捨一次積千年德。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.謙讓就是此事的解藥</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.凡事、做事不可投機，以自然方法行之。以「平常心」應之。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若是單身者，建議不要求姻緣，因為即使有了姻緣，反而增加苦惱與精神打擊。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前心儀的對象可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>建議你退去這種想法。心態不正做事，不會有好結果。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇當前交往的對象可否進一步發展<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若要問進展，也要等到雙方愛情穩定後再問。在爭爭吵吵的情況下，愛情不會有好收場。若要論進展，還請多多用寬容的心互相對待。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手想挽回<span lang="EN-US"><br/>爭爭吵吵互不退讓，也不承認自己有過，這又要如何挽回，就算能挽回，也還是老問題。還請多多自省，再問挽回吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前的對象可否結婚<span lang="EN-US"><br/>結婚乃是終身大事，不可馬虎，更不可勉強，即使你想辦法讓自己結婚了，這婚姻也難以幸福。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問訴訟、爭執、友誼者，以和為貴，謙讓能解。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問治病，溫和對待自己，不要過度疲勞，切忌強治反而更傷身，若能寬心解鬱愁，那就沒有痼疾與身傷了。(請用各種自然療法行之，忌用有風險性或副作用的療法)可求神佛加被。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試者，此籤不吉祥，最好退去考試，就算能考上，也沒有好結果。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>建議行寬慈積仁義，以後再考。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆升遷、徵選<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問升遷、徵選之類者，隨順自然不強求，更免巴結省送禮，莫行賄賂勿關說，如此應對更心安。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>以後除了充實自身實力外，還請多多廣結善緣。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問求孕或求子者，一切以自然行之，若不孕或不能生男，那就順其自然，而不要圖謀伎倆試圖懷孕，以免傷身卻還是沒有結果。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建議行善積德更有益。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職，心態要正，不要有投機的想法。若以投機心謀得工作，將來也是自傷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。建議多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這才有益你的工作。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問事業前途者，若遇到紛爭，當行禮讓，而不要試圖贏過對方，以免遭來後患。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若當前事業良好者，賺錢又獲利，當預防不測之災。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆投資、理財、房地產</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問購買房地產者，價格方面還有議價空間，東西太貴，還不值得買。買了此物，尚得預防糾紛。其他投資者，現在都不宜。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事依本分。自有前程。若用機關。反害其身。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>如作交易。當合人情。倘或妄作。難保安寧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">倘或<span lang="EN-US">→若見</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">交加二字必虛勤。若問財時必見侵。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡事只宜退一步。須知守己得安寧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">交侵<span lang="EN-US">→心田兩字在公平。財產交關勿見侵。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤切須依本分。自有前程。如有機關。反成害己利人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡謀望。自家商酌方好。名利未遂。宜守平常。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人有阻。病可禳。婚難成。謹保安康。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此言訟不成。凡事循理而行。不願乎外。自得亨利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">子孫殃者。本身無事。家口多難。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此。謀望。參商。功名阻滯。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">切宜自安本分。莫置度外。恐有彼此是非。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤示人當依本分平等。凡事再三籌議。不可涉訟。訟則終凶。若恃財勢賄囑。或情面請託。雖僥倖一時之勝。終必欺心害理。不免子孫之受報耳。占者戒之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">價貫商量。戒勿刻剝欺壓。刻剝必致爭訟。公庭浪費。彼此均不利。何益之有。機關得勝。子孫受殃。言心術狡詐。上千鬼神之怒。果報有不爽也。人務貪謀。顧不為子孫計哉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人卜米價。是年米不貴。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又桐城內一士人。有螟蛉子。弗受駕馭。<span lang="EN-US">(螟蛉子：</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義子、養子</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一日偶督責之。竟自逃去。莫知所之。其父百計圖謀。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">終無影響。迨占此之後。乃於勝果舖。尋得帶回家裏。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">旋染怪病。破費許多。未蜀冠而殀亡。三四兩之驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇被難<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">晉朝。石崇字季倫，當城陰太守。攻打吳國有功勞，被封安陽鄉侯。累積很多財富，房屋宏大美觀，吃遍山珍海味，與當時的王愷相當。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來當了交趾採訪（官名）。交趾有美女，名綠珠。石崇用十斛珍珠買了綠珠，把她藏在金谷（地名）。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來趙王司馬倫窺見綠珠，就設計害石崇，希望得到綠珠。石崇蒙難時，綠珠跳樓而死。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">虞芮爭閒田<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">殷商末期，虞國和芮國的人民爭訟不休之際，欲求鄰國的西伯（周文王）主持公道，進入周國即見人民相互禮讓，農夫互讓田界，年輕者禮讓年長者。虞國和芮國的人民深明大義以後，就不再自取其辱求見西伯，以後也不再爭執而互相謙讓了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""> </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 17;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.知君指擬是空華。<br/>2.底事茫茫未有涯。<br/>3.牢把腳根踏實地。<br/>4.善為善應永無差。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.我知道你所說的這件事，只是如空幻的花罷了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.這事發展下去茫茫無涯沒有結果</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3勸你腳踏實地經營</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.善有善報這是不會有差錯的</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.理意雖美，卻幻不實。行善積德，方有善應。務實經營，即有善果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.老實用心經營，才是成事的重點。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.全方位改運請看：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？◇若單身問姻緣何時來？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>對於愛情，不要有太多的幻夢。勸你還是把自己修為做好來，以便留著給人探聽。若能好好端正自己，將來才會有好姻緣。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手者想要挽回<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們的相處狀況你自己也清楚，有否必要挽回，這是你理性思考可以得到答案的。勸你好好反省，自思己過，改正自己壞個性，若想挽回那才有意義啊！若能如此，那以後才會有幸福啊！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前交往的對象可否結婚<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若想共同走向地毯的那端，也要好好的務實經營愛情，該怎麼相處，該怎麼對待，這都是你要學習的。勸你先把<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>修好，再論婚嫁吧！</span></span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇對於愛情困頓者，想要知道愛情前途者，這全看你會不會經營愛情而定。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職、升遷</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問求職、升遷，應該主動介紹自己，表現自己的能力和意願。心態上則要務實，不可有投機、幻夢想法。若想求職、升遷順利，還請提升自己的專業能力。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、創業、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作、創業前途、事業前途，經營事業應該務實，不可投機或做空泛不實的行為。意即，不要做美夢，而要老實經營，若能如此方有善果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、更換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你想要換工作或換學校就讀，理意雖美，但淪空幻。建議，安守當前，腳踏實地，老實經營，方有前途。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試或各種競賽者，努力用功，提升實力這是必須的。應試時不可輕敵，全力應戰，不可忽疏，鎮定赴試，再求神佑，以祈名望。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建議，平常當</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，以便未來競試中可以安然脫穎而出。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，你應該控制飲食，與端正自己的生活作息，這是養病的最根本。另外，心裡的苦惱心結也要解開來，這才是治病的根本所在。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作事未成。空自指擬。且宜緩圖。急則損己。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>更宜向善。禱神求安。轉禍為福。可免多端。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本分兩字到處諧。虧為妄想便生災。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>財源未遂徒勞力。且宜向善保亨來。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩字<span lang="EN-US">→安常</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜妄意求謀。無事空自指擬。定必有損。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">切宜向善。祈禱神靈。轉禍成福。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事有多般。功名無。訟勿鬥。行人遲。財難就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">向善保安。乃為上策。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">空華謂事無成也。未有涯亦空也。凡事宜緩。不宜妄動。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求名利者。難得易失。若從善事行去。則是腳踏實地。無失處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">善為善應。言天之報施。並無差謬。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如遇禍患。占此能修省向善。自然轉凶為吉。而天必佑之矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜妄意求謀。有名無實。只是空華。何用貪痴不已。不如按部就班。腳踏實地行去。內存善心。外行善事。將來自有善報。較之無益之求不已遠乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">空華。謂若鏡花水月。有影無形。可望而不可即也。未有涯。謂妄念無底止也。腳踏實地。諭令捨妄即真。去非就是。一味穩步徐行。庶乎所為皆善。自得善報。永無差。謂感應不爽也。由是科名遂心。財利稱意。子嗣獲吉。皆可操券而獲矣。占者消凶集慶。急自修省。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一道人遇寇。欲趨避。占此。潛隱草廬中。得脫去。是應腳根一句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人被訟。占此。有司公出。不得歸結。是應底事一句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生。占此。秋闈不中。是應第二句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孟嘗君招賢<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰國時代。孟嘗君，姓田名文。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">田文的父親田嬰，財產萬金。門下食客常有從未見過主人一面的。後來田文父親死了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟嘗君在薛（今</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C" title="山東"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">山東</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BB%95%E5%B7%9E" title="滕州"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">滕州</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東南）</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:11pt;">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">招攬諸侯賓客。亡命之徒、有罪之人都投靠他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟嘗君花用家產，寬厚對待賓客，所以天下人士都傾慕他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時，門下食客數千人，不分貴賤，一律平等。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王祐植三槐<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王祐曾經在庭院中種植三棵槐樹，三槐樹蔭滿庭，王祐對人說：「我的兒孫，必定有人作到貴為三公者，這三棵槐樹就是標示。」後來其子王旦，果然貴為宋朝名宰相，正應了王祐所說的話。天下稱為三槐王氏。<span lang="EN-US">   </span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><span style=""> </span> 「按」王祐平生多陰德，且當他面對利與義關頭，毅然知所抉擇，雖然遭到貶官，內心卻坦坦蕩蕩，自知一生行事作為，對得起天地良心，俯仰無愧，自信兒孫必有好報。其後果然應驗。足證天之報施善人絲毫不爽！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:細明體;LETTER-SPACING:2.25pt;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 18;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十九籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙壬<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.嗟子從來未得時。<br/>2.今年星運頗相宜。<br/>3.營求動作都如意。<br/>4.和合婚姻誕貴兒。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.感嘆你自始以來機運都不得意（意即當前不得意。若當前得意者，占此則反）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而今年開始各方面都將順利了（代表開始走運了）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.有什麼期望都能實現（代表心想事成）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.婚姻能和諧，也能誕生貴子。(代表事情能開花結果)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.當前不順遂者，在秋天後開始走運。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若當前所問之事順遂者，當防物極必反。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前愛情分手或困頓者，或來往冷淡者。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>過去的愛情困頓，將成為過去，在未來愛情將步入佳境。若到秋天，則是復合或是論及婚嫁最佳時機，請把握該時好好經營愛情，未來也可望結婚生子。<br/>請展現你的真愛情操，以為愛情加分。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來者。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>姻緣將來，可望秋天是最佳時機，屆時有人介紹或指引，往後來往順利，能成佳偶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前男女相愛合和者，則要小心物極必反，恐有爭吵或分手。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你的機會來了，你就大方的展開行動吧！好好的經營，有機會能為連理佳偶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問整體愛情運者，過去愛情不順遂已成過去，今後開始將邁入溫馨的時刻了，若想結婚的話，那秋天就是你們成事的好時機了，而且婚後能生貴子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、考試、升遷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職錄取、考試上榜、職場升遷者，過去的不如意已成過去了，今後在這方面終於可以順利了，因此這次的考試可以上榜，求職可以得職，升遷也有份，而且將來前途更好。你的好運可望在秋天開始。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆創業、轉業、投資、合夥、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問創業、轉業、投資、合夥者，或許你的過去做的不順遂，這是時機不好之故，今後的事業或投資，都值得一拼，而能有獲益，乃至開花結果。今年的秋天開始，就是你事業的好時機了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求孕或求子者，可望在秋天時懷孕，將可如期望想男得男，想女生女。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">久困沉埋。時運今泰。作事有成。名利俱快。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>更無阻滯。宜為買賣。士人占之。前程遠大。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">時來時去有其時。但要平心任所為。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>自此謀為皆遂意。孕生貴子時宗枝。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<br/>時來時去本參差。時運亨通任所為。<br/>財祿科名皆遂意。婚姻嗣息總相宜。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不問貴賤。皆有和合之象。謀為各事。從今以後可成就也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作客經紀吉。營與人索取吉。求要為此事吉。動力為此事吉。<span lang="EN-US">(吉本作曰)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作凡事。交秋來新運。自然無阻。無子者得子。無官者得官。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始雖頗相宜。終則滔滔順也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">從來未得時。有兩義。占者在得意之日。反不應。此在失意之日。許應此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又當推年命歲運相合。詩意為美。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不問貴賤。皆主謀為和合。年運亨通。從前阻滯。一旦稱心。凡動皆主有成。不須疑慮。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有所經紀曰營。有所謀望曰求。要為此事曰動。力為此事曰作。占此者。無子得子。無官得官。無財得財。婚姻有魚水之懽。親交有膠漆之應。凡事機緣。無不和合。向來運蹇。至此恰得亨通。失意時占此最驗。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生。占秋闈。得此。下第。蓋頗宜者。猶未甚宜也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">試畢。以歲者。准貢是小事吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又先兄。諱晴光。己亥科試。占此籤。自解曰。誕貴兒。是生子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">已完果入泮。為縣學生員。及咸豊登丑元旦。又占得此籤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">復自解曰。誕貴兒。是此生已完矣。果於是年三月卒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又余門人王景星。亦占此籤。入泮。蓋童生占之則吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡占科。各逢未年。必捷。應未便得時也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">內史王的識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">劉智遠得岳氏<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉智遠</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">知遠</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，沙陶</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">沙陀</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">起初當節度使，岳彥真是軍官時，彥真看智遠相貌奇特，就把女兒嫁給他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來智遠在晉朝當官，作邠州太原節度。契丹人消滅晉朝，中原無主，智遠就稱帝，改國曰後漢，仍稱天福而不改年號。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">裴航遇仙<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">裴航是唐朝的一個</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%80%E6%89%8D" title="秀才"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秀才</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。一次坐船時，他向同船的美貌女子樊夫人用詩歌表達了傾慕之意。樊夫人回詩：「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%93%9D%E6%A1%A5" title="藍橋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">藍橋</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">便是神仙窟，何必崎嶇上玉清。」然後就離開了。裴航不解其意。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">之後某一天，裴航路經藍橋驛，向路邊茅草房中一位正在輯麻的老婆婆要水喝。老婆婆讓孫女雲英給他倒了一杯水。裴航看到姿容絕世的雲英，便想娶她為妻。老婆婆要他用玉杵臼將一粒玄霜靈丹搗一百日，然後給她服下，以求長壽。裴航答應了老婆婆的要求，並定下百日之限。裴航回去後，費盡周折終於在</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%99%A2%E5%B7%9E" title="虢州"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">虢州</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（今</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97" title="河南"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">河南</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%81%B5%E5%AE%9D%E5%8E%BF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="靈寶縣 （頁面未存在）"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">靈寶縣</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）一個藥鋪傾其所有買下了玉杵臼，然後長途步行到藍橋，日夜搗藥。月宮中的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%8E%89%E5%85%94" title="玉兔"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">玉兔</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">被裴航的堅貞所感動，每天都來悄悄幫他搗藥，老婆婆也受到感動，終於答應了婚嫁之事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 19;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乙癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一生心事向誰論。<br/>2.十八灘頭說與君。<br/>3.世事盡從流水去。<br/>4.功名富貴等浮雲。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.心裡的心事要向誰傾吐</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.這麼多的苦水說給誰聽</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.世間事都如流水般而去</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.所有功名利祿就如浮雲</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.時機不遇，知己難逢，知音難尋。屢逢險地，無貴人助。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.十八灘頭，代表世事雜亂險惡，有惶恐之難，應當小心提防。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.盼事如流水。意即，期盼不得，大事已去。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.利祿如浮雲。意即，看淡名利可保安康。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. 凡事謀事：前進有險阻，退守則平安。己當更省思，不宜冒然進。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身者求問姻緣何時來。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>良緣難覓，知己難尋。目前不宜求姻緣，以免有禍患。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若已婚者求得此籤。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>目前的婚姻處在惶恐度日中，相處不睦。請多多拜神佛，多念經，以保心安。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手者問挽回<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想挽回，大勢已去，挽回無益。可省力氣，看淡此情。每次的分手，都是你省思的時候，經歷如此的挫敗，你也應該覺醒了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象，可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>與此人無好緣，散去為佳，不要自尋苦惱。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇或問當前交往中之愛情前途<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們的愛情，淚水多於甜蜜。還請多些理性在愛情中。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前交往伴侶可否結婚<span lang="EN-US"><br/>現在還不是論及婚嫁時候，再經過一段時日你再打算。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">最近在事業上不要有什麼動作，一切當守舊。在此時刻，建議多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，可減輕事業中的禍患。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作前途者，目前的你工作不順遂，滿腹心酸無人知。若問求職者，求職多時卻不能得志，真叫人心情惶恐不安。建議此段時間，多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這對於未來是有幫助的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試者，此時流年不利，多考多敗，還請另謀他圖。凡是各種競試都不宜，還請退守以保安康。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟、官司<span lang="EN-US"><br/>此官司讓人惶恐，要是可以的話，建議停止為安。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問治病者，請選有德之醫生。請修心養性，對於慢性病更有效果。若是病入膏肓者，應做最壞準備。</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉進、換職、換校、出國、遠行<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">以上各種謀求都不宜，還請緩後為之，以避險阻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求孕、求子者，現在先不要求，若求得反而不吉利。若實在想求，建議先消業障、行善積德一年之後再求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事未決。且宜緩圖。時勢縱吉。未有神扶。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡事退省。終保無虞。更加修福。可履亨圖。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡<span lang="EN-US">→心<br/>未有→須仗</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">險人求險地。說話險心腸。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>有人牢把作。凶事得安康。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">險腸<span lang="EN-US">→扁舟逢險地。傾覆善須防。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤得之外履。程途險阻。終不大吉利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟終凶。止則吉。功名輕。行人遲。婚未成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事到底不吉。宜謹守可也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始雖履險地。阻中多反覆。心事向誰論者。嘆不得逢貴人之焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十八灘屬贛州灘名。惶恐難也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此。主大事已去。有包羞忍恥之累。但當修省。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名富貴。雖得機會。終亦難就。切勿妄想。<span lang="EN-US">(得本作朔)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只宜謹守。凡事。照占者審之。病不可保。孕不可得。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主同心無人。孤立少助。險難在前之象。既經指示。宜早提防。然大勢已去。難可挽回。不啻流水浮雲之變滅。唯有達觀排遣。斬斷利鎖名韁。毋復繫戀。更生事故。占者悟此。則知患難中玉成不少。或又有困而得亨之日乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心事向誰論。踽踽涼涼。無可告語也。十八灘。屬贛州。灘名惶恐。言前路甚多驚險也。流水去。逝者不可復回。等浮雲。現在皆成烏有。尚何功名富貴之可至哉。知功名富貴之無常。而等之流水浮雲。是即與向誰論者。而與之論脫險之道。每遇之學也。慈恩豈有戰極哉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人買僕。占此後。僕逃去。應世從流水一句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又光緒間。安溪縣。一生歲試。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此後。惟草索取錄十八名。此係第二句之應也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又晉江蘇。郭姓問二子。執得入泮。占此俱失意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此乃第四句等浮雲之驗焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嚴子陵登釣臺<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。嚴光字子陵。餘姚地方人。年少就有清高名聲，曾和劉秀一起遊學。後來光武帝劉秀即位，嚴光改變姓名。隱居不作官。皇帝令人訪尋他。後來浙江桐廬縣長報告，發現有個人反穿了皮襖釣魚。皇帝懷疑此人就是嚴光，派人找他來，去了三次才請到他，讓他當諫議大夫（官名）但他不肯接受，在富春山耕作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">皇帝順從他的志向，為他興建釣臺。他是東漢第一清高人士。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(嚴子陵有機會成為丞相，而且皇帝再三邀請，為何還不肯就任呢？因為政場人心險惡，退之可保吉祥也。尤其忠良賢明者，更容易遭受小人陷害，故寧可退之。)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 20;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙甲<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.與君夙昔結成冤。<br/>2.今日相逢那得緣。<br/>3.好把經文多諷誦。<br/>4.祈求戶內保嬋娟。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.和你宿世以來就有冤仇、虧欠</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而今相逢那能得緣呢</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.多讀些經書吧（建議；誦經、持咒、懺悔一起來，改造效果更好）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.以祈能過的平安吉祥</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你與此人或此事不投緣，故事難以和諧。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.建議</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">可以減輕業障。另外，若是與人相關之事，請頌持「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"><font face="Times New Roman">◎</font></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=19016&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=19012"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:#24878c;">解冤咒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」化解。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情、婚姻<span lang="EN-US"><br/>◇若已結婚者求得此籤<br/>相欠故相逢，相處總有怨，若欲續此緣，寬慈便是道。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>命運的安排讓你們又相逢，若想讓愛情繼續下去，那你就當是還債吧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若已分手之情侶求得此籤，那就不必挽回了（建議）。若想挽回，那往後你會付出很多精神在維繫這個愛情。若你實在想要挽回的話，那就把相處當作還債，這也是可以啦！建議以寬容、慈悲的心對待他，可以讓減少你們的糾紛。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若你想追求他的話，那要有心理準備，往後相處像討債，也容易爭吵。若你很喜歡他的話，實在想追他的話，那建議先把道行修好再說吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">由於過去世的虧欠，今生特別容易在一起，而且容易結為夫妻，而且也容易為小事而鬧的不愉快，這是求到本籤者要認知的。問愛情求得本籤者，若想經營這段感情的話，那就「把愛情當還債，把生活當修行」，這樣你才能過的更好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆合夥<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問事業合夥者；這是冤家又聚頭，在相處上容易相爭計較，所以合夥上難以安定。</span></span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病，這是業障病，請多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">可以減輕病苦或提早痊癒。另外，可請神明代為解冤。自行解冤請用</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"><font face="Times New Roman">◎</font></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=19016&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=19012"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:#24878c;">解冤咒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競賽、升遷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">諸如此類之問；這個競試難以被錄用，因為業障之故。建議好好</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，方有改善機會。<span lang="EN-US"> </span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職者，你很難找到好工作，即使找到工作也是遇到不合適或是很差的工作。神明建議你還是多多讀經吧！建議用這個方法來全面改運：<span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業、工作前途者，此籤代表你和這個工作緣分不好，若經營下去恐將失敗，或是非常辛苦經營，但是效果卻不好，建議保守經營。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">另外，請好好</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，以祈能改造命運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉業、遠行、換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問轉業、出國、外出、遠行、換科系、重考、再深造者，一切以守舊為安。建議多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，以後再做打算。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆訴訟</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這是宿世的仇家相逢，冤冤相報。若想化解，只有寬慈忍讓，輸他一次，方能避免未來世再碰頭。若能和解，則是上上之策。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（以上各項目，建議好好消業障後，再去求籤，看看有否改造，再決定未來。）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">舊有夙冤。作事隨緣。急宜向善。方保安全。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>力行好事。心契上天。變凶為吉。出自福田。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但凡謀事要心機。只怕中間有病危。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>財物交加終到底。更防耗散待傷悲。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<br/>前因損害用心機。只怕中間有險危。<br/>財物存留防耗散。更憂人口得傷悲。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤舊有夙冤。問事無緣。訟凶。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">貴人占之不吉。庶人占之不利。行人未至。謀望不成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問病。宜禳謝方保。財物散。不吉利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事雖有好機會。終於無成。諺云。無緣對面不相逢是也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚姻不足說。難貴顯。庶人占之。皆有變更。不可妄為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人望前。有歸音至。病者在望前。難過嬋娟。陰像也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若朔日。占此。主陰人是非。謙恭以保之。勤儉以待之。則天佑之矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">望日得之不如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤係冤仇纏結。訟事最凶。急自耗財。和解為妙。貴人占之。謹和處世。多行善事。免遭凶禍。平人占之。求神懺禮。遷善改過。可得人口平安。一切謀為。均宜回心向善。乃可逢凶化吉。冤家宜解不宜結。明者悟之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">夙昔結成冤。嫌釁不起自今日也。相逢顯惡緣。今茲正圖報復也。經文諷誦。示人回心向善。存好心。行好事。感格神佛扶持。以冀解散也。嬋娟。指月光言。比譬婦女。言仰沐神祐。家中妻女人口。可保無恙。凡解冤釋患。禳病消災。均有感應。唯在善願甚切。可無憂也。嬋娟。十五月圓之候。時日或應在此。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一典<span lang="EN-US">(當)舖媳病。占此後。其婦讒語曰。我前世為盜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">所得物。俱質汝家。今來安享汝財。速與酬神。可保無恙也。后果如其言。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生。勦襲便文。騙進。因覆場文筆大相刺謬。幾於見黜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後宗師把他經取之。文多誦數遍。不忍割愛。畢竟無恙。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">方悟籤語明言。與君夙昔結成宜<span lang="EN-US">(冤)。無有他慮焉。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">科名之事。猜此卻合。若占別件。慎勿輕決。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孫龐鬥智結仇<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰國時代。孫臏，齊國人。龐涓，魏國人。同樣拜鬼谷子為師。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孫臏學得比龐涓好。涓為魏國將軍，與臏鬥智輸了，因此忌妒孫臏，就用計削去孫臏的腳，後來孫臏假裝顛狂，才脫逃。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">齊威王用</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">臏</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">為師，帶兵攻魏。孫臏用減灶增兵的計謀，騙了龐涓，追至馬陵道，用伏兵射死龐涓。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（由於忌妒對方才能而引發相害）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">須賈害范雎<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戰國時代的魏國有個名叫范雎的人，因家貧而投身在大夫須賈門下。有一次，他隨須賈出使齊國，齊王識得范雎的才智，欣賞他的辯才，便贈之以千金，但卻被他婉拒了。可是，大夫須賈卻懷疑他與齊國有所勾結，回國後，即刻向宰相魏齊通報，而使得范雎遭到逮捕及鞭打，甚至折斷了肋骨和牙齒，並關在相府的廁所裡。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（此乃忌妒而引發的禍患）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若人過去世與人有怨仇的，或互相有虧欠的，那很容易在某世中相逢，此一但相逢，若是夫妻或情人，或是合夥做生意，那雙方就容易計較與爭吵。而因果這樣安排，這是給你們機會去擺平過去的虧欠或怨仇。因此，若謀得本籤，當秉持著還債的心情來應對，凡事寬宏大量不計較為原則，若能如此，則能很快打平這虧欠。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 21;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙乙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.碧玉池中開白蓮。<br/>2.莊嚴色相自天然。<br/>3.生來骨格超凡俗。<br/>4.正是人間第一仙。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.碧玉池中開白蓮</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧玉，也代表女方、女兒。白蓮代表，純潔、孤傲、悽涼、冷漠、清高之相。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此話也代表，出污泥而不染。意即，能夠修行的性格。若能修行者，則吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. 莊嚴色相自天然，代表發展成如今，也是個天然的成果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. 生來骨格超凡俗，代表本身條件優越</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. 正是人間第一仙，代表一枝獨秀。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若你本身是修行者，占此則吉。若不修行者，占此，謀望如空花。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若今生全走修行路線者，有機會開悟證果。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆若問愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問愛情可否挽回？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你將可以奪回愛人寶座。請多多為對方著想，這有利你維持愛情氣氛。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問夫妻可否和好？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們將可回歸舊好。請多些寬容與關愛，這能讓婚姻更和諧。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身者問姻緣在何方</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的外觀條件很好（長相冷靜，心態上很有尊嚴），未來可以找到很愛你的對象。你的姻緣對象是你所認識的人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前所喜歡的對象可否追求？有無姻緣？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對方條件很好、個性冷靜，但要你自己主動，追求她時，要很有禮節，態度要恭敬。收穫如何，則看你的經營。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，能修行者則吉，因為修行本身即能治病。<span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問訴訟，可獲勝。若問誤會，可解。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競賽、求職、升遷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試、競賽、求職、升遷者，成績卓越，競試結果，快樂似神仙。（若非修行者，謀望如空花。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作、事業前途、創業，將有傲人的成就。若本身能修行，則更有利事業。（若非修行者，謀望如空花。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職，可以找到有名氣、各方面都好的公司，或找到高雅、或輕鬆的工作。在夏天與秋天，最有利你找工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉換、換職、重考<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問轉換、換職、重考，可得更理想的工作（或學校）。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問身孕者，懷女嬰。若未懷孕而問孕者，則不吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前有女兒者，求子可以成功。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事易明白。不假人為。更宜出入。切莫遲疑。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>士人占之。高攀桂枝。一切謀望。宜趁明時。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宜<span lang="EN-US">→好</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">更宜出入莫遲疑。士子高攀折桂枝。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>婚合自然生貴子。萬般謀望趁明時。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解曰一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤可謀財。可望事。若有現成。不圖自至。不勞心力。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟已決。名利成。病則愈。婚則成。凡事皆成就也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">花在上實在下。功名謀望。若在晚景。求則得之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不勞心力。早年未遂。病<span lang="EN-US">(者)。有孕吉。無孕凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問婚。得舊配。問孕生女。謀事夏秋則吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">璧玉池中開白蓮者。乃仙所有。有疑是空談之說。占者慎之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主瀟灑出塵之應。謀望須清高門路方可。一切財利塵俗事。不甚相宜。功名可許。當主翰苑清品。問孕恐涉空花。問病者。有意參玄學道則吉。佳世之人。亦恐辭座之忌。語皆著空故也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">池開白蓮。最為清高妙品。但朝榮暮悴。光景無常。恐難久遠堅牢。骨格超凡。言生質之穎異也。第一仙。言其身列仙班也。功名占此。必登清要之選。或係張留侯李鄴侯一流人物。尋常庸俗之人占此。多虛花。少誠實。若問出世因由。登真正果。指日可望。上上大吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生聞鄰邑考童生。欲往。占此後。為彼地所遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">路見一觀音坐白蓮。竟買之而還。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又余表叔。陳內史府試。占此籤。果結第一名。應在末句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又泉州有一副貢生鄉試。占此。竟中試。蓋應正是兩字也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">董事王錢識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">李太白遇唐明皇<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝。李白，字太白。成紀地方人。個性風流倜儻。善長作詩歌。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">天寶年中，在金鑾殿接受召見，討論世事。帝令李白為供奉翰林（皇帝祕書）。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">明皇愛其才，想用李白做官。高力土（人名）因為李白醉酒時曾叫高為他脫靴，覺得受辱。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就在楊貴妃面前說李白壞話，因此李白升官之路常受阻礙。只好遊歷四方，寄情在作詩喝酒。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">李泌七歲賦長歌<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">李泌從小就非常聰敏，書只看一遍就能背下來，七歲能賦詩。唐玄宗非常喜愛他，宰相張九齡、詩人賀知章等人一見李泌，也非常喜歡，並器重他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾輔佐玄宗、肅宗、代宗、德宗四位皇帝。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀得本籤者，象徵著當事著過去世就是修行人，只是今世是否還是修行人，這就不一定了，因為眾生是容易迷失的。若你能延續修行，那就能累積修行的道行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此外，也有人前世是天界的人而今生投胎為人的，因此殘留有清風道骨的風格。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 22;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙丙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.花開花謝在春風。<br/>2.貴賤窮通百歲中。<br/>3.羨子榮華今已矣。<br/>4.到頭萬事總成空。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.在春風得意時，命運時好時壞。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.在生命歲月裡，經歷了貧賤富貴、窮困通達。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.雖然羨慕你過去的榮華富貴，但是如今已成過去。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.當心到頭來好事都成夢幻。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤有警示之味，意即，生活不要荒誕、糜爛，以免萬事成空。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤屬於長線的命運，當注意前半期命運有起落，而後半期則是「泰極否來」<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">對於未來的災禍應提早預防，完整的改造之道請看：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、保持正念。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若能遵照以上，那本籤就非下下籤了。而是中平到上吉籤了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情婚姻<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問愛情前途者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在愛情上，也許你曾經經歷過春天的甜蜜，也經過紛紛嚷嚷的歲月，但是，這愛情在後半期，狀況將會更糟糕了，分手是你可能要面對難題。在此建議，愛情是不能勉強的，勉強而來的愛情是不會幸福的。若雙方難以相處，那你還是坦然的放下吧！若想改造愛情運，那</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">愛情學分</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就是你不可不修的功課了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的吸引力恐已螁色，對方對你不再吸引，你還是退去這種追求想法吧。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">每個人都有各自的不同姻緣，也有不同的愛情前途，也許你能得到一時的姻緣，與經過愛情中的各種滋味。但是，到了最後還是一場空。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若分手的愛情，欲問挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">經歷了愛情的甜、鹹、酸、苦、辣，如今走入分手的局面，若想挽回的話，越挽越不回，越著急就越糟糕，建議另覓良緣好些。若你想要未來愛情更好相處的話，建議改改自己的毛病，並建立好的愛情行為，只要你改造了多少，這對愛情就有多少的幫助。愛情是需要經營的，並非隨性相處就能甜蜜，所以，建議修點</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">愛情學分</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結：男女相處，切忌任性、計較、分別，而把好好的愛情弄砸了。因此，在甜蜜的愛情中，還是要維持莊重，以祈好事能長久。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，過去的病情起起落落，而未來這病情將每下愈況。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>每個人不論遲晚總是會離去，也不管這次的你是否真的離去，我們應該乘著還清醒的時候，</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=12120&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=12023"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">為自己的臨終做好準備</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問訴訟；剛成案者，能解散者盡速解散為上。已審理者，當防案情越來越不利。已判刑者，當防越上訴判越重。</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">可以為當事者消業障，減輕罪行，但是，這個悔改務必當事者自己發自內心的悔過，這才有有實效。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業、投資、理財者；在經營上經歷了虧與贏，但是事業的後半期當預防虧損。因此，若有投資者應提早縮手或做好預防，以免造成過大的損失。（在事業經營上，切記，不可獲取不義之財。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在工作上經歷了起起落落的待遇，但往後工作上恐怕會更糟糕，所以要提早做好準備。</br>◆求職</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在找工作的過程上，雖然也得到一些應試，看起來似有錄取機會，但是往往又落空了。你的求職運上往往就是差這麼一點點，建議積極的改運，可以讓你突破這個節骨眼。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、升遷、競賽、錄用<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試、升遷、競賽、錄用者，當防好事都成空。若想擺脫這宿命安排的話，這也是可能的，在競試之前請：一、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。二、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。三、保持正念。若能如此做的話，那就大有機會突破宿命了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"><br/>當預防流產或不測。若懷孕成功者，可生女。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡百謀望。有成有敗。始雖快意。終實成害。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>吉中有凶。否生於泰。若不歛藏。後憂方大。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">實<span lang="EN-US">→竟</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大不中。花開遇烈風。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>不利老人占。病訟盡皆凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">中<span lang="EN-US">→終<br/>烈→暴<br/>不占→榮華全剝落</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤求望有成有敗。初快意。終有害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉中有凶。否有泰。不善歛藏。後憂更大。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利虐。訟宜散。病防老人為凶。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚未成。行人遲。失物之憂。大不吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富貴窮通。四者循環。得失不久。如花之開落無時也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">今已矣者。言凡事泰必復否。否必復泰。乃數之極。變之始也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但占者不為泰所移。不為否所困。斯為人定亦能勝天。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病防老者。路防失財。婚防有別。孕必生女。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主前運起跌不常。富貴窮通。都經涉歷。後運則大不吉。如百花已經開過。從今搖落。無復榮華之望。是以萬事成空。總宜退謝。倘更勉強圖謀。徒勞罔功。終欠結果。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">花開花謝。榮悴無常。運程似此。立睹更變之象。榮華已過。萬事成空。復何望哉。凡謀不吉。訟宜散。病防老。財不久。祿將終。婚無成。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生未遇時。占此自謂。無發達之日。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後入場坐空字號。遂得中榜。應在總成空之句。聖詩微妙。人不易測。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又泉城內。郭生有子得病。延兩醫。一名榮觀。一名今先。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">因寒熱爭辯。遂入廟占此。猜者謂今已矣。決不合。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">勸其托榮觀調治。至年終。果愈。此又羨子榮華到頭總成空之驗矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吳王愛西施<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">吳國已滅亡越國。越王勾踐，謙卑請饒命。臥薪嘗膽後，果然報了在會稽亡國之仇。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">與大夫（官名）范蠡、文種商量計謀，乃挑選民間絕色女西施。送給吳王。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">吳王夫差很寵愛西施，以至於亡國。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（由於荒誕、離譜以致亡國）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">殷浩書空<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">晉代殷浩受命帶兵平定關河地區，以平定中原為己任。後討伐姚襄失敗，遭桓溫彈劾，貶為老百姓。口無怨言，只是整天對空中寫著「咄咄怪事」四字。（此事見晉書˙卷七十七˙殷浩傳。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（後比喻事情怪異，令人不可思議。清˙李漁˙閒情偶寄˙卷九˙居室˙廳壁：「流水不鳴而似鳴，高山是寂而非寂。坐客別去者，皆作殷浩書空，謂咄咄怪事，無有過此者矣。）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 23;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二四籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙丁<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一春萬事苦憂煎。<br/>2.夏裏營求始帖然。<br/>3.更遇秋成冬至後。<br/>4.恰如騎鶴與腰纏。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.這個春天的各種事情總是讓人憂愁煎熬。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.自從夏天開始的經營，才有了起色。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.當遇到秋天、冬至過後。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.各種營求終於有驚喜的結果了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">騎鶴：誰能騎鶴？只有仙人才能騎鶴。此形容心境如仙人快樂。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>腰纏；代表「腰纏萬貫」的意思。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">「恰如騎鶴與腰纏」此話代表一個人的功名利祿突然爆紅了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事做事：春天不利，且莫急躁，直待秋冬，終有善果。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在春天時，由於你的心情浮躁不安，或說</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不穩定，而影響了你在春天的運勢。而到了秋冬，這才是你發揮的好季節。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤隱喻，占者在秋冬之間，突然成為爆發戶了。但請誤失去節志，以免好運變卦。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇春時浮躁易紛爭，夏季好轉漸趨穩，若逢秋冬情意濃，更此約定過一生。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;">◇總結，若問愛情之事，在秋冬時會有驚喜的結果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在一年四季當中，除了春天之外，其他季節都是你姻緣來的好時刻。屆時，若能好好經營，則會有甜蜜的成果。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀對象可否追求</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想要追他的話，要避開春天，等到春天過後你才追求。若能從夏天開始追求，則可望到了冬天時，已經有溫馨的成果了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前交往中的對象未來前途</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇當前交往對象可否結婚</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們的愛情，在春天時顯得不安，而從夏天開始逐漸好轉，若到了秋冬，則是你們甜蜜的高潮了。但是，若要論及婚嫁的話，還需要更多時間的培養。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手問挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們的吵架是在春天吧！這是一年當中你們最容易爭吵的季節了。但是，只要秉持</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，相信你們很快可以復合了。當進入秋天之刻，就是你們復合的最佳時機了。建議多充實些</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，這對於你們的愛情是有助益的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求職、升遷、考試、競賽</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問各種考試、競賽者，除了在春天的各種應試對你不利之外，其他季節都是有利你的。因此，若是在春天的各種應試，你的成績總是不理想。而從夏天開始，才是你發揮的季節！而在秋冬，才是你實力高潮的展現。當處在不利的季節裡，請藉此機會多多充實自己的能力，以備好運來時水到渠成吧。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆事業、工作、經商、生意：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">欲求財利者，逢春不吉，但是不用著急焦慮，建議多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，那到了</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">秋冬之刻，你就有好收成了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆換職、更換</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若你覺得當前工作做的不順遂而想要換工作的話，其實，春天對你來說是不利的，因此有一些困擾或是倒楣事發生，但是，只要熬過春天，這一切逐漸可以好轉了。而秋冬之刻，就是你順遂的好時機了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆官司訴訟：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">秋冬之時，官司結束，終於化解，掛記結束。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病健康：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">逢春惡化，歷夏漸穩，秋冬好轉，但總反覆。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修心養性，寬鬆心情，化解鬱愁，療效更佳。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆投資、理財、房地產：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問各種投資者，若逢春天時，由於你的心情浮躁不安，因此對你的投資理財都不利，若逢秋冬則才是你獲利良機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆尋人、尋物、尋寵物：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若春天占此，則尋回無望。若秋冬占此可找回。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆遠行、外出、出國：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春天遠行不利，方待秋冬為宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想求孕求子者，你的身體狀況沒問題，但是要避開忙碌的春天。建議，在秋冬的美好氣氛下，好好的經營吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">春日謀望。事多不成。夏秋冬月。始見光亨。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>更宜出入。福祿豐盈。營求如意。時至即行。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如舟上高灘。險後得平安。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>勞心勤苦過。財氣不艱難。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如舟<span lang="EN-US">→舟楫</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先難後易。官員占之。有超擢之喜。士人占之。名利晚成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡諸謀望。只是後好。訟終解。婚姻宜。行人遠。病難好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事可為。自有成就也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">昔人一欲富。一欲貴。一欲仙。一欲腰纏十萬貫。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">騎鶴上揚州。時揚州吏最稱為富貴仙也。但此人有是說無是事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">欲求名利者。皆安於義命。不可妄為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事夏秋冬。但遂意。惟春則不利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利有</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫躁為</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">詞訟解</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚姻宜</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人遠</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病瘥遲</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富與貴</span><span style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">要待時</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先難後易。官員占之。有超擢之喜。士人占之。晚成名利。凡百謀望。收成在後。近占應在夏秋冬。遠占應在晚景。不可因現在憂煎。自行墮志也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人謁選。占此謂必得揚州為官矣。乃選得河南信陽州知州。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陽與揚同音。恰如二字之驗。<span lang="EN-US">(帖/騎或作揚)</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">張騫誤入斗牛宮<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。張騫，城固地方人。武帝時，奉命出使大月氏（國名），開拓西南夷（西南方外族）外交工作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾坐小船，直上銀河，入斗牛宮，看見一女子手弄金色梭子，此女子身旁有一石。張騫問她這是什麼石，此女子不答，只說問嚴君平便知道。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君平，四川人。善長天文術數。張騫去問他，君平說：此女子是織女（仙女），那石頭其實是她的織布機啊。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（籤詩故事隱喻，人要上天河，這是難逢之事，而「張騫誤入斗牛宮」隱喻著，有的人的財富或機遇就像這樣，突然之間成為爆發戶，短時間內爆紅了。）此故事也是「一步登天」的寫照。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">端木結駟連騎<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">端木；複姓。在此代表孔子弟子－－子貢。結駟連騎：四馬駕車，并轡而行。形容喧鬧顯赫，排場闊綽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">端木賜（<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D520%E5%B9%B4" title="前520年"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前520年</span></a>－<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D446%E5%B9%B4" title="前446年"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前446年</span></a>），<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F" title="春秋時期"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">春秋</span></a>末年<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%9E%E5%9C%8B" title="衛國"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">衛國</span></a>人，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%A8%E5%AD%97" title="表字"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">字</span></a>子貢（古同子贛）。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90" title="孔子"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">孔子</span></a>的得意門生，「受業身通」的弟子之一，孔子曾稱其為「瑚璉之器」，在<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AD%94%E9%96%80%E5%8D%81%E5%93%B2" title="孔門十哲"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">孔門十哲</span></a>中以言語聞名。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E8%90%AC%E4%BB%9E%E5%AE%AE%E7%89%86&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="萬仞宮牆 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">萬仞宮牆</span></a>典故，出自子貢稱贊孔夫子之學問高深。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">子貢利口巧辭，善於雄辯，且有幹濟才，辦事通達。曾任魯、衛兩國之相。他還善於經商之道，曾經經商於<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9B%B9%E5%9B%BD" title="曹國"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">曹國</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%B2%81%E5%9B%BD" title="魯國"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">魯國</span></a>兩國之間，富致千金，為<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90" title="孔子"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">孔子</span></a>弟子中<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C" title="首富"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">首富</span></a>。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 24;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.寅午戍年多阻滯。<br/>2.亥子丑月漸亨嘉。<br/>3.更逢玉兔金雞會。<br/>4.枯木逢春自放花。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">更<span lang="EN-US">→待</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若逢虎、馬、狗年多困頓。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若遇豬、鼠、牛年的10、11、12月則吉祥。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若遇到兔年、雞年，屆時一切都有了生機。各種謀求都通暢了，就如枯木遇到春天了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">註解：籤詩所提的時間都以陰曆為準。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆凡事、做事各種謀求的吉凶時間請看以下：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇不吉之年：虎、馬、狗年不順，這些年份應保守。並多懺悔。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇吉之年月：豬、鼠、牛年的<span lang="EN-US">10、11、12月。（亥、子、丑日亦吉。）</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇大吉之年：兔年、雞年。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若逢凶年，莫忘懺悔消業障。<br/>若逢吉年，更當行善積德。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆各種問題之吉凶，請自行比對以上時間。在此並提醒，當吉祥年月來臨時，當事者也是要認真經營你的謀求，而非閒坐空等，這樣好命運才會來。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆婚姻愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身者問姻緣何時來</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇或單身者有心儀對象問可否追求</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若盼望姻緣來者，請把握兔年與雞年尋找愛情，這兩個年份全年都有機會。若在豬、鼠、牛年，請在該年底，亦有姻緣機會。若處在這些時機，請自行把握吧！若在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">虎、馬、狗年，那你就放輕鬆，不用辛苦找愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象結婚時機</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="">  </span><br/></font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在兔年與雞年，是你們結婚的最可能年份，或者在豬、鼠、牛年的年底，若這些時間點沒有結婚的話，那其他時間就難囉。因此，若處這時間點愛情穩定的話，那就是你機不可失的結婚機會了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手者問挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若分手到了吉年和吉月則可挽回。若處凶年的話，則容易分手，且難復合。若到了吉年吉月還沒有復合的話，那這愛情就如流水一去不回頭了。因此，若逢雞兔之年，請自行把握吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆其他各種謀望，請自行比對以上時間。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">春夏秋時。作事遲疑。直至三冬。百事咸宜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>卯酉月日。降福孔皆。待此謀望。枯木開花。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">咸宜<span lang="EN-US">→亨通<br/>降花→所謀則吉。待此時來。枯木花開。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀事難成未可誇。枯木逢春始放花。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>敗了又成離又聚。不宜共事與陰家。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不家<span lang="EN-US">→及時雨露發光華</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤作事遲疑。至三冬乃通。卯酉日月作事得時。如枯木開花。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀望各事。不勞心力而成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">以寅午戍三者為凶。亥子丑年月日為吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若謀事決。宜審時。不得妄動。訟終息。名利遲。婚姻吉。行人歸也。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>————————————————————————————————</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇三冬：冬天這三個月（本籤的吉月，即陰曆年底的10、11、12月）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇寅午戍：虎、馬、狗年（本籤的凶年）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇亥子丑：豬、鼠、牛年，或<span lang="EN-US">10、11、12月（本籤的吉年吉月）</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">十二支干。凡寅午戍。人事有阻。不可進取。反是有禍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">遇亥子丑。漸見亨嘉。至卯酉大吉。名成利就。取青紫如拾芥。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事先看年月。以詳命運。正合亥子丑卯酉等字。遂意矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">君子得之。主仕<span lang="EN-US">(途)進。小人得之。逢恩赦至。<br/>————————————————————————————————–</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">卯：兔年或四月。酉：雞年或十月。本籤的大吉年。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在吉年（豬、鼠、牛）的<span lang="EN-US">4、10月也屬吉中之吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤作事遲疑。至三冬謀望亨通。卯酉月日。應在次年。或應在遠年。枯木開花。言時運先蹇後泰。如秋冬枯落之木。一到春來。開花結果。自有一番更新氣象。後福未可量也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寅午戌年。指歲運說。是時人事阻滯。不可進取。遇亥子丑。漸漸亨嘉。至卯酉大吉。名利成就。取青紫如拾芥。凡事先看年月。以詳運命。須合亥子丑卯酉等字。則遂意矣。君子得之主仕進。小人得之恩赦至。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span><span style="">  </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人久病。占得此籤。夏日請醫。來遲。問何以遲。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">曰看日食間。何為日食。對曰。日月交會也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病人大悟。籤語曰。吾病必痊矣。一劑而癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">唐明皇遊月宮<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐玄宗與道士羅光遠，在中秋的八月十五日舉辦宴會。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">光遠取桂枝杖擲向空中，變成大橋，形狀如銀色轎子。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">玄宗和道士一起由橋進入月宮，看見穿霓裳羽衣的女子在歌唱。曲調很新奇，玄宗默記曲譜，回去後教楊太真（楊貴妃）。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">芙蓉鏡下及第<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丞相李固言在元和六年（唐朝）的時候，科舉考試未中去蜀郡，遇到一個老婦對她說：「郎君明年芙蓉鏡下及第，二十二年後當宰相，並且將鎮守蜀郡，我這次看不到你當官的榮耀了，我想將女兒托付給你照顧。」第二年，李固言果然考中頭名狀元。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 25;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二六籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙己 中吉<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.年來豐歉皆天數。<br/>2.自是今年旱較多。<br/>3.與子定期三日內。<br/>4.田疇霑足雨滂沱。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自<span lang="EN-US">→祇</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.這幾年來收成不佳（景氣不好）這都是天數。（天數；此指人類共同的命運。在此指當事者這幾年的宿命不佳。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而今年狀況則又更糟。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.和你約定在三天之內</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.讓你感受到新景象。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">由於神明體恤眾生命苦，所以給予三天的好日子鼓舞。因此，凡事請把握這三天努力經營，以祈能轉凶為吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有所謀望者，神明在以「庚」日為準的之前或之後這三天，給予靈機，請自行把握。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.請在這些日子做好</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，以讓靈機成為最佳轉機。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情者，代表這幾年感情狀況不佳，而今年恐又更糟糕，神明體諒眾生心靈之苦，故給予暗中相助。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身求姻緣者，你苦等姻緣有些時候了，但是今年的姻緣更難逢。但是神明會在逢「庚」日的三日中，給你靈機或驚喜，請自行把握吧。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情關係不佳者，或求愛情挽回者，神明給你三天時間（這三天可以取得聯繫或相處）。請在此三天內自行扭轉愛情，而三天後就得靠自己了，請把握雙方相處的時光，展現你的真愛情操與改變自己的缺點和不好的個性，以便能營造新的愛情關係。若此三天你不能積極改造的話，那三天後事情又有變故了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問與當前交往對象何時可以結婚</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們雖然交往已久，但是感情一向不安定，卻又分不開，而今年狀況又如鬧乾旱一般，像你們這樣再拖延下去也不是辦法。若想結婚的話，神明願意暗中助你們一臂之力，讓你們有個結果，請在逢「庚」日時提出結婚要求，並在三天之中達成協議。另外還請加強你的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，以便讓愛情更溫馨。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤代表求職者一直沒有找到工作；<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若占得此籤，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在逢「庚」日的三日內</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有靈機，請在這三天全力尋找。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>建議多多</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想創業者，這幾年景氣不好，現在創業有點太早。建議晚些時候再做打算。但</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在逢「庚」日的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三日中，神明會給你靈機。你可以做好創業準備，但是市場狀態還是要觀察一下。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這幾年的工作或事業景氣原本就不好，而今年更是糟糕，但是，只要你能熬過這低潮，很快就會景氣回升。另外，神明會在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">逢「庚」日的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三天內中給你一些靈機。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、升遷、錄用、競賽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問能否考上、能否得到升遷、錄用，諸如此類之問題，若在過去參與這些應試，成績往往不理想，而今年可以說雪上加霜，謀望更難實現。但是神明會</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在逢「庚」日的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三日中給你靈機。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>在這慘澹的歲月中，建議多多</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆賣屋、賣物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問賣屋、賣物，代表當事者這東西很久都沒有賣出，詢問者寡。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求得此籤，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在逢「庚」日的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三天中會購買消息，請自行把握機會，若錯過這三天中的機會，那往後又很難賣出了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問治病者，代表當事者這幾年來健康狀態不佳，而今年狀況可能更糟糕。<br/>但是神明會暗中加持，給予三天的穩定期，若有事情要和患者交代或對話的，請好好把握這</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">逢「庚」日的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三天。而三天後回覆舊態。建議為患者</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，多說些有用的話。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶天數。目下多迍。直待時至。如木逢春。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>禱求皆應。定在三辰。謀望必遂。奸事相因。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">奸因<span lang="EN-US">→好事臨門</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶天數奈如何。且待時來福氣和。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>祈禱定應三日內。營為好事入門多。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">奈<span lang="EN-US">→竟</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀事先損後遂。問病。星運未順。目下多悔方吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病遇庚申日安。訟即解。名利難。行人三日內必至。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚未成。求財無。凡事不利達也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富貴皆有天數。非人力所為。凡百謀為。厄於時勢尚未順利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">定期三日內。言後必有變也。庚者事之變。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">前庚三日為丁。後庚三日為癸。二字則變凶為吉。名成利就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又當謹修。於始不可妄動。病宜祈禱。子有三胎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大底<span lang="EN-US">(抵)虛名而少實也。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀事。先損後遂。問病。星運未順。三日後或遇庚日。可望痊可。所謂先庚三日。後庚三日也。訟即解。利即得。婚即成。行人三日內必至。禱雨三日內必降。凡事利達也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">窮通得喪。皆有天數。非人力可為。凡百謀為。厄於時勢。尚未順利。定期三日內。言轉盻間。即有生機也。庚者事之變。先庚三日為丁。後庚三日為癸。主是時變兇為吉。名成利就。又當謹修慎守。不可妄動。須待氣機到時。自如枯苗得雨。大有勃然興起之象。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生。秋闈占此。三場連日皆雨。竟得中榜。應末兩句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生屢試不利。晚年與其子仝考。出場後甚得意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命其子代占。得此益喜。有為斷日決。應抽者次句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自是兩字。已說明其父不信。親到占。復得此斷者。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">弗辯。榜發。其子取進。方悟初次。果應自是兩字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">迨親身往占。乃示以與子定三字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565" colspan="2">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">邵堯夫告天<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋朝。邵雍，字堯夫。范陽地方人。於書無所不讀，善長天文易數。</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">程子讚揚他是發揚古聖賢道理的豪傑。若遇有天災，就焚香禱告上天，為民祈雨，都非常誠敬。</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">王拱辰、呂誨等，屢次推薦他，都不受重用。死時六十七歲。贈秘書省，著作郎等官位，元祐年間，諡號康節。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""> </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 26;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.世間萬物各有主。<br/>2.一粒一毫君莫取。<br/>3.英雄豪傑自天生。<br/>4.也須步步循規矩。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.世間上的各個物品都有主人</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.即使一小點的東西也不要隨便拿取</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">就算天生條件很優越<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">也是要按部就班的經營而得成果<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.此籤暗示求籤者，凡事不要走投機路線，也不能仗勢自己的權勢和條件，應該腳踏實地經營，按照規矩做事。就算本身條件很好，也一樣要努力經營而後才有好的果實。若是本身條件不佳者，那就更應該加倍付出了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若得到好處當記得回饋。請多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這有利你未來的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情，不能仗勢自己條件好，也是要務實經營，而後才能有好的成果。目前狀況則未定，能否有成果，全看自己按部就班的經營與付出。若愛情關係不好者，請展現你真愛情操，即可改善。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問搶奪愛人者，此籤示意「名花有主」，是別人的，你就不要去奪取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>當你喜歡一個人時，別人老早也喜歡了，所以，若你想要追他的話，你得先打聽看看此人是否已經「名花有主」，若是的話，那你就打消這個追求念頭吧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前交往對象愛情前途或可否結婚<span lang="EN-US"><br/>愛情，是需要付出心力經營的，而非閒坐等待幸福來，因此，你當在愛情中表現</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，若愛情已經穩定了，那你再求未來有好成果吧。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使天生資材好，一向功課也好，也是考試前也是一樣要老實讀書，這才能金榜題名啊，而你付出多少心血，你就能得到多少收穫。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆競賽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使當前很有勝算，呼聲最高，最被看好。但是，若是大意、鬆懈、輕敵，那就一樣還是會輸。所以，戰戰兢兢全力以赴，這才有致勝機會。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆升遷、錄用、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不能仗勢自己人際關係好或仗勢自己能力強、條件佳，不足的地方，自己還是要去彌補，當作的功課還要是去做，若能如此，則升遷、錄用有望。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆若問求孕<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只要按照就班，那就可得。請先養精蓄銳，算好時日，而後同房。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作或事業前途者，那還是那句老話「一分耕耘，一分收穫」，人生即使有很好的事業福報，這一樣要努力經營，這福報才會來。若是本身福報不是那麼飽滿的人，那努力就更需要加倍了。若人想要以投機方式謀得福報，這只是加害自己罷了。所以，老實經營自己的工作和事業吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富貴分定。切莫強求。若或妄取。必有後憂。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>且宜守舊。更勉進修。心行平等。自獲天佑。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">勉<span lang="EN-US">→務<br/>佑→庥</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">守分方可遇。欺凌必反災。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>妄為難自保。依理福田來。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">守<span lang="EN-US">→本</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤只宜守分。不可妄為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若要謀事。不可以強凌弱。以富壓貧。稍涉欺凌。反成災害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必和。名利有。財難求。行人有阻。病宜禳方可。婚不宜也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利近。不可得遠大。難<span lang="EN-US">(成)就。言萬物各有所主。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戒占者不可以強凌弱。且富貴貧賤。自有分定。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若妄為損其德行。安望名利之遠大哉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大抵。當循規矩。自獲大祐。病者弗藥而自癒也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤只宜守分。不可妄為。若謀事返成災害。不可以大凌小。以富欺貧。訟宜和。名亦有。財緩求。行人阻。病徐安。婚莫急。凡事守己。待時為得。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利近不可得。久後自有成就。一毫莫取。戒勿為貪心妄求之事。須循規矩。示作事當按部就班。不可凌獵無序。自取顛覆也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">江東神廟。有大樹一株。明太祖皇帝欲伐之。初占此籤。猶為偶然。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">復占仍得此籤。遂驚嘆以為神異而置之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一新科舉人。占得此。春闈大捷。應步步二字。若問一科者不利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又余族人。王生歲試。占此。入場東廊號舍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">與江生隔鄰為道。題解得竅。果入泮。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生。占此亦入泮。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蓋上三句。未明示。主取生三個字。至結句六字。復暗藏一員字之議。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王錢謹識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">江東得道<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">錢塘人。羅隱，號江東。唐末考取進士，求官不成。立志修道。幸運遇仙人，傳授心法。因而得道。故能開口成讖。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(故事對應籤詩至此)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾遊歷泉州，在羅裳山下乞食，鄉人怠慢他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他就在江東畫馬於石頭上，每夜馬出踏壞田穀。鄉人知道後請求原諒。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他就畫椿樹來綁馬。就不再踐踏穀物。至今遺跡還存在。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">項仲山飲馬投錢<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">飲馬投錢：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">使馬飲水後，投錢入水中以作為酬答。比喻做人廉潔不苟取。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤乃是對當事者暗示：<span lang="EN-US"><br/>一、福報不足，這也是因為過去少有行善布施之故。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二、怠惰警示，既然先天福報不好，個性又怠惰的話，那未來日子就會很難過了。因此，只有靠後天的努力，才能謀得一些福份。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀得此籤者，由於福報不足，故謀望不能順遂，因此只能安分守己，平凡度日。若想收穫更多，全靠後天努力，只是付出十分，只能賺到五分。若能多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，則有利後勢。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 27;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.公侯將相本無種。<br/>2.好把勤勞契上天。<br/>3.人事盡從天理見。<br/>4.才高豈得困林泉。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.公侯將相並非天生的，也不是遺傳的。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而是努力經營而來的</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.一切經營只要符合天理，所有謀望都可得。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.若是有才學、有本事的話，是不會受困的，不會寂寞的。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.凡事全杖勤苦經營而得，只要你的經營符合天理，那你的所盼必將如願。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你的本事、條件還在，只要你勤勞經營，凡事都可以如願的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">請多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這有利你的未來福報。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你的命運中是有姻緣的，本身條件也不賴，何怕沒有姻緣呢！但是你必須要有尋緣行動，而不能在家空等待。建議多多參加各種活動或出外時多多與人互動，那你的姻緣就在其中了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可某追求？與此人有否姻緣？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">要追當然可以追，至於成效如何，這是看你自己有多少本領囉！追逐愛情是需要付出些本事的，請多多展現愛情中美好的情操，這能讓你的追求加分的。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前交往對象未來前途<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>◇或問當前交往對象可否結婚<br/></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:maroon;">美麗的愛情是靠經營</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">而來的，而非自然掉下來的，因此，若期盼這愛情有好的果實，那沒有其他法門，全看你們的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">付出了。請多多展現</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，這可以為愛情加分的。因此，若想未來與他結婚的話，那就是努力經營而已。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情分手者問可否挽回</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若當前愛情困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在愛情中爭吵而分手這是稀鬆平常之事，但是，並非對對情人都有挽回就是了。若你實在愛他，那就更應該付出</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，凡事不要太計較、任性，那愛情要挽回也是很容易的。因此，若當前愛情困頓者，你應該再接再厲，不要隨便放棄，只要你勤於展現真愛情操，那</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:maroon;">美麗的愛情</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">將來即可實現。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問更換配偶或情人好否</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若當前的情人你覺得不好的話，並非你換一個新的就會更好。愛情，不能只是等著對方付出，不能只是索求，而自己也要奉獻些什麼，若你願意付出些什麼，那對方應該也會給你甜蜜的回應。因此，建議你把當前的愛情好好經營再說吧！<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作或事業前途者，你已經有了先天的福報，只是你的努力還不夠，所以這些福份還不能應現。只要你勤勞的經營，那將來自然有美好的收成了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆若問轉換、換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使當前辛苦，而能否得到好報酬，全杖自己的經營而定了。因此，不要一點不如意就想換工作。在當前職位上，除了要勤勞經營之外，在做人處世上，你也是要學習的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職者，若你想要謀得工作，這是需要付出勞苦去尋找的，而非找個二三家就能有工作的。所以，你還是辛苦些再繼續努力吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，只要你遵守養病規約，當禁之食物則禁，當遵守的生活作息則守，內心苦惱垃圾勤於清理。遵照以上辦理，百病都可痊癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、升遷、競賽、錄用</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問考試、升遷、競賽、錄用者，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">能不能金榜題名，全看自己努力，而不在於天命。只要不怕吃苦，又能勤勞善巧經營，那假以時日，你的謀望當然可以實現囉！若當前應試沒有成功者，請再接再厲必然可以成功。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆若問尋物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只要你不辭勞苦的找、善巧的找，那就能找到。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">榮華富貴。勤苦得之。目下雖困。後必逢時。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>切勿自怠。更勉修為。人事既盡。天理可知。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但存平等心。所作皆無慮。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若不勤謹修。歡處必生事。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事<span lang="EN-US">→愁</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤吉利。凡事切莫歎息。更須修心向善。自有好處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問訟。久方決。名利達。失物尋在。病宜祈保。行人還。求財得。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人之富貴。勤苦可得。豈限白屋朱門之說。所謂本無種者也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目下雖困。而未逢時。切莫嗟嘆。但當勇為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若才高而人事已盡。則天必假手薦拔。不求而自至矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名有天理之報。財有守時之益。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事只當循乎理法。不可妄為也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤吉利。凡事切莫墮志。更須修心向善。自有好處。問訟久方決。名利稍遲。失物可尋。病宜作福禳解。行人久後必至。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名富貴。勤苦可得。豈限白屋朱門之說。所謂本無種者也。目下雖困。終必逢時。但當自竭勤勞。人事已盡。天理無不準應。彼讀書者。才學既高。豈得久困林泉。不久即有飛騰之望。凡事皆然。唯先返求諸己可耳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一士人林某。問終身。占此後。習武不利。加納為泉州府牧。終於任。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又馬生。歲科試。皆列三等。及占此。加考古學。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竟以擬上林賦冠軍。遂得補廩。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">相如題橋<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。司馬相如，成都地方人。未當官時，曾過橋。見顯貴人士的車馬喧騰。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他感慨說：大丈夫應如此。就在橋上寫上他的志向，寫作子虛上林賦。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">武帝讀了賦，覺得很好。召見他做郎中（官名）。四川太守唐蒙出事時。帝令相如作文責備唐蒙。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">皇上又拜相如為中郎將（官名）。後來有人上書彈劾，相如出使西南夷時，接受賄賂，被免職一年多，又召為郎中。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤比上個<span lang="EN-US">27籤還好些，福報都有了，只欠後天的勤苦努力而已。因此，只要努力那福報就能源源而來了。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 28;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>二九籤</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>丙壬</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>上上</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>詩</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>祖宗積德幾多年。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>2.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>源遠流長慶自然。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>3.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若更操修無倦已。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/>4.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>天須還汝舊青氈。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>籤詩翻譯</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>祖上有德已經延續許多年了</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>而這個好德行也延續到如今</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若能不厭倦的在個人修為上加把勁</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">4.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>那上天還得還你原有的福報</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>本籤重點</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆凡事</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>「萬緣具備，僅欠修為。若升德性，好運即來。」</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>好命運的降臨，也必須時機、善行、品德等各方面條件都具足時，期望中的福報才會應現。求得本籤者，代表個人修為上還要補強，因此，當事者只要在這個科目補修一下，那期望中的福報就跟隨而來了。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>凡事都可行，重點在於要提升自己的德行。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>清涼月解</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆愛情</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若單身者問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>你出身在有德的家庭，你的姻緣是沒有問題的，將來也能如願得到理想伴侶。而當前你要補強的就是個人的修為、品德而已，只要把這部分修好來，姻緣就順水而來了。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若問當前心儀的對象可否追求</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>想要追求他是沒有問題的，你只要把個人涵養、</span><span style=''color: black; font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''>道德</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>做好來，那要追求他就容易了。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若問當前交往對象的前途</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◇若問當前交往對象可否結婚</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>你的交往對象條件也不賴，和你也門當戶對，若要愛情幸福安定，這是需要條件的。在愛情上不能高傲而要謙恭，對待另伴要有禮不可任性，請多多表現</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>那就可以為愛情加分了。而將來的你們可以共結連理、白首皆老。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若愛情分手或困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>此愛是否能挽回呢？這全看你的謙讓情操了。情人間難免會有鬧彆扭的時候，但是這種事情不要僵持太久，好好的改革自己不好的</span><span style=''color: black; font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''>態度，</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>以委婉溫和的語調向他致歉示好，多說幾句好話，那愛情就恢復正常囉！</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><span style="color: maroon;">◎</span><span style="color: maroon; font-family: 新細明體;">美麗的愛情靠經營</span></span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆求孕、求子</span><span lang="EN-US" style=''color: black; font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''><o:p></o:p></span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若不孕欲得子息者，夫妻的不好修為要提升。若能涵養好些，則子息不成問題。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若想生貴子者，夫妻在個性上要培養慷慨、奉獻的無私性格，若能如此則生子有望。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>以上祈求者，建議多多行善修德，則能增加效果。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆考試、升遷、競試、錄用、工作</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若問考試、升遷、競試、錄用、工作前途如何？這段期間天天行善修德，直到放榜，必有佳績。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>行善，是指給予他人利益。修德，是指提升自己的道德、涵養和無私的精神。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆創業、留學、外出發展</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若問創業、留學、外出發展好否？可以做，但要注重自身德行表現。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: maroon;"><o:p></o:p></span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆若問轉換、換職、換校好否</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: maroon;"><o:p></o:p></span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>不管是事業還是學業，若你想轉換，本籤的主旨在於給求籤者提示，提升個人修為、品德，會比什麼都重要。因此，可以在職場上或學校中，實踐德行的提升，而不必轉換工作或學校。因為，這才是你當前最該補修的學分，只要把這個學分補起來，那在原有的學校或職場，就能獲得福報了。意即，換不換都可以，只要在德行方面加強那就能順遂。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>◆治病</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若問治病，只要修好自己的心地，那一些慢性病自然可以痊癒。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若能心地寬暢，不累積苦惱，則不生腫瘤。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若不計小人過，不瞋怒、懷恨，則無心臟病。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若不生忌妒，則無糖尿病等病</span><span lang="EN-US">….</span></div>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>東</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>坡</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>解</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>善惡胚胎。由人自栽。修善暑泰。積惡者災。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若能修持。福自天來。依舊榮華。自有安排。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>碧</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>仙</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>註</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>積善之家。必有餘慶。子孫眾多。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>門戶昌盛。好修福祿。前程順應。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>應</span><span lang="EN-US">→</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>意</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>解</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>曰</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>一</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>此籤。士人占之大吉。官員占之高擢。庶人占之終有發達。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>訟得理。病易安。婚必成。名利遂。行人即回。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>凡事如意。但要修心積善方好。不可著急也。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>釋</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>義</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>一</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>凡事多得遂意。此皆祖宗積德所致。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>若果能順理而行。去其欺害。則天之報施。決然不爽。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>青氈者。舊物也。運乃失而復得。否而復泰也。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>操修或作修為。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>解</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>曰</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>二</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>此籤士人占之大吉。官員占之高擢。庶人占之終有發達。但要修心積善。方得源遠流長。不可變易祖德。自損心田。則亦有不應之時也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''><o:p></o:p></span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>釋</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>義</span><br/>
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>二</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>凡事多得遂意。皆祖宗積德之所致。若又能順理而行。益加培植。則天之報施。決然不爽。青氈者。詩書傳家之舊物也。還乃失而復得。否而復泰之象。占者須慎守之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''><o:p></o:p></span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"> </span></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>驗</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>一士以文考黜。占此。下科竟復優等。應在四句。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>又晉江王生。其祖父素世與考不利。即生日已。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>府縣試亦會。取結前。予而院考仍無名。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>光緒。乙亥。將應院試。入廟禱祈。占此。自謂無望。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>迨榜發。竟取進。因該生頗寒。欲做青衣。苦於無力不已。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>轉向親朋借舊者。漸川</span><span lang="EN-US">(</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>穿</span><span lang="EN-US">)</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>至簪掛日。諸同案皆衣冠蹌濟。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>而彼獨穿舊青衣。始悟神示靈驗異常。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>籤詩故事一</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>司馬溫公嗟困</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>宋朝。司馬光。夏縣人。次子寶元年初，中進士。一直做官至端明殿學士。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>光感歎民生困苦，上書極力批評新法不便。哲宗剛登基。召見司馬光做左僕射（官名）。罷除青苗法。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>有人說哲宗元祐年間，相</span><span lang="EN-US">(</span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>祖</span><span lang="EN-US">) </span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>事業，有旋乾轉坤之功。死後贈太師，封溫公。諡號文正。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=''color: black; font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''><o:p></o:p></span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>籤詩故事二</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>王孝先還妾贈金<span style="color: blue;">《太上感應篇》</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: blue;"><br/></span><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>王曾，字孝先。宋真宗咸平年間，由州縣的推薦，到禮部去應試，所以居住在京師（河南開封）。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>有一天，他經過甜水巷，聽見有母女二人哀戚的哭聲，因此向其鄰居詢問，鄰居說：「她們家因拖欠官府錢四萬枚（宋朝有鐵錢、銅錢多種，鐵錢值低而較多，銅錢價昂而奇缺），家裡僅有一個女兒，賣給商人來償公款，現在母女將離別甚遠，恐怕以後再也沒有見面的日子了。」</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>王曾知道事情原委後，告訴這位母親說：「妳的女兒可以賣給我，我往來為官，你們母女隨時可以見上一面。」於是以原價給了她，要她償還商人。並約定三日後，來帶走她的女兒。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>可是過了約定的日期，不見王曾來。母女到王曾所住的館舍拜訪，沒想到王曾已經走了。這一年禮部考試以及殿試，王曾都得到第一名。</span></div>
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span lang="EN-US"><span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>摘自籤詩網</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style=''color: black; font-family: 新細明體; mso-bidi-font-family: "Arial Unicode MS";''><o:p></o:p></span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext; border-style: none solid solid double; border-width: medium 0.5pt 0.5pt 1.5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 79.85pt;" valign="top" width="105">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>命理解析</span></div>
</td>
<td style="border-color: currentColor windowtext windowtext currentColor; border-style: none double solid none; border-width: medium 1.5pt 0.5pt medium; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; padding: 0cm 1.4pt; width: 423.75pt;" valign="top" width="877">
<div class="MsoBodyText">
<span style=''font-family: 新細明體; mso-ascii-font-family: "Times New Roman"; mso-hansi-font-family: "Times New Roman";''>你是出身在祖上有德的家庭，這也顯示你的過去世也是有過善行之人，這可以說你的命運比一般人還幸運。至於期望中的理想若要實現的話，那也是很容易的，只要提升個人德行與操守，那一切就能如願了。</span></div>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 29;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丙癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.奉公謹守莫欺心。<br/>2.自有亨通吉利臨。<br/>3.目下營求且休矣。<br/>4.秋期與子定佳音。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.做事當奉公守法，不要違背良心或違背天理。(本籤的忠告)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若能如此自然萬事亨通好事降臨</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.你當前想要做的事情當停下來<br/>（此有多種意思，一、是欲做之事不當做。二、此事當等待。三、當前的謀望不能如願。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.到了秋天時，這件事情就有好消息了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">等到秋天即能分曉或有個明確的方向。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.目前的憂慮、困頓來自處事觀念不正所致。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.凡做事情，心態一定要正，切莫違背道德、違背良心，若能如此則能安順。<br/>3.若能謹守清廉，那謀望之事在秋天時刻即能分曉。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.若是一連串發生倒楣事者，各種倒楣事到秋天時方才結束。但是，若你能提早修正自己的負面心態、情緒，那倒楣事還是可以提早結束。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身者問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">現在你的你也許為了姻緣而憂心，其實，你的姻緣在秋天的時候就會來囉！請先做好迎接的準備吧！但是，還請先建立好求姻緣的正確觀念。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若有心儀的對象，問可否追求？可否成為情侶？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若你要追他的話，尚不要著急，首先你的追求心態務必要「正」，不可有歪邪或偏差的想法，若能秉持「正念」而經營，這事情才會有好成果。若能如此，當到了秋天時，那就有好消息了！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象未來前途或問可否結婚。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">也許，你擔心著這愛情未來的發展是否有好結果，也許你當前正處在困頓的階段，但是愛情之事不要著急，而要先建立正確的相處觀念和態度</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請自行思考</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。若能如此，那到了秋天的時候，就是你們約定終身的時刻了。請在此段時間好好的思考他與經營他，多多發揮</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，這可鞏固你們的愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情分手欲問挽回</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們兩個到底適不適合，這是你自己要思考的，重要的是，在愛情上「不要欺騙自己」，這是給你自行反思的提示。每次的分手，都是自省的時候，所以，你當檢討一下分手的原因。若你想通了，你當有新的想法與做法。若想了過後要挽回的話，那秋天就是你挽回的時機了，就請自行把握吧！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想要找到好工作的話，那求職的心態很重要，不可有投機的想法，也不要想找個既輕鬆又多錢的工作，先端正自己的求職態度，若能如此，那到了秋天時就能找到好工作了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、生意、合夥、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業、生意、合夥、工作者，做事的原則就是要奉公守法，老實經營，這就是成功的要件了。若能如此經營的話，那就漸漸能擺脫當前煩憂而走向吉利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆選擇<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種事情的抉擇者，目前的你還是不要做決定，若在做各種選擇時，要記得「不要矇蔽了自己」。若能如此，等到秋天時局勢明朗，那你自然知道哪邊是最佳選擇了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、各種應試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試前途者，目前尚須等待，若是在秋天的考試則對你有利，這是上榜的黃金時刻。若在非秋天的考試即使這次沒考上，下次再接再厲還是有希望考上。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，首先要檢討一下自己的內心，是否為了哪些事情而憂鬱？是否哪件事情讓自己耿耿於懷？是否自己哪裡做了虧心事？等等的自我檢討可以讓你找到心理癥結所在，若能自我檢討，則此心結能解，若能如此則疾病也能不藥而癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求生兒子的話，你應該先修一些功德，然後再求。而當前使用的各種生男方法應當停下來。若能如此的話，那到了秋天時，就有懷男嬰的消息了。請記得待人要慷慨，並多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善布施</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">公平處己。切莫自欺。福祿雖有。漸且待時。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若要進取。未可施為。凡百謀望。秋以為期。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">漸<span lang="EN-US">→更</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先難後易莫相欺。謀望營為秋得宜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>謹守定應多福祿。且須從緩待其時。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤目下不宜妄取。只宜守己。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官員占之。必有憂疑。若能謹守。方得吉利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">士人占之。且待時來。庶人占之平順。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病宜服藥。訟宜和。婚有約。謀望先難後易。不可躁進。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">安分守己。秋月方佳也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">貴人占之有刑憲。士人占之進取未遂。秋期方有佳音。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宜好學養重。凡事占之。當正道而行。待時而動為要。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤目下不宜妄取。只宜守己。官員占之。必有憂疑。若能謹守。自有佳音。士人占之。且待時來。飛騰有日。庶人占之。平安。凡有謀望。先難後易。不可躁進。安分守己。交秋自有遇合。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官吏占此。現在風波。儒士占此。目前沉困。官吏須奉公守法。儒士須積德存心。自有亨通之日。秋期佳音。應在秋後。七八九月間。主有好消息也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人少入公門。存心忠厚。久無所遇。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占得此籤。至秋。偶與一貧士結親。聘其女為媳。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">日後其母貴顯。此人父子因而致富。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又泉州有林生。占財氣。得此籤。未幾。賈客郭秋期官。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一林姓店夥。無故自服毒身死。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">林生與認同宗。出為調停。因此得酬金二百。蓋神已先知之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生。占功。弟病。得此<span lang="EN-US">(籤)未歸家。而中途忽聞凶信。是第三句之驗。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竹平王錢敬識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">柳毅傳書<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">唐朝柳毅，考試落第後回到涇陽地方，遇到安子滿在落淚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">她自已說是洞庭龍王之女，嫁與涇陽龍王之子。遭夫婿暴力羞辱。她拿一封信，拜托柳毅送往洞庭湖。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">柳毅</span><span style="">以不能入水中為理由而推辭，女子說湖邊有柳樹一株，你搖它就會有人招呼你。<span style="COLOR:black;">柳毅於是</span>去搖樹，果然水中有人出來把信拿走。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來柳毅就被邀請入龍宮，洞庭龍王就把女兒嫁給他。後來就不知柳毅結局了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">做事需要正確的觀念，若是觀念或心態不對的話，那就會遭惹災禍，這也可以說，創造了壞命運。反之，觀念和態度都健康，那就能創造出好命運。所以，觀念和心態也是影響命運的一部分。而謀得本籤者，代表作事的態度已經有問題了，因此，只要將之修正，那就能改善問題。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.2pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解籤範例<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:418.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="558">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1610103008276"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">特殊問題解籤</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">範例：該網友求得此籤，要問的是選擇題，此網友求職應徵了三家公司，要問哪一家比較好或哪一家會錄用？這三家公司分別是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">奇美、華泰、日月光。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">從籤詩的最後一句「</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋期與子定佳音</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，答案就在其中了</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">……<br/>1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">其中的「秋」，若提到「秋」最突顯的象徵就是「月」，秋就是代表「月」，所以答案是「日月光」錄用他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「秋」中有「火」，「日」代表「火」，如此解法得到的答案也是「日月光」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">句中有「期」，此「期」望中有「月」，以此而解答案也是「日月光」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">綜合以上三種解法，答案都一樣，將答案和籤詩結合，就成了「日月光與子定佳音」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 30;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁甲<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.秋冬作事只尋常。<br/>2.春到門庭漸吉昌。<br/>3.千里信音符遠望。<br/>4.萱堂快樂未渠央。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.在秋冬時耕作，功效只是平平。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.要到春天時經營，才能昌隆發展。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.從遠方傳來的消息讓人寄望。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.母親快樂安然無恙。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.這件事情的經營只是平平，直到春天時刻好轉。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.這件事或人將有長距離的遙望時刻，但是對方還是安然無恙。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情求得此籤者，愛情狀況平平，而對於愛情的寄望，要到春天才有進展，請自行把握此時機。若分手或分離兩地者或愛情困頓者，會有長時間（或遠距離）的互相遙望時刻，但對方仍然安然無恙（沒有移情別戀）。接下來又會如何，且看你的經營囉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身者問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過去謀求一直沒有進展，其實你的姻緣在春天時刻才會來臨，屆時就能「有緣千里來相會」了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前心儀對象與他有否姻緣？可否追求？◇當前交往對象能否更進一步發展？◇若問遠距的愛情何時能進展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這些日子以來，你在愛情的表現上，平平沒有進展，但是你也不用急求成果，而要等到春天時刻（農曆過年後），這愛情就熱起來了。你想要追求的對象也可以追求了。你想要更進一步發展也能如願了。原本兩地相隔的愛情，在春天時也得到訊息了。若想創造佳績者，請充實你的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情分手者問挽回？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">過去的愛情經營，顯得平平，如今的愛情困頓，就在春天時刻終於有了起色。若未臨春天之時，你且不必著急，而要安耐等待著，屆時就能和樂融融了。請多多發揮</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，這對你的愛情可以加分的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情中有反對者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情中有家人反對者，就在春天時刻，家人也不再反對了。請做好和對方家人相處的禮儀。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象可否結婚</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你們過去的愛情表現只是平平，建議你加把勁，多些真愛情操，直到春天時刻，那就可以水到渠成了。請作好和對方家人相處，多些禮儀和關懷，可以贏得對方家人的贊賞。若能如此，對方家長也能接受你們了</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若已經交往一段時間想要告白者或求婚者，請把握春天時刻。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想選擇情人、決定愛情進退者，請在春天時再做決定。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、錄用、競賽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若在秋冬進行者，則成績平平，若是春季之競試，則有佳積。若在秋冬公佈成績者，成績平平。若在春天公佈成績者，全家樂融融。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若多時找不到工作者，請把握農曆過年後三個月內找到工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、各種轉換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想做各種變更者，你要知道你的狀況好轉是在春天，若想更換者，請在春天再做，而其他時間的轉換，成效平平。另外，在生活上，要做好人際相處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業前途者，秋冬時的經營平平，你的旺季在春天。若經營事業，記得「家和萬事興」的道理。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若是為人雇員者，你的工作表現平平，直到春天時刻，你的業績終有佳績了。在工作上，記得要善於和同事互動，做好人際關係。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問理財成果者，請在春天時記得收成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問何時生育為佳，此籤暗示春天即是良時。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡百謀望。秋冬平平。春來運至。次第光亨。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>遠行有信。所作皆成。家道清吉。可保安寧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">百<span lang="EN-US">→事</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事營求名以成。春來次第自通亨。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>門庭吉利皆平善。財物相應漸漸生。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名以<span lang="EN-US">→久必<br/>生→成</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤秋冬平平。逢春求財謀事。只宜漸進。不可急切。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人至。訟必理。病漸安。婚久成。凡謀事緩。則安康也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡百謀望。秋終尋常。至春方可求名者。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋闈未遂。春闈及第。千里信音。宜遠不宜近。宜緩不宜急也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若躁進有害。萱堂母氏也。快樂無恙也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大抵此籤言家眷有慶餘。須看時令。合則吉。乖<span lang="EN-US">(乖本作乘)便非。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤秋冬平平。一切事宜。交春方有起色。千里好音。是時可至。高堂白髮。尤保康寧。守己待時。吉無不利。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此者。秋冬不能動作。運限平常。凡有謀望。須待來春。是時好音到耳。門庭吉昌。所謀順遂。萱堂母氏也。快樂無央。主母氏福壽綿長。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生占秋闈不中。應秋冬只尋常也。若占春闈則有可望。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又晉江。鄭姓。倘弟戍杭城陷。眾皆謂。死其母患之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此。不數日可往者。有人逃歸。始知尚在越年季春。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乃以計脫。方回家。全詩俱驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蘇卿負信<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">漢朝。蘇武，字子卿。出使匈奴，被留了十九年。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">當時有一番女對蘇武很好，蘇武就娶了她，且生了三子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">蘇武回中國時，約定再去帶她。等到中國後，蘇武不能屨約。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他的二個兒子奉母親命令，來請蘇武屨約，但蘇武棄而不顧。番女因此責備蘇武，有節操無信用。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">狄仁傑白雲望親<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">狄仁傑，字懷英。唐朝并州（今山西省）太原人。生於貞觀二年，卒於武則天聖曆三年，壽七十一歲。贈文昌右相，諡文惠；睿宗追封梁國公。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">仁傑自幼好學，以孝聞鄉里。舉明經。薦授并州法曹參軍時，雙親俱在河陽（今之河南省），相距甚遠。仁傑赴并州，登太行山，舉目南望，見白雲孤飛，觸景傷情，顧謂左右曰：「吾親所居在此雲下。」悵然佇立，瞻望良久。俟雲移，始下山。世所謂「白雲思親」，即源於此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 31;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁乙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.勞心汨汨竟何歸。<br/>2.疾病兼多是與非。<br/>3.事到頭來渾似夢。<br/>4.何如休要用心機。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.這樣勞心尋尋覓覓究竟為的是什麼</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.都是口舌是非，身心都病了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.到頭來就如夢一場罷了</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.何必用這麼多心機呢</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.本籤主旨為「口舌是非之憂」，由於此患而影響運途。若人能擺脫用心計較，口舌是非，就能改善前途。求得此籤者，在生活中與人相處，當行和睦，建議多修「廣結善緣」以化解之。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.各方面問題，請遠離心機勞神、是非計較、庸人自擾。而要提升人緣，改善人際關係，則前途可化解。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情者，代表雙方口舌是非很多，因此容易分手。若想維繫或挽回者，請多自省，反思己過，常施包容，降伏私心，多多奉獻，常為對方著想，若能如此則能改善雙方關係或挽回愛情。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆考試、學業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若考試、學業者，讀書方面沒問題，問題在於人緣，由於人際上出了問題，這個問題就會影響考試或學業，故不可不慎。化解方法；廣結善緣、和睦周親。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆工作、事業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事業、工作前途，在工作或事業上，除了要善於本業的經營外，人際相處也很重要，若在工作中能廣結善緣，則有利工作或事業發展。這是問籤者自己要注意的地方。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想更換職業或工作者，你當前在工作中與人相處和睦嗎？這是你要自省的地方。若是這個毛病不改，那即使換了工作地點，那老問題還是會再發生。所以，當前的你要換的不是工作，而是心態。與人相處當秉持和善友好，不要有敵視態度，這對你的工作才是好的。若能在生活中與人建立友好關係，則有利你的工作前途。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心情會影響身體健康，若是與人口舌的話，那就會心情不好，心情一旦不好就會連累健康。因此，平常生活中當廣結善緣，與人相逢多說好話，若能這樣做，這是預防疾病。若已經有病者，當放下心結，以開闊的心胸與人相處，若能朝此方向邁進，這也是治病。問籤者當防身體在正六月爆發疾病。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事謀不成。徒自勞心。口舌立至。禍患來侵。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>不如退步。暫隱山林。處其所在。可遇知音。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀望事多嗟。徒勞心力賒。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若求婚與利。口舌見交加。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嗟<span lang="EN-US">→差</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤問病不利。訟不好。謀事皆不如意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">主口舌之憂。事雖有成。後必有敗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">空勞心力。只宜安分。不可妄為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀為動作。是是非非。何有歸一。徒弊精神。無益於己。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">且事以謀而成。以謀而敗。到底不吉。如春夢一番。有名無實也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者作事。可已則已。如不可已。則當循理而行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">使盡心力而為之。後必有災。正六月。防有疾。老者難保。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀事皆不如意。主口舌之擾。事雖有成。終必有敗。空勞心力。只有安分。不可妄為。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者徒勞罔功。既防疾病。並多是非。當由平日慣用心機。損人利己。行險僥倖。當得此報。急宜矢願懺悔。存好心。行好事。挽回天意。方有轉機。若仍恃奸狡圖謀。正如夢幻泡影。醒來空自懊恨耳。豈有實在歸宿矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事占之。多不吉利。因詩句無一字可人意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">惟有天啟甲子科。山東應試。三人同占得此籤。意謂俱不中矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後俱登科。解元名丁乙。乃悟。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤首數是丁乙。三人者合當中丁乙榜。丁舉人也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又同治乙丑。補行甲子鄉試。福建主考官。丁紹周。當未點差之先。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">晉江黃生。乳名頭。問科名。占此不解。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">迨中式後。始悟。亦丁乙到頭。四字之驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">盧杞陰司口舌<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">盧杞（生年不詳－</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/785%E5%B9%B4" title="785年"><span style="COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:11pt;"><font face="Times New Roman">785</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;FONT-SIZE:11pt;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">），</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">字子良，滑州靈昌（今河南滑縣西南）人，是范陽的大族，他的祖父<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%9B%A7%E6%87%B7%E6%85%8E" title="盧懷慎"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">盧懷慎</span></a>是開元初年丞相。父親<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%9B%A7%E5%A5%95&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="盧奕 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">盧奕</span></a>是<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BE%A1%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9E" title="御史中丞"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">御史中丞</span></a>。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建中初年，盧杞入為<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BE%A1%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9E" title="御史中丞"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">御史中丞</span></a>，升<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BE%A1%E5%8F%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%AB" title="御史大夫"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">御史大夫</span></a>。不久又升為<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%8B%E4%BE%8D%E9%83%8E" title="門下侍郎"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">門下侍郎</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%9B%B8%E9%96%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%B9%B3%E7%AB%A0%E4%BA%8B" title="同中書門下平章事"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">同中書門下平章事</span></a>。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">盧杞有口才，但是為人狡詐，相貌醜陋而臉色青藍，人都把他當鬼看待，<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%83%AD%E5%AD%90%E5%84%80" title="郭子儀"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">郭子儀</span></a>見過盧杞後說：「這個人要是能得志的話，那我的子孫就不得好死！」</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">盧杞忌能妒賢，曾陷害<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BC%A0%E9%95%92" title="張鎰"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">張鎰</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%A8%E7%82%8E" title="楊炎"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">楊炎</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A2%9C%E7%9C%9F%E5%8D%BF" title="顏真卿"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">顏真卿</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%8E%E6%87%B7%E5%85%89" title="李懷光"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">李懷光</span></a>等。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建中四年（<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/783%E5%B9%B4" title="783年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">783年</span></a>），爆發<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B3%BE%E5%8E%9F%E5%85%B5%E5%8F%98" title="涇原兵變"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">涇原兵變</span></a>，朔方節度使<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%8E%E6%87%B7%E5%85%89" title="李懷光"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">李懷光</span></a>彈劾其罪，十二月貶新州（今廣東新興）司馬，授澧州刺史，不久給事中<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E8%A2%81%E9%AB%98&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="袁高 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">袁高</span></a>認為盧杞姦邪敗政，貶官尚不足，貞元元年（<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/785%E5%B9%B4" title="785年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">785年</span></a>）又徙澧州（今湖南澧縣）別駕，途中，病死於船上。葬於嘉魚王家灣。德宗謂<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%8E%E5%8B%89" title="李勉"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">李勉</span></a>曰：「眾人皆言盧杞姦邪，朕何不知！卿如其狀乎？」李勉謂德宗曰：「眾人皆言盧杞姦邪，而陛下獨不知。此所以為姦邪也。」</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt auto;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人際、人緣，也是影響命運的一部份，若能提升人緣，善於交際，這有利前途發展。求得本籤者，代表人緣方面有了問題，以致事業、愛情、健康等方面都出了問題，因此只要從這地方著手，那就是改造命運了。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 32;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁丙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.不分南北與西東。<br/>2.眼底昏昏耳似聾。<br/>3.熟讀黃庭經一卷。<br/>4.不論貴賤與窮通。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.不管天南地北（意即不要去管世間閒雜事）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.眼睛當看不清，耳朵當聽不到。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.把經書好好讀一讀（有益人生、修行的經書都可以讀）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.也不管將來是貧賤、富貴、困頓、通達。（意即要練到「八風吹不動」）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.本籤主旨：這是你修行的時間到了（或你也該修行了），不用管世間發生了什麼事，也不管自己將來有什麼命運，一切通通拋諸腦後，你就從讀經開始，吸收修行的精華，這對你才是最重要的。當前所問之事，你就讓他隨風去吧。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若能走修行路線，則有守護神相隨暗助。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565" colspan="2">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情者，對於愛情應該看淡。愛情是你苦惱的來源，總是酸苦多於甜蜜，多少人追求愛情，卻為愛情所苦，與其如此矛盾，何不提早看淡它，人生反而更安祥。<span lang="EN-US"><br>若單身者，不必特意求愛情。若分手者，不必求挽回。若相處不睦者，直接分手。把你的心思寄望在修行上，這才能提升你的生命品質。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若無愛情如何度日？以下連結可作為填補心靈的方法參考：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作、升遷、考試、學業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業、考試前途者，你應該放下期望，隨緣經營，不必高掛理想。有多少功名就多少，以免心情跟隨前途起起落落。人生更重要的課題是「修行」，你可以在事業或學業中一面修行，而不要把專注力放在功名上。多多提升智慧，勝過你在學業或事業中的獲利。意即，把修行當作你生命的主軸，這對於你來說才是最大的利基。求得本籤者，未來謀望不順，只有安守當前，並多多修行，這才是你要決定的。若能勤於修行者，反而能得神明暗助。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉換、換職、換校、換系<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若工作者問轉換職業或學生轉換科系，本籤的重點不在轉換好不好，而在於提醒，「安於當下」，而要多花時間在「道業」上，這反而對你更有利。而你更換的結果，其實好不到哪裡，只是增加麻煩而已。所以，求得此籤，當立定修行的決心，以為自己創造更好的命運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前無業，試圖尋找工作者，此籤還是希望你藉此修行，你可以先修行一段時間，而後再行打算。不管是勤跑道場，還是支身深入山林，還是天天讀經念佛，還是參加佛門的短期活動，這都是你可以選擇的。藉此機會給自己生命不一樣的體驗，這可以讓你有所覺醒的機會。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆健康、治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問疾病，修行也有療病功效，只怕你不修而已，尤其是治療慢性病，更需要用修行的方法而治。拔除內心的「無明」即有療效。（請勿使用有副作用的方法治病）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶禍福。報應分明。若人祈禱。如谷應聲。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>無分貴賤。宜養精神。定則能應。福自駢臻。<br/>人禱→知祈禳</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">是非莫管。一任紛紜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>見如不見。聞如不聞。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜妄想。只宜守舊。自有成就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不意反成得意。無望反成有望。宜謹守所為。不可自專。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟莫興。病宜禳。利葵貪。行人阻。若修善。自有神助也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不宜妄動。佯為聾瞽。是非莫管。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">黃庭經。道書也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">士人占之。但當明其道。不計其功。貴賤窮通。付之天數。則天必祐之矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜妄想。只宜謹守避禍。作福修善。自有神助。失意反成得意。無望反成有望。若貪圖躁進。不唯無益。更恐反遭不測。占者慎之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東西南北。四方也。眼昏耳聾。戒勿招惹是非也。言凡四方閒事。總宜避之則吉。黃庭經。乃是修道之書。讀者消遣。不為貴賤窮通所縛。可得安靜之樂。凡事退守。動輒得咎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生會試。將揭榜。占此。竟不第。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人。問終身。占此後。中年失明。妻子俱喪。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寄居道院。至老安康。眼目反明。此熟讀黃庭<span lang="EN-US">(經)之應也。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又光緒。乙酉科。晉江一文會。十餘人。於鄉闈前同占此籤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">榜發。惟王生取。雖第四名。經魁。始悟黃庭經一卷五字之驗。如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一朱生。將應院試。亦占此入場。竟坐東號舍。有為解曰。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">逐句之未。暗藏東廊卷通四字。後果入泮。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">按聾與廊字異而土音相同。善解者自不拘執也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莊子慕道<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">莊子名周，蒙國人。當周國漆樹園長，學問廣博。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">楚威王聽說他賢明，派遣使者帶重金欲聘用他。莊子說：當卿相是千金重利的高位，可是你沒看見被養來當犧牲品的牛嗎？我寧願游戲來暢快自已的志向，我嚮往清淨無為的大道理。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他以老子為師，著作南華經。十多萬字。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">修行是需要條件的，最基本的條件就是要有足夠的「覺知性」，求得此籤者，代表已經有這個特性了，可以走修行路線了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 33;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三四籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁丁<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.春夏纔過秋又冬。<br/>2.紛紛謀慮攪心胸。<br/>3.貴人垂手來相援。<br/>4.休把私心情意濃。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.春夏天才過，秋冬又來了。（歲月如梭）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.但此事卻不順遂而令人搥胸。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.巧逢貴人得相助（若逢貴人莫錯過）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.停下私心多些真情義有助本事</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.求得此籤者，代表這件事進行的不順利，但在往後可望得到貴人的相助。此籤並提醒，應當淡化個人私心，多些真情義，這對於你所問之事能有幫助。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自己意見游疑不定，但他人意見，應當過濾而信。若貴人之言，當得採信。若遇到貴人，應當追隨採納，而不要輕易讓貴人離去。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在個性上對人要有感恩心。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫信花言巧語，忌沉醉於甜蜜。應防口舌之爭，當防私心之戰。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身者求姻緣，可望有媒人介紹。但在未來交往態度上，應該慷慨些，多些真情義則有利你的交往。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情分手欲求挽回者，可找貴人代為說服而挽回。但是，心胸寬大為懷，有助你的愛情發展。反之，個人私心太重，則有礙愛情順利。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若婚姻不合者，可由貴人勸和。但勸當事者，多些真情真義，可讓婚姻更穩定。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若當前喜歡一個人，尚未交往者，若想進一步發展，可求他人代為轉介，以期能正式交往。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往的對象要不要放棄，本籤詩故事暗示，你要學「蕭何追韓信」的精神，以挽留當前這個優秀的對象。（許多人在愛情上往往沒有眼光，不知當前的對象是優質的，而將之輕易放棄，這是很可惜的。）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇問愛情求得此籤者；<span lang="EN-US"><br/>一、當展現你的真心真情，降伏個人私我心，這對你的愛情才有幫助。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二、你當前所遇的對象是很好的對象，你當好好的把握，莫讓其離去。若你們感情不好，你要知道，這是你自己不好。你在挑人，人家也在挑你，所以，期望你不要被對方淘汰了。因此，你當提升自己的人格，以期在這場愛情選拔中，可以屏雀中選，而得到優質的愛情。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業前途，在經營上當網羅優秀人才，莫讓流失。在態度上對於員工當寬大為懷，並與員工培養好的感情。若能依此經營，則能有利事業前途。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職不能只看薪水高、事少又輕鬆，當看其前途性，並把未來工作當作自己的家，以此心態出發，再找工作。求得此籤者，可望經由他人介紹或引薦而找到工作。本籤暗示，可以找到很好的工作，但是，若是求職態度不好的話，那就與好工作無緣了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若受人雇用者，應當追隨優秀的主管，以讓工作更順遂。若政治人物者，應當找對跟隨的主子。若當主管者，應保留優秀的屬下，莫輕易使其離去。在工作中與同事相處，若能有情有義，這就是你致勝的秘訣。另外，在工作上應與人和睦相處，而不要與人紛爭、口舌，因此建議你在工作中，可以修「廣結善緣」。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">「紛紛謀慮攪心胸」所以，你要注意，有雜務事糾結你你心胸時，那你的心臟方面可能會出問題。若問治病，莫與人紛爭計較，寬大為懷，無私無我，以此性格處世，則有利治病。另外，找個善知識作為貴人，這有助你解開心結，而使身心都得到療效。心情，會影響健康，只要心情恢復正常，疾病自然康復。所以，你要治療的是自己的「心情」。記得在生活中，不要與人結怨仇。對於怨仇之人，應該以慈悲心對待。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆官司訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司前途，代表此官司進行的極為不順利，因此你需要有人協助。此籤並提醒，就算是對簿公堂之人，也要把對方當親人般對待，若能如此，則有助化解官司。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一歲營謀。未有發達。必得貴人。垂手提挈。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>漸漸亨通。可免激聒。莫信私人。巧語鬥謀。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">必<span lang="EN-US">→方<br/>謀→諜</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟則憂兮病不瘳。財物耗散莫相謀。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>行人動作婚難就。口舌須防免唧啾。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟謀<span lang="EN-US">→訟解憂兮病漸瘳。財物凋零莫妄求。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤空虛。指望無成。徒勞自己心力。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀事不就。所為虛費功夫。營求未有發達。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若得貴人提攜。漸漸亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫信私言巧語。方免聒聒也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一年之內。謀為紛紛。徙然勞苦。若得貴人提挈。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只宜迸去私慮。將心靠他。始得亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若惑于婦人之言。或因他事之累。則彼此之間。互相猜忌。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事便無益。占者得之。防口舌。名利休問。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀望難成。徒勞心力。幸有貴人接引。必須托以心腹。不得又聽邪佞之言。私心擬議。進退不決。失此機會也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">春夏秋冬。總計一年之久。謀慮紛紛。日久無成也。貴人相接。是好機緣。私意情濃。是自己遊移無主。聽信不實也。戒占者切勿如此。則貴人可靠。謀望有成矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人出外抽豐。其父在家。占此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其手子客居數年。竟空手而回。所得盡付花柳<span lang="EN-US">(煙花柳巷)之費矣。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蕭何追韓信<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">漢朝。蕭何，沛地方人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">韓信，淮陰地方人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">那時，漢王（劉邦）燒毀了<span style="COLOR:black;">棧道</span>，部下將士逃亡很多。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時韓信也打算投奔他處，當蕭何知道了，就連夜追回韓信。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">隔天漢王知道此事，生氣地說，將士逃亡超過一半，沒聽說你要追回其他</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丞相</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，卻只追韓信，這是為什麼？</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蕭何說，大王如果無意東征，那就算了。如果想要與楚霸王爭天下的話，那就非韓信不可了。劉邦於是拜韓信為大將。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:312pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不同的個性有不同的命運。由於此種個性，故有此種命運的困境。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">現實、短視會讓自己流失好命運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">優柔寡斷、不善用人，不知把握貴人，這會損失自己的機會。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自己毫無主見，無知跟隨他人起舞，容易陷入困境。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此種命運的改造之道，就是<span lang="EN-US">(1)做人要「有情有義」(2)跟好優秀的主子（重用優秀的屬下）。以此重點執行，就能改造命運。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 34;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一山如畫對清江。<br/>2.門裏團圓事事雙。<br/>3.誰料半途分折去。<br/>4.空幃無語對銀缸。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一個美好的環境就如一幅山水畫（家庭風水、環境很好）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.相處也很融洽</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.但是沒料到突來的意外，拆散了一家的團圓</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.空對著香囊無語問蒼天</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565" colspan="2">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇即使這件事當前看來似乎很好，但是「天有不測風雲，人有旦夕禍福。」此事先吉後凶，將來恐有變卦。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇求得本籤者，諸事不宜，出外有險，恐危生命，不可輕忽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在災難尚未降臨前，請提早預防，則有化解功效。請務必提前進行消業障，即使當前想要進行的事情已經停止，但是出門在外也是要提防意外事故發生。請隨時持咒或恭念佛菩薩聖號，這些念佛菩薩聖號的修練，務必養成習慣，以備緊急時還知道恭念，務必修練到惡夢時也能恭念這些聖號。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情前途者，即使當前愛情看起來好好的，但恐中途會有分離。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆學業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問學業，即使當前看起來好好的，恐畢不了業。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事業</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問事業，即使當前事業看起來昌隆順利，但是恐有意想不到之災難，而造成重大損失或結束營業。請事先做好預防措施。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即是現在是處於獲利狀態，但是結果還是虧損與套牢。請事先做好預防打算。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆遠行、出門、出國<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雖然這趟遠行看起來一片美景，但恐有意外事故，而造成重傷、殘廢或身亡之運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆健康、治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問身體健康未來狀態，即使當前看起來四肢健全，無病無痛，但恐爆發突然的疾病或意外。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前已經生病者，恐會惡化而有不測，因此當做最壞準備。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、錄用、中選、升遷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問此類問題，雖然極可能考上、中選，而呈現一片喜氣洋洋，但是錄選後恐爆發突然性的意外，而令人無語問蒼天。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆選擇、決定<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事情的選擇，不管你選的是哪一邊，雖然看起來都很好，一片祥和之境。但是，恐有不測之災。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你目前的決定，即使當前看起來很好，但是後續恐有不測。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求得本籤者，當提早預防，只要厄運尚未發生之前進行</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，都有避災之功。請誠心地、肯切地去懺悔。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">墳宅雖吉。命運未通。家門招禍。好事成空。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>夫妻離散。骨肉西東。凡事不遂。有始無終。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始終未必不貪圖。到底須知力枉勞。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>設得十分奇巧計。卻防中路被風濤。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始圖<span lang="EN-US">→漫誇根蒂自堅牢<br/>防→妨</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤墳宅雖吉。命運未通。謀望到底成空。先吉後凶。有始無終。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">須防有死亡之患。訟必凶。病主險。求財必無。行人有阻也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一山對清江。言風水雖合吉。但命運未通故也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">門裏團圓之事。半途分折。骨肉離散。名成而敗。利得而失。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若人有見機之智。不待時之過中勢之極盛。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先為趨避之計。則晚節末路可保無虞。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占家宅。親病必危。問行人。有阻。凡事欠順。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先吉後凶。有始無終。防有盜賊之侵。死亡之慮。夫妻折散之憂。親友嫌隙之咎。主家業退敗。人口凋零。大凶之兆。急須種德挽回。庶可化凶為吉也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一山如畫。言墳宅風水頗好。門裏團圓。言現在家口亦安。奈浮雲變幻。吉凶無常。忽有半途分折之憂。空幃獨守。言淒涼不堪也。凡事得中有失。吉處藏凶。早宜思患預防。或可減半。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人妻病。占此遂亡。應半途云云。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一堪輿託人薦于富室。彼已有先至者。應門裏云云。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩人各為異論。與主家不合。皆不用而反<span lang="EN-US">(返)。應半途空幃云云。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一婦人。產後未滿月。母子得病。占此。不數日俱亡。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">應事事雙。并後兩句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一家兄弟兩人。將應試仝占此。後俱遊庠蓋。誰料半得隹字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">途折去僅存道<span lang="EN-US">(道本作缺首，大五碼缺此部首字)。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二者合成進字。故宜其入學也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王昭君和番<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">昭君姓王。名嬙，字告月，歸州地方人。漢元帝的宮女。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">當時由於得罪畫工，以致畫工在她的臉上點個崩夫痣，他因此失寵。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">昭君才貌雙全，感傷自已沒機緣見帝王。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時剛好匈奴來求和親，她就自行上書請嫁。臨行前走入皇宮旁邊庭院顧影徘徊，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">漢元帝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">才驚見她的美貌，但是不能失信於單于，所以還是派她和番。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來畫工毛延壽等二百餘人都因此被斬殺。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">每一種好壞命運都是一種善惡因果，若能在惡報未降臨前</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，都有改造之功效。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 35;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三六籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁己 上吉<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.功名富貴自能為。<br/>2.偶著仙鞭莫問伊。<br/>3.萬里鵬程君有分。<br/>4.吳山頂上好鑽龜。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.各種好福報都是自己的善行造作而來的</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若偶然地福報不如人時，不用問他人。（這是因為「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">」不足故功名遲到）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.未來的前途上，你也有好前景等著</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.屆時你就可以再占卜了（再求籤、占卜看看自己</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">的成果如何。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇求得本籤者，代表「德行」尚不具足，故功名遲遲不到。凡是各種謀求者，當事者只要速補「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">」，則福報就會來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇德，一種利他之心即是。（例；品德、功德、道德、涵養等皆是「德行」）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不管當前所問是那個項目，請速「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">」，即可如願。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問愛情挽回，情人吵架，夫妻失和，請速「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，即可挽回，回歸舊好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若和公婆相處不睦者，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請速「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」即能建立良好關係。<span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前喜歡的對象能否進一步發展，能否有成果，請速「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」即有好成果。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問姻緣何時來，請速「</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，姻緣隨時就來。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">由於德行不足，故工作的業績上、事業的獲利上，遲遲未見功效，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請速「</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，則業績與獲利即可順遂而來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想在這方面獲利者，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">請速「</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」一段時間，而後向「南方」發展，則有利可圖。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試、競試成果者，這次不一定能上榜，但是只要你盡</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">速「</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，那下次就能金榜有名了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，請速「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">」即可改善或痊癒。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>待人寬容不記恨。對物慷慨不吝嗇。做事依理不超過。…等等</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不同的疾病，所當修的科目也不同。請自我檢視，當可知自己哪裡不好，那就補修哪裡。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不管是求孕、求子，所求可以如願。但是，當「</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">」修的越好時，出生的孩子素質就越好。若要補修者，請在未懷孕之前加強。另外，懷孕前，誦持<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=5144">《觀世音菩薩普門品》</a>，也有如願生兒育女之功效。若在懷孕中誦持，則可提升孩兒素質，而且生產後孩子好養。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富貴分定。遲速有時。藏器以待。切莫怨遲。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>掀天事業。時至即為。若到天邊。便可決疑。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">榮華有分。未得其時。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>他人早達。切莫恨遲。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不可躁進。欲速則不達。富貴遲速有時。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若在家則困苦。出外則震亨。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不宜守舊。訟得理。名利晚成。行人阻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚必成。病漸安。先凶後吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">窮通得喪。出於偶然。各有其時。凡事成之。必在於後。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">鵬程。名利之程。吳山即吳越之山。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">高宗即位。播遷至越。功名之會。南至於此。以應選。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者亦當進圖功名。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好鑽龜者。謂占其用否之兆。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自能為者。要在人當修為。以待時。不可委於時之未至。而嗟歎也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求財南方有。北方不穩。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不可躁進。欲速則不達也。功名富貴。遲速有時。待時而動則吉。鵬程有分。定可達到。名必成。財必遂。運程坦坦。轉瞬揚眉吐氣時也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名富貴。有志竟成。他人先鞭得意。不必羨慕。鵬程有分。科第無疑。不過稍遲耳。吳山係杭州山名。鑽龜。卜也。若問地方。當主浙省。凡事謀為如意。先難後易。晚景榮華。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一淅中人。父子因兵失散。占此。因上吳山卜卦。至廟門。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">見有父尋子招貼。遂訪見其父。驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又龔廣文。將應院試。占此。時學政吳伯新。尚書也。果入泮。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">羅隱求官<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">唐朝。羅隱，字昭諫，錢塘人。善長作詩，被稱為羅江東。吳越王錢鏐徵召為徒（官名），當節度判官的副使。他曾說：錢鏐討伐朱溫縱即使無功，猶可保住杭越地區的領土。奈何和盜賊（朱溫）和好，以圖謀顯達為目的，是古人羞恥做的事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">羅的著作甚多。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謝安石東山高臥<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東晉謝安，字安石，祖上世代為官，從小聰穎好學，有文學才能，年輕時即有名氣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謝安不願受做官束縛，藉口身體不好，辭官到會稽東山隱居，經常與文人雅士遊山玩水高談闊論。<span lang="EN-US"> 別人請他出山做官都婉拒，連朝廷要他當官也拒絕。謝安四十多歲時，家族接連出事，為免家族地位和經濟利益受嚴重影響，便不再拒絕當官。<br/>此時，掌全國政務及軍務的大司馬桓溫請謝安當部屬。當時高崧開玩笑地對他說：「先生幾次拒絕朝廷徵召。高臥東山。許多人都說，安石不出來做官，老百姓怎麼辦呢！今天，您出來做官了，老百姓怎樣看待您呢！」謝安聽了頗有愧色。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不過，謝安的確很有才能，最後當上宰相。淝水之戰就是在他領導下，由弟弟謝石及姪子謝玄指揮，打敗苻堅的九十多萬大軍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">福報光臨，必須條件具足，缺一不可。每個人由於狀況不同，故缺少的項目也不同。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">福報降臨的主要項目條件有；<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">善行：過去曾經有善行故有善報，若無善行則無善報。（壞籤，就是有惡行之故）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">德行：有德的行為稱為「德行」。如常所說的，品德、功德、道德、涵養等皆是「德行」。有的好命運是當事者「德行」不足，故好命運還不來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">時間：由於過去造作善業的時間不同，故善報降臨的時間也不同，若時間未到，則福報也暫不來。（例如：<span lang="EN-US">25籤、41籤）</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.人：與此福報相關的人尚未出現，故福報也還不來。（籤詩中提及貴人提攜的籤都是。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 36;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.焚香來告復何辭。<br/>2.善惡平分汝自知。<br/>3.屏卻昧公心裏事。<br/>4.出門無礙是通時。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你燒香來稟告神明又說了許多話</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.誰善誰惡，你自己心裡也知道。（這件事的對錯、是非、好壞、善惡，你自己心裡也知道。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.辭去昧公之事、心裡壞事。（把不好的那部份除去）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.當出門時沒有障礙（心理罣礙），那就是通達了。（遠離是非之地，就能事情通達。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若屬於糾紛事件者，本籤隱喻占者原本要害人，但卻反而被害。若能去惡修善，端正己心，則凡事有利。屬於此種事件者，當懺悔己過。平息紛爭，則事能吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若事情有困頓者，不是別人不好，是自己也不好，若能先從自己改過，則事能善。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.「出門」隨所問不同而有不同隱喻，可以代表「離去」、「到外面去」、「遠離」等等意思。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身者問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你也別怪罪姻緣都不來，因為自己也不夠努力尋求。若想得到姻緣，應該加強自己的德行，注重自己的涵養氣質，去除自己的缺點，而後多多出門參與互動或活動，若能如此則有機會遇到姻緣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前心儀的人，可否追求？這愛情要怎麼進展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">追她是好，這個人的狀況你也知道，但要提升自己的涵養與風度，而後多多互動。若能常常和他出門約會而能相處融洽，那未來就有好成果了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往的對象未來前途？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想在愛情上開花結果，不僅對方要努力，你自己也一樣要用心經營。若能排除自己的缺點或是不利的地方，那這愛情就有利。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情困頓、冷淡或分手者，<span lang="EN-US"><br/>也許你覺得他不好，他不對，其實，你自己也有過，若能懺悔自己，改正自己，提升自己的德行，多一分真愛，則愛情能化凶為吉。本籤也暗示，若雙方能常有互動或約會，這愛情就有利。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問工作，代表當前這份工作薪水少，但是，你也不要嫌棄，因為你表現的也不好。要是能勤於到外面奔走，和其他人互動、結善緣，這對你是有利的。若問事業，代表此事業利潤少，但是你也不要怪罪景氣不好，其實你自己經營的也不是很好，因此當提升自己的事業經營能力，而且要多多往外面拓展，這對於你是事業才是有利的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆更換、轉換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你想要換工作嗎！你也不要怪罪公司不好而要換工作，自己的能力也要提升才行。若想更換工作、換職業、換公司，「出門無礙是通時」，這是提示你，你還是到外面換個環境好了。但也別忘了要提升了自己的專業能力與德行，若能如此則往後將有一番新氣象。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試成果者，這次考的怎麼樣，你自己也心裡有數。你就不要妄想可以得到公職了，你就換個門路經營吧。若尚未考試者，請事先</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:#24878c;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">消業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:#24878c;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，則有改善之功。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆犯官司、犯小人<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這代表自己也有錯，導致犯官司或犯小人，其實，你自己也知道。而這件事能和最好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想擁有孩子，其實有了孩子好不好，你自己想想也知道。若實在想要有孩子，先把自己的不好狀況補正，而後多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，另外再求神佛庇祐，則能有好的成果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作善降祥。作惡降殃。何必禱神。當自揣量。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>公心莫昧。勉為善良。前程遠大。可保安康。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">爾欲陷人而自陷。欺心暗裡鬼神知。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若能改善求天福。轉禍為祥事事宜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">爾而<span lang="EN-US">→計終</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤顯然說。主人家人有害人之心。而又受人之害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若能悔過則吉。訟宜和。病祈福。求財少。名利難。婚可合。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只要心正。無事不吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人之為善為惡。人雖不知。己所獨知。若使欺其不知。而欲害之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不惟不能害人。抑反為人防害。不可不戒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者當公平正大。不可暗昧欺人。則凡事亨通。而無阻滯。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大抵此籤戒人為惡。勉人為善也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤顯然告人遷善去惡。秉心公正。自有通達之時。若不覺悟改悔。鬼神暗裡先知。何能掩蔽。恐不免咎殃之踵至也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡人為善去惡。人雖不知。己獨知之。若使欺其不知。昧公濟私。損人利己。必至自招凶咎。戒占者當公平正大。不欲勿施。自得人事亨通。全無阻滯。速宜返躬自問可也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人公門不利。占此。乃棄夫為商。大獲厚利。應在三四句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又晉江鄭生。將赴院試。占此後。果入泮。末句驗甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">邵堯夫祝香<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">宋朝。邵雍，字堯夫。三十歲時，跟父親遷居河南。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">邵堯夫</span><span style="">什麼書都讀，精通易理天文術數，言行恭敬謹慎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">所作禱告，皆為國家為親人祈禱。不曾為自己。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">起初考試及格，將派作監主簿但是沒去。後來又派任穎州團練推官，他也沒就任。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">死後追贈秘書省、著作郎</span><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（都是官名）</span><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元祐年間，諡號康節。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">周孝侯射虎斬蛟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">周處年幼喪父，年少時輕狂放蕩，縱情肆慾，成為鄉里中惡名昭彰、眾人唯恐避之不及的人物。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">有一日，周處問鄉里的長輩：「當今時局平和，又是豐年，大家為何苦悶不樂呢？」長輩嘆道：「三害未除，何樂之有！」周處追問哪三害，得到的答案是：「南山白額虎，長橋下蛟龍，若是你能先除掉這兩害，再告訴你第三害。」<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">於是周處自告奮勇，先入山殺了猛<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%99%8E" title="虎"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">虎</span></a>，又下水與蛟<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%BE%8D" title="龍"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">龍</span></a>纏鬥，浮沉數十里，飄流到陽羨東方的震澤（今<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%AA%E6%B9%96" title="太湖"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">太湖</span></a>），一連三天三夜沒有消息，鄉人以為周處死了，全都互相慶賀。周處活著回來看見了，才知自己在鄉民眼中是何等禍患，心生悔意。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">接著，周處拜訪名士</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%99%B8%E6%A9%9F" title="陸機"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">陸機</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%99%B8%E9%9B%B2" title="陸雲"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">陸雲</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">兄弟，告以實情，他想改過自新，但已蹉跎歲月，恐怕將來一無所成。陸雲勉勵周處朝聞過而夕改之，立定大志，尚有前途。於是周處勵志好學，文章有思想，志向存義烈，言談講忠信而守分寸。一年後，周處果然接到諸多州府下的聘書。周處在吳</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%A9%E7%B4%80" title="天紀"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">天紀</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">277</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年－</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">280</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年）年中擔任東觀令、無難督。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 37;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.蛩吟唧唧守孤幃。<br/>2.千里懸懸望信歸。<br/>3.等得榮華公子到。<br/>4.秋冬括括雨靡靡。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.在蟋蟀的鳴叫聲下，守著家門。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.寄望著千里外的音訊傳來</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.等著榮華富貴，等著期盼的人來</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.但如秋之悽愴，如冬之寒冷，又雨綿綿。（令人落淚之景象）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">所期盼之事，若屬於「人」者，即使得到一時的好訊息，也是淒寒落淚收場。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀得本籤者，各種謀求暫且停下，因為有喪服之累贅，或口舌之爭或哀傷之劇情。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">逢秋冬之際尤須特別注意不幸事件發生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若近日有多怪夢者，此即是不詳徵兆之預警。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，謀得本籤者，所問之事結局不善。但請好好</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，並行大功德（</span><span style="COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">）以減輕危難。另外還可以在平日頌唸佛菩薩聖號，以祈能度過難關。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問姻緣何時來？若心儀的對象問可否追求？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求得此籤者代表，即使姻緣果真來了，也沒有好結果。若得到愛情，恐怕也會因此而落淚哭傷，有始無終。故不求也罷。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若男女相處關係不好者，或欲求挽回者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此情即使一時能挽回，最後還是會悲傷的結局。故免挽回矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問雙方可不可結婚？有無結婚可能？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤詩代表要結婚大有困難。就算結婚了，恐怕還是悲傷的開始。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試者，代表考了多次，但是就算能考上，反而不吉。建議放棄此考。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若求職者求得此籤，代表找工作找了很多，或找了很久了，最後雖然找到工作了，看起來似乎是好工作，但是，這是個會讓人哭傷的工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業前途者，代表此事業一向蕭條，未來即使能旺盛一下，但是結局還是虧損累累。建議提早做好準備，以預防虧損。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、更換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種更換者，諸事不宜，無利可圖，現在不是時候。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問投資理財者，即使一時能得到歡喜，但是這只是虛喜一場，結果還是令人血本無歸。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，此代表這個疾病即使一時能治療，或許看起來似乎好轉了，但是，往後還是不樂觀，恐要做最壞打算。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求子、求孕<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求得此籤，代表這個期望已經守候很久了，但是，即使有懷孕訊息，這恐怕只是虛喜。建議，不要懷孕為佳，以免徒增憂傷。若已經懷孕者，請速為孩子</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">消業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作事無聊。空自惆悵。蹤得好音。依然悽愴。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>謀望不遂。心神徒喪。家道未安。禱神陰相。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不宜問事不宜行。九日常憂十日驚。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>一段榮華如一夢。翻來覆去總無情。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主有死亡之憂。哭泣之哀。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟休問。病有險。財莫求。婚難成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人不至。謀事凶多吉少。秋冬占之大不吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">縱有虛喜。終是大憂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">計出無聊。獨守孤幃。又聞秋聲唧唧。能不惆悵耶。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">千里懸懸者。目下謀為不遂。榮華公子到者。亦是虛名而無實事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雨靡靡者。言是非喪服之累。喜末完。憂纏之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者大抵不吉。秋冬尤宜謹之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋冬括括或作秋風括地。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主有死亡之患。哭泣之哀。凡事不利。有名無實。有始無終。家運凋零。前程蹇滯。作大陰功善事可解。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋景孤幃。蟲聲唧唧。最為淒涼苦況。千里懸懸。幾番盼望。等到榮華公子。似是好音。誰知意外不測。又生出一番苦惱。括括霏霏。正是不堪境象。凡事慎守為佳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占功名必得。但恐憂繼之。然所應又有不同。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有一生占此。入學抵家。遭妻之喪。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一生占此。中式。旋時則值淫雨連綿。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孟姜女思夫<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟姜女，秦始皇時人。丈夫是范杞郎，被派築長城。長久工作不歸，所以孟姜女思念丈夫。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">關盼盼獨守燕子樓<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">唐貞元年間，武寧節度使張愔鎮守徐州，為其愛妾關盼盼築燕子樓給予居住，張愔死後，關盼盼居此樓十五年不嫁，後不食而死。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本故事完整內容：<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://f5101231.myweb.hinet.net/f24.html">關盼盼魂斷燕子樓</a></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 38;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三九籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁壬<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.北山門外好安居。<br/>2.若問終時慎厥初。<br/>3.堪笑包藏許多事。<br/>4.鱗鴻雖便莫修書。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.山門外的北方，是個好安居的場所。（當前的你，在這安居之所，過著安閒生活，這是最佳的安排。此話也代表凡事守舊為宜。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若是問結果如何，那就要謹慎你的出發。（做任何事之初都要謹慎小心）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.對於內在包藏著不為人知的黑暗事，你就笑笑置之。（以免遭來口舌）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.書信上的訊息方便得知，但是不要隨便相信。（預防被騙）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(書信雖然方便，但是不要隨意興書揭發黑暗事。)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">開始做任何事時，都要謹慎與想清楚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不要隨便相信文字訊息，以防被騙。這些訊息不管是來自書信、電話、報章、媒體、電腦網路上，通通要小心。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">對於有風險或投機之事，更不宜進行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事求得本籤者，代表有機會遇到詐騙事，或者已經受騙，因此諸事當謹慎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">對於看到不法、無理之事，當以寬宏大量而包容之，而不要隨便用書信揭發或頂撞。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">6.過單純、安閒的生活最好。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若問愛情前途者，或問愛情挽回，代表對方不是真心，甚至是被騙了。因此分手者不必挽回。而當前正在交往者，應早早退出，不要繼續受騙。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.本籤示意過著單身、安閒的生活對你最自由。故單身者此刻不用求姻緣。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想要圖謀什麼時，一定要很小心，以免被騙。若是在找工作者，工作難得，而且要小心社會陷阱。若已經在工作者，績效不彰。若經營事業者，獲利不佳。若問工作或事業前途者，淡泊名利過個安閒的生活對你最好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若病者求得此籤，莫亂投醫，莫亂吃藥，莫迷信廣告或名醫名藥，以免越醫越惡化而有生命危險。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">現在安閒的你，莫做有投機性的投資以免虧損，若論理財成果，實在無利可圖。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">「若問終時慎厥初」意即，若想知道成果如何，那務必要認真謹慎你的功課。也要想好你應試的動機為何。此也隱喻此應試中包藏著不為人知的內幕。若想參與這個競試的話，本籤示意過安閒的生活比較好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若是求孕、生子者，此籤示意沒有孩子的生活更安閒，因此不要求孕求子。另外，當預防社會的黑暗與陷阱。越是迷人之事，越應該避開。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">靜處安身。不堪比匪。欲保終吉。作事謹始。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>無感人言。切防害己。勿輕傳信。暗中有鬼。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不匪<span lang="EN-US">→是非莫理<br/>感信→惑書</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好把工夫作吉鎡。有時暗地結姻緣。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>對面好談心曲事。莫將隱奧與人傳。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好鎡<span lang="EN-US">→仁里安居善自全<br/>面→我</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤只宜守舊。不可妄想。謀望遲遲。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">且待時至。還須退步。方得安寧。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病擇醫。訟宜解。求財無。婚宜審。行人阻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謹慎修為。庶幾得以長保。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戒人安身靜處。慎擇交游。防閑詐偽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言他人包藏禍心。久欲中我。我則付之一笑。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但當作事謀始。謹慎修為。勿囂囂口舌。以招禍非。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫修書言欺詐之不可為也。處訟宜和。求財以信。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有病者不保守。則死亡必至。末句或作好修書欠妥。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜守舊。不可妄為。作事謀始。無貽後悔。凡事謹密為要。不可浪透信息。反此。則有意外之咎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好安居。現有一安樂境界。慎厥初。須是早為區畫。不可妄動。事多包藏。自具寬宏之志。修書慎重。莫通鱗鴻之音。機事不密則害成。更防口舌之釁也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">江右一貴人。寓金陵。卜墳葬父。占此後。屢擇不中。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">因出麒麟閣觀地。偶見門外一山。遂問鄉人山名。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">對曰北山。即得佳地。乃悟首句之驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陶淵明賞菊<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陶淵明</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（西元<span lang="EN-US">365～427）東晉潯陽柴桑人，陶侃的曾孫，一名淵明，字元亮。後來</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">改名陶潛，號靖節先生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陶淵明年少就有高尚志願，博學多聞善長作文。陶潛在其居所屋旁有五株柳樹，故又自號五柳先生。後來當彭澤縣長時，督郵（官名）到縣視察，照慣例，陶應該整裝迎接。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陶嘆息說：我不能為五斗米折腰，就自己辭官。寫歸去來辭（文章）來表達本意性格。陶愛菊花，每清晨必賞花。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 39;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">丁癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.新來換得好規模。<br/>2.何用隨他步與趨。<br/>3.只聽耳邊消息到。<br/>4.崎嶇歷盡見亨衢。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.最近有了新的轉變、新的發展、新的作風。（當前的轉變是好的。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.不用跟隨他人的步伐與趨勢（不再受他人牽制、不必再聽他人使喚、不用跟著他人屁股走、不必再依靠他人…）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.只要聽到消息來到</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.那就是崎嶇道路的盡頭而要邁入平坦順利之境了</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.此籤顯示你最近做了大轉變，往後不必再依隨他人步伐了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. 當前進行的轉變這是好的，但要用自己的主張莫聽人言。此事即使剛開始有些辛苦，將來勢必更亨通。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若當前事情有困頓或遊疑者，請換個新的做法或換個新的環境，或換個新的觀念而經營。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身問姻緣何時來</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你應該重新整裝自己，給自己新的面貌，營造一個不一樣的自己，然後就會有姻緣的消息了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">是可以追求，但也建議你，打造一個容光煥發的自己，給對方全新的好感覺，雖然追求過程有些辛苦，但是此姻緣也是未來幸福的立基點。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象的愛情前途？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宜將此姻緣做個確定，以免未來有變故。若已經交往多年者，應朝結婚方向走，因為這是能否和他結婚的關鍵點，若此刻沒有確定，那以後會有變數。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問愛情分手問挽回？或當前交往冷淡者、困頓者應如何是好？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">應盡力挽回，並且重新出發，並以新的面貌、態度相處，以新的風格、環境相聚，若能如此則能穩住愛情。此是繼續交往的關鍵，也是幸福的轉捩點。雖然過程辛苦些，但也要保住這份愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、升遷<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雖然過程有些辛苦，只要肯努力勢必能成功。依自己的看法去做，而不要聽外人之言。往後可以得到提拔。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當前你的工作或事業有了新的轉變或發展，這是好的，往後不用在受人牽制，雖然這經營起來有些辛苦，但是將來勢必亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、學業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試或學業者，最近有了新的發展，若問考試者能過關。而往後的學習也是辛苦的，但是只要能堅持到底，勢必能學有所成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">都可以求，也可以如願。前孕生女，後孕生男。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉換、換職等類變更<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不管是換職業或轉換跑道等各種轉換，都值得這麼做，即使個人力量微薄，經營辛苦，但也可以轉換成功，並成為將來發達的轉捩點。但以自己的意思去做即可。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問投資理財者，你要改變新的做法、觀念來經營這件事，這樣才不會被套牢。若能這樣改變，這就是好的，在未來就能獲利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆房地產買賣<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想購買房地產者，這對於自己也是新的改變，這個改造是可取的。若問賣出的話，只要有客人來到，那當前的困境就可以解決。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司者，最近有新的轉變，只要來了法院的消息，那你的崎嶇道路就亨通了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，疾病可以痊癒。請換個新的治病觀念，或換個新的療法，或換個醫生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀望更改。修為儘好。何必依人。自可達到。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>須歷艱難。必獲好報。平步青霄。榮捧恩詔。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好把工夫改換般。門庭增喜轉眉攢。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>文書到手皆成就。宜訟宜婚病亦安。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好般<span lang="EN-US">→改換規模又一般<br/>攢→顏</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀望更變儘好。莫聽人言閑是閑非。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">何必依人。自可遠到。名後成。訟得勝。孕生子。保無病。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人回。婚宜定。凡事宜。遲必有餘慶也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">百事規模多。主更變。名利遲遲。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若能歷涉艱難。必獲薦拔。平步青霄。榮捧恩詔。以處順境。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者只宜守己。不可隨人是非。以招禍患。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始孕生女。次孕生男。自用則吉。用人則凶。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀望儘好。須是自己變更。莫聽人言主使。誤走程途。不久好音即到。始雖崎嶇難行。後自亨衢通利。是為先難後易之象。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">規模新換。去舊從新也。何用隨他。自作主張也。耳聽消息。好音即到。崎嶇歷盡。苦去甜來。亨衢。是康莊大路。一往平平坦坦。吉無不利也。占者須謀為決斷。志氣堅定始驗。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.3pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.3pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吳下一富生。隨友南京。援例占此後。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">因循花柳金用過半。而事不成後。過耿姓年諠。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">稍為青口。竟以儒士。得中鄉試。應在後三句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:252.5pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:252.5pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:252.5pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">漢光武陷昆陽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">漢朝光武帝劉秀，還沒稱王時，帶兵至昆陽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">王莽派王邑、王尋帶數十萬軍隊，又驅趕猛獸虎豹、犀牛、大象，以助威武。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">光武軍隊僅數萬，劉秀自己帶步兵、騎兵千餘人當前鋒，打敗王莽先鋒部隊，其他將領接著進攻，王莽軍大敗，又有大風雨，虎豹顫抖都被殺。不久以後，王邑逃走，光武虜獲對方兵器軍糧。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東漢建立，全靠此戰。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（此故事意味著，以寡擊眾，並成為新朝代的轉捩點。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:36.4pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:36.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:36.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:18.2pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:18.2pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:18.2pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 40;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊甲<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉→上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.自南自北自東西。<br/>2.欲到天涯誰作梯。<br/>3.遇鼠逢牛三弄笛。<br/>4.好將名姓榜頭題。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.人生志在四方</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若想攀登高峰有誰能依靠、引薦（靠人無力）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若遇子丑年、月、日，則有貴人扶持</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.此時所求之事也能順遂</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事全憑自力，無人可靠。若逢鼠年、牛年，或逢陰曆<span lang="EN-US">11、12月，或子日、丑日，所問之事則吉，或有貴人。在這時段內，問求職者可找到工作，問考試者可金榜題名，問競賽者有好成績，問升遷有望。問事業、工作者，這時段生意特別好，也特別忙碌。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若單身問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇有交往對象者問何時可結婚？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你期盼的姻緣，在逢子丑之日，可望有媒人介紹。若逢陰曆年底，則是姻緣最多的時刻。若要論及婚假的話，逢鼠、牛之年，有結婚之喜。每年陰曆的十一、十二月，亦是結婚的最佳、最可能時機。屆時請自行把握。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前交往對象好不好？</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇當前心儀的對象可否更近一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當前心儀的對象可以追求，但要靠自己的努力經營，而不能空坐等待，且要三番兩次的追求，才得到他的允諾。請把握陰曆的十一、十二月時進行互動，這是進展愛情的最有利時機。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情面臨分手或已分手</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇夫妻面臨離婚處境</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問挽回情人或挽回外遇的配偶，請掌握陰曆年底十一、十二月好好把握。在平常請掌握逢子、丑日，在這段期間好好相談復合。但是，這些時機過後，可能能又分手或又要鬧離婚了。因此，在復合時應該培養更進一步的感情，以免得又復失。總結，愛情鬧分手者，你們會有三次的分分合合，請發揮</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">情操，與改變自己不好的態度，以祈愛情早日復平。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司者，這案情總是反反覆覆，若訴訟期發生在鼠牛之年則吉。若案情結束在陰曆的十一、十二月，則有最佳結果。若在其他時間結束案情，則狀況糟些。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求孕、求子，請掌握在鼠年、牛年，做好懷孕準備，這兩年是得孕最佳年份。而在其他年份，請把握每年陰曆的十一、十二月的時候，更是懷孕良機。請事先做好懷孕各種準備。若想生男者，請補充</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功課。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若要找到工作，這全要靠自己，這次的求職可能需要三番兩次的奔波，而後才確立了工作。找工作的最佳時間在每年陰曆的<span lang="EN-US">11、12月。若逢子、丑的日子，也可以一試。依這個時間而找工作就能如願了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業前途者，你的事業還是要靠自己的經營，他人是不能依靠的。此事業在逢鼠、牛之年則吉昌，或每年底的<span lang="EN-US">11、12月亦佳，而其他時間，請保守經營。若問工作者，你的工作需要來回奔波與辛苦，但是終究能熬出頭，而在上面的吉昌時段中，你也會特別忙碌。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種競試成績者，若在鼠年、牛年，則整年的考運都很好。若逢每年底的<span lang="EN-US">11、12月考運亦佳。若考試之日在子、丑，亦有勝算。而其他時間，請安分守己。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆疾病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，此病多憂苦，而且病情起起落落，請選擇好醫生以期能快速康復。但是此病還是有死亡之風險。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問投資理財者，你的好運在鼠牛之年，在這兩年間長期投資則有佳績。若在每年陰曆年底的<span lang="EN-US">11、12月，亦是你投入理財的好時機，若過了12月，請記得收成。而在其他時間請勿躁動，以免虧損。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆房地產買賣<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問房地產買賣者，若屬於自住的房屋購買，或自用的土地購買，請在陰曆年底的<span lang="EN-US">11、12月進行。若屬於投資性的購買者，請在鼠、牛年進行，但請記得見好就收。若屬於賣出者，在過了這些時機就務必賣掉。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若求名利。先難後有。白日青雲。必在子丑。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>聲譽顯赫。題名榜首。百事亨通。顯然有後。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有<span lang="EN-US">→在</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">歷涉艱難。求謀未遂。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>富貴榮華。顯達在後。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">顯後<span lang="EN-US">→晚景順利</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤妄意。事務皆無定準。須緩求之。方有成就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必反覆。婚有三變之說。遇子丑日。或姓蕭之人方可。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名。初年難。望病多變。信能到。婚姻好。名利得。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">必待子丑年月。方得顯達也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人生志在四方。欲到天涯。不得人指引。靠人無力。前程有阻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">遇鼠逢牛三弄笛者。謂子丑年月日自有貴人拔擢。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">聲譽洋溢。名登金榜矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問婚姻。得葛姓之力。占病有死之兆。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事守之。必遇子丑二字方遂。此籤大抵始難終易。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤現在事務皆無定準。訟必反覆。婚有變易。遇子丑月日。或年分。可許遂意。功名初年艱難。子丑科青雲直上。吐氣揚眉。凡事先難後易。盡人事以待天時可也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">南北東西。乃男子四方之志。天涯遼遠。日前不得階梯。進身無路。待遇鼠逢牛之年。或月日。自有貴人提拔。士人聲譽洋溢。名登金榜。商賈財利勃發。家宅產業興隆。婚姻和合。冤枉申雪。凡事有成。時運未至不應。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:7.25pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:7.25pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生甲子科。占此。鄉會連捷。是應遇鼠逢牛四字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蓋占科名。凡遇子丑年。必捷也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">惟泉州一生。科試。占此。場內經題。自西自東。兩句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">放榜時。剛值子月丑日。竟列在三等。首名全詩之驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:90.7pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:90.7pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:90.7pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">劉文龍求官<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">劉文龍，漢時人。學問極淵博，與王昭君一起出塞和番。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">昭君請求一個才貌不俗臣子伴隨她，元帝命令劉文龍相隨，但是文龍新婚不久，心雖不捨，但國事重要，就答應。劉文龍與妻分別十八年，解決許多困難，於昭君死後回漢國，回家時，老幼都不認識他。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:365.75pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:365.75pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:365.75pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">李固言柳枝染衣<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">唐代元和年間的李固言生於鳳翔農村。性格敦厚。沒有人薦舉，就去參加京試，住在表親柳家。柳家的兄弟們，經常嘲笑他，說他不明白事理。他們認為不求人舉薦沒有能考上的道理，等候聽他失意的消息。還偷著寫了「此處有屋出租」的字條貼在李固言的頭巾上。李固言自己一點不知道。出門，看見的人都偷著笑。許孟容當時做右常侍（官名），是一個沒權勢的官，不被人看重。人稱常侍官為貂腳，沒力量替年輕人說話。李固言想拿自己的文章去求教人，跟柳氏兄弟商量。柳氏兄弟就帶他到許孟容的住地，讓他去見。許孟容遜謝說：「我是個閑官，沒能力幫你。但是，你的心意，我記在心裏。」又看到李固言頭巾上的紙條，知道他忠厚。《太平廣記‧卷第一百八十<span lang="EN-US">‧貢舉三》</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">李固言未及第前，嘗從一古柳下行走，忽聞柳樹內有彈指聲，李固言大驚，急問是什麼。裏面應道：「吾為柳神九烈君，已用柳汁染了你的衣服。如果你果得藍袍，當以棗糕來祭祀我。「李固言依言照辦，不久就狀元及第。《三峰集》（藍袍是官服的意思）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">第二年許孟容做主考官，取李固言作狀元。《太平廣記‧卷第一百八十</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">‧</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貢舉三》</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">故事來源《太平廣記‧卷第一百八十</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">‧</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">貢舉三》</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">‧</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">《三峰集》</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://www.chance.org.tw//籤詩集/雷雨師一百籤/籤詩網‧雷雨師一百籤.htm"><br/></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="HEIGHT:18.15pt;">
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:18.15pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;HEIGHT:18.15pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="564">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 41;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊乙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.我曾許汝事和諧。<br/>2.誰料修為汝自乖。<br/>3.但改新圖莫依舊。<br/>4.營謀應得稱心懷。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">汝<span lang="EN-US">→果</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.我曾經答應你把事情弄好</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.誰料到你的行為違背因果</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.你要改過自新不要如以往（改變作風則能改造命運）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.這樣的話你的人生經營才能稱心如意啊</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.此為「警示籤」，由於當事者行為違背因果，所以神明就不幫你如願了。切記，神明只幫助好人而不會幫助壞人。所以，祈求神明協助者，一定要謹守</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=15247&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=15147"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:red;">五戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，並多行仁義，這樣的話神明才會暗中協助你如願 。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若是本身道德情操良好者，即使沒有求神，神明也會暗中相助，就如籤詩故事中的董永故事一樣。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.求得本籤者，應該改過向善，多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，若能如此，則所求之事即能順遂，並得神明暗中相助。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求姻緣來，請先端正自己的德行，多行善事，若能如此，神明即能暗中安排。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若心儀的對象問可否追求？ ◇當前交往對象問未來前途？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想追求當前喜歡的他，那你先要培養個良好的涵養，並且多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這對於你的追求就有加分的功效。若想未來愛情前途順遂者，也是一樣。另外，請多多充實</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，這對你的愛情是有幫助的。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手者<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>◇或愛情困頓者</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當愛情分手了或是困頓不前了，你當好好圖改自己不好的個性，且要懂得關懷對方、讚美對方，這能增加你們的感情。若你</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">他的話，更應該展現無私與包容，若你能這樣改造自己的話，那愛情就能有所起色。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">請多多充實</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，以幫助你扭轉愛情。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作者，若想工作更順遂的話，你應該換個工作態度。若能把這份工作當作是做義工的話，那就不會抱怨了。若想業績更好的話，那請補修</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">學分。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><br/>若問事業經營者，若想獲利更多的話，不僅要圖改經營上不好制度與作風，且要展現奉獻、服務大眾的精神來經營，若你願意這樣圖改自己的話，那事業就能穩定發展了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、升遷、求官、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問找工作（升遷、求官、創業）者，首先要圖改自己不好的態度、觀念與個性，更要持守</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:#24878c;">戒行</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，若能如此的話，神明也會暗中助你找到工作（升遷</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、求官、創業</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）。請為自己加油，好好的改造自己，讓別人看出你的不一樣，若能如此則謀望即能如願。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問換工作、換職業者，想必是你做的不順遂，所以想要換工作了。其實，你當更換的不是工作，而是自己的不好行為與個性，若你能這樣改造自己，那就可以不用更換工作了。建議在工作中多多廣結善緣，同時</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這有利你的工作發展的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種競試成果者，目前的各類考試成績不佳，但是，若你能多多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">與培養自己良好的行為風範，不好的命運也是可以改造的。若你願意這樣圖改自己，心存善念，那神明也會暗中相助的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病者，只要修正自己不好的個性，即有治病功效。凡是內心有什麼不好的念頭，通通要除去。若能如此要求自己，這就是治病了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問投資理財者，若想在這方面獲利的話，應該改變你的經營模式，和一些不好的觀念，不好的操作習慣，通通把他調整過來，若能如此，這才有利理財。另外，個性也會影響操作，所以你當檢討自己有哪些不好的個性，若能將之調整，那就有利投資理財了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆房地產買賣<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問房地產買賣者，自己的買賣行為與心態，應該導正過來，若能如此則有利你的買賣成交。若想在這方面獲利的話，那你更應該</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，只要你願意這樣修正自己，那對於這些買賣就有利了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想求孕或生子的話，那你當先端正自己的行為與個性，若能如此的話，則能助你懷孕。若期望是生兒子者，更應該</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這才能為願望加分。若你願意這樣圖改自己的話，那神明也會暗中相助。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆官司訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問官司者，由於行為違背因果、違背道義，因此惹上官司。建議你面對這官司的判決，若你能表示懺悔之心，則能獲得輕判。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">神許和合。自乖所為。急須更變。方得其宜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>心行正直。無好自欺。若能悔過。天必相之。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只好從新莫依舊。自然百事稱心神。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>莫愁中路無成就。當遇舟航涉利津。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<br/>改舊從新別有因。莫乖行止拂天神。<br/>管教中路多成就。穩趁舟航涉利津</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜更改。問婚當有再合之意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟宜和。利吉。孕生男。求利改圖方好。病更醫。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名未遂。凡事更改方稱意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事只當遷改。不可蹈襲故常。積弊至蟲。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利未遂。若因改圖。庶幾提攜。有人向之。自乖者今得寧矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">營謀或作榮華未妥。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜反己問心。毋乖神意。恐有惡事惡念。急須改悔。前次所謀不合。從此更新整頓。自有稱心之時。若怙惡不悛。及畏難苟安者。則無濟也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">前事見許。本有機緣。修為自乖。所謀欠妥。改新圖。另作計較。莫依舊。戒勿因循。營謀稱心。往者可復。失者可追。否則可泰也。凡事去舊從新之象。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生久困。科場不利。占此遂改武學。後奉旨文料。中武生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人此生竟聯捷。成文進士。應改圖而遇。仍獲所求也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">董永賣身<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">漢。董永。千乘人。年少時失去母親，獨自養父親，流浪到孝感（地名）。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">父亡沒錢安葬，就向人借錢一萬，日後無錢還，賣身作奴隸。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">董永安葬父親後，在路上遇到一婦人，和董永結婚為夫妻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">債主令董永要織縑布三百疋來償債，一個月就織好了。後來其妻告辭董永要離去。妻子說，我是天上的織女，因為你很孝順，<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">所以玉帝令我助你償債。說完，升空而去。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">班定遠投筆從軍</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">班超（</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">32</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年－</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">102</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年），字仲升，扶風平陵人，東漢班彪之子，班固之弟。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">班超小的時候家裡很貧窮，所以他常常要替官廳抄寫文件，來獲得一些微薄的酬勞維持家用，抄書的工作既無聊，而且也沒有什麼前途，時間久了以後班超開始感到非常疲累，所以常常嘆氣。有一天正在寫字的時候，他突然把筆丟在地上，嘆息著說：「大丈夫就算沒有別的志向，也應當仿效傅介子、張騫那樣的英雄，他們都是到遠地發展，立下了很大的功勞，最後得到了朝廷封賞的爵位，我又怎麼可以長久在筆墨間討生活呢？」他旁邊的人都取笑他不自量力，但他並不放在心上。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來，班超果然被派出使西域，他發揮了最大的智慧和勇敢，先後降服了西域五十多個國家，因為功勞很大而被封為定遠侯。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解籤範例<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤意味著，當你出外旅遊時，要注意自己的行為不可違背因果，不可違背安全守則，心念要維持正念、善念，若你能堅守這些原則，那就安全了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 42;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊丙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一紙官書火急催。<br/>2.扁舟速下浪如雷。<br/>3.雖然目下多驚險。<br/>4.保汝平安去復回。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.來自官方的文件，火速催急著。（比喻此事有著催促之感）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.乘著小舟速去處理，但是潮浪的聲音如雷。（比喻勢單力薄又逢局勢驚危）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.雖然眼下看起來有多麼驚險。（此事令人感到驚險）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.但是保證讓你平安往返（終渡難關）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事、各種謀求，在神明的庇祐下，有驚無險，逢凶化吉。本籤代表終究能度過難關。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前愛情前途？</span><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇或問喜歡的對象能否有好發展？</span><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤代表此愛情的道路令人倉皇無措之感，總讓人感覺愛情就要失去似的，而過程中難免有分手疑慮，或</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">看起來似乎是障礙的因素，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">但是經過多時的經營，與智慧的化解，最後終究能化險為夷。建議堅定你的方向，以讓你的愛情走的更穩定。</span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">或問分手的愛情能否挽回？</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇或愛情困頓者</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你當前的愛情處境是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">倉皇無措的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，有分手疑慮，但是這個困境是可以化解的。請多些智慧與</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=14559&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=14531"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真愛</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，必能脫離困境。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問求職者，當前看起來工作不好找，其實問題並不難，就在這慌亂的情景下，你還是能找到工作。請繼續加油。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業工作<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問工作或事業前途者，這是個有風險的工作或事業，經營起來起落不定，讓人心驚膽跳，但是只要以智化解，多求神明，則能安然脫離各種危險，而達到獲利目標。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、競試、選舉<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問各種競試成果者，此次的競試看起來很危險，但是這是「有驚無險」，最後仍然脫穎而出。但是，這次的競爭恐讓人累出病來。若所問屬於政治選舉者，當防與人口角紛爭。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問投資理財者，這次的投資是有風險性的，也會讓人心情驚恐的。雖然最後能獲利，但卻因此嚇得一身病。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆房地買賣<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問買賣房地產者，過程中會出些狀況，但是事後終能化解。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"><br/>代表求孕過程有些風險，但終究能化險為夷，而後如願得孕。（若懷孕期間，建議誦持</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=5144">《觀世音菩薩普門品》</a>以保平安。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">急症、新病者能度過難關而痊癒。若屬於慢性病者，可以度過難關，但只是暫時，而後續治療則要靠自己。（建議以修行來治療慢性病，方有痊癒可能。)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種官司結果者，這次的訴訟看起來很驚險，但是最後則是「有驚無險」，終於平安化解了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官書火急。激聒之兆。目下雖驚。終無紛擾。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>有神陰扶。收功談笑。來往平安。吉星高照。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">高<span lang="EN-US">→拱</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先驚未是驚。後喜方為喜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問謀事多。連綿無定止。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先凶後吉者。謀望終有好處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病者虛險。自然解散。大事成。求官遂。問訟好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚姻不難。失物還。行人至。凡事大吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">火急催者。王有激聒。是非占者。目下驚恐。到後無事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">新病易療。久病難保。凶事化吉。大事變小。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求名利者。有疾病是非之累。方應其占。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">而得選舉。否則難遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">回字或作來字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先凶後吉。若問謀望。自有好處。病者慮險。自有解脫。訟事驚惶。漸得安泰。宦途主有風浪。終不為害。凡事存心。默仗神祐獲吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一紙官書。乃系衙門公事。火急催者。急如星火也。浪聲如雷。江行驚險之狀。保汝平安。遇險不為害也。去復回。言去來得以自由。終獲安貞之吉矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生會試。值以人命搆訟所阻。占得此後。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">司憲見而奇之。許令應試。遂中。春榜全詩皆應。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此占。凡問病無有不療者。惟<span lang="EN-US">(清)道光(年)間。一人患中瘋症。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此後。雖平安。但病根終不能除耳。是去復回。句之應也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">玄德公黃鶴樓赴宴<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。劉備，字玄德。獻帝時，周瑜為了奪取荊州，邀請劉備過江赴宴，劉備知其有詐，不敢前往，孔明派趙雲隨行，並交給他一支內藏錦囊妙計的竹筒，囑咐他臨危開看，可保無事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉備與趙雲一同過江之後，周瑜在黃鶴樓設宴款待，席間，周瑜和趙雲因荊州之事，口角相爭，劉備勸解無效，周瑜一怒下樓，傳令不見令箭不得放走二人。趙雲見狀，知事態嚴重，只得打開竹筒錦囊，見內藏周瑜令箭一支，此乃孔明借東風時所用，如今，正好讓劉備與趙雲逃出黃鶴樓，待周瑜得知，追之不及，劉備與趙雲早已安然返回。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陳平亡歸漢<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陳平，漢初陽武人。在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">秦末時，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A1%B9%E7%BE%BD" title="項羽"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">項羽</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%88%98%E9%82%A6" title="劉邦"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">劉邦</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">起兵反秦，陳平毅然從戎投奔到項羽麾下而稍器重，卻又因事受牽連而被項羽下令追殺</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:blue;">一紙官書火急催</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他又改投奔劉邦時，曾在小船上差點遭強盜打劫</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:blue;">扁舟速下浪如雷</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來雖然迭遇兇險。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:blue;">雖然目下多驚險</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">而皆以智計化解。最後安全來到劉邦營中</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:blue;">保汝平安去復回</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">協助劉邦打敗項羽而得了天下。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 43;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四四籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊丁<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.汝是人中最吉人。<br/>2.誤為誤作損精神。<br/>3.堅牢一念酬香願。<br/>4.富貴榮華萃汝身。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你是大眾中的大好人（你是個好好先生，你是個最好命的人…）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.由於錯誤的認知而做錯了事情而損傷精神。（一時做錯了決定）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若能堅心悔過並行善，以酬報你的願望。（堅持原來的道路）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.則能榮華富貴能聚集在你身上。（即能順遂）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.由於一時的錯誤行為，而導致做錯了事情而遭惹困擾。若能悔改則名利雙收。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.應堅持原來的道路繼續前進，此刻不要隨意改變。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.由於一時糊塗而做錯事，而導致精神損傷，但是只要懺悔己過，並多行善事，則人生即能好命運。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.當前所做的決定或已作的行為，是個錯誤的決定，只要將之改過來，那就能前途看好。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.停下當前的謀求即能順遂</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.一心堅持原有，則是最佳前途。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:-11.9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問現在心儀的對象可否追求？若現在想要求姻緣可否？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤代表不宜，你應該等待，則未來有更理想的對象。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:-11.9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問想要和當前交往的對象分手好否？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這是個錯誤的決定，你應堅持原來的對象，這就能有好前途。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:-11.9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前愛情前途？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若能堅持此愛，不要有所改變，則能有好結果。</span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:-11.9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問愛情挽回？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">由於一時的錯誤而導致愛情分手，你應當向對方道歉認錯，若能如此，則能挽回愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:-11.9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，已有情人者，堅持此愛。尚無對象者，則應等待。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、轉換等各種改變<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你目前的職務（職位）、工作，算是大眾中最好的。而你當前決定要做的轉變，此會損傷你的精神，若能將之調整過來，則能前途順遂。若想要改變，則應等待時機。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前可否投資、創業？此籤代表當前各種改變和謀求都不宜。若能等待，則未來更有利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不要給予各種藥物或治療，以免多做多錯，越療越糟糕。可以祈神庇祐。若是慢性病，在此建議走修行路線，則有益一切。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心行平等。反誤為非。急宜改過。切莫自欺。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>盡誠作福。神必佑之。榮華富貴。付汝非遲。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">萬事皆從忙裏錯。但將心地細思量。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若能謹守無他望。可保終身大吉昌。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">無望<span lang="EN-US">→祈神佑</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤防有橫逆事。若能改過。則吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事且也不宜躁進。訟莫作。利未有。婚莫求。病禱神。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人未歸。悔過名利雙全也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉人善人也。言人雖善。作事狂謬。所輔非人。作為皆誤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但能堅心向善。謹而行之。則富貴可得。終身榮華矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者不宜欺妄輕躁。先自知戒。可免其悔。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求財無利。求名未亨。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">萃字或作在字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤本非惡人。卻有惡事。當由見識不明。及被人引誘所致。未免得罪神明。速宜悉心懺悔。力持善願。以冀感應。將來富貴有准。榮華可期。唯在一念挽回。毋終執迷自誤也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉人。善人也。言此人向本善良。現在作為皆錯。損精神。所圖無益。只害自身也。堅牢一念。戒占者即宜回心向善。酬香願。言善功久積。心願可酬也。富貴榮華。前因過誤削除。後此善願堅牢。仍萃於一人之身矣。轉禍為福。明者悟之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生本富人子。性傲不敬其父。屢中副榜。占得此籤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">改悔行孝。父子俱安。享壽以終。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">倘不能改。豈惟不中。禍將不免矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">全詩之意。顯然能改過勝酬香願矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又咸豐間。郡西華仕舖。端許節。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">土著循俗。例迎木刻龍頭。與東佛舖民口角。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">邑尊聞知。飾差嚴拿該舖。惟奇仕官香火甚盛。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">老尼有錢怕累。因到廟占此。迨事情完局。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">富貴之家。分文不肯看破。衙行賠禮等費。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">悉萃老之身。第四句之驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王莽篡漢<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">王莽字巨君。漢朝孝元皇后的姪子。以國戚身份全家富貴顯赫。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莽繼承叔父當成、哀、平帝時的大司馬，三位皇帝都在位不久。王莽位居宰相，又封新息侯。假裝施行仁義，仿傚周公輔成王。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">平帝死後，立孺子嬰為帝。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">王莽偷學周公的法，主政改年號。竟然篡漢，國號新。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後被漢兵所殺。傳說首都百姓，爭吃他的肉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">留侯博浪椎</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張良，字子房，封為漢留侯，諡號文成。漢初名臣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張良本是韓國公子，秦滅韓後，張良為了要為韓報仇而散盡家財求得一大力士</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">相助</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，用一百二十斤的大鐵椎，伏擊行刺秦始皇於博浪沙（今河南原陽縣），卻擊中副車而未獲成功。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 44;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.好將心地力耕耘。<br/>2.彼此山頭總是墳。<br/>3.陰地不如心地好。<br/>4.修為到底卻輸君。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.努力的修好自己的「心」</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若是彼此對立總是不好的。（彼此對立或劃分山頭，這都是畫地自牢）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.祖墳風水好不如心地好（心地好比較重要）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.修行好反而受委屈</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤是「好心沒好報，人善被人欺。」的寫照。但是，這只是一時，因果到了最後還是要擺平一切。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（道行好的人常常是屈居下風<span lang="EN-US">–人善被人欺。但是你要知道</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:maroon;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=17464&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=17431"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">退步原來是向前</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:maroon;">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">正直忠義之人，容易遭殺害。小人反而能得志，此話即是這個意思。但是堅持道行，最後必能脫穎而出，而小人只是一時得意罷了。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.各種事情的進退，取決於天理（以因果法則為依歸），即使因此遭受侵害，也不要放棄這個原則。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.堅持出污泥而不染</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.雖然你的德行好，是個善好之人，但是別人可能對你無禮、無理，這是你當要有的心理準備。堅持此德，將來勢必有善報。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、學業、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作或學業前途，此籤提醒把心地修好來，不要與人對立畫分山頭。在工作上表現好、做人好、心地好，而沒有得到應有的待遇時，你也不要因此退縮，你還是要堅持這個良好的道行。在學校或職場上與人相處時，把自己品德做好來，雖然可能發生「人善被人欺」之處境，你還是要堅持這份德行。總之，「人在做天在看」，老天爺總不會虧待你的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求財、求功名、投資<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求財謀利、求功名等類問題，此籤詩提醒，心地好比什麼都重要，只管修持自己的心，而沒有必要與人爭名奪利，平常多多行善積德，這才是人生最重要的課題。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情前途發展者，即使本身條件很好，是個好丈夫或賢妻，但是，即使無人欣賞，你也不要氣餒，你當「寧缺勿濫」，而不要隨意降低自己的人格而去追求人品差的對象。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若對方條件上，品德很好時，你當堅守這份愛情而不要輕易放棄。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若已經分手者想要挽回者，或雙方鬧僵者，彼此對立不語總不是辦法，應該試圖去化解這個僵局，多多在道行上提升自己，若能如此，則有利愛情。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若無對象求姻緣者，或者喜歡一個人想要追求者，你應先把自己人品修好來，而目前先不必急著追求，應當把心思花在修行上，以期待將來好姻緣出現時，能有好的結局。但是，即使你的道行很好，是個好丈夫或賢妻，對方不見得會賞識，這是你要有的心理準備。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，你的條件可能很好，但是對方不見得會賞識，這顯然你們的緣分不是很好，或是對方沒有眼光，既然如此的話，分手有必要挽回嗎？這是你可以思考的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想治病，只要把心地修好，該好的病自然會好。不與人爭，不與人計較，不懷恨，不結怨仇，心情平靜，若能如此，就算有病也自然能痊癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想治病者，請走修行路線。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉變、換職、各種改變、各種謀求<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種改變或謀求，籤詩提醒，你當把心思放在「修心」上，這才是你需要進行的轉換。若這點能做好，那當前的換職等謀求就不重要了。若你能這樣轉變自己，把自己道德做好來，那自然在工作上能獲得更多好處。就算沒有得到好處，這也沒有關係，因為這份修行的功德是不會流失的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆衝突、摩擦、交友<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若在這方面出問題者，你當以「德」為著眼點作為處理這件事情的原則。各種事情盡量和平解決，不用計較輸贏得失，儘管以最高品德要求自己。即使發生「狗咬呂洞賓」事件，你也不用氣餒。總之，藉這個機會修行就對了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">千求萬求，不如求自己有個好德行，此籤的意思是要當事者放棄這些祈求，而要把注意力放在道行上，因此，只要你能隨時行善積德，那就比懷孕生子更有價值了。雖然世俗人對於好人、有道行的人總是任性無禮，但是這也是讓你修行的課題，只要你堅持這份德行，那你就是「出污泥而不染的淨蓮」了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好修心地。莫用他求。但依本分。可獲天庥。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>勿與人競。福力自優。子孫之慶。皆善之由。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人己初來用意同。好將心地問天公。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若還虧卻分毫理。萬事教君吉又凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">初來<span lang="EN-US">→營謀</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不可妄求。但依本分。方得天之祐庇。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問地利。不宜遷改。行人必至。病則安。求財無。且宜守舊。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必凶。宜和息。凡事只宜修積善心。庶免災禍也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人之名勢凌逼。我固不能勝彼。然不可處之太驟。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">惟務修為。天必佑之。而使輸於我。所謂卻輸君也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者貨財生殖。但當守舊。不可妄為。功名在後。方得榮華。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">風水不宜更改。雖好無益。終不如心地好也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事不可爭長競短。但修為以待之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤勸人竭力存心。中心為忠。如心為恕。凡事人己兩平。不可為損人利己。及欺心謀吉之事。心地好時。自沐天心庇蔭。發福悠長。彼謀吉者。欲得陰地。先損心地。計亦左矣。豈能及存心者之萬一乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心地。心中隱曲之處。力耕耘。如力田者之用意栽培也。山頭之墳。彼此皆係祖宗。不可侵害謀佔。陰地猶是地理。心地乃是天理。天理作主。地理隨之轉移。陰地不如心之地。彰彰明矣。修為。指耕耘心地者言。卻輸君。言不知存心者。未可同日而語也。善惡分途。吉凶自判。占者審之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生原籍江右。在南京應考。府縣俱取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人知而攻之。不得進院。占此遂往原籍。竟首取。係二句三句之驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(清)道光。戊戍。先嚴秋嵐公。將應院試。占此時。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">杜給諫胞弟。亦在廟求此籤。榜發先嚴與杜之弟。皆入邑庠。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">應彼此總是四字也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後先嚴中式。而杜以庠生終。并尾句亦應。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王錢謹識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">高祖遇丁公<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">丁公是楚國項羽的將軍，在彭城困住劉邦，兩方短兵相接，高祖（項羽）急著回頭說，兩個賢人難道要互相陷害嗎？丁公於是退兵。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">等到高祖登基，丁公來見。皇帝說丁公當臣子不忠，是讓項羽失天下的人，於是斬殺丁公。又說要警惕人臣不要效法丁公。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">丁公告高祖<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">喻世明言第三十一卷載。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">閻王殿上。丁公控訴曰。我在戰場包圍漢皇。項羽答應平分天下所以放走劉邦。劉邦稱帝後反殺害了我。漢皇（項羽）說，丁公背叛項羽所以殺他。丁公辯解說。<u>紀信</u>替皇帝死，卻不封贈。<u>項伯</u>不忠，反而封侯。雍齒也是項羽將軍，後封什方侯。漢皇無言辯解。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事三<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">夏侯嬰滕公居室<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">夏侯嬰，沛（治今安徽濉溪）人。漢之</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%AA%E4%BB%86" title="太僕"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">太僕</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉邦平定</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%A6" title="三秦"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">三秦</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後，夏侯嬰隨從漢王（劉邦）進軍</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BD%AD%E5%9F%8E" title="彭城"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">彭城</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，後來劉邦被項羽打得大敗，在逃跑的路上，遇到了</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BC%A2%E6%83%A0%E5%B8%9D" title="漢惠帝"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">漢惠帝</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">和</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%B2%81%E5%85%83%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB" title="魯元公主"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">魯元公主</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，夏侯嬰就把他們兩個帶上車，但是因為後面追兵緊隨其後，劉邦好幾次把他們兩個踹下車，但每次夏侯嬰都下車把他們再弄上來，一直把他們載在車上。劉邦為此非常生氣，有十多次想殺夏侯嬰。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">但最終還是逃了出來，把孝惠帝、魯元公主送到了</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B1%90%E9%82%91" title="豐邑"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">豐邑</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">夏侯嬰因功勞而被封為滕公，等到他去世將要安葬的時候，靈車尚未到墓地，拉車的馬便仆倒在地再也不往前走。派人在這裡往下挖掘，竟然挖到一個石屋。石屋中刻有銘文寫道：「佳城郁郁，三千年見白日，吁嗟滕公居此室！」</span><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">於是將滕公改葬在這裡。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 45;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四六籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊己<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.君是山中萬戶侯。<br/>2.信知騎馬勝騎牛。<br/>3.今朝馬上看山色。<br/>4.爭似騎牛得自由。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你是個地方的首長（富貴人家）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.相信你也知道騎馬比騎牛更有利</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.但是若騎馬游山玩水的話</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.這就不如騎牛這麼自由了</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇事不兩全，利弊一體，得之非福，失之非禍，若欲謀求，當行省思。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.此籤原意是，身分地位高的人，在處事上有贏人的地方，但是，也因此缺少自由，而不如百姓的消遙。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.此籤也是提醒人們可能發生「種芭蕉又怨芭蕉」的窘境。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.此籤也是告訴人們，事情總是沒有兩全，若是謀望如願時，你可能又後悔。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.此籤也代表，你當前想要做的事情，不見得做了就是好，也非沒做就不好。所以，事情當不當作，這是你自己要想清楚的。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若問愛情前途？<br/>那你要先想好，單身時渴望結婚，結婚時又渴望單身，這是人們常有的矛盾，因此，當你經歷愛情後，你可能發生這種矛盾。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若求問姻緣何時來？<br/>有了愛情雖好，但是也因此失去自由。沒有愛人雖然寂寞，但是卻更自由。在此兩者之間，你應該做好決定，以免將來後悔。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若問愛情挽回？<br/>這也是你要想清楚的，沒有愛人在身邊雖然寂寞，但是有了愛人卻常常要吵架，到底哪個好，這是你自己要設想好的。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、生子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這首籤詩也是提醒你，求之雖然可得，但是，有了孩子之後，你可能又後悔。若是經濟狀況不好者或沒能力養育孩子者，勸君打消這個念頭。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若是你在做健康檢查，沒檢查時擔心這可能是重病而憂心，若是檢查看到了結果，那你還是一樣擔心。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>建議好好修行以能養病，也建議放下對生命的執著，人當離去時，你就隨順接受。<br/>疾病，不療讓人擔心，而上醫院治療亦不見的會好，甚至更糟糕。所以，若尋求治病，這是你自己要想清楚的。（在此強烈建議，慢性病不要上醫院治療。請勤修行為上。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本自富貴。己勝常人。愈有愈貧。禍及自身。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>宜依本分。當享平和。勸君靜守。可免災罹。<br/>→<br/>本等富貴。己勝常人。愈有愈貪。禍及己身。<br/>宜依本分。當享和平。勸君靜處。可免災迍。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">要作惺惺成懞憧。誰知懞憧勝惺惺。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>多生巧計須成拙。守己方纔事有成。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">勝<span lang="EN-US">→作<br/>有成→稱心</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜守舊。不可妄作。遠行必有阻滯。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必凶。病多險。婚兩平。有是非。名利休問。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事不好。但安分方亨榮華。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">許君靜處安身。可免災禍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">萬戶侯。富貴人也。神言君固勝乎常人也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">今朝馬上看山色。亦只當如是。反涉險道心。多悒鬱。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">爭似騎牛得自由。不如安分守舊。則是非莫及。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寵辱不驚。享清修之福。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利婚姻諸事。交午字上可。丑字上大利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜守舊安享。自有山林之樂。不可貪求意外。如其不然。或嫌遲求速。或厭舊而喜新。或捨近而圖遠。或棄小而謀大。如騎牛者改換騎馬。及至騎馬。又想騎牛。懊恨躊躇。勢難中止。事貽伊戚耳。少年未經閱歷之人。每每似此。切宜戒之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">萬戶侯。富貴封王之。山中境遇。暢快者亦不減此。騎牛雖遲得安穩。騎馬雖速冒險阻。馬上看山。言捨安穩而就險阻。不自安常處順也。及至馳驟驚惶。勞苦困頓。不能收韁。卻想騎牛時。安步徐行。何等自在。然已追悔莫及矣。何如先時慎重。勿至輕舉妄動之為得哉。馬牛。或斷年月亦驗。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生丑年歲考三等。午年考優等。科舉省城。占此下第。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但生本貧士。邊方僻遠。盤費不資。大為所困。此不如騎牛之驗也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孤兒報冤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">孤兒即是春秋時代晉國的趙武也。歷史記錄他的父親趙朔，被屠岸賈所殺。趙朔妻子是晉成公姊。趙朔死後生下趙武，被追殺得很緊急。幸虧程嬰、公孫杵臼二人救了趙武。公孫杵臼抱假孤兒出面自首後又自殺。程嬰抱真正的趙氏孤兒，躲在山中十五年。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來，韓厥向晉景公報告，扶立趙氏後代即孤兒趙武。武就攻打屠岸賈，消滅屠家。報趙家之冤仇。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">馬伏波征蠻<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">馬援，字文淵，扶風茂陵（今<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%99%95%E8%A5%BF" title="陝西"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">陝西</span></a>興平東北）人，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89" title="東漢"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">東漢</span></a>著名的軍事家。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B1%89%E5%85%89%E6%AD%A6%E5%B8%9D" title="漢光武帝"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">漢光武帝</span></a>時，拜為伏波將軍，封<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%96%B0%E6%81%AF%E5%8E%BF" title="新息縣"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">新息侯</span></a>，世稱「馬伏波」。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">馬伏波在年高<span lang="EN-US">62歲的時候，有五溪蠻反叛，他就自請率兵前往討伐，但是皇帝以他年事已高而不准。於是，他就披甲上馬，據鞍顧盼，以示可用。他的這番老當益壯的豪氣，終於感動了皇帝，在「矍鑠哉！是翁也！」的讚美聲中，率師出征，最後死在軍中，終於以「馬革裹屍」而還。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td colspan="2" style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 46;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.與君萬語復千言。<br/>2.祗欲平和雪爾冤。<br/>3.訟則終凶君記取。<br/>4.試於清夜把心捫。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.給你說過多少話了（我一再給你交代這件事）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.只為了能得到和平和雪恥冤仇（若想和平了事的話）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若走訴訟則結局是凶，你當記住。（各種造作反是凶）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.請在清夜捫心自問，好好自我檢討。（還得自我反省、自我懺悔）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤精要：反思己過<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡是求得此籤者，諸事不宜，應停下各種作為，只能以平和的模式處事，並自我反省檢討、自我懺悔，若能如此，才能有好前景。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？請多多修持自己，持戒、行善、積德，以後再求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情能否挽回？若欲挽回、復合，請自我檢討為先，導致分手往往是自己有過，若自己不能改過的話，這又如何能恢復愛情。請展現你的「無私」與「真愛」，這才能挽回，對於你的愛情才有正面作用。只是不知你是否還有機會表現自己的「無私」與「真愛」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求，與某個對象能否有進一步發展？此有高攀之象。屬於此種問題者，當修正自己的行為，舉凡各種動作都要有涵養，對人要注意禮節，說話要有氣質，若能提升自己的德行，那你的謀求才有展望。若能這樣做的話，即使當前的追求不能成功，也能為未來奠定好姻緣的基礎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結，問愛情求得此籤者，都應自我檢討，反思己過，這才能改善愛情運。此籤也代表，若是雙方老是吵架的話，那結果就是「無緣的結局」。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">過多的醫療只是加重病情，此疾病當懺悔消業障，以便能減輕病苦。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子、求財、求功名、求職、各種謀求<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各種謀求，請先持守五戒，並行善積德，最好維持「正念」不要有邪思，而後再求，這才能成功。建議先修個一年，明年在求。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆更換、轉變、換職等各種轉換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">持戒行善，老實經營，勝過你的轉換。當前做的不好，或想轉變，因為你的「德行」不夠之故，因此，只要在這部份作提升，自然能越作越好或事事昌隆，而沒有必要轉換。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業，當自我檢討當前的事業，自己的能力是否足夠擔當，自己的德行是否有資格擔任這個職務。若能提升自己的德行與專業能力，則對自己事業有利。若是不能提升的話，那自己的職位就不保。請先從做人方面開始自已的提升，把人緣先做好，而後並提升專業能力。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟則終凶。不必多說。若得和平。舊冤可雪。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡所謀望。皆當謹節。反求諸己。禍端自滅。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">必<span lang="EN-US">→可</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心地好時身自吉。何須巧計去纘天。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>勸君靜處勤修省。禍及身來不可損。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不可妄意。切莫貪求。但要和平。冤自可雪。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀事有反覆。婚難成。久而後成。財莫貪。疾未安。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必凶。若有害人之意。反成殃也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戒人不可興訟。訟則終凶。不可成也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若能自處和平。則禍端自絕。冤抑可雪。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者凡事不可貪取。晝之所為。有一毫不善。清夜間。鬼神森列。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雖不以為禍。而禍自生矣。<span lang="EN-US">(豈)不戒哉。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤。凡事心氣和平。聽人勸阻。錯誤早悔。反自問己。毋使剛愎自用。怙過不悛。致成凶咎。訟事尤戒。雖有怕生冤抑。只宜平情解散則吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一而再，再而三地交待，以和平的方式處理，不可因為自認有理，就對簿公堂，只要以訴訟的方式處理，則必招來厄運，不可能有對自己有利的結果。不如自己平心靜氣下反問，也許會覺得有失公道，但不是自己認為的就是對的，只要早日打消訴訟的念頭，則早日去除厄運。不可急進，只宜退守，則不會有難。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一富人累為少年無賴所騙。不下百金。欲往訟之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占得此籤。乃清夜捫心。昔未富時。曾得一人數十金未償。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其人卒無後。記其死之日。即此人生之時也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乃驚悟。再與少年十餘金。約有死者兩倍之數目。此不復生端矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">楚漢爭鋒<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">項羽滅秦國，控制天下，自立為西楚霸王，封沛公劉邦為漢王。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">項羽在江南暗殺義帝。漢王（劉邦）就拜韓信當將軍，出兵攻楚，平定三秦地方，攻佔咸陽，為義帝辦理喪事，並責備項羽殺君之罪，與項羽戰於成皋、榮陽（地名）間。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">總共大戰三十餘回，小戰七十多次，互爭當皇帝五年。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">等到英布投降漢，范增貶死。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">西楚霸王</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">項羽才勢力單薄，而後被漢王（劉邦）消滅。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 47;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.登山涉水正天寒。<br/>2.兄弟姻親那得安。<br/>3.幸遇虎頭人一喚。<br/>4.全家遂保汝重歡。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">幸<span lang="EN-US">→不</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">遂<span lang="EN-US">→誰</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.登山涉水本是險，卻逢天寒增困難。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.如此際遇人不安，連累全家都心慌。（前兩句代表當事者所問之事目前處在困境中）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.幸遇貴人來呼喚，引導此事渡難關。（虎頭人就是你解開這個問題的關鍵，此貴人與「虎」有關）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.團圓和樂又相聚，順遂歡喜又安康。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤精要：困境當前，逢貴則安。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事、各種謀求，代表當前處在困境中，若要脫離難關，則需要有貴人指引或從中協助。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當遇到與人相逢時，他可能就是你的貴人，因此不能錯過。在貴人的指引和幫忙之下，這件事情可以脫離困境。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當有人找你要進行各種謀求時，此人就是虎頭人，也是你事情出發的關鍵點。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，求得此籤者，要期待的就是貴人（虎頭人）出現。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解：<span lang="EN-US"><br/>虎頭人：號召你的人，能讓你走出陰霾的關鍵人物，呼喚你要做某些事情的人，諸如此類之人都是本籤中的「虎頭人」。虎頭人通常是別人，但有時候，虎頭人就是自己。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇求得此籤者，代表當前愛情陷入困境，如何化解或挽回愛情呢？未來能有好姻緣嗎？或當前喜歡一個人，能否追求成功，有無緣份？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>諸如此類問題；這需要有貴人從中幫忙。因此，若與人相逢，他可能就是你的貴人，改造你的愛情運的關鍵人物，因此不能錯過這個。<br/>◇此籤代表，若欲挽回愛情者，需要有貴人幫忙，從中說說好話，以能化解。<br/>◇求姻緣者，需要有媒人介紹。心儀的對象想要追，也要有人從中引線。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結，貴人就是你解決這個問題的關鍵人物。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤代表你當前需要有工作或事業，因此，當有人邀你做事業時，或有人給你介紹工作時，此人就是虎頭人，這也是你從事事業的開始時刻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">虎頭人的範例如下：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一、這個<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1610070507364">範例</a>中的「老闆」就是虎頭人，所以可以去就職。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二、<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1006121905124">有朋友要找我做年底禮盒</a>，這個朋友也是虎頭人，所以可以去做生意。</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，若期望生命中多些貴人，請多多廣結善緣，常常助人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">歷涉艱難。時運輒左。家道不齊。事多坎坷。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>遇富貴人。提挈方可。倘無所濟。難逃後禍。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先難後易本天然。只恐勞心事不全。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若得貴人提挈處。管教騎鶴與腰纏。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只恐<span lang="EN-US">→幾度</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤家道不安。須防人口舌。怨恨臨門<span lang="EN-US">(怨恨本作孝眼。意不明)。財有失。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">逢貴人提挈方保。漸亨不成。多口舌。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問婚訟平。病有驚。財物耗散。名利空虛。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只宜守舊。不利遠行。防親人侵損也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">登山涉水。謂艱難也。姻親那得安。謂舉家多坎坷也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">虎頭。謂盧虞之姓。或云虎頭顧愷小字。得此三姓提挈。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利方遂。保汝重歡。謂失而復得。漸入佳景也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名。目下有阻。後方顯達。婚姻主妯娌乖張。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">家宅主兄弟分散。訟有驚。財有耗。守舊則害可免。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤景況艱難。人口欠安。凡事類多齟齬。倖轉眼之際。恰有一貴人從中得力。誠以指示迷途。須識機緣所在。悉心聽從。自得骨肉團圓。人情和合。凡謀遂意矣。否則倀倀然之。豈有安全。保聚之樂乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">登山涉水。謂涉歷艱難也。兄弟姻親。合內外言。那得安寧。內外不寧也。虎頭。謂盧虞之姓。或虔州處州上虞虞城各地名。一曰晉顧愷為虎頭將軍。應在顧姓。必得此人。為之喚醒。自保安泰。重歡。謂離者可使復合。失者可使復得，危者可使復安也。若遇此人。而不知省。則失之矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嘉靖間。上海城被倭寇番圍急。城中之人占此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不數日。果有盧參將統兵解圍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人官派築。占此得顯宦。顧姓者求解始免。俱應虎頭人一喚也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又晉江縣。謝生。光緒七年。科試場前占此。寅日發榜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">取列一等。遂補廩。查該生歲進科幫。是應保汝重歡四字也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">趙五娘尋夫<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">趙五娘。漢朝人。蔡伯階的妻子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">蔡伯階進京應試，及第後當「議郎」的官，就在京都另外成家，入贅牛相府。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">趙五娘在家克盡孝道奉養公婆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:14pt;">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來父母死了，為其辦理喪事。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時正逢荒災，趙五娘到京都尋夫，夫妻終於團圓。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竇長君至長安<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">西漢時，漢文帝的竇皇后有兄弟二人，兄長為竇長君，弟為竇廣國。廣國在四、五歲時，因家境貧困，被人</span>擄掠<span style="COLOR:black;">販賣到外地，渺無音訊。後又被人輾轉販賣了十幾戶人家，最後到了宜陽（今河南宜陽西），在那裏替人挖掘石炭。一天黃昏，山崖邊有一百多人在睡覺，山崖突然崩塌，睡在崖邊的人都壓死了，只有少君脫險逃生。沒幾天，他跟隨主人到了長安，在那裏他聽說新封的皇后姓竇，原籍在觀津。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">竇廣國離家的時候雖然年紀幼小，卻記得自己的籍貫和姓氏，還隱約記得與姊姊一起去採桑葉，從樹上摔下來的情景。他把這些事詳細的寫下來後，託人轉交給了竇皇后。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">竇后見到了這些資料後，把廣國召來並詳細問了其他一些情況，果然是她的親弟弟。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="COLOR:black;">此時竇后握著弟弟的手已經泣不成聲。竇后和兩個兄弟重逢後，就把他們安置在京師居住。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 48;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">四九籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊壬<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.彼此家居只一山。<br/>2.如何似隔鬼門關。<br/>3.日月如梭人易老。<br/>4.許多勞碌不如閒。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.雙方家居相近（相逢即是有緣，應當惜緣。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.何必見人如見鬼（若想萬事興旺，應當同心協力。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.歲月有限，光陰如梭，再不把握，則恐空過一生。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.做好人際，勝過逃避。過多轉變，只是徒勞。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心裡懷有某種不好的心態，以致事情受困，若能自我檢視，將這心態移除，那問題自然化解了<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前處於困境尋求轉變者，你所要轉變的不是事情，而是自己的「心態」。若心能轉善，則事自然也變善。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">與人相處當廣結善緣，珍惜當下，則能改造。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問姻緣何時來？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">姻緣就在你身邊，只是你沒有好好經營，若是再不努力經營話，人是會老的，到時候要求姻緣就更難了。在此提醒，若求姻緣不能太被動，而要有所作為，更應該提起勇氣去做。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情挽回<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤代表你應該好好的經營愛情，彼此不要嘔氣，任何相處上的摩擦、誤會、誤解，勢必要化解，以免活在不愉快的陰影中。因此，你當提起精神，以愉快的心情向對方示好，以化解這個僵局。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前沒有工作正在求職者，此籤代表你的工作就在你的居所附近，但是你不要嫌棄，因為工作難找，若是再挑剔工作的話，恐怕會成為無業遊民了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業前途<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若目前已經有事業者，此籤在於提醒，若想事業興盛，務必「家和萬事興」。<span lang="EN-US"><br>◇若是和他人合夥者，也是要意見統一，而能有展望。若是彼此有歧見，各不相讓的話，那事業就做不好了。<br>◇若是經營小店者，把人際做好，給客人好印象，多多服務客人，這就能增加生意。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇此籤詩只是暗示當事者當前的人際關係還要加強，以讓事業能做的更順遂。當事者只要把「做人」這門功課修好，那運途就不一樣了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆轉變、更換、換職等類問題</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若尋求轉變者求得此籤，此代表當事者人際關係不好，由於和大眾處的不好，因此想要更換，但是這樣勞途奔波的結果，只是增加疲勞而已。若當事者能在「做人」這領域提升，那是沒有必要更換的。</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆健康治病</span><span lang="EN-US"><br></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問治病者當注意，若是「心裡有鬼」、「心裡作祟」的話，那時日一久就會生病。自己內心懷有不健康的想法，這是你自己檢視可以發現的。若能將內心的「鬼」除去，這病自然會好。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">安閑易處。出門有阻。時迍易過。枉自勞苦。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>且宜守舊。隨分而處。運未亨通。不宜進取。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">處<span lang="EN-US">→去</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寄跡相親心不親。如何要作契深人。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>謀為動作皆無定。只恐虛名不得在。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寄人<span lang="EN-US">→形跡如親實不親。相看只作鏡中人<br/>在→真</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤事有阻滯。且隨緣分。切莫貪求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟宜和。病有祟。名利阻。問婚不和。家宅有難。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陰人有災。凡事防凶人中途侵害也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">彼此家居內外。一般也。兩山成出。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只有一山似隔鬼門關。有阻礙不得出也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">日月如梭。易催人老。勞碌無成。不如閒坐也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利皆迍。隨時修為。俟其自通。方可進取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚姻不成。家宅主陰人謀害。行人至途中侵損。切宜謹防。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者凡事守舊。為上策。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主情意隔角。不遇扶持。看似密邇相連。其實咫尺天涯。勢同秦越。智士知己知彼。捨此另投。或有遇合。若信。文貌周旋。口頭熱鬧。外密中疏。終鮮實際。不唯耽誤時日。更費趨候奔走之勞。此等人為世詬病久矣。奈何其弗之省也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">彼此家居。誼屬鄰里。只一山。過從甚便也。鬼門關。言其肝膽隔別。不啻陰陽分界也。歲月如梭。言盼望無期。空自遲誤。許多勞碌。言所倚非人。所謀非計。枉受奔波之累。則何如識透人情。消閒自在。其不綽綽然有餘裕哉。戒占者勿妄交。勿枉己。勿輕信。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人居住省城。欲往外驟生理。占此。人以籤不吉。止之不聽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">離家只四十里。在外終日忙碌。無人可安。三年不得回。竟卒於外首。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">二住之驗也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又光緒<span lang="EN-US">(年)間。桐郡。鄭姓有子。染病延醫。許氏服藥未效。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有人薦一何姓老醫。其父遲疑莫決。占此乃信。必託與高年者。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竟不數日而愈。益恍然於。如何似人易老許不如。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此九字。儼若為斯人作焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">張子房遁跡<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">漢朝。張良，字子房。韓國人。祖先五代當韓國宰相。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">秦國滅韓國，張良散家財躲藏，想為韓國報仇，派大力士暗藏鐵錐，在博浪沙（地名）擊殺秦始皇，卻誤中副車。秦始皇全天下通緝張良，找了十個月都抓不到。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">張良後來佐助漢王平定天下，功成不管世事。傳說與赤松子學神仙。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 49;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">五十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戊癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上平→上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.人說今年勝舊年。<br/>2.也須步多要周旋。<br/>3.一家和氣多生福。<br/>4.萋菲讒言莫聽偏。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">舊<span lang="EN-US">→去</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">周<span lang="EN-US">→週</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若要今年比去年更好（若要事情更好的話）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.也需要更多的經營和措施（需要更多的努力與付出）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.家和萬事興，意和同事順。（把人際、人緣搞好，這就比去年好的秘訣）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.別人說的話不管是好是壞，都不要聽偏了。（與人相處時言語上不要隨著他人言語起舞）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若要比以前更好，若要成功，則須更多的付出，更多的努力。<br/>2.不管是職場或是家庭，把人際相處做好來，有助凡事的改善。<br/>3.若閒話當前時，或不樂聽之言面臨時，則應鎮定。若是讚美之言降臨時，不要得意失形。（同一句話每個人的解讀都不同）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.本籤的重點在於</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=69"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">提昇人緣</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，若能如此則「</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">今年勝舊年</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若期望在愛情上有所收穫、進展、情人挽回、夫妻挽回諸如此類問題者。愛情是不會平白變好的，因此更多真愛情操表現這是你需要做的，你當表現的自已的優點、真情，表現自己是個好丈夫（賢妻），若你願意這樣經營，則能如願得到愛情的果實。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想考試上榜，或考的比去年更好，更須要加把勁，用功讀書，則可望成功。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">欲知工作、事業前途，只要在本業上更努力經營，有更好的措施，並把人際（人緣）關係弄好，可望有輝煌的成果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若想更換職業者，其實，你當在人際相處上努力，若能與人和諧，那這份工作就能做得愉快，那就不會想要換工作了。另外，若你能在這份工作上認真，那業績就會好，業績既然好那收入就會多，若能如此，那就不用換工作了。建議在工作中</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=69"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">提昇人緣</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀望勝先。進取攸利。人事周密。禍消福至。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>勿信讒言。惶惑思慮。慎終如始。切莫猶豫。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">先<span lang="EN-US">→前<br/>進利→卻宜進取<br/>密猶豫→旋顛墜</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此心有主何憂懼。須管今番勝舊番。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>婦人言語君休聽。家道興衰在此間。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此番<span lang="EN-US">→剝復亨迍遞往還。今番管許勝前番</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大吉。富貴榮華。門庭興旺。見喜添丁。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但謀事要和合。莫信讒言。只宜保守。方得安樂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">出入吉。財可求。婚可結。行人至。病得痊。訟宜和。百事亨泰也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名未遂。若謀為他事。今春頗勝。如不能周旋。亦只是去年榜樣也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">周旋謂進步。要慎審的。蓋作事須要周旋也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">卜者。得之人事。能周旋。則一家之內。禍災消滅。和氣自生矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫聽偏者。戒人不可聽信讒言。以致惶惑也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主年運亨通。時和歲稔。家旺人興。然修身乃齊家之本。禮教實門內之防。必須周規折矩。仁讓雍雍。方遂和平之福。更忌婦人搬弄。宵小離間。是為萋菲讒言。不可偏聽。斯家道成而流澤長矣。凡事謹慎和平則吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><span style="">    </span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">今年勝去年。人事漸漸順利。步步循規矩。舉動不可疏虞。和氣致福。須宜妻子。睦兄弟。感召吉祥。讒言莫聽。須存見解。厚包容。慎防偏倚。凡事盡人事以應天時則可。恃天時而廢人事。則不可。可不慎諸。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人惑妻言。欲與弟分家。占此感悟。依舊同居。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後其弟遠商獲利數萬。與兄同享。數世安居。第三句驗甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又鯉城。郭補卷與余總角交也。庚寅病重。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其弟以年近五旬。且身體素弱。非溫補不宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">余薦種禾堂醫士。吳和。尚舍力。用清涼。闔家訝焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此服之。火候始見。竟以和藥奏功。亦第三句之驗也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竹坪又識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蘇東坡勸民<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">宋朝。蘇軾，字子瞻，號東坡居士。當杭州太守。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">饑荒之年，蘇勸民平穩物價，並且打開倉庫救濟。又派人四出治病，救活萬人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有逋</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">欠</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">稅不交的人，軾叫他來問。他回答賣涼扇謀生。天寒難賣，不是故意欠稅。軾令取廿多柄扇來，蘇軾在扇上寫字，及畫枯木竹石。賣者拿出，眾人爭相用千文錢要買一扇也搶不到，還光欠稅。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">牛宏不聽射牛<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">牛宏，隋朝鶉觚地方人。本姓寮，魏時賜姓牛，隋初當秘書監，後又當吏部尚書，又封奇章群公，史稱大雅君子，平生愛惜牛，所到之處不許百姓鞭殺生牛。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 50;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">五一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">己甲<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.君今百事且隨緣。<br/>2.水到渠成聽自然。<br/>3.莫嘆年來不如意。<br/>4.喜逢新運稱心田。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 21pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事情你就隨緣（隨順因緣，事要你進你就進，事要你退你就退，這就是隨緣）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 21pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若能如此則事情能順利發展（水到渠成）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.不用感嘆過去幾年的不順遂 （困境已過）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.現在新的運勢已經降臨了（新運稱心）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事、各種謀求<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">谷底已過，陰霾已散，好運將來，隨順因緣，聽其自然，漸入佳境，新運稱心。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問各種愛情問題，低迷的氣氛即將逝去，你們將漸入佳境。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若有心儀的對象，可以追求，而有成績。若是別人追你，你就隨緣接受。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若想挽回，現今開始可以進行，得以復合。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若交往多年者，想要結婚則可論及婚假。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？就要來了，你就隨順因緣，姻緣會自己來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">為了讓愛情更甜蜜，請加強愛情學分。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使過去考的不好，而今已不同以往，今後各種考試都可以嘗試，只要不懈怠，那各種考試都將如願。在此恭喜！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使過去已經求職多時未果，如今氣象已不同已往，只要認真點，則可找到喜歡的工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕、求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雖然過去用過各種方法沒有成功，而今只要隨順自然，即能如願懷孕。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建議：再</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=5144"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">以《觀世音菩薩普門品》為功課</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">則效果更好，能生福德、智慧之男女。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業、轉換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">即使過去至今曾經不順利，而讓你想要轉換，其實，谷底已經過了，接著下來就是漸入佳境的時刻了。新的運途，會讓你稱心如意的。你就隨順新的機緣而走即可。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">由於過去事情不順，心情不好，以致身體累積了一些疾病，而今後命運漸入佳境，當各種運途順遂之後，心情也好轉了，身體上的一些大小毛病，不用吃藥也可以自己痊癒了。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>心情是會影響身體健康的，所以往後要注意調適自己的心情。<br/></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目下謀望。且隨緣分。一朝榮達。身顯如願。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>休自嗟怨。待時遷變。漸遇亨通。好事疊見。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生勞碌不曾閒。也是心緣倍累關。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>漸遇亨通有生意。後來容易嘆先難。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有生意→堪稱意<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤好事重重。名利漸達。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">財緩發。婚可定。行人有信。病漸安。訟得理。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">時運亨泰。孕生貴子。風水合利。自有稱心之望也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目下功名謀為。多不如意。且隨分而行。所謂莫歎不如意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">以後來極容易者也。直須交運眼。或交節候。自然漸亨。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">重重好事。稱吾心田。占此大抵先否後泰。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤暫時安分。後此漸有機緣。不求自至。切勿因近年謀為不遂。常自嗟嘆。人事有得有失。命運有否有泰。一到亨通之時。名成利就。自有吐氣揚眉之日也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">百事隨緣。言目下聽天安命。不用強求。水到渠成。言水勢所到之處。自成溝渠。原係自然之理。非人力所能逮也。前不如意。往事困頓之境。喜稱心田。後此行運之時。凡事不可欲速。久久自有成就。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人占得此籤。屢涉江湖不利。一人解之自君命。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">日子屬土。以水為財。四柱無水。屢行不遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三年之後行癸水。自當大發。其後果然。應水到渠成。喜逢新運之驗也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">御溝流紅葉<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝。宣宗宮內。韓夫人不受寵幸。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">偶而在紅葉上題詩一首，流出皇宮水溝外。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一應試官人，顧況</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">于佑</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在皇宮水溝外，拾得紅葉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">葉上題詩：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">流水何太急。深宮盡日閒。殷勤謝紅葉。好去到人間。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">顧況拾到紅葉。開玩笑應和紅葉詩：</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">愁見鶯啼柳絮飛。上陽宮女斷腸時。君恩不禁東流水。葉上題詩寄與誰。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">也從皇宮水溝中把紅葉流進去，天子知道此事，就把韓夫人嫁與于佑，夫婦百年偕老。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
