UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚甲<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.嘯聚山林兇惡儔。<br/>2.善良無事苦煎憂。<br/>3.主人大笑出門去。<br/>4.不用干戈盜賊休。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.遇到盜賊、小人、惡人侵害。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.善良的人沒事卻擔心煎熬（比喻不用窮擔心）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.主人卻大笑視若無事出門去。（輕鬆生活即可）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.不用武力就把盜賊解決了。（不用比試、鬥爭，這個苦惱、問題自然解決了）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點：這事不必窮擔心，勢必沒事，。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.最近發生受惡人侵害等令人擔心之事</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.是善良之人故能逢凶化吉，因此免擔憂。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.此事可以安心，如常作息。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4守護神暗中相助，故禍害、障礙自消除。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5.忠直之人，往往人善被人欺，但是善神保佑，故能逢凶化吉。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？你當開開心心的出門到處走走，這才能遇到姻緣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前認識的對象可否進一步發展？或問當前喜歡的對象、暗戀的對象能否成為愛人？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>本籤代表，你要放輕鬆生活，你要是追的越勤，他就越不在乎你，你越是不理他，他反而會著急，反過來會找你。所以你就「欲擒故縱」、「愛理不理」應對即可。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若交往多年者，問可否結婚者，<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若愛人、夫妻，已分手或將分手，感情有阻或欲求挽回者，你就當做沒事、無所謂、不在乎，照常生活作息，找空彈琴唱歌，此問題自可化解。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若尋求愛情者，在此提醒，追的太緊、愛的太黏，會讓人喘不氣來，而有反效果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這個考試競爭激烈，令人擔心。但是，「主人大笑出門去」也意味著，你就開開心心的出門去吧，「不用干戈盜賊休」代表這個競爭就不用比試了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若很在意這個考試者，請平常心應試，依正常作息讀書，不要熬夜苦讀，以輕鬆的心情應考。但是，這些日子要多做功德，多求神明庇祐。如此應對，可以提升考運，化險為夷。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職，請放輕鬆心情去應對，若面試時要表現得開朗大方、笑容可掬，那就能輕鬆的錄取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆離職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若當前工作有困境想要離職者，此籤詩代表職場內多有惡人、小人，相處不易，善良之人容易遭受欺負，因此，只要大笑離職去，那問題就解決了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">惡疾當前，令人擔心，但是不療反而更好，療的越多，傷的越重。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">請放輕鬆心情，找空彈彈樂器，唱唱歌，心情輕鬆了，則有助康復。若越擔心反而加重病情。找空開心的出門去旅遊（主人大笑出門去），若能如此應對，反而能康復（不用干戈盜賊休）。屬於腫瘤之類疾病者，更是該如此應對。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">惡少操心。欲害良善。彼何能為。徒逞強健。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>君子善勝。收功不戰。有神相之。陰消禍變。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心→戈<span lang="EN-US"><br/>有神→神明</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心驚如踏一層冰。長敬番成度量生。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>一葦一航波浪足。駸駸喜色藹門庭。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">長生→戒懼何憂險阻深<span lang="EN-US"><br/>足藹→定靄</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主有驚險。防小人侵害。若能守性存善。卻有德曜及身。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">神明助之。陰消禍變。病恐險。訟必散。財平平。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚宜審。凡事有陰。及後平和。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">灌嬰將兵擊尉陀。人民驚恐。神在南越山上。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">告將軍曰。干戈不動。而盜賊遽休。後果奏凱。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此主小人侵害。事多驚恐。若能修福。則惡不能侵害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">危病小口<span lang="EN-US">(心)無事。家主見凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事先憂後喜。名利險中可得。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主道途驚險。小人侵害。唯是善良之人。遇凶不凶。遇險不險。則意外憂懼。彈琴可以解圍。焚香可以卻敵。彼自談笑。賊已遁逃。非所謂吉人天相者乎。凡事凶中得吉。陰蒙神祐。當益勉之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嘯聚山林。乃是盜賊當前為患。凶惡可知。善良。循理守分之人。無事煎憂。言冥冥中自有庇蔭。大笑出門。自來自去。坦蕩如故也。不用干戈。言無事鬥狠為勇。盜賊休。禍患自散也。修德遠害之報。有如此者。凡遇凶危。修省可免。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生試事畢。卜捷音。占此後。不得中榜。則此籤大不利於求名也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蒯輒見韓信<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%92%AF%E9%80%9A"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蒯輒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，字通。范陽地方人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時韓信，被劉邦立為假齊王。蒯輒知天下大權在韓信手中，前往遊說韓信：今大王威震天下。投靠楚項羽則楚勝，投靠漢劉邦則漢勝，大王若不投靠楚也不投靠漢，就可三分天下，可長保富貴。韓信拒絕說：漢王對我寬厚，我終身不忍背叛漢王。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來韓信被呂后（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B1%89%E9%AB%98%E7%A5%96" title="漢高祖"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">漢高祖</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉邦的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%9A%87%E5%90%8E" title="皇后"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">皇后</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）所殺，臨死之前後悔沒聽蒯通之言。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">祭征虜雅歌投壺</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">祭遵，字弟孫，潁川潁陽（今河南許昌）人。</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%BA%91%E5%8F%B0%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E5%B0%86" title="雲台二十八將"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">雲台二十八將</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">之一。（征虜，是其官名。）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">祭遵為人廉約小心，克己奉公，所得賞賜，盡給士卒，家無私財，身無華服，取士專用儒術，對酒設樂，必雅歌投壺，饒有儒將風規。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">祭遵出身豪門，但生活簡樸知書達禮，且執法嚴明不徇私情。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉秀在河北時，任命祭遵為軍市令。其執法嚴明，不徇私情。劉秀有個小侍從（舍中兒）犯法，祭遵依照法令將其處死。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉秀大怒，逮捕祭遵。主簿陳副諫曰：「明公常欲眾軍整齊，遵奉法不避，是教令所行，奈何罪之？」不久赦免了祭遵，加封刺姦將軍。建武二年（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/26%E5%B9%B4" title="26年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">26</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），任徵虜將軍，封穎陽候。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 61;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚乙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.百千人面虎狼心。<br/>2.賴汝干戈用力深。<br/>3.得勝回時秋漸老。<br/>4.虎頭城裏喜相尋。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.敵方人多勢眾，甚為猖獗。（代表當前的你遇到缺德之人、小人）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.有賴你的貴人全力扶持。有賴你盡全力的付出。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.嘗到果實時，已經是秋末。（成功的時間）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.就在虎頭城裡歡喜的互相尋找（成功的地點）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">「虎頭城」，「虎」字上方這個部首相關的人事物。或與「虎」相關的事蹟之場所。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">1.有小人之害（或有敵人競爭）</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">2.有賴貴人全力協助，或令當事者全力以赴應對。</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">3.逢秋末或逢「寅」的日月，或西方是你勝戰逆境的最佳良機。</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，若遭小人或缺德之人侵害者，除了本身要提升德行之外，也可以使用「咒語」以加強擊退小人效果。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？即使當前有過追求你的人或結識過的對象，只是他們的條件都不好，還不是你的理想對象。而你的婚姻屬於晚婚型，所以需要時間而覓得良緣。若想早早得到良緣，請把握在每年的秋天時刻進行，若主動尋找者，請往西方的方向尋覓。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求？當前認識的對象可否進一步發展？本籤代表，你要等待最佳時機再著手，在秋末或逢「寅」的日月，則是最佳良機。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若交往多年者，問可否結婚者？此婚事可成，若論婚嫁者，請入秋後表白或進行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情經常吵鬧或分手者，或雙方關係冷淡者，此籤代表你和當前的對象在個性上不是很相融，或遭遇某些困境，或遭小人作梗等等，以致雙方冷淡或相處不睦，若想挽回的話，會發去不少時間和心血。若想愛情更順遂的話，雙方都該修行，好好改造自己不好的個性，則能讓愛情轉好。若能修行的話，這些小障礙更容易排除，而後恢復愛情。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此代表你沒有遇到好醫生，以致病情延誤。如此周旋下去，恐會耽誤不少青春歲月。此疾病在逢秋天時好轉，但是不保證就此康復。因此往後的治療，則有賴你當事者以全面性的、徹底性的、根本性的方式治療。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職前途？何時能找到工作？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤代表目前沒工作的人多，找工作難獲得，若想得到工作，有賴你使出渾身解數。若想快速尋得工作，請在秋天時積極進行，最佳尋找方向則在西方。而在逢「寅」的日月，則對你的求職最有利。所以請把握最佳良機。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作、事業前途，此籤代表職場敵人競爭激烈或景氣不佳或與人相處不易，你必須使出渾身解數去應對這些逆境，而在每年的秋末會是你的事業最佳表現良機。若屬於人際問題者，請多多修「廣結善緣」。若屬於職場競爭之問題者，請做好職場人際關係且以服務取勝贏得客戶。而這個惡相要多年後才能化解。若能在每年逢秋末時進行協調，則有良好效果。若屬於景氣不佳者，逢秋全力以赴，而其他季節請放慢腳步，而此不景氣也要多年後才能改善。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試前途，此籤代表考場競爭激烈，錄取率低，即使拼命苦讀，要贏得考試也不容易。因此，這個考試恐要多次競考才能錄取。建議選擇秋末放榜的考試，則對你大有展望。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆失物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此物品被惡人所竊，若想尋回，恐得大費周章，更有賴眾人協力才能找回，而找回的時機可望在秋末，尋找方向請向西方。失物在與「虎」字相關的場所。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人多謀害。汝善卻敵。縱有憂驚。終自消釋。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>得勝回時。定在秋日。圖向西方。事事皆吉。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各人心術各人行。須要心機更自精。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>只恐榮華方到手。秋風吹散葉飛聲。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各精→英謀勇略出奇兵。此去功名得意成<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤其先險阻。後卻亨通。凡事遲滯。防有後難。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若遇秋日。事事皆吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚成訟勝。病防反覆。財有進退。遠行有傷。名利終不遂意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">干戈謂貴人扶持也。言人聚集之眾。人面獸心。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">咸欲謀害善良。賴有干戈護衛。縱使目下驚憂。不足為懼。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">終自消釋。季秋之期高折桂枝。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡百圖謀。決勝於前始。雖險阻。終卻亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">虎頭城乃贛州也。舊為處州。趙清獻公知處州。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有詩曰。乍辭鳳尾闕來到。虎頭城裏喜相尋。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">偶然事機之會也。占此遇寅字始能發福。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤主克敵戰勝之兆。言虎狼之人。百千為群。勢甚猖獗。賴汝整頓干戈。殲擒不遺餘力。是以振旅凱還。正在秋色將老之際。一時功成名遂。恰於虎頭城裡。喜氣相逢。追尋快意。其亦有行藏自適者乎。凡事先險阻。後亨通。應在秋日。或西方或虎字頭州縣地名。或應在晚景</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">百千虎狼。乃是為害之人。干戈用力。恰遇就援之助。得勝而回。策勳持賞。秋光漸老。好景無多。虎頭志喜。因依或有夙緣。冠蓋追尋。居處誠為樂地。武士占之功名顯達。將帥占之。勳猷烜赫。玩末二句。似亦有時行時止之意。占者細參。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">昔劉誠意。占此後。輔太祖興王。辭榮歸隱。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蓋論秋漸老三字。乃盛名之下。難久居也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">歸隱處州。亦虎頭城也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又泉州許生。咸豊己酉。科鄉試。占此中第二名解元。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乃盧姓。虎頭也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">韓信戰霸王<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D203%E5%B9%B4" title="前203年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前203年</span></a>，劉邦與項羽議和，兩分天下，以<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%B4%BB%E6%BA%9D" title="鴻溝"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">鴻溝</span></a>為界。不久劉邦聽從陳平之計毀約，出兵追擊東歸的項羽，但韓信及<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BD%AD%E8%B6%8A" title="彭越"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">彭越</span></a>沒有派兵助戰，漢軍在<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E5%9B%BA%E9%99%B5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="固陵 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">固陵</span></a>被項羽大敗。劉邦一方面固守，另一方面答應韓信及<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BD%AD%E8%B6%8A" title="彭越"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">彭越</span></a>事成後封地為王。韓信及彭越終於帶兵會合劉邦，韓信以十面埋伏之計大破楚軍，最後迫使項羽撤退到<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%9E%93%E4%B8%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%98" title="垓下之戰"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">垓下</span></a>，項羽突圍到<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%83%8F%E6%B1%9F" title="烏江"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">烏江</span></a>，自覺無顏見江東父老，不肯渡江，遂自刎而亡。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE:11pt;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">李愬雪夜入蔡州<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">李愬。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%94%90" title="唐"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">唐</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%B4%E6%BD%AD" title="臨潭"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">臨潭</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人。字元直。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%8E%E6%99%9F_(%E5%94%90%E6%9C%9D)" title="李晟 (唐朝)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">李晟</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">之子。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元和十二年，朝廷封西平郡王李愬為唐隨鄧三州節度使、左散騎</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E4%BE%8D" title="中常侍"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中常侍</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，令他到唐州平亂。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">李愬上任後，親自慰問將士，安撫傷兵，以穩軍心。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">同時又故意向淮西示弱，在蔡州的敵軍吳元濟誤信李愬無能，對他不加防範。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">李愬見時機成熟，在風雪交加的夜裡，以九千人秘密奇襲守衛空虛的蔡州，大敗吳元濟，平定了淮西。唐朝恢復統一，出現短暫的中興局面。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 62;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚丙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.曩時敗北且圖南。(曩同昔)<br/>2.筋力雖衰尚一堪。<br/>3.欲識生前君大數。<br/>4.前三三與後三三。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">敗→征<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.往昔南爭北討有得有失</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.雖然筋疲力盡，但還可以支撐。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若想知道自己好運的數字</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.前後與三相關的數字都是</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.因為得故有失，因為失故又得。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.此事尚有可為</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.逢三、六、九的數字，都是你此事的重要數字。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這件事情若要成就，需要耐心、耐勞。若堪得起反反覆覆的操勞，那就能出頭天。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問愛情前途者，由於曾經得到愛情，故又失去愛情，也因為失去愛情，又讓你再度尋求愛情。你的前後將娶妻三次，或前後共有三個愛人。而你和愛人的年齡差距，也可能是三、六、九歲之差。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？你必須經過一而再，再而三的交往選擇，最後才找到你的配偶。所以，你將認識許多的異性朋友，而經過三番九次的交往，而後才決定了你的終身愛人。而每逢第三個（六個、九個<span lang="EN-US">…）的結交對象，是你最可能私定終身的對象。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前喜歡的對象可否追求？當前認識的對象可否進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br>本籤代表你需要不斷的和他互動與交往，這愛情才能逐漸成熟。而這愛情也可能讓你分分合合不斷的重複，這是你要有的心理準備。但是，這愛情還是有一分希望可以得到果實的，這就要看你的耐力而決定了。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若交往多年，問可否結婚者？何時能結婚？若想要求婚者，你的求婚一次恐不成功，而要有三次求婚的準備才可望得到答應。若一次求婚失敗者，請隔三個月後再求。如此再三，最後就能得到應允。（若三次沒成者，恐要六次、九次<span lang="EN-US">…）</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若愛情經常吵鬧或分手者，或雙方關係冷淡者，代表這愛情讓你筋疲力盡，而當前雖然陷入低潮期，若想挽回者，尚有可為。請發揮你的真愛情操，若能每天展現三次真愛的言行，這愛情就能美滿收場。總結，挽回這愛情需要耐心、耐勞，若想挽回的話，那就發揮你堅強的意志力吧。</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病，代表患者已經南爭北討，四處醫療過，而如今尚未全盡人意。但是此病還是有康復的希望，儘管這是難治的慢性病，但是要用對方法。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">想要找工作者，何時才能找到工作？此籤詩代表找工作讓你南爭北討，三番九次，最後才找到。每逢第三、六、九次<span lang="EN-US">…的求職，最可能讓你如願。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆轉換、換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問此類問題者，此籤代表你將經歷多次的轉換，而後才得以安定。所以，你要有三、六、九次的轉換心理準備。而每逢第三次的轉換，是你最容易安定的時刻，因此請在這次要特別珍惜，隨遇而安，盡量安貼自己，以免將來還有三次的轉換，這可很累人的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若在工作上不順遂求得此籤詩，代表問題一而再，再而三的發生困擾，但是，問題並非不可解，每逢第三次的狀況，將是安定的最佳時刻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若生意不佳者，求得此籤，這代表這生意做的也辛苦，總是賺了又虧，虧了又賺，周而復始，令人疲勞。建議，改造一下經營策略和經營心態，這可以讓你提早停止這種循環。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問工作前途者，你的工作可能屬於如機器人般的作業員，每天重複同樣的工作，讓人感到疲勞。若找到這類工作者，是你要有的心理準備。萬一找到這種工作時，建議你可以在工作中「念佛」（或唸各種佛菩薩聖號），那此份工作就不空過了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆失物<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若尋失物者，這件事情恐得反反覆覆的尋找，再三的尋找，若堪得起這樣操勞，那此事尚有可為，最後可以找到。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">前後謀望。皆有所成。晚年經商。尚堪一行。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>福分數定。不虧不盈。若欲多取。徒芳神精。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">芳精→自勞神<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作事當圖共老成。莫疑阻漸沒通亨。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>要知勤苦勞神處。正是皇天玉手更。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫處→若還疑滯欠通亨。桑榆晚景堪願。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀望有成。晚年經商。正可一行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若欲多取。徒勞心力。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問訟宜和。婚主三娶。財如常。信準有。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名未遂。病可醫。凡事當隨分也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">頭句言不如昔日之遂意也。一句言人不可自也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但人自有大數。不可強求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三三俱九數。九者陽之名。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡老陽則變。而動占者主泰極變否。棄極變泰。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶得失。輒相循環。所謂有數存焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">老此當以所占之期。合成九數。則可趨。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不合則否可避。斯得之矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大抵此籤。問名主晚成。問子推主旱得。婚主三娶。宜謹詳之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤前途亨通。中間不免折挫。現在雖極疲困。然有一番光景在後。不可墮志。亦是大數注定。必其人平日居心及行事。克邀天鑒。故能不終沒沒也。三三。乃大數應驗處。凡事失中有得。難中有易。晚景榮華。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">征北圖南。言往事遂意。如征戰者之幾處成功也。筋力既衰。一旦傾跌。似乎無濟。然始則由成而敗。後則由敗而成。尚一堪者。言尚可有為也。大數如此。生前預定。前三三。後三三。大數之驗也。或應在三數或應在六數。或應在九數。臨事參詳。不可執一而論。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一頁生在京十年。值試期。人勸與考。偶展卷被雞抓破。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">遂立意就選人強之。乃占此。復溫習赴試。中六十六名。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">應前後三三之數。授辰州推官。一任而罷。次句并驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又南安一拔貢生。欲進京供職。并應北闈。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此改就鄉試。竟中副車。蓋渠屢應京闈未第。是敗北。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宜圖南也。筋力雖衰。亞於正也。尚一堪。宜共副焉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">楊令公撞李陵碑<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">宋朝。楊業。太原人。先在北漢朝庭當官。屢立戰功。號稱楊無敵。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">後來，楊業歸降北宋，任左領軍<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D" title="大將軍"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">大將軍</span></a>，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%84%AD%E5%B7%9E" title="鄭州"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">鄭州</span></a>防禦使，主要負責與潘仁美共同防禦北方的<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%81%BC" title="遼"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">遼</span></a>國南下。</span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;">當時楊業孤軍深入，被遼國將領耶律斜軫在陳家谷設伏兵所困。由於<span style="FONT-SIZE:11pt;">潘</span>仁美妒恨楊業，故意不派援兵，想害死楊業。<span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">楊業被困又無援兵，不食三日後，撞李陵碑而死。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">廉頗用趙<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%BB%89%E9%A0%97">廉頗</a>食量驚人，年老時每頓飯還能吃一斗米、十斤肉，並經常披甲跨馬馳騁校場。其晚年趙王曾想重用廉頗，派使者請其出山，廉頗為顯示自己未老，當著使者面吃下一斗米、十斤肉並披甲跨馬馳騁校場。但遭<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E9%83%AD%E5%BC%80&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="郭開 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">郭開</span></a>排擠，使者謊稱廉頗「一飯三遺矢」(吃一頓飯拉三次屎)。趙王遂以為廉頗老而無用，便不復用。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">命理解析<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 63;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六四籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚丁<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上上</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.吉人相遇本和同。<br/>2.況有持謀天水翁。<br/>3.人力不勞公論協。<br/>4.事成功倍笑談中。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.善人相逢一起做事，原本就好合同。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.更何況有貴人來主導這件事。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.不用多費力氣，公平，同心協力。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.事情就在談笑之中加倍成功。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">貴人者：天水翁，貴人是也。該人資料中有天或水的人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">合夥者：名字中有趙或胡。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.這是個值得合作的好夥伴（這是個好溝通的對象）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.還有貴人主導</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.這件事情應該好好溝通就可以解決</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. 由於以上原因，故事情可以順利進行。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問題屬於其中有問題者，進行溝通即可解決。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問題屬於合夥或兩個人的事情，此事將可以順利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問題屬於個人問題者，此事可以如願。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若需要貴人者，請找和天或水有關的人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若問姻緣何時來？其實你是個好溝通的人，若想得到姻緣的話，這需要有媒人替你從中穿線，只要有了貴人，那你就能找到臭氣相投的另一伴了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前喜歡的對象、暗戀的人可否追求？當前認識的對象可否進一步發展？若你想要更進一步發展的話，其實是很容易的。若有貴人從中引薦的話，這事情就更是容易。因為你和他格調很接近，對方也很好溝通，所以能一拍即合。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若交往多年者，問可否結婚者，你們原本就處的很好，若想結婚的話，只要把媒人找來，那就可以進行婚姻事宜了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或雙方關係冷淡者，或愛情有危機者，若求得本籤，這件事情是很好解決的，雙方只要和氣的溝通一下，即能達成協議，而讓愛情恢復，甚至比原來更好。因為你們倆原本就是好說話的。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試，由於此考試原本就很適合你發輝，因此，你將可以輕鬆的通過考試。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職者，你可以順利找到很適配的工作，而讓你發揮的很好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇在事業這方面，若尋求合夥者，可以和容易溝通的夥伴一起經營事業，而後成順利的發展。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前事業已展者，你在工作崗位上，將有合作無間的好夥伴，因此讓工作進行的極為順利。要是遇到任何困難者，都可以進行溝通，事情都可以公平的解決。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">與人謀合。況遇朝貴。援手提攜。事皆稱意。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>勿勞餘力。成就甚易。出入皆宜。吉無不利。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">作事須知兩不同。主謀全仗貴人功。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>但凡事事皆如意。只恐人生談笑中。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>作事事今迥不同。主謀全得貴人功。<br/>蒲帆能趁東風便。望裏蓬萊咫尺通。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀望和合。遇貴人提挈。凡事稱意。出入皆宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟即了。名得成。財有望。婚亦合。病可醫。信決至。無不遂也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言功名謀為。凡遇趙胡二姓者。為協力。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">贊攘則意氣和合。事無不成功。無不就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不勞一毫心力。只恐談笑中三字。主事有阻滯。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">中道而止。半途而廢也。俱宜謹言慎行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉旡不利。天水不止。姓趙凡郡中有天水者皆是。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀為和合。得遇貴人提攜。凡事稱意。不勞而成。必其人素為人所敬信。其事又為眾所欣悅。是又恰遇機緣。一倡百和。談笑中。事立而成功。豈非天人相應。相時而動者乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉人。善人也。本和同。言吉人天相。遇合自亨也。持謀。猶言主謀。天水翁。指所遇貴人而言。或應天水趙姓。或應天水二字郡縣地名。公論協。事合人心。人心歡悅。是以不勞人力。自得水到渠成之妙。笑談成功。所謂不言而信。無為而成者也。上吉何疑。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人作縣官。被論。占此後。賴闔城紳士。力保留任。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">應在第三句。人力不勞公論協也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又同治丁卯科。晉江謄錄書。占所謄諸生誰是榜上人。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">迨出榜。惟一陳姓乳名吉字。故籤語明不以吉中兩字也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">管鮑分金<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春秋時代，管仲與鮑叔未做官時，合夥經商。分紅利時，管仲多拿。鮑叔知道他貧窮，不認為他貪心。後來鮑叔當齊桓公大夫，竟推薦管仲當齊國宰相。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">管仲佐助桓公，尊周攘夷，稱霸諸侯，平定天下。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">管仲曾說，生我者父母，了解我者鮑叔也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">魯仲連排難解紛<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%AD%AF%E4%BB%B2%E9%80%A3"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">魯仲連</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（約</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D305%E5%B9%B4" title="前305年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">305</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">—</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D245%E5%B9%B4" title="前245年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">245</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B" title="中國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">古代</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%88%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3" title="戰國時代"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">戰國時代</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%BD%8A%E5%9C%8B" title="齊國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">齊國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（今王老鄉望魯店村）名士。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">魯仲連不願出任官職，在</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B" title="趙國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">趙國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">遊歷。趙國在</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%95%B7%E5%B9%B3%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0" title="長平之戰"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">長平之戰</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">慘敗後，</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E5%9C%8B" title="秦國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秦</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">軍圍困趙都</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%82%AF%E9%84%B2" title="邯鄲"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">邯鄲</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%AD%8F%E5%AE%89%E9%87%90%E7%8E%8B" title="魏安釐王"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">魏安釐王</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">派</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%A3%E8%A1%8D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="新垣衍 （頁面未存在）"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">新垣衍</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">進入邯鄲遊說</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B9%B3%E5%8E%9F%E5%90%9B" title="平原君"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">平原君</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，勸平原君說服趙王尊秦王為帝。魯仲連知道此事，便請平原君安排他與新垣衍會面，令新垣衍放棄原來的意見。秦軍聞知此事，便退兵五十里。這時候</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%BF%A1%E9%99%B5%E5%90%9B" title="信陵君"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">信陵君</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">率魏軍擊秦，秦軍便撤圍而去。事後平原君欲封賞魯仲連，魯仲連始終不肯接受。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">十餘年後，</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%BD%8A%E5%9C%8B" title="齊國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">齊國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">攻</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%81%8A%E5%9F%8E" title="聊城"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">聊城</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，兩年來久攻不下，死傷慘重。魯仲連致書守將，勸他棄城歸</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%87%95%E5%9C%8B" title="燕國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">燕</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">或齊，守將未能作出抉擇，自殺而死，聊城便被齊軍佔領。魯仲連不願接受齊國的封賞，又逃隱起來。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 64;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上上</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.朔風凜凜正窮冬。<br/>2.多羨門庭喜氣濃。<br/>3.更入新春人事後。<br/>4.衷言方得信先容。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">多羨→漸覺<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.北風呼呼吹著，正是冬天的盡頭。（困頓就要過去）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.此時漸漸感覺家庭喜氣變濃了</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.到了新春之刻，人事方面更順遂後</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.得到貴人之忠言，壞事化吉，信息通達。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">困頓已久，直到冬末之刻即有轉機。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">到春天之時，有關「人」的事情變得通達。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.春天時，貴人接引，訊息明朗，壞事化吉。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前單身無對象者問姻緣何時來？此事到了冬末時，會有些消息，到了農曆年後，可望有媒人替你介紹對象。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前正常交往者，問未來愛情前途？或交往多年者，問可否結婚？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>過去的愛情困頓，在冬天時即將結束了。進入冬末時，你們情意轉濃，到了新春時更是遂意，若能找個媒人的話，還可以論及婚嫁。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否進一步發展？本籤代表，此事困頓你已久，但進入冬末之時，即有喜氣誕生，又到春天之時，你們的關係又更明確。所以要加油囉！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或雙方關係冷淡者，或愛情困頓者，此事到了冬天之末，即有改變之兆，到了春天之時，亦能得到貴人衷言而化解。分手者可得挽回，關係不睦者，恢復情誼。但是，求得好籤時，自己也要努力才能應驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問懷孕、生子者，在冬末就有消息了，到了春天之時也能確定懷孕和男女了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆官司訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此案件到了冬末有轉機，到了春天時，在貴人的巧妙言辭之下，可望勝訴並定案。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">困頓的日子就要結束了，此事業到了冬末就有轉機了，而到了春天時事業可以順利進行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職者，到了冬末就有工作的消息，而過年後，就能確定工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試可否錄取，若是農曆過年前的考試，放榜在新春者，可望錄取。但是，其他季節的考試，則未必。求得好籤時，請勿懈怠，以免變卦。常有人求得好籤，但卻沒錄取。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">數極于冬。窮久則通。交季冬月。喜氣重重。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>新春一至。和氣愈充。好遇貴客。百事皆同。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不意反成得意歸。入門一卦見仙機。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>當時險難皆平靜。百事和諧沒是非。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">不→失<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤數極于窮冬。遇變而通。貴人提拔。百事亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病者安。訟宜和。財有望。婚可求。名利高。行人來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事死中求生也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言氣數之窮。有變亨之兆。時值冬月。雖多喜事。不若新春。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人事之後。方始遂意。謂加以人為之周旋也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">衰言者。貴人之言也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">信先容者。凡事至春。凶變為吉。好事重重。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤沉滯既久。困而將亨之象。譬寒冬凜冽之際。剝極陽生。漸得交泰更新。萬物從此發生。正多美景。占此者冬季有喜。交春人事遂意。另有一番好消息。指日俟之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">朔風凜凜。冬時窮悴極矣。門庭喜氣。生機勃勃欲動矣。更入新春。三陽開泰。光景榮華。衷言。指衷曲謀望之事。信先容。言此時信息通達。必有貴人為之接引。為之揄揚。衷曲得以開陳。好音不日到耳也。應驗已速。事到功成。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生科舉。占此。臨試給冬字號簽。至春發案不取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">所謂窮冬者。此也。後遺才收錄。此又更入之。應窺則通之意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蒙正木蘭和詩<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋朝。呂蒙正，字聖初。河南人。困窮時曾在尼姑庵居住。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在木蘭寺內作詩，他的作品和一般人大不相同。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">到了宋太宗時，果然考進士第一名。後來三次當宰相，引薦人材。使人盡其才，是賢明宰相。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">馬周獻策<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%A6%AC%E5%91%A8"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">馬周</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/601%E5%B9%B4" title="601年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">601</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">－</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/648%E5%B9%B4" title="648年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">648</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%A8%E5%AD%97" title="表字"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">字</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">賓王，博州茌平人（今屬</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C" title="山東"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">山東</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD" title="中國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中國</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%94%90%E6%9C%9D" title="唐朝"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">唐朝</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">初年名臣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">馬周早年孤貧，然熟讀</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%AF%97%E7%BB%8F" title="詩經"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">詩經</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">和</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B" title="春秋"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">春秋</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%AD%A6%E5%BE%B7" title="武德"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">武德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">年間一度出任州助教，但因不理政事而被</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%88%BA%E5%8F%B2" title="刺史"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">刺史</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E8%BE%BE%E5%A5%9A%E6%81%95&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="達奚恕 （頁面未存在）"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">達奚恕</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">指責，遂辭官而去。後至汴州，被浚義令崔賢羞辱，於是西入</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89" title="長安"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">長安</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，投入</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%95" title="常何"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">常何</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">門下為</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%A8%E5%AE%A2" title="門客"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">門客</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B4%9E%E8%A7%82" title="貞觀"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">貞觀</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">五年（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/632%E5%B9%B4" title="632年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">632</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%94%90%E5%A4%AA%E5%AE%97" title="唐太宗"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">唐太宗</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">下詔令各官言得失，馬周為常何捉刀代寫二十餘策，得到唐太宗的賞識，入</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%8B%E7%9C%81" title="門下省"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">門下省</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">為官，次年升任</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%9B%91%E5%AF%9F%E5%BE%A1%E5%8F%B2" title="監察御史"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">監察御史</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。馬周辦事周密，尤擅言辭，為時人稱頌，唐太宗曾表示：「暫不見周即思之」，因此升遷快速。貞觀十八年（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/645%E5%B9%B4" title="645年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">645</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），馬周升任</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%A6%E4%BB%A4" title="中書令"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中書令</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm 6pt 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 65;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六六籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚己<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上上</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.耕耘只可在鄉邦。<br/>2.何用求謀向外方。<br/>3.見說今年新運好。<br/>4.門闌喜氣事雙雙。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">見說→只見<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.只在家鄉經營即可</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.莫遠求、莫外求、莫遠出</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.今年將有新的好運勢</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.恭賀雙喜臨門</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.凡事莫向外求、守舊好</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.今年雙喜臨門</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？姻緣在何方？<span lang="EN-US"><br>若當前單身無侶者，姻緣就在你的居家附近，今年當可逢遇，而有快速的進展。若上班族者，姻緣就在你的工作職場附近，或許就是你的同事，所以不用外地遠求。好好的注意誰對你有好感，而後兩人的感情能快速發展，今年就有愛情的果實。若你所遇到的姻緣是在外地或離你遙遠者，恐會成為無聲息的歌唱。</span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？或更進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br>本籤代表，今年展開追求，將有佳績。請發揮你的真愛，積極行動，以便趕在未來的年節時，有愛情的成果。</span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若交往多年者，問可否結婚者，在逢年過節時，就是你們定親之刻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前交往的對象，未來愛情運發展者，當前這份愛情就是你的正緣，好好的經營他，不要移情別戀，以免節外生枝耽誤愛情，專心的經營真愛，可望今年就能雙雙入洞房。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情分手，或欲求挽回者，這份愛情要保守經營，不可劈腿，以免節外生枝，惹出愛情糾紛。請好好向你的另一伴道歉，以恢復愛情。專心的經營這份愛情，可望今年有喜酒可喝。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問求職或創業者，工作或創業都在自己家鄉發揮，即能獲得好成果。找工作者，可望在年節時刻找到工作。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇當老闆者，今年要以保守方式經營，莫擴廠，免增員，保守經營。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇當員工者，若想要離職，不必離職，維持原工作，必得佳績。若想出外創業，或找找工作的話，也在自己家鄉即可。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇問工作前途者，盡本分做好份內的工作，必能得到回饋。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問找醫生者，尋找居家附近的醫生即可，不必遠出他鄉就醫，也不用尋求名醫名藥。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問醫療方向，請向自己內心或身上治療即可痊癒。此代表這疾病是心理問題引起的。只要心情恢復正常，或心事解決，那此病也自然康復。或請調整自己的生活作息或飲食，只要將之調整過來，此病自然康復。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆財運<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問錢財運，此籤詩提醒，若要花錢，只能用自己的錢，而不要向外面借錢。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在錢財困境方面，今年將可獲得舒緩，甚至還清。請好好工作努力賺錢吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆購買<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問購屋等事，請在居家附近尋找，今年可望完整這個購買理想，此乃一喜。若在年節前完成，則是雙喜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 6pt 6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">今年的投資理財當行保守，不可擴充信用，或高額投資，一切以保守模式行之。若能如此，可望在未來有良好的成果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇今年可望能順利懷孕生子，而且就在年節前後，產下貴子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若多年不孕者，不用另外求孕，今年即可順利懷孕。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試成果者，今年將有佳績。請選擇家鄉的考試為佳，遠地的考試未必有利。請務必在家好好讀書，而不要外出亂跑。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">出外不宜。在家必達。時運將亨。財祿俱發。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>好事重重。門庭改革。若欲遠圖。弄巧成拙。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自家安分莫他求。自有榮華切莫憂。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>喜得一陽天氣象。也知春煖勝三秋。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>自家安分莫他求。俯仰寬舒得自由。<br/>現在陽和春已到。桃紅李白樂悠悠。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜遠行。只宜守舊。自有超達。時運漸亨。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">財祿俱發。訟不宜。財自至。婚可求。名利高。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病獲安。孕生貴子。風水利順。家宅昌隆也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名利只宜近處。不宜遠行。守舊好。進步難見。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">說新運好者。不是決。許其好。尚當待時發達也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此者。凡事皆利。且得護喜。婚姻事尤宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">耕耘或作經營。向字或作出字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤不宜遠行。只宜守舊。鄉邦之地。自有榮華。耕耘之中。亦有發跡。況值運限更新。門庭以內。喜事重重。自可享受優遊。倘捨現前實地。希冀遠大不可知之數。將貽後悔。居易俟命者得之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">耕耘。係農家之事。正鄉邦中所為也。外方。則非耕耘之地矣。捨近圖遠。豈有濟乎。新運好。福氣將來也。喜氣雙雙。好事不止一件。言門庭中自有至樂。總見不可騖遠之意。占家宅。財旺人興。流年大吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">正德間。京師揚惟聰占此。後以鼎元歷官翰苑。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">至宮保學士尚書。凡十餘任。並不出京。正應首句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">杜甫遊春<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">唐朝。杜甫，字子美，杜陵地方人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">玄宗時，獻三大禮賦（文章名），命待詔集賢院，後轉檢校工部員外。（二者皆官名）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">杜甫博覽群書，善長作詩歌。氣勢廣大，內容豐富。論述時事，確切深刻，當時人稱他詩史。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元稹說：沒有其它詩人成就比得上杜甫的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">杜甫喜好賞春山，所以每當晴朗春天，必到郊外玩。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">諸葛隱南陽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">諸葛亮（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/181%E5%B9%B4" title="181年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">181</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">－</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/234%E5%B9%B4" title="234年"><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">234</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%A8%E5%AD%97" title="表字"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">字</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孔明，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%90%85%E7%90%8A" title="琅琊"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">琅琊</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陽都（今</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%9C" title="山東"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">山東省</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%82%E5%8D%97" title="沂南"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">沂南縣</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）人，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD" title="三國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">三國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">時期</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%9C%80%E6%BC%A2" title="蜀漢"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">蜀漢</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">重要大臣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時諸葛孔明隱居在南陽，不輕易出來做事，等到劉備勤勤懇懇三顧，才願效命。名流的出仕或隱遁，如此慎重，哪是凡人所能比得上的！三國人才雖多，無如孔明者！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 66;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.纔發君心天已知。<br/>2.何須問我決狐疑。<br/>3.願子改圖從孝悌。<br/>4.不愁家室不相宜。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你才動念，上天就知道了</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.何必問我來決定這個疑惑呢</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.願你改過向善，兄友弟恭，孝敬父母</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.若能如此，不愁家室不安寧。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.人在做，天在看。若有善惡念，天神即知。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.百善孝為先，求福善為本。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.家和萬事興，人和好成事。有困境者做好此點即可改善。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.善有善報，惡有惡報。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5.家人的感情與你當前謀求衝突時，要先把感情弄好。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若是好端端的愛情突然變卦者，愛情有困境者當知，這可能是天神有意折騰你，你要自己檢視，是否做了哪些不公不義之事。只要悔改，愛情就能恢復正常。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情是雙方爭吵而分手者，此乃理所當然，你應當學習「尊重」，不管言語和行為，都不可觸犯情人，這才能保證愛情品質。若想復合的話，則應在此方面改進。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前愛情前途者，你當注意幾個重點，除了你和情人間感情要和睦之外，你和對方的家人也要處得好，這才能保證這個愛情穩定。平常應當多行善事，不做任何壞事，即使惡念都不要有，這才能保證你的愛情始終如一。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否進一步發展？若未追求的，你可以追求。若已經來往者，可以進一步發展。但是有個前提，你的更近一步發展的心態必須是「正」的，若是負面的態度的話，那天神都會折騰你。另外，若想進展順利，請先做好兄友弟恭，孝敬父母，若能如此的話，則能順遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、應徵、考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想在這方面順利者，應注意幾個重點，若能遵照辦理，則有利謀求：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.謀職的發心要正，不可有缺德想法。<br/>2.做好與家人相處，孝敬父母。若求職者更應修持「廣結善緣」。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.多</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤提醒想要發財的人，你應當先經營家人感情，當全家和睦相處，兄友弟恭，父慈子孝時，那此價值就勝過你的求財美夢了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若求治病者，先把家人感情、人際間的正面感情培養好，即有療效。若與人相處不睦，這種不愉快的心情，就會讓人生病。所以，要能調適自己的心情，且不與人結怨仇或爭是非。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">所謀未善。何必禱神。當決於理。改過自新。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>但能孝悌。敬君事親。和氣生福。家道回春。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">悌→友<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">立志須行在善中。天難瞞隱意先通。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>能行好事有功效。管取家門喜氣濃。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">在善→善道<span lang="EN-US"><br/>有效→培根本</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤。好善有善報。作惡有惡報。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">君當決狐疑之也。改過自新。禍去福來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但存好心。和氣自生。求財先難後易。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚姻吉。行人遲。孕生男。風水利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言天之禍福由人善惡。不必問我以決狐疑。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但當改過遷善。自然福至禍消。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孝悌者。百行之先。萬善之本也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人能孝悌。則和氣充溢。而家室自宜矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目下名利難得。後有生意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此主先難後易。宜改圖之則吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤好善有好報。作惡有惡報。示人早知警悟。現在所謀不善。天神早已洞照。自是必不可行。何須啟問。唯有改悔前過。力從孝悌上起見。自有家室和平之樂。趨吉避凶。唯人自擇。可不悟乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">才發君心。指一念初動之際。天已知。人可瞞。天不可瞞也。何須問。言善惡彰著。可否分明。自心當自知之。不待神言之告也。改圖。去不善。以遷於善也。從孝悌。以祇父恭兄為根本也。孝悌良善。天自降福。可得家室相宜。不足慮矣。改圖者吉。怙過者凶。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(宋)。萬歷(年)間。一廣文選遼東部司學訓時。以遼左方亂為憂。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此。遲疑未行。值遼陽陷。沒改選湖廣。孝感縣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">教諭屢掌縣印。大有所獲。應第三句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又<span lang="EN-US">(清)光緒甲申。余室得病。諸醫調治未愈。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">余占此。乃延一醫家。在孝悌境者。遂漸痊。後二句驗甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">江遺囑兒（</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://www.amtb.org.tw/wanxi/zebe/24-9.html"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">江革負母</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">—-</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二十四孝之一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東漢時有一個叫江革的孝子，字次翁，從小就失去父親，而與母親相依為命。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時，到處都有盜賊作亂，江革就背著母親到其他地方逃難。在路上，好幾次碰到盜賊，盜賊見他年輕力壯，就想捉他一起做強盜。江革每次總是哭泣地說：「我還有一位無人照料的老母親，我跟你們去了，誰來照顧她呢？」強盜聽了這番誠懇的告白，又見他這樣孝順，也就不忍心殺他們。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">江革背著母親，一路逃難，後來居住在下邳這個地方。他窮得連衣服、鞋子都沒有，以至於裸著身體、光著腳。後來江革當傭工做苦力，賺些微薄工錢來供養母親。雖然家裡十分貧困，但凡是母親日常需要的東西，不論是吃的、穿的、用的卻一應俱全，沒有缺乏。後來他的母親死了，江革哭得很悲哀。住在母親的墳旁，連睡覺的時候，喪服也不脫掉。後來有人見到他的德行不錯，就推舉他為孝廉，最後做到了諫議大夫。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蘇瓊下淚</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有百姓乙普明兄弟爭奪田地，多年未能斷清，他們各自提供證人。竟然有一百來人為他們雙方作證。蘇</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">瓊召集乙普明兄弟，當著眾人勸告他們說：「天下難以得到的是兄弟，容易尋求的是田地，假如讓你們得到田地而失去兄弟之心，將會怎樣？」蘇瓊說著就掉下淚來，眾人無不哭泣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乙普明兄弟叩頭請求到外面去再加考慮，他們兄弟已分居十年，於是又搬到一起居住。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 67;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.南販珍珠北販鹽。<br/>2.年來幾倍貨財添。<br/>3.勸君止此求田舍。<br/>4.心欲多時何日厭。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.大江南北到處做生意</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.幾年來獲利無數</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.勸你適可而止，莫再投資</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.貪欲是個無底洞</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆本籤重點，「適可而止」<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.過去經營的很好</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.食髓知味，貪得無厭，並非好事。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.知足常樂，知止守成，方為良策。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？想必你已經見識過多位異性，只是當前還沒有找到自己認為適合的。但是，此籤詩是提醒，不要眼光太高，對於異性的條件不要要求太多，以免找不到愛人。因此，只要你降低自己的擇偶條件，那就有許多適合你的對象了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前的愛情陷入困境者？此籤代表你們的愛情發展已經有好幾年了，而雙方一向處的很好，但是當你們相處時失去敬重，或變得任性，那就會破壞原來的感情。因此，若想恢復原本的情誼，務必把持自己的個性，還是要維持一貫的敬重態度，更不能因為雙方很熟悉了，就變得隨便，或有過多的要求，若能如此的話，這愛情就能維繫。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前愛情順利者，欲問未來愛情前途者，此籤詩提醒，若異性緣很好者，在交往期間，請勿腳跨多條船，以免失足落海。也不要對情人有過多的要求，以免惡化了愛情。此籤也建議你，當前交往順利者，可以就此做個決定，緣定終身。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象能否有更進一步的發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若對方看起來，條件比你好，此有高攀之相，事情就難成就。若雙方看起來，感覺門當戶對，那就可以追求。</span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若結識的對象或喜歡的對象已經有情人者，此籤代表，你不要去貪求別人的愛情，以免壞了人家的感情，而且將來自己的愛情也一樣不順遂。總結，在愛情上，不要當第三者。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若追求某人沒有下文或回音，這要怎麼辦</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤的提示是「適可而止」，既然求愛不得其果，那就「適可而止」，而不用再浪費光陰了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目前的官司已經處在勝訴狀況，莫得寸進尺。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、找工作、換工作、事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇目前無工作或事業者，求問新的事業發展方向，此籤詩代表你適合做生意（中間商尤佳），將來可以獲利滾滾。屆時，你只要記得守成就好。另外，只要你尋找的工作性質屬於南來北往性質，需要四處奔波的行業，都是適合你的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若已經有事業者，此籤詩代表你已經做的很好，也已經獲利無數，而此刻正是你守成之刻。建議，布施就是投資未來的富裕。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前工作表現不佳想要更換職業者，此籤詩暗示你，做生意才是你的本行，好好的經營生意，將可獲利無數。只要是需要四處奔波的行業，你都可以在其中發揮的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇總結，本籤代表當事者適合做生意、買賣而富裕，屬於此性質的行業都適合。若當前或未來致富者，應記得守成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆購屋、投資、理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">購屋若屬於投資性質者，則不宜。若屬於自用者、保本者則可。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>各類金融投資都不宜，此有貪財之嫌，故有虧損之疑慮。<br/>總結，凡各種投機性、風險性質的事業都不宜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問疾病者，此籤代表這個疾病是奔波、勞碌引起的，由於家事或事業忙碌或負擔重，而導致身體欠安，若你要找醫生的話，那不必了。此病只需要多多休息，不要給自己過多的負擔，那自然就康復了。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">屬於這方面祈求者，若本身已經有子女者，那就不要再求了，而要安於現狀。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀望既遂。利亦倍收。貪心不止。必獲後憂。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>知足不辱。可樂優游。凡事如意。可休則休。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">游→遊<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一樣工夫不兩般。得寬閒處且寬閒。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若謀富貴不知足。自有災愆不待言。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>人事茫茫在世間。得寬閒處且寬閒。<br/>倘謀富貴無知足。併惹愆尤自往還。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大吉。謀望有成。諸般遂意。家道亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟必勝。莫再興。名利有。婚自成。行人回。病莫憂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">財利一倍。任意求。風水利。孕生女。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡謀事。要謹慎。且安分守己也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">昔<span lang="EN-US">(宋)太祖即位應天。故時人以應天為南。以汴城為北。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡求名。得此往往顯達。以膚拔擢。蓋以帝畿在南也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者謀為。或自南而此不逆其方。則所為遂意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又當戒其貪心。之不可妄求。止此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求田舍者。言不可過貪。而其為田舍翁也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若人不能謹守而冒進。千祿則并其所得而亡之。反為不義矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤勸人知足不辱。知止不恥之意。凡人前事謀為。既已遂意。現在境地。亦可粗安。即當持盈戒滿。自守清靜。就此求田問舍。自得安常處順之樂。若貪多不已。終無厭足。不唯自取煩勞。有不更招意外者乎。進退行止之幾。當自決之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">販珠販鹽。言前時謀為多端也。貨財倍添。則可以少休矣。求田舍。乃退守者所為。勸君止此。言當為此退守之計。庶可免咎。心慾多。心中貪求不已也。厭。足也。貪多者。足愈不足。豈有止息。不至傾覆禍患不止。所以深戒之也。知者務為恬靜。則亨貞之道矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生占科舉。不得。觀場是止。此求田舍之應也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">錢大王販鹽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:24pt;BACKGROUND:#f8fcff;MARGIN-LEFT:12pt;"><span style="">（吳越太祖武肅王</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%8C%A2%E9%8F%90">錢鏐</a></span><span style="">，字具美（一作巨美），</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F" title="浙江"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">浙江</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E" title="杭州"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">杭州</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%B4%E5%AE%89" title="臨安"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">臨安</span></a></span><span style="">人。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD" title="中國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中國</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%BD" title="五代十國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">五代十國</span></a></span><span style="">時期</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Times New Roman'';"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%90%B4%E8%B6%8A%E5%9B%BD" title="吳越國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">吳越國</span></a></span><span style="">的創立人。）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE:11pt;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">唐朝。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">錢鏐，臨安人。貧賤時，以販賣</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%81%E7%9B%90" title="私鹽"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">私鹽</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">謀生。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">遇黃巢作亂，帶鄉間義勇軍趕走黃巢兵。又以八都兵，攻打劉漢宏破越州。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">迎接董昌將軍，而自居於杭（浙江）。董昌反錢鏐，捉董昌至杭。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">昭宗拜錢鏐為鎮海鎮東兩軍節度使。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">朱溫纂唐，封錢鏐作吳越王。傳至孫，忠懿王錢俶，就投降北宋。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">呂不韋居寄<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%91%82%E4%B8%8D%E9%9F%8B"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂不韋</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">出生於</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%AB%E5%9B%BD" title="衛國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">衛國</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BF%AE%E9%98%B3%E5%B8%82" title="濮陽市"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">濮陽</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，在</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD_(%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD)" title="韓國 (戰國)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">韓國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陽翟經商，因「販賤賣貴」而「家累千金」。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂不韋在</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B" title="趙國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">趙國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">邯鄲經商時，偶然結識</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E5%9C%8B" title="秦國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秦國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">交給趙國的王室人質</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AC%B4%E7%95%B0%E4%BA%BA" title="嬴異人"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嬴異人</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，認為「奇貨可居」，決定幫助嬴異人返回秦國，又將</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B5%B5%E5%A7%AC_(%E7%A7%A6%E5%BA%84%E8%A5%84%E7%8E%8B)" title="趙姬 (秦庄襄王)"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">趙姬</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">送給嬴異人，生下一子</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%87" title="秦始皇"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嬴政</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，並資助嬴異人千金，將他返回秦國。又以五百金購珍寶獻與</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E8%8F%AF%E9%99%BD%E5%A4%AB%E4%BA%BA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="華陽夫人 （頁面未存在）"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">華陽夫人</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，華陽夫人勸安國君嬴柱立異人為嫡嗣，改名子楚。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D251%E5%B9%B4" title="前251年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">251</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E6%98%AD%E8%A5%84%E7%8E%8B" title="秦昭襄王"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秦昭襄王</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">嬴稷斃，太子安國君繼位，為</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E5%AD%9D%E6%96%87%E7%8E%8B" title="秦孝文王"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秦孝文王</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，立一年而卒，嬴異人繼位，即</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%A7%A6%E8%8E%8A%E8%A5%84%E7%8E%8B" title="秦莊襄王"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">秦莊襄王</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，以呂不韋為丞相，封文信侯，食河南洛陽十萬戶。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">三年後秦莊襄王病卒，十三歲的</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AC%B4%E6%94%BF" title="嬴政"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嬴政</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繼位，即後來秦始皇，尊呂不韋為「仲父」。呂不韋常與太后私通，後以「大陰人」</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AB%AA%E6%AF%90" title="嫪毐"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嫪毐</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">偽裝成宦者而進獻給太后。甚得太后專寵。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AC%B4%E6%94%BF" title="嬴政"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嬴政</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">發現母親趙氏與呂不韋、嫪毐有姦情，並傳出</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AC%B4%E6%94%BF" title="嬴政"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">嬴政</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">為呂不韋之子，先誅嫪毐，後將呂不韋遷蜀，呂不韋不能自安，飲鴆自殺。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 68;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">六九籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚壬<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.捨舟遵路總相宜。<br/>2.慎勿嬉遊逐貴兒。<br/>3.一夜樽前兄與弟。(樽指酒杯)<br/>4.明朝仇敵又相隨。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">1.捨棄搭船遵循正路總是適宜的（出外有搭船或飛機者也當注意安危）</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">2.切勿嬉玩或追逐明星偶像或攀附富貴人家子弟（預防週邊人侵害）</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">3.與朋友喝酒稱兄道弟（預防口舌）</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">4.明早仇敵可能又來</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.各種謀求當行正道，腳踏實地，莫存僥倖。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.莫追逐名人、偶像明星、富貴人家子弟（不要有虛榮心）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.交友小心（若本身是善良之人、老實人，更要預防被朋友所害）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.交友預防口舌、預防受害、喝酒是大忌。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5.與人相處當注意「口德」，以免誤傷他人而不知。請多說好話。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">6.各種謀求時，若能遵守以上則安。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤提醒交友、約會期間、求姻緣的注意事項：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問愛情前途者，當預防情人成仇人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">與情人相處說話時應當維持敬重，以免說話傷人而成怨偶。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">男女交往要預防感情被欺騙。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">小心不要被花言巧語迷昏了頭。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.選擇對象或尋找姻緣時，心態不要大小眼，以免錯失姻緣。不要有虛榮心，若專挑富貴豪門，不會有好結果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5.約會期間更勿喝酒。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">6.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若愛情困頓者，或分手者，或吵架者，「明朝仇敵又相隨」意味著同樣的困境可能還會發生，而這些困境少不了都是來自言語不相容，或是當初交友的態度就不正確所引來的後遺症。因此，你當思慮，當前的對象是否適合你，再決定要復合或放棄這個愛情。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">「明朝仇敵又相隨」，此話也意味著，這次考試恐又落榜了，所以還沒考完者，應對考試不可輕忽，若能提防幾個重點，也許還有機會。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試者，本籤提醒要用功讀書，不要到處嬉玩，不要到處交友，不要追逐明星，不要被其他事情分心等等，若能這樣讀書，務實讀書，才有機會考上。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">建議，針對此考試應該全力以赴，使出渾身解數，各種有助考試成績的方法都可以用上。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">也許你是問何時才能找到工作？應該找什麼樣的工作？求職方向如何？但是，這有比你所問更重要的，神明要提醒你。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇本籤提醒求職者在求職期間要注意的事項：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.求職期間小心社會陷阱，一些看似條件很好的工作，都要提防其中有詐。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.求職時，心態要腳踏實地，莫尋投機性的工作，或看起來浮華的工作。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.求職者若屬於老實人，更要預防被騙、被害。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤提醒經營事業幾個注意事項：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若作事業，當老實經營，不要有投機行為。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若與人合夥生意者，應當小心，預防被朋友連累或受害。或當預防有口角、經營糾紛，利益爭奪。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.交際應酬喝酒的行為，都要小心因此誤事。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.若事業經營有困境者，本籤提醒，同樣的困境可能再度發生。因此當檢討出問題的根本原因在哪裡，從該處下手，這才能遏止困境再發生。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆更換、換職、轉變<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問各種轉換，本籤第一句「捨舟遵路總相宜」，捨棄當前更有優勢者（優勢中含有不利者）而換另外一個單純的（單純中少了優勢但有其他好處），這也是可行的。但是，利弊得失要自己評估，是否真的要更換也要自己衡量。若沒有更換的話「明朝仇敵又相隨」，代表這個逆境還可能重複再來或延續一段時間。總結，在得失之間還是要自己評估再決定要不要更換。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤提醒療病期間的幾個注意事項：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.醫療期間預防被騙</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.選醫生要選有醫德的醫生</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.莫迷信名醫名藥</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.不要喝酒</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5.請用「自然療法」更佳（意即沒有副作用的療法，調控飲食和生活作息、調適心情、心態等等自然療法都可以療病）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆官司訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤意味著此糾紛將反反覆覆，目前尚無結果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官司之事，若能和者最佳。若是贏了，將來也是冤冤相報，雙方都受害，不會有好結果。所以，官司之事能停下來最好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">捨舟登路。宜踏實地。莫伴貴兒。自當年記。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>好中成惡。口舌立至。戒之慎之。樽節遊戲。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自記→事當牢記<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">得意濃時終失意。親朋遇我莫相隨。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>強言說得如甘蜜。那得開心見膽時。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">親蜜→浮華隊裏莫相隨。翻雲覆雨炎涼態。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤出入道路。宜踏實地。謹防親人侵害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">時酒遊戲。好中成惡。口舌立至。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟者休。病審醫。終不利。行人至。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名與利。莫貪求。宜謹慎。省是非也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言謀為。當擇交遊。凡事好中成惡。是處成非。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">所謂樽前兄弟。明朝仇敵也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若占名利。得此只宜安守。不可強求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡有出入。宜向善背惡。切勿輕忽。以貽後悔。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占孕生男。主有產難。慎之慎之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤一切所為。宜踏實地。交遊間更宜慎擇。謹防所與非人。侵耗陷害。口舌是非。酒色財氣結仇等情。唯冀慎之於先。免致受其籠絡。斯全身遠害之道得矣。凡事趨吉避凶。改惡從善。不可自誤。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">捨舟遵路。言風濤之險。不如道路之安。此譬為人。不可行險僥倖。須知安步徐行之意。故曰總相宜也。貴兒。乃富貴家子弟。看似聲勢可依。實則多華少實。多邪少正。多狡詐。少忠信。多狠惡。少良善。故戒勿與相逐也。樽前兄弟。是一時同流合污之態。明朝仇敵。或因乾餱失德。或因利盡交疏。小人反覆無常之狀。勢所必至矣。占者慎持則吉。忘戒則凶。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">楚中一士人。遠至晉地。干謁顯宦。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占得此籤後。果與公子笑言相席。謔前鬨鬧。其人忽悟籤語。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">次早不辭而歸。怨者欲害之而不得。其驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孫龐鬥智<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">齊國。孫臏，魏國人。龐涓。二人起初共同拜鬼谷子為師。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">龐涓之才學不如孫臏，曾經與孫臏鬥智卻輸了。龐涓忌妒孫臏的才能，以致兩人反目成仇，彼此謀害。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君子觀察此兩人，後來龐涓削孫臏的腳，而孫臏殺害龐涓，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">互相殘害，此二人非常不仁不智了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（好友因為互忌而成仇）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蕭朱隙末<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好朋友後來因誤會而反目成仇。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">語本後漢書˙卷二十七˙王丹傳：「張、陳凶其終，蕭、朱隙其末，故知全之者鮮矣。」<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（好友因誤會而成仇）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 69;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">庚癸<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.雷雨風雲各有司。<br/>2.至誠禱告莫生疑。<br/>3.與君定約為霖日。<br/>4.正是蘊隆中伏時。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.每件事情都各有管理者。（人間的每件事情，各有天神主管。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.你只要誠心祈禱不要懷疑（若能真誠祈求，天神可相助。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.和你約定連續三天以上的好日子（不同的項目則由不同的神明負責。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.應驗是在酷熱的夏季，中伏的日子時</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">中伏指夏季大暑後第二旬庚日<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">中伏：三伏的第二伏。指夏至後第四庚日。亦稱為「二伏」。（請查農民曆即知。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">三伏：初伏、中伏、末伏的合稱。從夏至後第三個庚日起，每十日為一伏，分別為初伏、中伏、末伏，是一年中最熱的時候。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各種求問之事，只要至誠求神，不管是難關或非難關者，神明將暗中幫助。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.此事應待時，每逢「庚」日為吉。每次神明會給予最少三天的應驗。請自行把握，若屬於扭轉或改變之事，請在此三天好好發揮，過了三天就要靠自己了。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.屬於長時效問題者，神明可以保佑三年三個月又三天的平安期。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">祈願者請持守五戒、行善修德。自己該努力的地方則要努力，不可閒坐等待。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.神明的暗助，隨著事情種類不同，可能暗助三天或三次或三年三個月又三天。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身求姻緣來臨者，請至誠求神，愛神可以為你安排，屆時還請自行把握。過了這段時間，續緣就要靠自己掌握了 。姻緣可望在逢「庚」之日降臨，請做好經營準備。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若求愛情挽回者，或有心儀的對象想要進一步發展者，天神可以暗助，請至誠求神，神明將暗助你們有三天的時間相處，請在此日子中自行把握，表現無私的真愛情操，而三天過後，就要靠自己了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問考試能否錄取者，本考試可望由神明暗助。請加緊用功，至誠求神，謹守五戒，廣修十善，以免變卦。<span lang="EN-US">(若考試求籤者，請稟報考試日期給神明。)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若在夏季求得本籤者，可望由神明的暗助而錄取。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若其他時間的考試，若本次沒有考取者，可望在三年三個月又三天之中再度赴考可以考取。但是，還是請努力準備不可懈怠。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇神明暗助是讓你的實力可發揮，而非牽你的手寫答案。所以，你還是得充實自己的實力為上。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問事業前途者，請至誠求神加持，以祈在三年三月又三日之內，事業順利成長。在此期間請多行善修德，不得造惡，以免事有變卦。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想要找工作或換工作者，神明將暗助讓你找到工作，但是此份工作的取捨還是在你自己。當過了暗助期，那找工作就要靠自己了。請在逢「庚」之日，全力尋找工作。神明可以暗助三次。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若屬慢性病者，神明暗助保佑三年三個月又三天的平安期。但是過後還是得靠自己。若想靠自己，請把握這三年中好好修行，以祈扭轉命運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶悔吝。各有神司。若問濟事。在中伏期。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>如旱得雨。恰慰雲電。凡所謀望。直待其時。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">期→時<span lang="EN-US"><br/>電→霓</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">貧富當知各有司。功名姻事待其時。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>謀望定應庚日至。季夏交臨事合宜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>富貴功名各有時。婚姻遲速待相宜。<br/>須逢庚日探消息。季夏交臨爾自知。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先凶後吉。凡事謀望。且待季夏中伏時。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">運漸亨。訟即解。名利且待時。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚宜遲。行無信。病且禳。謀事逢庚日。方得成就也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雷雨風雲。天之變態也。吉凶貧賤。人之變態也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求名者占此。期在三年三月三日之內。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">為霖雨者。事之濟也。爾雅云。雨三日為霖。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">夏月有三伏。占者必過三數。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">逢庚子為大利。若夏月占之亦利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤言世間一切事故。冥冥中有主之者。須待時候已到。機緣自就。如禱雨者。至誠感動。亦須仰奉天命。然後風伯雨師。方得應候施行。後二句。是言雨降之期。在中伏之際。凡事皆可類推。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">雷雨風雲。天之變態也。各有司。言各有管攝之權。非可任意操縱也。人生窮通得喪。亦復如是。至誠禱告。神鑒占籤者之忱悃也。霖為時雨。左傳雨三日以往為霖。亦可作三數斷。定約。以示定期。蘊隆。乃大旱之際。中伏乃大暑後第二旬庚日。言雨降在此時也。雖藉禱雨為詞。一切希望。皆作是觀。總以待時為妙。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生科舉。占得此後。取二等。應中伏時也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">發案在三月。應在為霖日也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王曾祈禱<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋朝。王曾，字孝先。益都人。自小聰明，善作文章。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">咸平年間，鄉試、會試、殿試都第一名，做僕射、同平章事…（宋朝宰相）等官。封沂國公。諡號文正。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">做官時，遇到乾旱。就虔誠祈禱，直到降雨才停止。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他在朝廷。言行正直，舉止合宜。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾說：執政者。如果只想把恩德歸自己，那做錯了誰該負責呢？范仲淹很佩服他的話。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">戴平仲禱祈格天<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戴封，字平仲，東漢時濟北剛人</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">今山東寧陽</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Arial Unicode MS'';"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戴封十五歲時，就去首都洛陽的太學讀書，跟從東海籍的鄮地縣長申先生學習。申先生去世後，戴封護葬至東海，歸途中經過自己的家。戴封的父母以為兒子要回家長住，預先為兒子娶妻成親。戴封拜見過雙親後，不過夜就返回京城，繼續自己未完成的學業。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時戴封的同學石敬平，染瘟疫而死，戴封先是照顧，後來又為他辦喪事，拿米糧換錢買小棺木，送喪到石家。石家重新埋葬，開棺時看見石敬平時的書籍物品皆在棺中，覺得很奇特！（意思是戴封不貪朋友財物）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戴封後來遇到盜賊，把他的東西洗劫一空。戴封只剩下七匹綢緞，因為賊不知戴封把綢緞藏在何處而未掠走。戴封追上盜賊對他們說︰「我知道你們是因有困難而當強盜，所以才趕來，把這七匹綢緞，一並送給你們，希望你們以後，從事其它的正當職業。」盜賊聽了感動的說︰「你真是好人呀！」就把搶劫的東西全還給戴封。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來被推薦是孝廉（漢朝選拔人才的標準），做光祿主事的官，伯父死時，戴封辭官。皇帝下詔，徵求賢良方正，敢正直發言之士、有好品行能消災降魔</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">的人，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">朝廷內官和地方首長各推舉一人。郡長及大司農（朝廷官名）都推舉戴封。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">舉行朝廷考試得第一名，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">官車送</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戴封</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">晉見皇帝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，又被提拔做議郎（官名）。又改派任西華縣長。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時汝、穎地方有蝗虫災害，蝗虫不飛入西華地方。當時督郵（官名）巡視縣境，蝗虫忽然大批飛至。督郵當日即離去，蝗虫也馬上消失，全地方人都覺得奇特。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">那年也鬧旱災，戴封在祈禱無效下，就堆積木材，自己坐上面自焚。當火起時，卻突然降大雨把火澆熄了，於是大家都佩服戴封是有德人士。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來，又改當中山相【官名】，那時各縣死囚四百多人，判決已定，就要行刑。戴封哀求，把死囚遣送歸家，與死囚約好日期來受刑，全都沒違約者。皇帝下詔讚美此事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">永元十二年，又被徵拜當太常（官名），死在任上。</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 70;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛甲<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.喜鵲簷前報好音。<br/>2.知君千里欲歸心。<br/>3.繡幃重結鴛鴦帶。<br/>4.葉落霜飛寒色侵。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">鵲→雀<span lang="EN-US"><br/>飛寒→凋暮</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.喜鵲飛來屋簷前報告這個好消息（你事先得知有關他的消息）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.知道你在千里之外急欲歸來（你急欲知道這重逢能否實現）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.重繡香囊與鴛鴦帶（鴛鴦帶：男女期盼久別重逢的飾帶）（你準備了期盼重逢的黃絲帶或各種飾帶，或做了有助重逢的行為。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.正逢落葉霜飛的秋天與寒氣逼侵的冬天（在這氣氛下你們終於相逢了）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.各種謀望，可望在秋冬間達成。需要進行各種事宜者，請在此期間進行。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.本籤對於已經分離之男女來說屬於吉籤，對於其他狀況則未必。若愛情平順者求得此籤，則本籤成為預言之凶籤，故屬不吉。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.本籤也代表事情又重來。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"><br/>◇若單身求問姻緣何時來？<br/>此籤代表姻緣晚成。大約在三十歲以後。（還請忍耐點吧）</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>本籤代表即使能追到手，結果還是會告吹。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前男女相處尚稱順意，欲知未來前途者，本籤暗示，你們的結局還是分手。若這些日子以來，你覺得此對象很優秀而不想放棄的話，那你就得賣命修行，提升道行了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若情人即將分手者，或有分手疑慮者，不管怎麼樣，你還是得力挽狂瀾，以最快速度挽回，本籤意味著，這一分手恐會造成長長久久的分手。所以，若你要保留這份愛情的話，不管怎麼樣，你都要謙讓一切，以試圖恢復愛情。在此關鍵時刻，請好自為之。（在此奉勸吵架者別嘔氣太久，若不原諒對方的話，那就會苦等許多年，這可不好受的。若能一念覺醒，拋開怨仇，寬容以對，那就能提早改善宿命。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 23.9pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若情人分手許久或夫妻分離多年者，本籤代表經過多時（多年）的思念日子後，相聚重逢的日子即將來到。就在那秋冬之際，在那淒滄氣氛之中，你們久別重逢了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="a1" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 23.9pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">總結，本籤代表愛情會分手，而分手後很多年，才又重新再來。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若久年無孕或無子者，問能否懷孕或生子，你的謀望可望在秋冬之間達成。請多做功課、功德，多求神佛加被，以祈順利成功。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、各種更換<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若當前工作不稱心，想要離職更換工作者，在秋天和冬天則是良機。若在其他季節更換，則未必有利。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆理財<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問財運者，此籤代表這幾年你的財運還是老樣子，總是處在期盼狀態下，沒有機會收成。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好音報喜。遠涉方回。交冬之際。家室和諧。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡事終吉。且待將來。自有成就。不必疑猜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">將→時<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事要經畫。須待好時來。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>到底方就成。何必致疑猜。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡事要經畫。求謀且待時。<br/>當年悲破鏡。暮景得相隨。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先難後易。凡事守舊。謀望待時。心無掛礙。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好行陰騭。神明來佑。遭保亨通。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟事有理。功名漸通。婚主再合。求財未遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">問病主凶丑。凡事謀望。宜在秋冬方知也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名多不遂意。所期在後。而謀事求財在深秋。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">早冬之際。必有成就。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">禽鳥得氣之先。故鵲知遠人有佳信至。則報之圖事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">有成就則報之。但所惜者不久。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若吉者處方亨之日。必有意外之禍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求全之悔。家宅主有陰人。疾病又當慎之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤離而又合。去而復還之象。凡事機兆已動。現有好音。如歸家者已通消息。不日間可團聚。自有夫妻諧和之樂。但暮景霜侵。草木零落。必主晚成。及年力衰遲之際也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">喜雀善能報喜。行人將至。預報好音。是以歸心一動。雖隔千里之遙。識者已先知之矣。杜詩。柴門烏鵲噪。歸客千里至。此其驗也。鴛鴦重結。久別乍歸之情。葉落霜凋。應在秋冬時也。然幾經艱難盼望。而始得有今日。則其時亦已晚矣。故曰暮色侵也。占者事有成就。難望早達。重字或主重婚之應。他事亦可作兩次斷。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人妻子。深秋抱病。占此其妻遂亡。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">第三句苟之。應直如面告也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蘇武還鄉（蘇武還漢）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。蘇武，字子鄉。杜陵人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">天漢年初，以中郎將身份，奉命出使匈奴的蘇武，被滯留在匈奴，蘇武為了維持其忠於漢朝的節操，在海上（居延海，匈奴地名）牧羊十九年。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">那時，單于留下蘇武，騙漢朝說蘇武死了。後來漢使節至匈奴，探聽知蘇武所在。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就請匈奴放人，漢使者騙說蘇武曾用飛雁傳信，使漢皇知道他正在海上牧羊，請單于放人。匈奴驚訝以為他是神，就放他回去了。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 71;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛乙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.河渠傍路有高低。<br/>2.可歎長途日已西。<br/>3.縱有榮華好時節。<br/>4.直須猴犬換金雞。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.河渠旁邊的道路高低不平（比喻事情困境難行）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.又感嘆長途跋涉又遇到日落西山（又逢機緣不好）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.即使有好的命運</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.也要等到猴、雞、狗這三年</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.目前運勢不佳此乃命運。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.當前的各種謀求都不容易。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.長線的好運將在猴、雞、狗這三年（其中雞年最佳）。每年的好運在陰曆七、八、九月（其中八月最佳）。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"><br/>◇若問姻緣何時來？◇若問當前心儀的對象可否進一步發展？<br/>此籤代表你的姻緣路走來坎坷難行，而且現在時機也不利於你的求姻緣。還請等到猴、雞、狗這幾年，你才有好姻緣出現。雖然每年陰曆的七、八、九月你有機會遇到姻緣，但是這姻緣不會有好成果。所以還是等待吧！而這段期間建議多多充實<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，這能讓未來的愛情運加分喔！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前已經交往的姻緣前途？或問何時可以結婚？你當前的感情狀況還不穩定，若想論及婚假，還得等到猴、雞、狗這三年。婚架若決定在雞年進行者，則最稱意順利。建議還是先充實些<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前分手者，欲問何時能復合？你的感情經營的不好，以致如今分手了，若想復合前，還是得先充實<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>。以期盼在陰曆七、八、九月間能復合。但是你的感情路還是起起落落，這是你要有心理準備。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試能否錄取，若考試在陰曆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七、八、九月者，可望考得佳績。<span lang="EN-US"><br/></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若考試放榜日在申、酉、戌者，可望錄取。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">而其他時間的考試，請自求多福。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若想要找工作者，請於每月陰曆的</span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">申、酉、戌日全力尋找，可望獲得成果。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">最佳的求職時機在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陰曆的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七、八、九月。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"><br/>當前事業表現不佳，又逢景氣不振，此要等到猴、雞、狗這三年，才是你大展宏圖之年。每年的陰曆七、八、九月，也是你振作的月份，而其他月份，還請作較壞的打算準備。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若當前工作狀況不佳想要換工作者，那陰曆七、八、九月，是你跳槽的最佳時機。只是跳歸跳，你還是得等到猴、雞、狗這三年才算順遂。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆創業<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若想創業的話，那現在時機不好，你還是在猴年開始進行吧！但是，狗年過後，可要自求多福了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問病況前途者，本籤顯示此病有惡化之危險。<br/>請給予</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">消業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">處理，以減輕病苦。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆失物<span lang="EN-US"><br/>失物遺落在西方，但是尋回不易。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你的最佳的投資理財時間在猴、雞、狗這三年。每年的最佳時間在陰曆七、八、九月。其他時間請務必保守。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">修路崎嶇。況當衰晚。求事多難。徒自嗟嘆。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>逢申酉戍。年月日見。若遇此時。稍可如願。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">平川靜處被風傷。愛巧番成拙一場。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>縱饒願得平川靜。只恐榮華不久長。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>多少登場沒下場。平川靜處被風傷。<br/>眼前光景渾如夢。只恐榮華不久長。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤干防有險阻。平地濃難。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">俗云。閉門家裏坐。禍從天上來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">逢申酉戍年月日方吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟凶。財遲。功名難。婚姻晚。孕生必驚。病主險。事多凶也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">主日平地涉險。凡事掣用。是乃命之所致。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此。不必嗟嘆。遇申戍年月日。頗得遂意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">至酉上大得利。所謂崎嶇歷而通衢至也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤險阻多端。事有蹉跌。人防陷害。如行河畔崎嶇之路。又值日色將晚。險何如乎。凡事勉強前進。凶不可言。就此中止。庶可免禍。縱有晚景。須遇申酉戌年月日。或申酉戌運限。可冀有成耳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">路有高低。險阻之象。況在河渠之傍。則更險矣。長途可嘆。何等艱難。況日晷西移。轉瞬將就昏黑。欲能出險得乎。申屬猴。戌屬犬。酉屬雞。縱有榮華。等待申酉戌年月日時方應。言現在運程甚凶。切宜耐守也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生宗師考試。占此獲二等科舉。發案得報消息。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">乃丙申日黃昏時榮華二語。應之不爽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">范蠡歸湖<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春秋時代。范蠡，字少伯。吳地方人。與文種（人名）同為越國大夫。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">吳國滅越國，范蠡與范種，為越王勾踐獻策略，謙卑投降。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">又求民間美女，將西施獻給吳王。等到滅吳國功成，范蠡知勾踐可與共同患難，不可共享安樂，就辭官。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">乘小舟遊西湖，定居在陶（地名）。又從商致富，稱陶朱公。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">搬家三次，才出名。後來不知去向。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">荀卿五十遊學<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">荀子，</span></strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:11pt;">名</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">況，又稱孫卿，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD" title="戰國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:11pt;">戰國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">時期</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%B5%B5%E5%9B%BD" title="趙國"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:11pt;">趙國</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">人。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">五十歲的時候才到齊國來遊說講學。鄒衍的學說曲折誇大而多空洞的論辯；鄒奭的文章完備周密但難以實行；淳於髡，若與他相處日久，時常學到一些精闢的言論。所以齊國人稱頌他們說：「高談闊論的是鄒衍。精雕細刻的是鄒奭。智多善辯，議論不絕的是淳於髡。」田駢等人都已在齊襄王時死去，此時荀卿是年紀最長，資歷最深的宗師。當時齊國仍在補充列大夫的缺額，荀卿曾先後三次以宗師的身分，擔任稷下地方的祭酒〈負責祭典的官〉。後來，齊國有人譭謗荀卿，荀卿就到了楚國，春申君讓他擔任蘭陵令〈縣長〉。</span><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:''Arial Unicode MS'';"></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春申君死後，荀卿被罷官，便在蘭陵地方定居。李斯曾是他的學生，後來李斯在秦朝任丞相。荀卿憎惡亂世的黑暗政治，亡國昏亂的君主接連不斷地出現，他們不通曉常理正道，卻被裝神弄鬼的巫祝〈祭司〉所迷惑，相信求神就能賜福去災，庸俗鄙陋的儒生拘泥于瑣碎禮節，再加上莊周等人狡猾多辯，敗壞風俗，於是採究儒家、墨家、道家思想活動的成功和失敗，編著了幾萬字的文章便辭世了。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">被</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">埋葬在蘭陵地方。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 72;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛丙<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.憶昔蘭房分半釵。<br/>2.而今忽把信音乖。<br/>3.痴心指望成連理。<br/>4.到底誰知事不諧。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.回憶往昔在居所互定盟約（分半釵：雙方各執釵的一半，以誓盟約。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而如今忽然違背誓言（乖：背離。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.痴心等待此事能有好結果（不死心等待能有好結果）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.到底這事情還是不能和諧啊（事情終究不容易）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.事情有差錯不和諧、不湊巧，故終不能如願。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若與人有約，當防毀約，更防事後有糾紛。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.各種好事，當防變卦。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.事情一旦去了，就不再回頭了</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問姻緣何時來？ ◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你當前的狀況不是很好喔！即使能得到姻緣或追求到手，也會因為「變心」而結束這傷痛的愛情。建議以後再求吧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若男女分手欲求挽回或當前關係不和諧者<span lang="EN-US"><br/>此籤詩應該最符合你們處境，過去的相愛（海誓山盟），如今已毀約（變心），而如今痴心期盼能有和諧的日子，這是有困難的。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇雖然曾經相知相憶又相愛，但由於時局不湊巧或人的變心，此段戀情只能成為追憶。既然對方都已經變心了，時局也不同以往了，那你還期待什麼呢！放下吧！因為你還有新的戀情在後面等你呢！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，愛情求得本籤者，剛開始雖然曾經遂意一時，但是人性難免會變心（花心），而令愛情走樣，因此導致你的傷心、難過，而勢必要曲終人散，即使痴心的等待，也一樣不會有好結果，因此建議，早早放下這種傷痛的愛情吧！<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若已婚者求得本籤，雖然夫妻勢必分手，但是可望再婚。而未婚者分手後，則可另遇姻緣。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、換職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>此籤詩代表你在工作上不稱意，做的不能得心應手，而導致你想要離去這個工作，就算等待事情能好轉，這似乎也是有困難的。因此，你只好換個工作吧！可以找到工作的。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.此事業一旦衰敗了，就再也不能興起了。（這大概是黃昏事業吧！）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若合夥事業者，代表盟友違背契約，而導致事業停擺，以致這個事業將曲終人散。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、升遷、升官、競賽、錄用<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問各種功名者，雖然喜訊傳來了，但是恐怕事後又消失了。你也不用痴心等待了，因為結果還是「空」。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆失物、尋找<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">各種東西、人、寵物一旦遺失，就再也找不回了。即使痴心的找，也找不到了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問治病者，若屬慢性病或腫瘤之類者，當今醫學都無法醫好，這是以人的宿命而言。若你的病狀還不嚴重的話，也許，修行可以讓你改造命運。只要走修行路線，這病就沒那麼嚴重。得腫瘤但卻沒依照醫生宣判時間死亡的人，也是有的。若還在中年者，更應該以修行來治療自己，而不要淪落宿命安排。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事多離散。難望再成。痴心未解。尚自客情。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>縱能強合。終必敗盟。凡事謀望。守宇真誠。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">自情→有縈情<span lang="EN-US"><br/>守誠→另改途程</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟事有阻。問財成空。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>家人嗃嗃。憂心忡忡。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟空→婚姻莫問。財利落空。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤事多散。艱再合。雖強合。終不久長。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病險。訟不吉。功名虛喜。婚主重娶。終不到頭。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行人不至。孕驚恐。墳宅空虛也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言婚不諧。訟者休問。名利始終更變。決難永保。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但人之痴心未絕。徒勞指望。凡事皆難。不止名利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">孕不成。子難養。雖無鼓盆之怨。亦有陰人之損。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(註▼鼓盆或指包公之烏盆案。謀財害命。搬屍窯洞。火化造盆)</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤戒勿輕信。凡事與人有約。始雖和合如意。亦是巧言虛花。終無準實。如婚姻之轉瞬敗盟也。及早參透。免自擾累。或可另作亡羊補牢之計。若終受愚弄。非徒無益。而受害多矣。人情如此。其可不知悟乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蘭房。指女子閨閣之地。分半釵。各執釵之半。以為信也。人情始約之稠密。大都類此。信音乖。情意中變。翻雲覆雨之習態也。則知此婚已不可合。此事已不可成明矣。連理。比夫婦成雙之義。癡心指望。繫念不已。自坐癡迷也。謀不可合之婚。圖不可成之事。是以到底無成。旁觀早已知之。當局者苦不知悟耳。占此可以知返矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人為子擇媳。占此。不信籤意而強成之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其子婚。不數月。出外經營。失意浪蕩不歸。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其媳堅志。苦守清節以終。其驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又<span lang="EN-US">(清)光緒間。晉江縣。有人為其妻問病。占此。竟斷絃。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">王昭君憶漢帝<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">昭君，歸州人，是漢元帝宮女。匈奴和親時，昭君上書皇帝讓她和親。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">嫁單于後，昭君的心不曾忘漢王。曾上漢帝書說：「臣妾僥倖當後宮妃子，以為身在宮中，死了也能留名，沒料到被畫師陷害，遠嫁番邦。是我命不好，奈何我還有父有弟，願君王因為可憐我而疼愛他們。」</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">齊侯興師伐蔡<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%BD%8A%E6%A1%93%E5%85%AC"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">桓公</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二十九年（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D657%E5%B9%B4" title="前657年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">657</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），桓公和蔡姬在水中遊玩，蔡姬晃船，桓公心怕，阻止蔡姬。蔡姬不聽，晃個不停。齊桓公出船，大發雷霆，把蔡姬送了回去。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蔡國也不高興，把蔡姬又嫁給別人。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">桓公發怒，興兵討伐。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">桓公三十年春（</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%89%8D656%E5%B9%B4" title="前656年"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">前</span><span style="COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;"><font face="Times New Roman">656</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">年</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">），齊桓公帶領魯、宋、陳、衛、鄭、</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%AE%B8" title="許"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">許</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、曹七國諸侯伐蔡。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">（此故事意味，事剛開始，雙方雖然情同意合，但是事後雙方毀約，而後卻戰爭一場。）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 73;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七四籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛丁<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.崔巍崔魏復崔巍。<br/>2.履險如夷去復來。<br/>3.身似菩提心似鏡。<br/>4.長安一道放春回。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.危險危險又危險(崔巍指高峻崎嶇)</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.經歷了危險如走平地般的來回</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.身體如菩提樹，心如鏡子。<br/>（代表聰慧能幹，就能解決問題。也代表要反思自己即是解藥。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.終於傳來好消息（長安：首都、京城，代表與所問事相關的最重要地方。春，代表一種成果。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.有驚無險，先難後易。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.只要反觀自照就有答案，就能解決問題。（意即要反思自己，或要反向操作這件事情）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若能這樣這樣做，事情反而有大利。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"><br/>◇若單身者問姻緣何時來？或問未來愛情發展？<br/>此籤說明你未來的愛情發展，會經歷一段瀕臨分手的過程，當面臨此際遇時，若你能聰慧的處理他，就能化險為夷。這可以說，此愛情要經歷一段長時間的發展，而後能有好成果。此籤詩也暗喻，你接下來遇到的姻緣，你們將可能因此結婚。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？可否進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>是可以追求，也可以進一步發展，但是請準備好應對吵架或分手的應對招數，以便將來可以逢凶化吉，若能通過這關卡，就能奪得愛情歸。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或關係困頓者。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>此刻正是你發揮聰明智慧的時刻了，只要有佛法就有辦法，任何大小困境，只要你發揮智慧處理，那就能迎刃而解這個困境，而後使愛情有個好歸宿。請自反思，看看自己是否犯了什麼錯誤，只要能發現自己的過失，那就知道怎麼處理這問題了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、各種競勢、事業、學業等各種前途<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">謀得此籤，代表此事會經歷一段危險期，這個困境要用自己的智慧去化解，只要能通過這困境，那此事最後就能有好成果。因此，當你處在目前的危機時，不用急著逃跑，也許你可以為此事助一臂之力，也許你要反思自己，也許你必須反向思考這件事情，因而化解難關，此難關通過後，則是柳暗花明又一村。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆官司訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">屬於此類之問題，本籤顯示這個官司會經歷一個對己不利的階段，但是只要你發揮聰明智慧，這也是可以平安脫險的，而後還能得到最後的勝訴。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這個疾病會經歷一個危險期，但其實問題不大，從你的身與心之內，就可以找到解救之方。請自檢視疾病的來源，若能發現是作息、飲食不當者，將之調整過來即可病癒。若本身可以發現是最近心情有問題者，將心情調適好，此病也自然康復了。此籤也暗示，疾病的病源就是在自己內心，因此多多自我反思，就能找到藥方。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想投資理財者，這次的投資是有風險性的，局勢如驚濤駭浪，但是只要「反思」，就知道事情該怎麼做。只要你能多多動用智慧，那就能獲得這個好前途。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">路途嵩險。心卻平夷。轉凶為吉。終免憂疑。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>更宜守正。切莫改移。履道坦坦。何福不隨。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嵩夷→傾彝<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">至再至三方見效。聿然機會可重逢。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>此心無愧何憂事。謀盡終成不計功。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>至再至三險已深。天公默鑒後凋心。<br/>從茲坦蕩長安道。出谷遷鶯到上林。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤重有重險。心似平康。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事先難後易。婚久方成。病險後安。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟凶。財可緩求。行人匆匆。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">萬物至春後。諸事轉凶成吉之象。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">唐。宣宗時。則諒荒酒。為邪魔委于深崖中。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">家人不知其處。默禱于神。有履險如夷之說。明蚤得從間道歸。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡占名利也。主三數之巧。春夏頗利。至秋大利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大抵人能平其心。正其身則吉福自臻矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤事有重險。目前甚屬艱難。然賴神明默相。雖在危險之中。如履康莊之路。蓋緣平日身具善根。足以感格天意。此時心含智慧。足以權度機宜。故能脫險而亨。行登長安道上。春色滿前。正有無限好景。占者唯慎持身心。益加積累。以迓天麻斯善耳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">崔巍。高峻崎嶇之地。重言以申警之。險之至也。夷。平地也。去復來。言行止得以自由。險不為害也。菩提。善果也。鏡明也。身似菩提之善。而心如鏡之明。是以自天祐之。吉無不利。長安道上。功名富貴之路。放春回。言功名富貴逼人而來。如春色之榮暢也。占吉而身心皆吉。斯應驗如何矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人求婚。占此。娶妻至家。好著聰慧。應身似菩提一句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人鄉居。四面皆倭寇。急欲脫去。占此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">夜從閒道得入郡城。應履險如夷一句。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又<span lang="EN-US">(清)同治。甲子。福建鄉試。晉江一生。問名占此。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">迨到省後。忽值鄰省有警停考。回路又問沿途。劫掠大慘。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">正躊躇間。適有崔姓武官。邀他隨同。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">林提軍來泉。中途遇雨。延至十月初四日。乃到家。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此占不特全詩多應。連題亦驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">崔武求官<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東周列國，晉國襄惠王時代，崔武上書，議論國事，惠王認為崔武賢能，降旨聘崔武入朝，官封右丞相，專理國事，此後晉國興盛，都因為</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">崔</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">武忠心護國，百姓安樂，崔武功勞浩大。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竇禹鈞折桂<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">三字經云：「竇燕山，有義方，教五子，名俱揚」，即為此處所指之「竇氏」，竇公乃為五代後周時燕山人，救濟窮困之人，不遺餘力，而他原本命中無子，後因力行善事，日夜不怠，而改變了命運。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">竇公家中有一位僕人，偷了他二百千錢，寫了一張賣身契，掛在自己的幼女背上，將她送到竇家，說：「永賣此女，以償債務」，遂逃離家鄉，不再回來。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">竇公憐其苦情，反將契約焚燬，而撫養他的幼女。到了該女成年時，並為其選擇一位好人家將其嫁出。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡是親友中有喪不能葬者，出錢為他埋葬，有女不能嫁者，出錢為她嫁出。每年收入，除去生活必需費用之外，全部拿來作周濟他人之用。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">竇公又在住宅南端，建立一座書院，藏書數千冊，以優薪禮聘名師，教授四方清寒之士，由此而顯揚之人，不在少數。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不久之後，連生五子，皆聰明英俊，後又夢見他的袓父告訴他：「你數年來所做的功德，很是浩大，上天都把它記下了，並延長你的壽命三紀（十二年為一紀），五子皆顯耀，你更當勉勵，不可懈怠！」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">而後，長子儀做了禮部尚書，次子儼做了禮部侍郎，三子侃做了右補闕，四子偁做了右諫議大夫，五子僖做了起居郎，所生八孫，亦皆顯貴。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">竇公的善行，讓他得到五位顯揚的孩子，就像被他折下五枝名貴的丹桂一般。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">　　竇公享年八十有二，無病談笑而逝。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆註解：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">竇禹鈞即竇燕山</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">僕人偷竇公的錢，竇公反而養他的幼女，竇公如此反向操作，故後來贏得好命運。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 74;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七五籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛戊<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.生前結得好緣姻。<br/>2.一笑相逢情自親。<br/>3.相當人物無高下。<br/>4.得意休論富與貧。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.由於過去生曾經結過好緣</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.因此相逢之下格外親和</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.彼此都是相當人物沒有高下之分</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.事情都能得意，也不用談論有多少富與貧</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你和此事或此人過去有很好的緣</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.你對於此人或此事，情有獨鍾，不用挑此事或此人的條件。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.終將和此人或此事結為連理</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"><br/>眼光獨到，情有獨鍾，非君莫娶，非汝不嫁，此乃宿緣，故必連理。<br/></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問姻緣何時來？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你可以不用著急，你的他也正等著你，雖然當前尚未出現，但是，他勢必不會被他人搶走。當你遇到「一見鍾情」的對象時，那就是和你互定終身的另一伴了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？當前交往的對象可否進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>本籤代表，你當前遇到的他（她），就是你的真命天子（天女）了，你們將是「非汝不娶，非君不嫁。」所以，就請安心展開你的進展吧。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若交往多年者，問此愛情前途或可否結婚？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你們是天生的一對，自過去生以來，已經多生結為連理，而此生當然也不例外，若想結婚，那就隨時進行吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或關係困頓者，或問此人是否正緣？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤代表你們之間從過去世以來就已經有很深的緣分了，因此，即使你們總是吵吵鬧鬧，或是分分合合，你們也是分不開的。所以，當前的你們只能好好相處，而不要計較是非、貧賤富貴了。請充實些愛情學分吧！</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作、求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">屬於這方面的問題者，你只要選擇你喜歡的、投緣的那種工作就行，因為你只鍾愛這種工作，也因此你將專精於此道。既然對此工作這麼鍾愛，那就不用問此工作有多少榮華富貴了，相信你可以把這工作，做的很專精的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆學業、考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你就選擇一個你喜歡的科目去考試與就讀吧！因為別的科系你也沒興趣，你只鍾愛自己所喜歡的這個科目。所以就放心去考去讀吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資理財<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問股市投資者，請作長期投資，則對你有利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">既有夙約。一見如故。所謀皆同。事多就緒。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>何必相逢。又分爾汝。且順而行。事無齟齬。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩情如水素流通。何況機緣舊日同。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>分外人交分外話。如鴻遇順穩乘風。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>兩情如水素流通。恰有機緣向此投。<br/>鳥集高林魚躍浪。春風和煦任優遊。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大吉。凡事遂意。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名高。財物聚。病即安。訟者得遇清官。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚合。行人回。孕生男。更修善。祈神佑吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">結得好緣。言緣雖多。得處甚少。功名必<span lang="EN-US">(遂)。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">舊有根基。今始得濟。財貨如前。無損無益。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡百求謀有傾。蓋如故之人扶持無高下。謂彼此兩平配。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若得意。休生議論。要當知足。訟必准。終難嬴。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤事有前緣。不須勞力。自然遇合湊巧。蓋稱量彼此之間。彼既脫去俗塵。此相遇可落凡近。是以一見傾心。格外投契。不復在世情貧富間論也。婚姻和合。諸事相宜。道途遂意。謀望皆能如願矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好姻緣。姻緣正好也。然由生前培植所致。甚非偶爾。種麻得麻。種豆得豆。自然之效也。一笑情親。相見恨晚之意。人物相當。言其才具品地。兩不相下也。既有前緣。均堪匹敵。自不以富相耀。以貧見疏也。觀此。而所以自植其才與德者。可不豫乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一顯宦欲與貧士結親。占此後其婿果登上第。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一富商欲與貧友經營。占此後。其友果能興財致富。皆不論貧富之驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又表弟陳遠江。內史府試時。臨結榜占得此籤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤意明示以前列結得好緣。是指第一也。後果結榜首。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又晉江。郭氏子。科試占此。入場坐結字。其前號乃生字。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">係渠等友陳子也。二人相逢。同發一笑。至掛榜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">郭在二字二十三名。陳在二等二十四名。此則上三句摘摯之應也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">秋嵐王嚗識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">劉小姐愛蒙正<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">呂蒙正，太太是劉氏。國防部劉文茂之女。蒙正未顯貴時，劉文茂輕視蒙正，後悔將愛女嫁給蒙正。但是劉小姐獨愛蒙正，兩人同居於破窯。她看蒙正舉止不凡，知蛟龍非久困池中物也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來果然成名天下，三次當丞相，封侯庇蔭子孫。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">梁鴻配孟光</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">『舉案齊眉』這個成語講的是東漢賢士梁鴻的妻子孟光的故事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">相傳孟光隨梁鴻至吳地為人傭工。梁鴻歸家，孟光每為俱食，舉案齊眉，以表示對丈夫的敬重。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">但這位賢婦的模樣卻『粗陋無比』，『肥醜而黑』，能『力舉石臼』。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">梁鴻未婚前，名氣就很大，許多人家都要把女兒嫁他，他都不答應。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">孟光未嫁時，有人給她做媒，她都不肯嫁，說是『必嫁梁鴻』。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">夫婦婚后第二天，孟光就脫去新娘綺羅之服，換上粗布衣衫，操持家務。後隨梁鴻隱居霸陵山中，男耕女織，吟詩彈琴，夫婦唱和，過著清貧而和諧的生活。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="TEXT-JUSTIFY:inter-ideograph;TEXT-ALIGN:justify;LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 75;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七六籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛己<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.三千法律八千文。<br/>2.此事何如說與君。<br/>3.善惡兩途君自作。<br/>4.一生禍福此中分。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一切因果報應條文多如麻</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.這事如何跟你說清楚</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.一切善惡，都是自作自受。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.禍福果報，就此中分。（意即，若決定以善而行者，則未來善報之。若以惡而作者，惡報必隨之。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這件事情，你要自己思考，自己決定，你心理應該有個譜才是。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">思考的原則；只要事情的出發點是「善」，那你就可以做。反之，若做此事的用意是「惡」那你就不當做。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你要知道；善有善報，惡有惡報，不是不報，時機未到。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">考慮事情當不當作，你要自思；<span lang="EN-US"><br/>「我為什麼要做這件事？」、「我有沒有能力做這件事？」、「做這件事的價值在哪裡？」種種的思考…，若能如此思考，你就得到答案了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這次的決定，將關鍵你未來的禍福，所以要理性想清楚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆各種求問，請參考以上，自行思考，自行決定。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若單身問姻緣何時來？可不可求姻緣？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>自己的狀況自己最清楚，求姻緣是好是壞，自己當思量。當你決定了，這也是人生命運禍福的分界點。若此事是「善」，那當然可行。若思考結果發覺這是「惡」，那你當阻止自己。要不要求因緣，那請自思吧！</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？當前的愛情可否進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若交往多年者，問此愛情前途或可否結婚者？<br/>本籤意味著，這件事情還是需要由你自己決定，自己思考。只要你理性思考，你應該可以知道，這事要不要發展下去，可不可和他結婚。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若愛情不睦或分手者，或關係困頓者，此段愛情要如何走下去，該不該繼續下去，這都是你自己要審慎的，也是你自己可以思考而得到答案的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;TEXT-INDENT:0cm;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，若選擇姻緣者，若知對方品德很差、好賭、好鬥、作姦犯科等等問題時，那你還要選他嗎？像這類似這些問題，那就是你要自己思考的。若決定錯誤了，那命運也從此中分了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問這個事業要不要做，這個工作好不好等類似問題，你要自行思考：<br/>1.此事是善是惡，若是惡那就不做。<br/>2.若非惡事，還要考慮現在作適合嗎？有必要這樣做嗎？這事值得作嗎？自己有能力、時間做嗎？我做這事的目的？種種的思考……<br/>總之，這事情都要自己相清楚，然後自己決定。只要你知道善惡，那自然能自得最佳解答。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">吉凶多變。非止一端。言不盡意。當以心觀。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>福因積善。禍胎稔惡。知所趨避。宜自先覺。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟庭有險莫求尋。只恐憂疑亂了心。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡事要知前定數。但將善惡自浮沉。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>訟庭有險莫胡行。無是無非夢不驚。<br/>禍福原來無定數。權衡善惡自分明。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀事。陰人議論不盡。當以心觀。積善福來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">積惡禍胎。修善避惡。宜自先覺。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚宜審擇。財未遂。病不防。訟主凶。宜作福。方吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言吉凶通塞。當遂所占之事。以理推之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如作善降祥。作不善降殃。所謂此中分也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求功名者。初未遂。後顯擢。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事營謀。有二條路。占者宜審決於善趨惡避。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">切莫貪取躁進。大抵先憂後喜也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤謀為陰事。神不之告。如法律操自官府。豈得預行宣洩。唯是禍福無門。全憑善惡判斷。所為善。自應得福。所為惡。自應得禍。禍福之機。人自知之。將求福而避禍。可不急去惡而遷善哉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">律文。刑書也。三千。以罪條言。八千以字數言。生死輕重。權歸刑曹。非外人所得與聞。故云如何說與君也。然有不可知而可知者。決之於善惡兩途而已。善惡唯人自作。則禍福亦唯人自求之耳。蓋凡事當務善以去惡也。聖意深切著明。人其凜之。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生人場畢。自謂文字得意。占此竟無名。後收原卷觀之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">前場密圈擬元。後場則塗抹不堪矣。此三四兩句之驗也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又余姑丈。龔慎齊。明經當廩保時。占財氣。得此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">時府試挨保無贄。敬惟院試每人送百文計。文武塗并進。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生三款。合算得銅錢八千文。籤經之明示。其驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又<span lang="EN-US">(清)光緒。己卯。泉州南臺寺。文會晉江。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">邱生帶籤普。在大魁殿用錢卜此。後鄉闈。惟邱生卷八次到取中。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此亦八千文。及與君數字之驗焉。王錢謹識。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蕭何註律<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。蕭何，沛郡，豊地方人。未顯貴時，曾當訟師（替人打官司為業的人）。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來助漢高帝平定天下，為宰相，有功勞而封為酇侯。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢既統一，只靠約法三章，無法長久治理天下，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">就命令蕭何制定法律，使人民知道如何守法。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">申屠嘉檄召鄧通<span lang="EN-US">(申屠，複姓)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">申屠嘉也在漢文帝時任宰相，而鄧通作為弄臣極受漢文帝之寵。一回申屠嘉上朝奏事，鄧通就站在皇帝身邊，態度傲慢不恭。申屠嘉奏事完後，砲口立即對準鄧通，說：「陛下幸愛群臣則富貴之，至於朝廷之禮，不可以不肅！」這已經是在教訓皇帝了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:6pt auto 6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">隨後，申屠嘉命鄧通親至丞相府；鄧通嚇壞了，但不能不去。「通至丞相府，免冠，徒跣，頓首謝嘉。嘉坐自如，弗爲禮，責曰：『夫朝廷者，高皇帝之朝廷也，通小臣，戲殿上，大不敬，當斬。史今行斬之！』通頓首，首盡出血，不解。」（以上《漢書</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman">˙</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">卷第五十三》）總算漢文帝隨後派人召喚鄧通，這才救他一命。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（故事喻；律法、因果，犯之不得，違者難逃制裁。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:150%;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 76;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七七籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛庚<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下→中下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style=""><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">木有根荄水有源。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君當自此究其原。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莫隨道路人閒話。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">訟到終凶是至言。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">到→則</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">樹木有其根幹，水有其源頭。（發生一件事情，總有其起源）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你當追尋其根源（解決問題要從根源著手，而非看一時的現象）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莫跟隨他人閒言雜語起舞（事情當自己思考，莫聽外人言）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若是訴訟，結果都是壞事收場，這是至理名言。（訴訟無贏家，只有大輸與小輸）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">凡事宜當自省發生的根源，不要只看過程的表相</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">莫聽外人言語，因為外人不知你的事情根源。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">訴訟是最笨的決定，因為訴訟之下無贏家。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">各種謀求，當務實根本。把根本照顧好，各種謀望自然順利。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有否姻緣也是人生宿命之一，若是期盼多年，又過了三十，還是沒有姻緣的話，那你要好好的</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">才行。若你願意這樣做，也許，心靈上還可以得到一些的滋潤。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？交往對象可否進一步發展？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這要看你們的緣分而決定了，也要看對方是否喜歡你。若你可以感覺到對方是喜歡你的，那你就可更進一步。若對方對你根本沒有意思，根本不來電，那你就放棄吧！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若愛情吵鬧或分手者，或關係困頓者，你可要探索你們為何分手、困頓的原因了，只有把原因弄清楚，然後再決定要怎麼做。若是因為個性不合的話，那往後還是會吵鬧不休。若是他已經變心了，那這事情就不用挽回了。若只是一些小事的爭吵，那就還有挽回空間。所以，你要自己反省看看你們雙方的問題出在哪裡，然後再對症下藥。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">考試</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若問此考試能否錄取？那你要自省自己的實力有多少？自己有否用功讀書？自己有否功名的福報？</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">建議多多行善積德吧！這對於你的前途才是有幫助的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求子</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">俗話說：「有子有子命，無子天注定。」若是當前無子的話，建議放下這種謀求，提起各種善行，這對於你的未來的命運才是有利的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">問治病者，若想疾病能根本消除，這要從「病根」處醫療才有效果，若只是頭痛醫頭，腳痛醫腳，這當然是不會痊癒的。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆其他問題</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇有人問是否能中樂透？這要看你是否有</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6399"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">偏財運</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">囉！在此奉勸，不要妄想了，還是務實的工作賺錢比較務實。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇若各方面命運都不順者，請</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">懺悔消業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，往後要</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=15247&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=15147"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">持守五戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">，更要</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:windowtext;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">行善布施</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">…</font></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">禍因惡積。當究其源。最宜向善。病保安存。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>自當謹慎。勿信人言。若有偏徇。禍及家門。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">口是禍之因。人言有過迍。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>訟則終不利。謹守福隨身。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">→<span lang="EN-US"><br/>口是禍之門。人言總見真。<br/>公庭無一字。謹守福隨身。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">□<span lang="EN-US"><br/>註→百家姓起頭。趙錢孫李。<br/>公庭無一字。暗指錢行頭。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先凶後吉。根原已定。不可妄為。自宜謹慎。禍去福來。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">訟當審。財利無。婚不好。有口舌。行人未至。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">病猶可禳。凡事不可信人。自宜省察。免災也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">善者福之本。惡者禍之本。讀書積蓄。求名利之本。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">無其本而欲名成利。就福得禍遠。難矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">然又當推其既往。驗其將來果。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目前之得而吉。則今日亦得而吉。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>目前之失而凶。則今日之失亦凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事皆然。不可不慎言。不可聽。訟不可成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">目下求財。不可得。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤戒宜謹讓。凡事準情酌理。探取根源。自能明其是非。審其進退。切不可聽傍人言語。妄搆訟端。訟必有凶禍在後。至此時悔之晚矣。何如慎之於先之為得也。凡事宜止不宜進。宜解不宜結。宜靜不宜躁。占者慎之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">木有根而暢達。水有源而流長。物理有之。人事亦然。如善為福之原。仁為壽之原。讀書積蓄為名利之源。得其原而萬事理矣。最人所宜究其心也。若歧路悠悠之口。常誣妄不可信。倘一時通聽。至涉訟端。必屈於理而左於計。此終凶之道也。人可不慎於始乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一士人占功名。得此。遲數科至甲子。始中。應首句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後謁選官至司理。因斷獄受賄而敗。應第四句也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人先習儒。後習賈。因當家生理不定。欲覓別途。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">迨占此籤。始仍舉業。不數年。果入學。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">克紹乃父書香。此上二句之應也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">呂后害韓信<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢高祖得到天下，韓信功勞居多，先封為齊王。後改封楚王。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">高祖後來懷疑韓信造反，就假裝去雲夢（湖南）玩，把韓信抓回京師，降封淮陰侯。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">韓信因為被降職，處在怨尤、期望、羞辱之下。又曾經與絳侯、灌嬰等為伍。正值高祖親征陳豨的時候。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在諸多因素之下，呂后乃與蕭何設計，引誘韓信入朝廷。在未央宮斬殺韓信，並且殺韓信</span><span lang="ZH-HK" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">父、子、孫</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">三族。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">伯州犁上下其手<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">春秋楚襄王二十六年，楚國出兵侵略鄭國。以當時楚國那麼強大，弱小的鄭國，實在沒有能力抵抗的。結果，鄭國遭遇到戰敗的厄運，連鄭王頡也被楚將穿封戌俘虜了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰事結束後，楚軍中有楚王弟公子圍，想冒認俘獲鄭頡的功勞，說鄭王頡是由他俘獲的，於是穿封戌和公子圍二人便發生爭執，彼此都不肯讓步，一時沒有辦法解決。後來，他們便請伯犁作公正人，判定這是誰的功勞。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">伯州犁的解紛辦法本是很公正的，他主張要知道這是誰的功勞，最好是問問被俘的鄭王。於是命人帶了鄭王頡來，伯州犁便向他說明原委，接著手伸二指，用上手指代表楚王弟公子圍，用下手指代表楚將穿封戌，然後問他是被誰俘獲的。鄭王頡因被穿封戌俘虜，很是恨他，便指著上手指，表示是被公子圍所俘虜。於是，伯州犁便判定這是公子圍的功勞。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「上下其手」這句成語便是出於這個故事；是表示玩弄手段，暗中作弊。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">——————————————————————————————-</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">上下其手<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">楚國的穿封戌在攻打鄭國時俘虜了鄭國的守將皇頡，王子圍欲與之爭功，請伯州犁為其裁決，伯州犁有意偏袒王子圍，以手高舉和向下的動作示意皇頡承認自己為王子圍所俘。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt auto;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">典出左傳˙襄公二十六年。後比喻玩弄手段，暗中作弊。</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm auto 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 77;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七八籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛辛<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.家道豊腴自飽溫。<br/>2.也須肚裏立乾坤。<br/>3.財多害己君當省。<br/>4.福有胚胎禍有門。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">豊→豐<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.家庭物質豐富可以溫飽</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.也要多多在本質上下工夫（若肚子已能溫飽，也要在心地與內涵上充實。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.錢財太多反而害自己，這當節制花用。（人生不要光只是賺錢）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.好命有好命的業因，壞命有壞命的業因。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事要有自思、自省、自制能力，知善惡，知行止，知進退。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫貪財、貪色、貪名，以免惹來禍害。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">多多充實自己的學問，提升自己的內在。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">多多</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=16845&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=16769"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔</span></a><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=1779"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">止惡持戒</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"><font color="#800080">修德</font></span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這就是好命運的根本</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤雖掛名為「下下」，此乃占者心態或觀念上已經偏差，故神明以此籤給予糾正。若人能自省而修正，那就不是下下籤了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情、姻緣<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情者，原則上；<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若屬於選擇性的問題者：本籤的旨意是，不要貪圖別人的美色、錢財、權勢等等。依這個原則，決定你的愛情選擇。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.多多充實<a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=18758&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=18538">愛情學分</a>，而後實踐他，提升自己的內在美，這才能穩定你的愛情。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.先健康自己的性格，若有個好個性，那就好相處，若能好相處，才能帶來幸福。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若想在愛情上更進一步發展者，請注意第<span lang="EN-US">2、3點給你的指示。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問疾病者，此病即使求神亦無益，若要求，只能求自己。在此建議，<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=19229&amp;prev=-1&amp;next=19171">走修行路線，這是有益治病的</a>。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問治病或健康者，「也須肚裏立乾坤」此話代表你要注意控制飲食。這樣才能改善你的健康。另外，肚子裡<span lang="EN-US">(心裡)的垃圾也好好處理，這有益治病。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求子、求孕<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若期望能懷孕生子的話：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">家道豊腴自飽溫：你家庭物質已經能溫飽了<span lang="EN-US"><br/>也須肚裏立乾坤：也應該肚子裡懷個孩子（此代表你有生子壓力）<br/>財多害己君當省：錢財太多會害自己的，所以個人花錢上應該省省，這些錢財當拿來布施。若你對人能夠慷慨大方，這就是生兒子的性格。（反之，若性格屬於精打細算、斤斤計較者，則會生女）</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">總結，按照籤詩重點而作，就可以懷孕生子成功了。建議這段期間多多<span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470">行善布施</a>。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試者，「也須肚裏立乾坤」代表你應該多多讀書，充實學問，這考試才有希望。而在錢財方面則應節制。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職、換職、工作、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">屬於這方面的求問者，你應該多多充實自己，提升自己的專業能力，專長越多則越有利你的職業發展。若能如此，才能提升你在工作上的表現。「財多害己君當省」則是意味，人生不能光是賺錢而已，若在經營事業上，不能凡事都以「利」的多寡為決定行事的標準。若能給予大眾精神糧食或心靈上的彌補，這也是有利你的事業的。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">家道昌盛。猶宜謹守。自立主張。祈求獲佑。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>輕財重道。方能長久。善善惡惡。自作自受。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">獲→護<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人會處一人事。莫管他人閑是非。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若能作福求安靜。雖否還能轉福機。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一事→自家心地自家知<span lang="EN-US"><br/>否還→禍終</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤家道雖然昌大。亦宜謹守。不可倚強欺弱。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">主有口舌是非。財多害己。不可妄求。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">只宜集善去惡。財莫貪。訟亦休。問婚不宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">行未回。病求神。休妄想也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">肚裏乾坤謂自主張也。可行則行。可止則止。一事三思。切勿貪戀。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">胚胎有門。言一善一惡。俱是人之所為。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">功名有分。終必不失。目下求財不利。尤宜謹省。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤家道雖然溫飽。宜自謹守。不可倚強欺弱。主有口舌是非。更防貪求不已。致生後禍。禍福無不自己求之。可不慎乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">衣食溫飽之人。常欠諳諫。肚裡立乾坤。謂須自作主張也。可行則行。可止則止。不可輕聽人言。自取煩惱。財多害己。則過分貪求之累也。福有胚胎。善是也。禍有門。惡是也。審於善惡之途。禍福唯所自擇矣。此示人趨吉避凶之道也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span style="">    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(宋)天啟時。一臺諫不順閹宦。恐有他禍。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此乃休官散財。安居林下。後權閹勢敗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此公仍復趣擢。此自明禍福之驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人。春月。妻病寢食不安。子又患痘。占此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫識所指。有為解曰。妻病無妨。肚裏有孕也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">子出天花。禍不遠矣。而渠云。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">天癸纔去。廿餘日焉。有胎于出痘。並未危。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">奚能死。均信。不數日。其子竟死。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">至冬間。妻舉兩子。一男一女。其人始服二句與四句之驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">袁安守困<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。袁安，字邵公。汝南地方人。年少時貧困，志氣行為卻很清高。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曾在下大雪時，僵臥家中，說不想打擾人（他人皆除雪出外乞食。比喻寒士不願乞求於人的氣節）。後來被推薦為孝廉（孝廉，漢朝推薦人才標準）。擔任陰平縣長、任城縣長。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對部下嚴格，大家都敬畏他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在朝廷勢力三分時，朝廷由外戚（皇帝母或妻的親戚）專制掌權。朝廷之上，則倚賴袁安一人安定。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇錦絲步帳<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">石崇。（西元</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">249</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">～</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">300</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">）晉南皮（今河北南皮東北）人，字季倫。</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">元康初累官至荊州刺史，以劫掠客商致財無數。在河陽營建金谷別墅，後拜衛尉，與貴戚王愷、羊琇之徒，以奢靡相尚。八王之亂時，他與齊王冏結黨，為趙王倫所殺。</span><span style="" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US">———————————————————————————————</span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇錦絲步帳<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">晉武帝的時候，有一個人名叫石崇，他官封安陽卿候，作到荊州刺史，他竟然派人暗地裡去劫掠航海的商販，因此而得到不少不義之財。他這個人只知道自己發財。從不為人民打算。平常他專門以和別人爭強鬪勝，來滿足自己的虛榮心。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當時朝廷皇親國戚王愷、羊琇等人，也都非常豪華奢侈。王愷作絲步帳四十裡，石崇就作錦步帳五十里。有一天皇帝賜給王一棵三尺高的珊瑚樹。王愷就拿出來和石崇比較石崇隨手那起一隻鐵如意，用力一擊，把珊瑚樹打的粉碎。王愷正準備和他理論，石崇命下人把他所有的珊瑚樹，全部搬了出來，其中有六、七棵，竟高達四尺多。像王愷那樣三尺高的真是不計其數。石崇隨便拿了一棵賠給王愷 。<span lang="EN-US"><br style=""><br style=""></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">經過這次事件，再也沒有人敢自不量力，和石崇來比財寶了。當然石崇心裡沾沾自喜，更加的傲慢而不可一世了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇以他無比的財力，在安陽地方建築了一所金谷別墅。從重樓疊閣，畫棟彫樑，真是金堆玉砌，說不盡的富麗堂皇。他擁有的姬妾使女數以百計，個個都穿戴錦繡珠翠，服飾華麗，豔光照人。絲竹管絃，音樂之聲，終日不絕於耳。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">那時有一位叫賈謐的朝廷權貴，因賈后事件的牽連，被趙王所殺。石崇因為也有附和逆黨的嫌疑，被革去官職。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇有一位寵愛的侍妾名叫路綠珠，長得非常的美豔動人，可以說是國色天香。有一天被趙王的心腹孫秀見到了，驚為天人，於是就派人去向石崇示意，希望石崇能夠割愛，把綠珠送給他。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">但是綠珠是石崇最寵愛的女人，他怎麼可能捨得讓他投入別人的懷抱，因此一口回絕了。孫秀懷恨在心，立誓要報復，就找了個機會向趙王進讒言，陷害石崇，硬説石崇有叛國造反的意圖。趙王不察，就下詔判石崇死罪。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當石崇被押赴刑場，走在半路上的時候，他不禁感慨的高聲叫著：「你們這些奴才，想要霸佔我的家財，竟然不顧道德來誣陷我，要把我害死 ！」<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">旁邊監刑的官史聽覺了，卻冷冷的，反問他：「你既然知道多足以招禍，當初何必要非法聚歛呢？家財既然富足了，又何不趁早疏散，多做點施貧濟困的善事，積積陰德呢？」 <span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">他聽了啞口無言。他的全家同時遭到誅連，龐大的財產也全部被充公了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">石崇的病是貪婪驕奢，他的財富是由搶劫，並且殺了不少無辜商人而得來的。所謂劫財越貨，與強盜沒有兩樣。古人說：「多行不義必自斃」結果滿貫家財免不了被人家奪回去，還賠上了一家老小的性命！可見天理昭彰，報應不爽。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（財物非份的來，則不義的去。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 78;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">七九籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛壬<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.乾亥來龍仔細看。<br/>2.坎居午向自當安。<br/>3.若移丑艮陰陽逆。<br/>4.門戶凋零家道難。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當→相<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.東南西北觀方向，來龍去脈看清楚（意即，做事要善惡、對錯、方位看清楚。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.座北朝南自然安適（意即，做事要順乎天理，自然能趨吉避凶。朝南發展則吉）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若是顛倒座向這是陰陽違逆（意即，若違背天理則諸事不順，惡果頻頻。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.門戶凋零家庭不安</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事依天理而求，自可趨吉避凶。若違背天理者，自有災殃。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若各種謀望不順者，請自檢視行事是否有違背因果法則，違背做人處世原則。若知行事方法或態度不對者，只要將之調整，則能遏止凶事發生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤是吉是凶，全看當事者行事方法、心態是否符合天理。選擇方向是否正確而定。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 24pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事、各種謀求<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問題屬於各種謀求者，只要行事順乎自然，合乎人性，順應天理，合乎道德，符合善的因果法則等等，那此事自然順利成功。反之，若是違背的話，那就災殃免不了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆問各方面未來前途<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問各方面的未來前途者，未來能否有好的前途，這全看你怎麼經營而定，若能處事順乎天理，其有不順之理。反之，若違背道義、天理等等，其有順利之理。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆問各種選擇<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問題屬於選擇性有關南北方向者，「坎居午向自當安」意即「座北朝南自然安適」，意即你要選擇南方這一邊的人、事、地，則對你有利，這就是你的最佳選擇了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若選擇屬有關年齡差距者（年或月的差距都適用），相差四或八者為吉。相差二者為凶。相差六者大吉或大凶。其他差距者則屬普通。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>◆各方面不順者</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若各方面不管是愛情還是事業、考試、工作等等，若是不順利的話，那你要自我檢視，是否做事做人的方法不對，違背處事原則，是否有做了哪些違背天理之事等等，若是違背的話，那當然會不順。反之，若能將之調整過來，那就可以順利了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情發展或選擇者，若符合以下則優：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">門當戶對<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">個性相融<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">6. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本身德行好。若雙方德智都很好，那自然幸福，不易吵架。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-9pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 33pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">7. </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">結婚的訴求符合道理。某些人選擇對象不是因為愛他，而是另有欲求，這樣的婚姻必不長久，而且難以得逞、順遂。因此，你為何要結婚，先要自己相清楚。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>反之，各方面條件差距過大者，勉強湊合也是凶。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">（以上僅以愛情舉例，其他類型問題請自行思考。）<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">立宅安墳。當明正向。龍穴雖吉。向差則病。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡百謀望。南向則善。一或他向。恐不如意。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">天然得個好規模。心計雖靈莫改圖。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>妄作妄謀終是拙。吉凶分界莫岐趨。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">靈→多<span lang="EN-US"><br/>岐→歧</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤凡事宜依理順行。不可妄意強求。反招禍患。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如相地者。一乾亥來龍。自以坐坎向午為順。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若獨執偏見。改作丑艮坐穴。是為陰陽背逆。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">豈不致門戶凋零之咎乎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此以見。吉可趨。凶可避。慎無顛倒錯亂。自貽伊滅也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此以羅經方位比喻也。言乾亥位居西北。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">來龍由此脈。甚分明。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">坎為正北。子位。午為正南。離位。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">坐坎向離。自與乾亥。來龍有陰陽交媾之美。安穩奚疑。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若丑艮位居東北。則與乾亥陰陽相反。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">奈何移穴坐此。豈非自是其愚乎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">門戶凋零。丁口不旺也。家道難。財產退也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人不可逆理數以妄行。斷斷明矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">方向西北。正北正南皆利。東北不利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">年運亥子午年頗佳。丑寅年欠吉。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤凡事宜依理順行。不可妄意強求。反招禍患。如相地者。乾亥來龍。自以坐坎向午為順。若獨執偏見。改作丑艮作穴。是為陰陽背逆。豈不致門戶凋零之咎乎。此以見吉可趨。凶可避。慎無顛倒錯亂。自貽伊戚也。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此以羅經方位比喻也。乾亥位居西北。來龍由此。脈甚分明。坎為正北子位。午為正南離位。坐坎向離。自與乾亥來龍。有陰陽交媾之美。安穩奚疑。若丑艮位居東北。則與乾亥陰陽相反。奈何移穴在此。豈非自是其愚乎。門戶凋零。丁口不旺也，家道難。財</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">退敗也。人不可逆理數以妄行。斷斷明矣。方向西北正北正南皆利。東北不利。年運。亥子午年頗佳。丑寅年欠吉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一人擇婿。占此不解。後得姓馮。屬豬者。為婿。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">蓋乾象為馬亥。屬豬來龍者。乃乘龍佳婿也。應首句奇驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宋神宗誤圩牛頭山<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">圩，就是山丘。扜，超越也。意思是神宗誤闖牛頭山。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">神宗</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1068~1078)</font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">牛頭山位湘澶。也許是把宋高宗</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">康王趙構</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1127~1131)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">誤寫成宋神宗。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋康王被困牛頭山。故事見于岳飛傳</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清。錢彩</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">敘述金主兀朮搜捕康王。康王逃亡至一山頂。後被岳飛所救。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解籤範例<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">範例一：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.knowledge.yahoo.com/question/question?qid=1610053004529"><font color="#800080"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">我與老婆在台北工作，家人親戚都在南部，我們想回高雄定居</span><font face="Times New Roman">/</font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">工作，不知是否妥當</span><font face="Times New Roman">?</font></font></a></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解：「</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">坎居午向自當安</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">」，故回南部定居</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">/</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">工作是最佳選擇。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 79;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">八十籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">辛癸<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>中平</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.一朝無事忽遭官。<br/>2.也是門衰墳未安。<br/>3.改換陰陽移禍福。<br/>4.勸君莫作等閒看。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.原本平安無事卻突然遭惹了小麻煩（原本沒事卻突然有個謀求或狀況）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.這是陽宅、陰宅不安所致（風水、地理、居家環境要調整一下）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.改變一下居家格局，調整一下方位可以改變禍福（造化個好環境可以換個好運氣）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.這件小事可別小看他喔（環境影響心理，心理影響處事，處事則影響運勢，故不可小看。）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.請把居家環境打點整潔，空間重新佈置一下，則有助命運。（把風水照顧好）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.行善修德亦可改造命運</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=2043"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">懺悔業障</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，可以消減壞命運。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.祈求神明保佑加持，也有效果。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">5. 本籤的重點在於，先把居家環境照顧好再說。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆各種謀求，或改善，請參考以上四點，多管齊下，則效過更佳。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"><br/>你有這個謀求或小困擾，這是因為風水不佳所致，因此，只要把居家環境調整好，你就可以心安了，當前的謀求也許就不想了，這個小麻煩也許就消失了。譬如，有人想求姻緣、求生子等種種的祈求，其實，你只要把居家風水照顧好，你的「心」就安定了，就不再祈求了，或者所求順利了。所以，你當把風水先照顧好，那再說吧！照顧風水不用找風水師，你只要維持居家環境的整潔、順暢那就是好風水了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問考試前途者，請先把讀書空間調整一下，讀書的地方力求安靜、整潔，光線適中，這樣讀書效果才會好。讀書期間，各種雜務事力求排除，以免影響讀書。以最好的環境讀書，則能得到最佳的考試效果。若環境雜亂，則心情也會亂，那讀書效果就不好。反之，環境安逸，則讀書效果好。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若欲求職獲得錄用，除了考試方面遵照以上辦理外，若有面試者，穿著要整潔，談吐要表現溫文，儀態要高雅有禮，….等等的重點，請自思考這類的求職面試重點，而後自行準備。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若想求孕求子者，臥室空間要重新調整一下，室內優雅氣氛好，感覺舒服溫馨，請自行調整適合的床位與空間氣氛。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若問疾病治療者，請換個好醫生。也請同時改造患者居住空間，基本原則就是臥室要整潔、看起來清心。請重新打點臥室環境，讓居住者感到安適、歡喜為原則。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">風水不利。門戶衰蹇。致招殃咎。有此禍變。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>急宜速改。避惡向善。若能戒意。庶幾脫免。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">禍福無門咎有因。免求地理與星辰。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若能積善祈天佑。禍自消除福自新。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">咎→各<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">無予遭官訟非平起也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">門衰墳未安。是其陰陽二宅風水不利所致。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">改換陰陽吉。更改宅安墳方向移禍福。由此轉禍為福也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">莫作等閒言。禍福隨人轉移。迴非泛常無根之論。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">必身體力行。親睹其效。始信為千古至言耳。胡不勉而行之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜避凶趨吉。是故從新不可妄為。亦不可坐守。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">始以無故而得禍後。亦可以作善而致福。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">如人家墳宅未安。必須改換陰陽方向。乃可化凶為吉也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若自己毫無轉動。福何由而集。禍何自而消乎。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜趨吉避凶。革故從新。不可妄為。亦不可坐守。始以無故而得禍。後亦可以作善而致福。如人家墳宅未安。必須改換陰陽方向。乃可化凶為吉也。若自己毫無轉動。福何由而集。禍何自而消乎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">無事遭官。訟非乎起也。門衰墳未安。是其陰陽二宅。風水不利所致。改換陰陽。言更改宅墳方向。移禍福。由此轉禍為福也。莫作等閒。言禍福隨人轉移。迥非泛長無根之論必身體力行。親見其效。始信為千古至言耳。胡不勉而行之。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生占此。中武會試。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生占之。因墳傍開門。構訟。蓋求第者遭官。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">則受職。置產。置營葬者遭官。則應不宜也。俱首句<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陶侃卜牛眠<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">所謂「牛眠吉地」由來，乃東晉陶侃將葬父，家中牛忽走失，侃因尋至某處，適逢一老父謂之曰：「前岡見有一牛，眠山汙中，若葬之，位極人臣」，又貫指其修處曰：「此亦吉地，當出二千石」，言訖不見，侃尋牛於山下，遂葬父於此地，而侃與周訪至交，乃以修地告之，後侃位三公，訪亦三世為益州刺吏。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">所謂「牛眠吉地一當指其龍穴形如一牛臥於水澤之狀，圓聳端秀，龍虎有力，堂前有秀池相映。後世因稱吉穴為牛眠地。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 80;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">八一籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">壬甲<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>中平→中吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.假君財物自當還。<br/>2.謀賴心欺他自奸。<br/>3.幸有高臺明月鏡。<br/>4.請來對照破機關。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">心欺→欺心<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.借你的財物應當還你</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.欺騙良心賴皮不還，這是他造奸業</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.還好有公平的因果報應（還好能遇到清官、能洗清冤屈）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.有一朝就得還你公道（有朝他的心機就會露出來）</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若問事情前途者，預防被小人侵害、欺負。防借給他人財物而不還。預防遺失財物。預防彼此的誤會。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.若事情不順者，受到的侵害，可以昭雪。誤會可以釐清。被虧欠可以得到償還。事情可以回歸原來。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若事情不順者，可能是被小人侵害或被誤會之故。但是，只要尋求正途，勢必可以回歸原有。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-12pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情前途者，你們的相處要預防彼此間有誤會，要預防有第三者（或外人）介入而壞了當前的感情。請持信任、寬容態度交往，以能保住愛情減少挫折。若這一關通過了，你再問能否開花結果吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;TEXT-INDENT:-12pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt 24pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><font face="Times New Roman">◇ </font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若愛情困頓者或分手者，恐是因為彼此有誤會之故，但是這個誤會可望釐清，請把誤會說給對方了解（或讓對方訴說誤會），以便洗清冤屈。若是你誤會對方，那你應該向對方道歉。若是對方誤會你，那你當原諒他。若能如此，則此愛情才能恢復。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、錄用、競試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這次的考試將是公平的，不能投機而考取，若參與各種考試、競試，請勿走後門，只能憑藉實力。一分耕耘，一分收穫。奉勸老實用功，才有機會。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆訴訟<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">能遇到清官，本事可以昭雪。小人終受懲罰，被虧欠可以得到償還，冤屈可以洗清。可望在中秋或中秋之後得到答案。每逢月圓時刻，亦是昭雪時刻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問工作或事業前途者，當防在工作中與人有誤會或被小人侵害，或防財物失竊。只是這些逆境終究會過去，而能回歸原來的你。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆換職、各種更換<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你想要更換工作，是否因為當前做的不順遂呢？其實這是被小人侵害或被誤會的結果，其實你可以不必急著退出，因為，這事情終究會露出真相。因此，若想離去工作的，那當考慮看看，有無必要因此離去。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問疾病者，可以遇到良醫，因而病癒。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求得此籤者，此病可能是業障病。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">負人財物。欺賴自奸。幽有鬼神。顯有清官。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>一朝照破。難逃其禍。每事依心。無施不可。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本分兩字。合天合地。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若有虧心。神明共棄。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">兩字→公平<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤先難後易。欺人自欺。反惹其禍。只可修心向善。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">暗有神明佑護。不可妄為。訟終凶事莫想。休求名利。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚宜審可也。病者醫。行人緩。風水遷改。孕生女。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">求財依本分。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事在前半月。占者防小人侵害。財物欺賴在後。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">半月占者主訟得理。財得利。病得脫。要當事。莫相欺也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤被人欺凌。暫時耐守。自可昭雪。如人負欠不還。多方謀賴。理曲在人。我何畏哉。自有清正官司在上。恰似高台明鏡。一經照察。機關立破。謀賴者從此敗矣。此以見凡事當依本分。毋逞狡詐。本分到處可行。狡詐適自害其身而已矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">借物當還。情理之常。謀賴欺心。情理之變。受欺者勢雖弱。欺人者天不容也。高台明鏡。比公正明決之官。明鏡足以察秋毫。明智足以摘奸伏。無有機關而不破者。欺心者盍早悟乎。占事者或應在秋。或應望後。月圓時有驗。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">江右一人負屈。屢訟未勝。後遇山東趙耀為按察使。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">其冤始白。趙本清廉。且趙與照同應明月照耀之義。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又<span lang="EN-US">(清)同治。甲子。九月髮逆陷漳州城時。(髮逆指太平天國留髮)</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">晉江令葉公。為霖占此籤。至十一月。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">果有高提臺帶兵來剿賊。應高臺破機關也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一婦人往府口探親。回時遺失一釵。遍尋無蹤。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">因到廟占此。有為解曰。何不再向姻家覓看。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婦從其言。果於外戚門前府。照墻腳拾得銀釵。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">己被糞穢遮蓋。惟一柄露出。故路人莫之知也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此自當還句之應巧甚。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寇公任雷陽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋朝。寇準，字平仲。下邽人。年十九考取進士。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">真宗時任知同州判（官名）、永興軍（官名）。盡心為人民做事。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">每日一有空閒，就有一事被耽擱。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來當宰相為皇帝定決策，成就澶淵戰役之功。因為政治鬥爭眨到雷陽（廣東海康）。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">準對家人節儉，對外人奢華。臥室一幅蚊帳用二十年。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仁宗朝贈中書令，封為來公。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">寇公任雷陽<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E5%85%B4%E5%9B%BD" title="太平興國"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">太平興國</span></a>年間<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%BF%9B%E5%A3%AB" title="進士"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">進士</span></a>。寇準為人剛直，因多次直諫，漸被皇帝重用。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AE%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%AE%97" title="宋太宗"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">太宗</span></a>時官至<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8F%82%E7%9F%A5%E6%94%BF%E4%BA%8B" title="參知政事"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">參知政事</span></a>。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AE%8B%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%97" title="宋真宗"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">真宗</span></a>即位後，先後在<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%A8" title="工部"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">工部</span></a>，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%88%91%E9%83%A8" title="刑部"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">刑部</span></a>，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%85%B5%E9%83%A8" title="兵部"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">兵部</span></a>任職，又任<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B8%E4%BD%BF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="三司使 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">三司使</span></a>。<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%99%AF%E5%BE%B7" title="景德"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">景德</span></a>元年（<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/1004%E5%B9%B4" title="1004年"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">1004年</span></a>），與參知政事<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%95%A2%E5%A3%AB%E5%AE%89" title="畢士安"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">畢士安</span></a>一同出任<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%AE%B0%E7%9B%B8" title="宰相"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">宰相</span></a>（<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%90%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%AB%A0%E4%BA%8B" title="同平章事"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">同平章事</span></a>）。當年冬天，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A5%91%E4%B8%B9" title="契丹"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">契丹</span></a>南下犯宋，包圍了<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%E7%80%9B%E6%B4%B2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" title="瀛洲 （頁面未存在）"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">瀛洲</span></a>等<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8C%97" title="河北"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">河北</span></a>地區，朝野震驚，<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%8E%8B%E6%AC%BD%E8%8B%A5" title="王欽若"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">王欽若</span></a>、<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%99%88%E5%B0%A7%E5%8F%9F" title="陳堯叟"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">陳堯叟</span></a>皆主張遷都；唯寇準力主真宗親征，反對南遷。真宗抵達<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BE%B6%E5%B7%9E" title="澶州"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">澶州</span></a>（今<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97" title="河南"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">河南</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BF%AE%E9%98%B3" title="濮陽"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">濮陽</span></a>）後，寇準力促宋真宗登上澶州北城門樓以示督戰，「諸軍皆呼萬歲，聲聞數十里，氣勢百倍」。宋將張環射殺遼軍主帥撻覽，於是訂立了「<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%BE%B6%E6%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E7%9B%9F" title="澶淵之盟"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">澶淵之盟</span></a>」。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">景德二年，升任<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%A6" title="中書"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">中書</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%BE%8D%E9%83%8E" title="侍郎"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">侍郎</span></a>兼工部<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B0%9A%E4%B9%A6" title="尚書"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">尚書</span></a>。當時朝廷無事，寇準頗恃其功，在庭院燃巨燭，耀如白晝，「座上客常滿，樽中酒不空」。帝亦待寇準極厚，王欽若很是嫉妒。乘機挑撥離間，讒言中傷，欽若說：「城下之盟，《春秋》恥之，澶淵之舉，是城下之盟也。以萬乘之貴而為城下之盟，其何恥如之！」又說「寇準之孤注也，斯亦危矣。」。景德三年，因<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%8E%8B%E6%AC%BD%E8%8B%A5" title="王欽若"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">王欽若</span></a>等人排擠，辭去相位。降為刑部尚書，知陝州。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%A9%E7%A6%A7" title="天禧"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">天禧</span></a>元年（<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/1017%E5%B9%B4" title="1017年"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">1017年</span></a>）又恢復宰相職務，後因參與宮廷權力鬥爭，被<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%81%E8%B0%93" title="丁謂"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">丁謂</span></a>等人排擠。貶至<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%A1%E5%B7%9E" title="衡州"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">衡州</span></a>（今<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B9%96%E5%8D%97" title="湖南"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">湖南</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%A1%A1%E9%98%B3" title="衡陽"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">衡陽</span></a>），<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%9B%B7%E5%B7%9E" title="雷州"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">雷州</span></a>（今<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C" title="廣東"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">廣東</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%B7" title="海康"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">海康</span></a>）等地，被貶後有一天宋真宗問：「吾目中久未見寇準，何也？」左右畏丁謂之淫威，竟不敢言。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後來<span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E4%B8%81%E8%B0%93" title="丁謂"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">丁謂</span></a>同黨<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E9%9B%B7%E5%85%81%E6%81%AD" title="雷允恭"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">雷允恭</span></a>因先帝陵寢工程事故，坐「擅移皇堂」罪，丁謂受牽連，貶為<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%AA%E4%BF%9D" title="太子太保"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">太子太保</span></a>。後以「丁謂前後欺罔」罪，被貶<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%B4%96%E5%B7%9E" title="崖州"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">崖州</span></a>（今<a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%97%E7%9C%81" title="海南省"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">海南省</span></a><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%90%BC%E5%B1%B1%E5%8E%BF" title="瓊山縣"><span style="COLOR:black;TEXT-DECORATION:none;">瓊山縣</span></a>）司戶參軍。丁謂路過雷州時，寇準派人送一蒸羊在路迎他。丁謂想見寇準，但寇準拒絕。寇準最終病死於雷州貶所，留有《寇萊公集》。</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE:11pt;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 81;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">八二籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">壬乙<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>上吉</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.彼亦儔中一輩賢。<br/>2.勸君特達與周旋。<br/>3.此時賓主歡相會。<br/>4.他日王侯卻並肩。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.你也是這行中的賢輩（優質人選、老手）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.勸你對這事多多用心經營</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.屆時雙方都能相談甚歡</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.而後你也能與之並駕齊驅</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若遇賢明之人，應特與之交往，這也是你將來發達的墊腳石。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.當前所問的這件事或人，不要放棄，這是你幸福的所在。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若單身問姻緣何時來？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你的條件也不賴，在結交異性朋友上不成問題，當你在生活中遇到門當戶對或心儀的對象時，你可以和他進一步發展，此對象就是你的終身伴侶了。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若問當前心儀的對象可否追求？當前交往對象可否進一步發展？<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你的素質也不錯，也知道該怎麼應對愛情，勸你和當前認識的對象繼續進展，你們將可以相談融洽，而後結為夫妻。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◇若當前愛情困頓者，勸你對這愛情多多用心經營，即使目前已經分手，也應該試圖挽回。或者即將分手者，也要好好周旋別讓他跑了，只要堅持當前的愛情，讓雙方都能相談甚歡，來日他就是你的配偶。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆工作、事業、換職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.若問當前工作發展，你是這個工作的賢輩（主管），你也能勝任這個工作，你應該繼續在這工作上經營，因為這是你事業發達的所在，所以不要輕易放棄。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.在生活中，應注意週遭之人，若遇到賢明之人或前輩時，應與之特別交往，這是你將來事業發達的墊腳石。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問考試，你的功課一向也很好，這個考試值得你去好好周旋一番，只要你把握這次的考試，就能為將來建立功名富貴。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">當前產生這個疾病，是因為你有願尚未償還之故。那就趕快去「還願」吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求孕求子<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">你的身體狀況都很好，足以懷孕生子沒問題，你倆只要多多努力，倆人在愉快的氣氛下，那就能如願懷孕生子了。另外，再</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=6470"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行善</span><font face="Times New Roman">.</font></a><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=126"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">修德</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，可以讓生子更穩當。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此外，若有興趣的話，還可以</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:maroon;"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="COLOR:black;"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=5144"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">以《觀世音菩薩普門品》為功課</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">，這可以讓你生下福德、智慧之男，而且讓孩子好教養。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事有相干。宜與效力。君既周旋。他必報德。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>凡所謀為。遇貴方得。神力陰扶。福報有日。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡事成全必有因。交情初淡後相親。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>貴人提起無難力。君子相逢便認真。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">起→挈<span lang="EN-US"><br/>君真→魚水相逢信有神</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤大吉。凡事謀望。無不遂意。婚必合。財必遂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">名遇薦。行人至。病有願未還。訟得理。孕生子。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">風水利。家道昌。貴人提挈。當在平日所交處。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">故彼此相逢。不求自至也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">言占者當推己及人。能處事周旋可獲厚報。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">能謹慎擇人可獲倍利。若問功名。能先自治己身。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">則人之薦舉。有不能逃矣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤凡事早植因緣。後此自有莫大利益。如往來儔類中。現有一賢士在前。必須特與訂交。厚相結納。日後此人得志。乃是王侯之貴。幸得以故人肩隨上下。託末光而附尾後。易易事耳。若待臨時攀扶。豈有濟乎。凡事予則吉觀此益信。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一輩賢。出類拔萃之品也。此時彼亦未遇。人或習而忽之。特達周旋。從眾人中特加物色也。賓主歡會。此日交契之情。王侯並肩。他年富貴之侶。事有無心得之。而或以有意遇之者。多此類。非具遠大器識者。未足以語此。人不可以無友。尤不可不知所擇矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">(清)嘉靖。中豊城。雷禮會試不第。占此。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">下科中第。前一名王宗本。後一名侯岳牧。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嗣後三人。同時為南部尚書王侯。並肩之言益驗。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">宋仁宗認母<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宋史。仁宗。李娠妃所生。劉后抱養為己子。左右皆為畏后威。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">沒人敢說話。所以仁宗皇帝不知。娠妃卒。后想以婢禮葬之。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">宰相呂夷簡請用隆重禮葬娠妃。后生氣說：一宮女死。相公為何這樣說。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">想離閒吾母子感情嗎？夷簡回答：太后不感恩劉氏。臣就不敢說，如果還感恩劉氏，就應厚葬她。太后領悟，就用以一品夫人禮葬劉氏。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">夷簡再請求，舉辦皇后入棺禮，外棺灌水銀。太后答應。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">等到太后崩，有人告訴皇帝說他是娠妃所生，及娠妃被草率埋葬之事。帝大哭，即去祭拜，親自開棺，看到娠妃的外棺灌水銀，面色如生前。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">衣帽全如皇后穿著。帝歎息說：怎可完全相信他人的話。對待劉氏的子孫更優厚。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">陶母截髮留賓<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">陶侃母，姓湛氏，晉朝新淦人，家貧且早年喪夫，守寡教子成器。一日，陶侃親友范逵乘馬來訪，正好大雪，留宿在陶家，侃母割臥蓆飼馬，並剪髮換錢買酒肴款待，范逵聽說此事嘆氣說：「若非有這樣的母親，怎能生此優秀孩子。」</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來陶侃任尋陽縣長，監理漁業時，託人帶回醃魚奉母，侃母氣憤，吩吋來人送回，並附書信嚴加訓戒，真是明理之賢母也。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 82;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">八三籤<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">壬丙<span lang="EN-US"><span>  </span>下下</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>詩</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.隨分堂前赴粥饘。<br/>2.何須妄想苦憂煎。<br/>3.主張門戶誠難事。<br/>4.百歲安閒得幾年。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩翻譯<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.隨緣認份接受自己所得到的</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.而不要妄想更多而讓自己苦煎憂</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.若想自立門戶的話，這難以成事。（此事想要成就，這是困難的。）</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.人生百年歲月中，又有多少歲月可以安閒呢</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤重點<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">1.隨緣認份不貪求</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">2.</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">恬靜安守則吉，妄動貪求則凶。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">3.由於最近運途不佳，請進行改運。</span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">4.淡泊名利，修心養性，此乃安頓人生之道。</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">清涼月解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆凡事<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">凡是各種謀求發問，本籤主旨在於勸請當事者<span lang="EN-US">—-隨緣，那你就認份吧，不用再為此事煎熬了。也不用妄想挽回或改變了。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆愛情<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問愛情前途者，你只要隨緣即可，不用擔心愛情會怎麼樣。畢竟，該你的跑不掉，若非你的強求亦無用。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆投資、理財、房地產<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">若問買賣房地產者，不吉也，難以成交，若成交也不能因此致富，反而成為日後的憂鬱所在。各種投資、理財都不宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆求職<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">最近工作難找，要找到滿意的工作也不易，除非你隨緣認受，但你也不用為此苦煎憂，若沒有工作的話，那你就暫且修身養性吧！建議，利用沒有工作時刻，四處充電吧！<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆事業、工作、創業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">事業景氣不佳，工作運途不順，此乃命也。若想創業，此難成事。建議看淡事業，多多在修心養性下功夫，這反而是好事。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆考試、學業<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">本籤主旨在於，不管你有無考上，你都隨緣。若考上了，那就讀吧，但也不用高興，因為後面的日子也不輕鬆。若沒考上就另求打算，也不用苦煎憂。總之，一切隨緣。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">◆治病、健康<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此種疾病康復的慢。若欲治病，請從「心」著手。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">東 坡 解<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">好事隨緣。莫貪莫競。且宜守成。庶保安靜。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>若更妄求。必主多憂。何如退省。以遂優游。</span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">碧 仙 註<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">守己當知事莫為。莫將心術肆凌欺。<span lang="EN-US"><br/>依然舊日規模好。休聽閒人說是非。</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">守欺→貧賤安常識者希。天時人事貴知幾。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜守成。不可妄為。凡事且隨緣分。不宜出行。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">婚未成。財莫貪。名利休問。訟宜和。病未痊。六甲保。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">墳宅改移。安分謹守持家。方吉利也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">大抵妄想則貪求。貪求則取禍。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">人生百歲。其中無禍無虞。安亨和平之福者。能有幾時。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占者當退卻一步。坐食饘粥以待時至。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">主張門戶誠難事者。蓋言繼述無人。所以不得相助有成也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">解 曰 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">此籤宜隨分退守。恰得安常處順之樂。若貪現前而圖意外。不唯無益。更增煩惱而已。雖則家計艱難。然安閒境地。不可多得。何不愛惜光陰。甘守清況之為得乎。凡事恬靜則吉。妄動則凶。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">釋 義 二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">隨分粥饘。言一粥一飯。皆係人間清福。儘堪享受。妄想。是冀倖富貴利達。一切本分所無之事。苦憂煎。是自尋苦趣。言當以妄想為戒。定不應如此也。主張門戶。猶言做人家。誠難事。言非不知做家之難。但人生百年有幾。安閒一時是一時。妄想勞苦何為也。占此者可知止矣。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占<span lang="EN-US"><span>    </span>驗</span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">一生小考。占此。發案列優等補廩。應赴饘粥也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一大剎。僧欲謀為住持。占此遂止。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">後見主僧操持勞苦。迎送干謁煩惱。怨恨不好。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">己之安閒清靜。始悟籤言不謬。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又余妹倩。按照磨林名樹立之。母病危。占此獲痊。應百歲安閒得也。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">又一人。被人討欠。討欠人債迫太急。欲賣屋償之。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">占此竟賣不得。後果就收入。還出了時事。方悟二三句之驗如此。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">竹坪王錢識<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事一<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">諸葛孔明學道<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">漢朝。諸葛亮，字孔明。瑯琊人。漢末避居南陽地方。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有心學清修、養生之道。研究奇明</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">門</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">遁法、天文術數、卦算策略，無所不精。起初不求名聲被諸侯知道。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來徐庶薦孔明於劉備，劉備共三次前往請教，聘為軍師。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">劉備稱帝，拜孔明作丞相。又把孤兒劉禪託付他。劉禪封孔明為武卿侯。卒諡忠武。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">籤詩故事二<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">嚴君平卜肆垂簾<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><a span="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%9A%B4%E9%81%B5"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">嚴遵</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">。字君平，西漢</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">蜀郡人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當時在成都幫人算命，每天賺百錢能自給自足，就關店放下布簾。富人羅沖想提供他車馬衣糧，君平曰：「吾不是不富足，為什麼你不足？自以為富足？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">沖說：「吾有萬金，你無一石米糧，為何說有餘？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君平曰：「不對。吾如果住你家，住處安定，但是工作不停，晝夜忙碌，不曾富足。現今我以卜卦為業，不出門而錢自至，日用支出外，還餘數百錢，不知如何用呢。這樣看來，不是我有餘而你不足嗎？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">君平曾嘆氣說：「提供我物質的人，損害我精神，稱揚我名聲的人，害我身命。」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">向子平讀易經，至損益卦，感嘆說：「吾已知富不如貧，貴不如賤，但不知死比活命好嗎？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN:6pt 12pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">兒女嫁娶後，他交代家事說：「當如我已死。」與好友秦子夏一起遊五嶽名山，不知所終。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>' WHERE id = 83;
UPDATE HCJFDG.Poem SET inner_content = '<tbody>

<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">八四籤</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">壬丁</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">  </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">中平</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">    </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">詩</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">箇中事緒更紛然。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">當局須知一著先。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">長舌婦人休酷聽。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">力行禮義要心堅。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">箇中→君家</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩翻譯</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這件事情雖然顯得紛嚷曲折（事情像迷霧般）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">處在當局者，對於事情來龍去脈要領先知道（對於事情要有主見，莫被人牽著鼻子走）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他人的讒言不要聽（要預防被他人之言語迷惑而誤判行情）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">堅定實踐禮義，有利自己前途。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">本籤重點</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此事自己要有主見，莫聽婦人言。（預防小人不實惑言）</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">實踐「禮」和「義」要堅定（禮：做人有禮節，不做缺德事。義：做事有正義、公平，有感恩心。）決定事情時，以禮義為準則。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若最近運途不順者，代表過去世曾經違背戒律，故不可不慎。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若屬人際之間衝突者，當事者能自覺過失，悔悟己過，則天神讚嘆矣。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">清涼月解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆凡事</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇事情若屬於困境者，自己要有主見，莫聽讒言。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇凡事只要符合「禮」和「義」者，都值得作。若違背則不做。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◇運途不佳者，或有各種謀求者，請補修「禮」和「義」。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆愛情</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">對於愛情要謹慎，莫被對方或他人花言巧語迷惑。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不要想高攀</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">在生活中遵守禮和義，有助你的愛情運。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4.</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若感情不睦或分手者，這愛情原本就是紛紛嚷嚷中度過，彼此在言語上當注意不要說傷人的話，態度上應該多行尊重。另外別忘了補修「禮」和「義」，這影響未來的愛情運。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求孕求子</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若最近懷孕者，那就是生女。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若想求子者，請先修禮、修義一年後再求籤，若得生子籤再生。建議各種善事固定功課而作，為人慷慨不計較，此有加強「生子命」功效。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆求財、事業</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">你還是一樣，先修禮、修義一年後再求籤，若得發財籤再做。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆治病</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">這個煩人已久的毛病是業障病，所以看了許多醫生還是好不了。這必須以</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/come1to2my3blog4-for5more6wisdom7/article?mid=11251"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">業障病</span></a></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">處理。除此之外，全面行善積德，做人有禮有義，也可以改善此疾病。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">求得此籤者，更應持守「不殺生戒」。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">要是能全面性修行的話，那對於各方面的命運都有改善功效。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">◆各種謀求</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若屬於各種謀求者，還是這老話，「力行禮義要心堅」，這就是你順遂命運的關鍵所在。也是你當補修的命運學分。若想全面性改造命運者，請持戒、修行。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">東</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">坡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">萬事一理。各有先見。莫聽人言。激成多變。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">依理而行。禍自可免。當堅乃心。毋或退轉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">碧</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">仙</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">註</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">雨下相謀要見他。更然未可便平和。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">若從音信求安靜。只恐將來事轉多。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">→</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">理煩治劇有先幾。莫聽纔言是與非。</span><span lang="EN-US"><br/></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">任爾風濤千萬狀。漁翁穩坐釣魚磯。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤占之。謀望平心。禍去福來。若強求。福轉生禍貽。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">病則安。訟宜和。休聽讒言。財有失。名勿貪。婚莫強求。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">行人至。或有失物。隨機應變。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">可得陰人。切莫交言。須謹慎也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">言事之未來。既要先見。又要豫圖。莫聽人言。致生變故。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">名利進步。則得遲疑。則失慎。勿貪取。依理而行。隨機而應。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不患眾事之紛也。長舌婦人是陰人之言。決不可聽也。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">解</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">曰</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">此籤示人扼要爭先之道。頭緒雖煩。目應批卻遵竅。恰得妙著。儘先佈置。恐有陰私小人。從中挑撥。不可過聽。總須自作主張。依理而行之。積久勿替。則紛煩定而事緒理矣。凡事不可遊移無主。持正有守則吉，治家者切不可聽信婦人之言。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">釋</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">義</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">事緒紛然。現在危難之境。一著當先。局中制勝之要。如奕棋然。一著得力。全局皆勝矣。此須自持定見。不可聽信人言。婦人長舌。尤宜戒之。故曰休酷聽也。義以制事。禮以制心。先著實在乎此。要心堅。言須永遠堅牢。不可始勤終怠也。必知明處當。不為浮言所搖惑者而可哉。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">驗</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一人惑於婦言。欲與弟分居。占此遂止。其後因弟克勤克儉。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">興財致富。其兄安享終身和樂。聖言之化人也如此夫。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事一</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">須賈害范雎</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">戰國。范睢，字叔。魏國人。事奉須賈，出使齊國，攘王賜金及牛、酒，范睢都辭謝。須賈回去告訴大臣魏齊。魏齊怒打范雎，打斷范睢的肋骨牙齒，范雎裝死才脫逃。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">後來范雎入秦國遊說昭王當了宰相。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">不久，須賈出使秦國，范睢穿著破衣至大使館見須賈。須賈驚訝說：「范先生沒事吧？為何如此貧困？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">須賈就拿出錦袍、馬匹贈予范睢，范睢因為過去遭須賈的陷害，如今就釋放了這個心結。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事二</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繆彤閉戶自撾</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繆彤，漢朝人，字豫公。繆彤在童年時父母即過世，由繆彤一人承擔家庭責任，照顧弟妹，直到大家長大結婚。但家庭變大，人口變多，紛爭在所難免。每當妯娌間有所爭執時，繆彤則深感未盡責任，有愧對祖先。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">一日，弟媳們為了小事而紛爭，繆彤感到羞愧難當，即閉戶責打自己，其自罵與自打聲音驚動弟媳們循著哭聲聚攏過來。弟媳們聽到兄長的自責，亦感愧疚而深自懺悔。自此之後，全家不再隔閡，而和樂生活。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">————-</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">完整版</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">————————————————</font></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繆彤，漢朝人，字豫公。在他小的時候，父母雙雙過世了，留下繆彤兄弟四人相依為命。作為長兄，繆彤自然就承擔起了照顧撫養弟弟們的重擔。家庭的不幸，使繆彤兄弟過早地嘗到了人生的艱辛。但是，生活的磨煉，也鍛造了繆彤堅毅正直的性格。尤其難能可貴的是，艱苦的處境，將繆彤的孝悌之德徹底從心底激發出來。他深感自己責任的重大，如不把幾個弟弟順利撫養成人，自己就無法告慰父母在天之靈。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">他們兄弟雖然生活艱難，但是由於長兄無微不至的照顧，繆彤弟兄四人均得以健康成長。弟弟們同樣深刻感念哥哥的付出，對於長兄，他們尊敬異常。如此患難相依，兄弟們手足之情日深。就這樣，一家人的生活雖然清苦，但是不乏甘甜。家庭的融融暖意，也令大家羡慕不已，人們不敢相信這是一個父母雙雙過世的家庭。兄弟們的和睦贏得了鄰里的交口稱嘆。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">幾年的光陰，轉瞬即逝。兄弟四人均已長大成人，到了婚娶的年齡，兄弟們也相繼成家了。但是，結婚只是責任承擔的開始。喜慶的氣氛在帶給家庭短暫的歡愉之後，新的生活如何展開，已經是兄弟們必須面對的現實了。由於家中增添了不少新人，生活已不再像以前那樣方便。同處一個屋檐下，妯娌們往往心各所執，因此生活中難免會出現不和諧的音符。生活的磕碰，有時也會傷及感情；偶爾的口角，大多會使大家鬧得不歡而散。於是大家不免各自思量家中財物，打算分開單過。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繆彤看著這樣的情景，想起兄弟們當年和睦的日子，不禁十分感慨：「要是父母仍然在世，面對孩子們的不和，又會有多麼的失望。」嘆息之餘，繆彤不由感到萬分悲涼，痛苦的自責湧上心頭。一日，又聽到兩個弟媳因為一點瑣事爭執不休，繆彤感到羞愧難當，他心中想到：「全家今天這種不和之相，都是因為自己的錯，是自己沒做好，纔感召家中矛盾重重。」為此，繆彤獨自關鎖門戶，在屋中抽打自己，厲聲自責道：「繆彤啊繆彤，你天天都說要修身謹行，學習古聖先賢的教誨，以求齊整風俗，匡扶正氣。可怎麼現在連自己的家庭都不能導正，看來都是妄談，你辜負了祖宗的諄諄教誨，實是不孝子孫啊！」說罷，繆彤便已失聲慟哭。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">　　弟弟、弟媳們循著哭聲聚攏過來，他們靜靜地守候在屋外。聽到長兄的自責，大家慚愧地低下了頭。想到長兄為家庭和睦，日夜操勞，殫精竭力；想到長兄平日那張和藹的笑臉，此時在屋裡卻是淚流滿面；想到長兄時常對大家殷殷地教誨，而自己卻一次次置之腦後……眾人想起自己過去種種錯誤，懺悔的眼淚，一時都是難以抑止。弟弟、弟媳們於是跪在門外，大家一同對屋中說：「哥哥，都是我們的錯。因紛爭而忘了手足之情，我們對不起祖宗，對不起父親的教誨，對不起您對我們的期望，我們真的好糊塗，請您把門打開，責罰我們吧！」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">至誠懺悔的言語，深深地感動了繆彤，「沒想到自我的譴責，會換來弟弟、弟媳們真心的懺悔。如果家人都能反躬自省，今後家庭一定會重迴和睦溫馨的幸福日子，父母在天之靈定將倍感欣慰。」想到這裡，繆彤便起身打開屋門。見到房門打開，弟弟弟媳們便一同說：「兄長，我們以後決不再提分家的事了，決不再做出讓您傷心的事情了。無論怎樣，我們都要和和氣氣住在一起。」說罷，弟弟們上前緊緊地擁住了繆彤，家門重歸和睦的氣氛感染了在場的每一個人。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">從此以後，繆家又恢復了往日的和樂氣氛，家人們不再有隔閡，真正做到兄友弟恭，夫義婦順，大家團結和睦地一起生活。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">摘錄來源：</span><span lang="EN-US"><a span="http://www.dfg.cn/big5/dygsh/bdgs/47-miutong.htm"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">繆彤自撾</span></a></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">近代</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">籤詩故事三</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:12pt;">康熙上課遲到</span></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;FONT-SIZE:12pt;"></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">康熙算是中國歷史上任位最久的皇帝了，他足足做了六十年的皇帝。在他小的時候，皇室聘請全國學識最豐富，德行最好的老師來教育他。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">有一次，皇師要給年少的康熙上課了，可是時間已到，卻未見康熙到達書房，這時皇師就跪在先皇聖像前，等待康熙來上課。十五分鐘後，康熙終於出現了……</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「皇師！你為何跪在先皇聖像前呢？」</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「因為皇帝上課遲到十五分鐘啊！」皇師說著</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「就算我遲到，那也是我的錯啊！為什麼是你長跪在此呢？」康熙說</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「你遲到因為我沒有把你教好！所以是我的錯！我當向先皇祈求懺悔啊！」皇師說著</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「那好吧！朕原諒你的錯，你可以起來了！」康熙說</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">「除非皇上也跪下來認錯，我才能起來，否則我便長跪不起！」皇師說</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;" class="MsoBodyText"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;">這時，康熙只得跪下來認錯，並答應以後上課不再遲到。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:79.85pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 0.5pt solid;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="106">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
<td style="BORDER-BOTTOM:windowtext 0.5pt solid;BORDER-LEFT:#c0c0c0;PADDING-BOTTOM:0cm;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;PADDING-LEFT:1.4pt;WIDTH:423.75pt;PADDING-RIGHT:1.4pt;BORDER-TOP:#c0c0c0;BORDER-RIGHT:windowtext 1.5pt double;PADDING-TOP:0cm;" valign="top" width="565">
<p class="MsoBodyText" style="MARGIN:0cm auto 6pt;"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"></span></font> </p>
</td>
</tr>

