<p class="MsoBodyText" style="LINE-HEIGHT:18pt;MARGIN:0cm 12pt 0pt;"><span style="FONT-FAMILY:新細明體;COLOR:black;">趙開道焚香告天<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>
